NK011(da)001:0: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i sgrub skor las /
NK011(da)001:1: rong zom lugs kyi phur pa'i gzhung pod bstan pa rgya mtsho'i snying bcud ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:2: na mo gu ru badz+ra ku m+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:3: de la 'dir phyogs dus kyi rgyal ba yongs kyi
NK011(da)001:4: phrin las kyi rang gzugs dpal rdo rje gzhon nu
NK011(da)001:5: yin la / de nyid sgrub pa'i chos skor las bka' brgyad bde gshegs 'dus pa'i dkar chag las /
NK011(da)001:6: rdo rje gzhon nu phrin las kyi rgyud la bid+yot+ta ma la 'bum sde phur pa pha yi rgyud /
NK011(da)001:7: rnal 'byor dam pa gsang chen ma yi rgyud /
NK011(da)001:8: k+ai la yi bcu gnyis phur pa gnyis ka'i rgyud /
NK011(da)001:9: ces gsungs pa ltar bid+yot+ta ma la zhes pa bod
NK011(da)001:10: skad du rig pa mchog gi rgyud 'bum par grags
NK011(da)001:11: shing rtsa dum sogs pha rgyud /
NK011(da)001:12: phur pa gsang ba'i rgyud chen po sogs ma rgyud /
NK011(da)001:13: k+ai la ya bcu gnyis sogs gnyis ka'i rgyud du
NK011(da)001:14: mdzad pa'i phrin las phur pa rol pa'i rgyud sde
NK011(da)001:15: rgya mtsho'i dgongs bcud man ngag gi phye ba'i bka'
NK011(da)001:16: srol mi 'dra ba du ma yod pa las khyad
NK011(da)001:17: par du gyur pa rong zom chos kyi bzang po'i
NK011(da)001:18: bka' srol las byung ba'i rong phur zhes yongs su
NK011(da)001:19: grags pa 'di ni brgyud gsum rig 'dzin rgya mtsho'i
NK011(da)001:20: mnga' bdag dpal o rgyan gyi slob dpon pad+ma 'byung
NK011(da)001:21: gnas nas ring brgyud bar ma chad pa dang /
NK011(da)001:22: nye brgyud khyad par ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK011(da)001:23: rong ban yon tan rin chen gyis slob dpon chen po dngos la thug /
NK011(da)001:24: mi yul du lo sum brgyar bzhugs te mthar sku lus ma spangs par mkha' spyod du gshegs /
NK011(da)001:25: de'i sras rong ban rin chen tshul khrims dgung lo phyed dang nyis brgyar bzhugs /
NK011(da)001:26: de'i sras rong zom pan+di ta chen po chos kyi
NK011(da)001:27: bzang po yin te dgung lo brgya dang bcu dgu
NK011(da)001:28: bzhugs shing sku la bsgres rgud mi mnga' zhing 'dzam
NK011(da)001:29: bu'i gling na yongs su grags pa'i mkhas grub gnyis
NK011(da)001:30: ldan du gyur pa yin pas de rnams las grub
NK011(da)001:31: thob kyi brgyud pa bar ma chad par byon pas
NK011(da)001:32: byin rlabs kyi tshan ka gzhan las 'phags pa'i sgrub
NK011(da)001:33: skor gyi rim pa 'di la nang gses su /
NK011(da)001:35: jo mo'i lugs kyi yig cha gnyis su bzhugs pas /
NK011(da)001:36: dang po rong zom gyi lugs kyi yig cha la ///
NK011(da)001:37: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i lo rgyus chos kyi byung
NK011(da)001:38: tshul ngo mtshar rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs zhes bya ba
NK011(da)001:39: bzhugs so // dpal rdo rje phur pa'i lo rgyus ngo mtshar rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs zhes bya ba /
NK011(da)001:40: bla ma dang dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:41: rig 'dzin bla ma rgyal ba sras dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:42: yi dam lha dang mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho la //
NK011(da)001:43: bdag yid gus pas rtag par phyag bgyis te //
NK011(da)001:44: yang gsang chos kyi gtam rgyus bsgrag par bya //
NK011(da)001:45: de la ston pa phun sum tshogs pa dang po'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang pos /
NK011(da)001:46: dus phun sum tshogs pa dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dus /
NK011(da)001:47: gnas phun sum tshogs pa 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi zhing khams su /
NK011(da)001:48: skye med mtha' bral chen po'i dgongs pa las ma
NK011(da)001:49: g.yos bzhin du 'gag med kyi cho 'phrul bdag nyid
NK011(da)001:50: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum
NK011(da)001:51: du sku bzhengs pa thabs shes gnyis su med par
NK011(da)001:52: sbyor ba las / 'khor phun sum tshogs pa phyogs bcu'i khro bo khra thabs dang /
NK011(da)001:53: phur pa sras kyi dkyil 'khor mngon par sprul nas /
NK011(da)001:54: chos phun sum tshogs pa bid+yot+ta ma la 'bum sde
NK011(da)001:55: la sogs pa phrin las phur pa'i rgyud mtha' dag
NK011(da)001:56: gsungs so // rgyud de dag kyang /
NK011(da)001:61: bram ze mi'i thod pa can la sogs pas yang dag par bsdus so //
NK011(da)001:62: ci 'khor gyis bsdus par rigs kyi /
NK011(da)001:63: ston pa nyid kyis bsdus pa mi 'thad do snyam na /
NK011(da)001:64: de ni 'di skad bdag gis bshad pa'i dus gcig na /
NK011(da)001:67: slob dpon mtsho skyes rdo rjes mdzad pa'i gsang ba grub pa las /
NK011(da)001:68: slob dpon kha cig 'di skad du //
NK011(da)001:69: dpal ldan 'dus pa mdangs can gyis //
NK011(da)001:70: rgyud kyi sdud par byed pa po //
NK011(da)001:71: dpa' bo 'jig rten dbang phyug zer //
NK011(da)001:72: bla ma'i zhal gyi bka' drin gyis //
NK011(da)001:73: dpal ldan 'dus pa'i sdud pa po //
NK011(da)001:74: gzhan dag yod pa ma yin zhes //
NK011(da)001:75: bdag nyid 'ba' zhig smra bar byed //
NK011(da)001:76: rgyud mdzad po ni thugs rdo rje //
NK011(da)001:77: zhes rgya 'grel las 'byung bas gsal ba yin no //
NK011(da)001:78: de nas mkha' 'gro ma dang mi'i yul du rim gyis dar ba yin te /
NK011(da)001:79: ston pa kun tu bzang pos /
NK011(da)001:83: de dag gis rgyal ba rigs bzhi //
NK011(da)001:84: de dag las slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis gsan no //
NK011(da)001:85: yang rdo rje sems dpa' des dga' rab rdo rje la bshad /
NK011(da)001:86: des sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs kyi sprul pa bzhad pa'i rdo rje la bshad /
NK011(da)001:87: des rgyal po u ru sha ne la bshad /
NK011(da)001:88: des klu'i bu mo rgya mtsho ma la /
NK011(da)001:89: des rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti la /
NK011(da)001:90: des slob dpon d+ha na sam skri ta /
NK011(da)001:92: blo ldan mchog sred gsum la bshad /
NK011(da)001:96: bal po sh+ai la many+dzu gsum la bshad do //
NK011(da)001:97: yang rdo rje sems dpas rgyal po dzahl glegs bam
NK011(da)001:98: gyi char dngos grub tu phab pa las brgyud pa
NK011(da)001:99: yang yod de / ji skad du /
NK011(da)001:100: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK011(da)001:101: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK011(da)001:102: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:103: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la /
NK011(da)001:104: po ti glegs bam snang bar byed //
NK011(da)001:106: rgyal po dzah lha lcam go ma de wi /
NK011(da)001:107: rgyal bu sha kra pu ri nas rim par brgyud de rgya bal bod gsum du dar ro //
NK011(da)001:108: yang kun tu bzang pos rdo rje gzhon nu la /
NK011(da)001:109: des bram ze mi'i thod pa can /
NK011(da)001:110: des mkha' 'gro ma las kyi dbang mo che la
NK011(da)001:111: gtad de mchod rten bde byed brtsegs par gter du
NK011(da)001:113: des za hor gyi mkhan po pra hasti /
NK011(da)001:114: des lha lcam u ma d+aa na /
NK011(da)001:115: des slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas la brgyud do //
NK011(da)001:117: brgyud tshul gzhan yang mang du yod mod kyi /
NK011(da)001:118: 'dir ni bdag cag lta bu mthong ba chung ba
NK011(da)001:119: dag gis ji ltar thos pa nyid bris pa tsam
NK011(da)001:120: mo // da ni sangs rgyas gnyis pa mi yul
NK011(da)001:121: du byon pa slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas zhes bya
NK011(da)001:122: ba 'di'i sku che ba'i yon tan mdo tsam smos
NK011(da)001:123: mo // na / 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las /
NK011(da)001:124: dpal ldan sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes //
NK011(da)001:125: kun mkhyen ye shes mdzod 'dzin pa //
NK011(da)001:127: che ba sangs rgyas rig sngags rgyal //
NK011(da)001:128: zhes gsungs pas brjod bya bshad thabs phyogs gcig gis
NK011(da)001:129: chos dang gang zag gnyis ka lung bstan pa ltar
NK011(da)001:130: du spyir slob dpon chen po 'di pad+ma las bardzusa
NK011(da)001:131: te skyes pa yin na yang /
NK011(da)001:132: phrin las phur pa'i chos 'di spel ba'i slad du
NK011(da)001:133: mngal du skye ba bzung bar mdzad pa yin te
NK011(da)001:134: / de'i rgyu mtshan mngal skyes kyi sems can rnams bardzusa skyes kyis mi thul bas /
NK011(da)001:135: sangs rgyas rnams kyang mngal 'dzin pa'i tshul ston dgos pa'i phyir /
NK011(da)001:136: slob dpon gyis kyang mngal du zhugs pa'i tshul bstan pas /
NK011(da)001:137: rgya bod gnyis su slob dpon gyi chos gzhan bas phur ba dar rgyas che zhing /
NK011(da)001:138: 'di'i sgo nas grol ba thob pa dang /
NK011(da)001:139: grub pa brnyes pa byon pa'i rnam grangs brjod kyis mi lang ba'i rgyu mtshan de yin no //
NK011(da)001:140: de yang o rgyan gyi yul na srid skyong ba'i
NK011(da)001:141: rgyal po ma nu si ta bya ba'i bu d+ha
NK011(da)001:142: na rak+shi ta zhes kyang bya /
NK011(da)001:143: sh+aan+ta rak+shi ta bya ba kha dog dkar la dmar
NK011(da)001:144: ba'i mdangs dang ldan pas pad+ma'i rigs kyi mtshan dang
NK011(da)001:145: ldan zhing / sgyu rtsal thams cad rdzogs pa mgo dang sked pa rgya mdud /
NK011(da)001:150: mi sdug pa phur pa'i mtshan nyid can zhig skyes so //
NK011(da)001:152: yul de'i rgyal po sras kyis phongs pa zhig la /
NK011(da)001:153: nam zhig na sras gcig byung nas /
NK011(da)001:154: de skyed mos tshal du bza' shing gi bsil grib
NK011(da)001:155: la bsnyal ba'i mgo la sha sbrang gcig gis za
NK011(da)001:157: d+ha na rak+shi tas rgyal bu shi yis dogs te
NK011(da)001:158: sor rdo 'phangs pas rde'u dang sha sbrang sbrags klad
NK011(da)001:159: pa'i nang du song nas rgyal bu shi'o //
NK011(da)001:160: 'di la kha cig blon po'i dbu la tri shu la phog nas bsad zer te /
NK011(da)001:161: bardzusa skyes kyi lo rgyus su de ltar yin gyi /
NK011(da)001:163: de nas mi rnams kyis khyod kyis rgyal bu bsad do byas pas /
NK011(da)001:164: bdag gis ngan sems kyis ma rgyab ste /
NK011(da)001:165: rgyal bu'i mgo la sha sbrang cig za zhing mchis pas /
NK011(da)001:166: sha sbrang la 'phangs pas sor rdo dang bcas pa klad par song nas gum mo //
NK011(da)001:173: tha ma lo gsar lhags sgong la nang ma re
NK011(da)001:174: la bag phye khal brgya pa re 'jal du 'jug
NK011(da)001:175: pa las / 'dis da res rgyal po'i sras bsad pa yin pas nyes pa rab tu 'ong ste /
NK011(da)001:176: ngan sems kyis ma brgyab pas spyugs par rigs so //
NK011(da)001:178: der mda' lnga dang gzhu thogs nas rgya gar gyi dur khrod so sa gling du byon /
NK011(da)001:179: yo byad gzhan ni ci yang med pas /
NK011(da)001:180: ro zas 'bras chan zas su za zhing ro ras gos su gyon /
NK011(da)001:181: pho byung tshad btags shing btang /
NK011(da)001:182: mo byung tshad spyad cing btang bas dur khrod na srin po sh+aan+ta rak+shi ta bya ba snang ngo //
NK011(da)001:183: zhes grong khyer kun tu gleng ngo //
NK011(da)001:184: de'i tshe yul de'i rgyal po 'thab par dga' ba zhes bya ba khros te /
NK011(da)001:185: 'di ma bsad na yul khams phung ste 'gro bas sod cig ces bskos nas dmag bcas te /
NK011(da)001:186: rgyal po'i bu in+d+ra r+aa dza dpa' zhing gtum pa
NK011(da)001:187: la lung pa'i dogs dur khrod mdo 'gag dam par
NK011(da)001:188: dgug tu bcug / rgyal po dmag dang bcas pas ri rong dur khrod kun tu bshus pas /
NK011(da)001:189: sh+aan+ta rak+shi tas bros pa dang /
NK011(da)001:190: dur khrod kyi mdo 'gag na rgyal bu in+d+ra r+aa
NK011(da)001:191: dzas dgug pa dang 'phrad de der sh+aan+ta rak+shi tas
NK011(da)001:192: mda' 'phangs bas / in+d+ra r+aa dza'i snying la phog ste bsad do //
NK011(da)001:193: de nas bros te song ba na re zhig na lam du mi gnyis dang 'phrad nas /
NK011(da)001:194: khyed gnyis gar 'gro dris pas za hor gyi mkhan po la chos nyan du 'gro zer /
NK011(da)001:195: der sngar gyi rang gi spyod pa la skyo ste
NK011(da)001:196: grogs dang bsdongs te chos la phyin pas lam du
NK011(da)001:197: slob dpon sh+aakya bo d+hi dang mjal nas gsum ka
NK011(da)001:198: rab tu byung / dge tshul gyi khrims mnos te /
NK011(da)001:202: de nas za hor du phyin pas /
NK011(da)001:203: slob dpon pra ha sti dang mjal /
NK011(da)001:204: grogs gnyis kyis gser gyi man+dala phul nas chos zhus
NK011(da)001:205: pas gsum ka la yo ga'i dbang rdzogs par bskur
NK011(da)001:206: / gsang mtshan las kyi rdo rje /
NK011(da)001:208: sh+aakya seng ge'i mtshan sems dpa' rdo rje zhes btags so //
NK011(da)001:209: ta th+aa sam ga ha'i rgyu mtshan nyid sde gsum ltar bshad nas tshim mam gsungs pas /
NK011(da)001:210: sh+aakya pra b+has tshim zer nas song /
NK011(da)001:211: gnyis pos ma tshim byas pas sngags phyi ba sde gsum ltar tshar gcig bshad nas tshim mam gsungs /
NK011(da)001:212: sh+aakya mi tras tshim zer nas song /
NK011(da)001:213: sh+aakya seng ge mi bsad pas yul du 'gro sa med pas ma tshim byas pas /
NK011(da)001:214: slob dpon gyi lag mthil du yo ga'i lha rnams gsal bar bstan nas /
NK011(da)001:217: der slob dpon la zhu byas pas /
NK011(da)001:219: rigs dbang rig pa'i sras yin pas //
NK011(da)001:220: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor nga las sprul //
NK011(da)001:221: nga ni thugs kyi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK011(da)001:222: nga las thams cad 'byung bas na //
NK011(da)001:223: nga yis bstan pa bzhin du nyon //
NK011(da)001:224: zhes gsungs nas yo ga'i chos thams cad rdzogs par bslab /
NK011(da)001:225: de nas gsang ba bla na med pa sgyu 'phrul gyi dbang rdzogs par bskur /
NK011(da)001:226: de nas phur pa 'bum sde'i chos thams cad rdzogs par bshad pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:227: de nas gnyis su med pa'i ye shes rtogs /
NK011(da)001:228: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob /
NK011(da)001:229: za hor rgyal po'i bu mo me tog man+da ra bya ba bsgrub byar bkug nas /
NK011(da)001:230: nub phyogs kyi ri go ma ha ti sha ga'i
NK011(da)001:231: brag phug m+aa ra ti ka ru bsgrubs pas rnam
NK011(da)001:232: par smin pa'i rig 'dzin thob bo //
NK011(da)001:233: de nas bsad pas mi 'jigs snyam ste /
NK011(da)001:235: sngon rgyal po in+d+ra r+aa dza bsad pa'i mi thong po yin par ngo shes nas /
NK011(da)001:236: rgyal po 'bangs dang bcas pas slob dpon lha lcam dang bcas pa tsan+dana gyi me la bsreg ste /
NK011(da)001:237: zhag bdun nas du ba chad pa dang bltas pas /
NK011(da)001:238: mtsho'i dbus na pad+ma'i sdong po gyes pa la slob
NK011(da)001:239: dpon lha lcam gnyis bzhugs pa mthong nas ngo mtshar
NK011(da)001:241: mchod gnas su bzhugs par zhus pas ma gnang ste /
NK011(da)001:242: rgya gar du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rgyas par gyis shig /
NK011(da)001:243: de ltar ma byas na khyed cag nyams par 'gyur ro gsungs nas o rgyan du byon no //
NK011(da)001:244: der yang sngon gyi ming thong po byung ngo zer nas /
NK011(da)001:245: yul gyi mi res shing khur re bsdus nas me
NK011(da)001:246: dpung chen po'i dbus su bsregs pas ma tshig ste
NK011(da)001:247: / sngar bzhin mtsho'i dkyil nas pad+ma'i sdong po skyes
NK011(da)001:248: pa'i lte bar bzhugs pa mthong nas thams cad ngo
NK011(da)001:250: sngar gyi nyes pa bshags nas /
NK011(da)001:251: o rgyan gyi yul du chos kyi bstan pa rgyas par mdzad do //
NK011(da)001:252: de nas slob dpon gyi dgongs pa la /
NK011(da)001:253: skye shi 'khor ba'i chos dang ni bral /
NK011(da)001:254: mi brjed pa'i gzungs ni thob /
NK011(da)001:256: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin ni brnyes /
NK011(da)001:257: da phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin cig bsgrub dgos dgongs nas /
NK011(da)001:259: yang le shod kyi brag phug tu yang dag mar me dgu pa'i sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK011(da)001:260: yul de'i klu gyong po zhes bya ba dang lha 'dre yongs kyis bar chad byas te /
NK011(da)001:261: lo gsum du gnam las char ma babs /
NK011(da)001:262: sa la rtsi shing nags tshal dang lo thog thams cad bskam /
NK011(da)001:263: chu bo dang chu bran kun kyang rgyun chad de
NK011(da)001:264: dus ngan byung ba'i tshe slob dpon gyi dgongs pa
NK011(da)001:265: la / 'di ni cis kyang ma lan te /
NK011(da)001:266: bdag byang chub sgrub pa la bar du gcod pa zhig go snyam nas /
NK011(da)001:268: lha la gsol ba btab pas /
NK011(da)001:269: nam mkha' las sgra byung ste /
NK011(da)001:270: bar chod 'di gzhan gyis 'dul ba'i thabs med kyis /
NK011(da)001:271: rgya gar sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang nas rdo
NK011(da)001:272: rje phur pa'i rgyud sde spyan drangs shig ces sgra
NK011(da)001:273: byung ngo // de nas bal po'i mi gnyis la
NK011(da)001:274: gser phye bre gang bskur nas pan+di ta lnga brgya
NK011(da)001:275: byung ngo // la phul / lo rgyus gsol bas /
NK011(da)001:276: rdo rje phur pa'i chos skor 'bum sde tsam zhig bzhugs pa'i nang nas /
NK011(da)001:277: pusti mi khur gnyis pan+di ta rnams kyi bardzangasa so //
NK011(da)001:278: de yang le shod du sleb pa tsam gyis lha
NK011(da)001:279: 'dre'i bar chad rang sar zhi ste dus kyi 'brug
NK011(da)001:281: char babs te rtsi shing nags tshal lo thog thams cad phun sum tshogs par gyur to //
NK011(da)001:282: de tsa na phur pa'i chos 'di bkra shis shing
NK011(da)001:283: byin rlabs myur bas phyogs thams cad du rgyas par
NK011(da)001:285: rgyud sde rnams kyi dgongs pa 'brel ba'i bstan bcos /
NK011(da)001:287: sgom pa phun sum tshogs pa /
NK011(da)001:288: phrin las rdo rje gzhon nu /
NK011(da)001:289: gdab pa las kha tshar dang bzhi ru phye ste mdzad /
NK011(da)001:290: dus der slob dpon pad+ma dang /
NK011(da)001:291: bi ma la mi tra dang /
NK011(da)001:292: bal po sh+ai la many+dzu gsum gyis yang le shod du bsgrubs pas rtags thon te /
NK011(da)001:294: dus der lung tshad du phyin nam ma phyin dgongs
NK011(da)001:295: pa mdzad pas rtags mngon sum du gzigs pa dang
NK011(da)001:296: / phur smad nyi shu ru bsdus te /
NK011(da)001:298: lung k+ai la ya bcu gnyis kyi tan+t+ra /
NK011(da)001:308: nam mkha' rol pa'i rgyal po'o //
NK011(da)001:321: de tsa na lha bdud du sprul nas drod nyul ba ni /
NK011(da)001:322: lcags kyi sdig pa nag po 'jigs su rung ba
NK011(da)001:323: gcig thog babs su tho 'tshams su byung ba la
NK011(da)001:324: / slob dpon nyid phag tu bardzusa nas zos par chas pas /
NK011(da)001:325: sdig pa de bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu ri rab ltar brjid pa'i skur mthong /
NK011(da)001:326: drag shul gyi las la thogs pa med pa'i dbang thob ste /
NK011(da)001:327: de'i dus su bsnyen phur bsgril zhing /
NK011(da)001:328: nga che nga btsan mgur bzhes pa ni /
NK011(da)001:330: mthing nag gcer bu ral ka can //
NK011(da)001:331: sku stod khro bo chen po la //
NK011(da)001:332: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste //
NK011(da)001:333: lte ba man chad phur pa'i dbal //
NK011(da)001:334: drag por gyur pa'i phur pa ste //
NK011(da)001:337: btab na lha yang brlag 'gyur na //
NK011(da)001:338: gnod byed rnams la smos ci dgos //
NK011(da)001:340: de nas bstan bcos rnams pan+di ta lnga brgya la gzigs su phul bar chas te /
NK011(da)001:341: rgya bal gnyis kyi so mtshams chu mig byang chub
NK011(da)001:342: ris su gzims pa na mnal lam du sku grongs
NK011(da)001:345: thugs ka nas sems can gyi dngos po gcig zin te /
NK011(da)001:347: phyag mtshan rdo rjes rgyas btab nas bzhag /
NK011(da)001:349: bu mo mtshar sdug dang ldan pa bzhi 'dug ste /
NK011(da)001:352: sngon bcom ldan 'das dpal chen pos dregs pa pho
NK011(da)001:353: bsgral mo sbyor ba'i dus na dam la btags te
NK011(da)001:354: / 'gro ba'i srog la dbang bskur ba'i ma mo bzhi lags te /
NK011(da)001:355: de'i thugs dam gyi dbang gis 'dir 'ong ba lags kyi /
NK011(da)001:356: slob dpon gyis kyang bdag cag la dbang bskur cig zer /
NK011(da)001:357: slob dpon gyi dgongs pa la /
NK011(da)001:358: sngon dbang thob pas nga tshe la dbang ba'i rig
NK011(da)001:359: 'dzin 'di yang 'chi ba snyam byed na ngas kyang
NK011(da)001:360: dbang bskur na 'gro ba thams cad gsod snyam nas
NK011(da)001:361: / rdo rje phur ba nyan pa'am /
NK011(da)001:363: sgom sgrub byed pa la bar du gcod pa'i srog la dbang gyis shig /
NK011(da)001:365: bswe mo bzhi dang bka' bgros nas /
NK011(da)001:366: bswe lug gsang ba'i yang gter mdzad de /
NK011(da)001:367: de ltar snga 'gyur gyi phur smad nyi shu rtsa gcig bsnams te /
NK011(da)001:368: sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang du byon nas pan+di ta lnga brgya'i spyan sngar 'grims pas /
NK011(da)001:369: chos shin tu legs pas rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags /
NK011(da)001:370: pan+di ta rnams kyis kyang slob dpon la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:371: de nas mkhas pa rnam gsum gyi bka' bgros te /
NK011(da)001:372: bid+yot+ta ma la 'bum sde thams cad gzigs te /
NK011(da)001:373: rdo rje phur pa gsang ba'i rgyud la sogs pa
NK011(da)001:374: rgyud sde sum cu rtsa gnyis la 'grel pa sgrub
NK011(da)001:375: thabs t+ai ka la sogs pas phyes nas rgyas par
NK011(da)001:376: mdzad do // de'i dus su srod la shwa na ma bzhis srog snying phul /
NK011(da)001:377: nam gung la bdag nyid ma mched bzhis srog snying phul /
NK011(da)001:378: de nas ji ltar dar ba ni bi ma las gzungs ma dam pa la bshad /
NK011(da)001:379: gnyis kas rgya gar gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti la bshad /
NK011(da)001:380: de nas rgya gar gyi yul na dar zhing rgyas par spyod do //
NK011(da)001:381: slob dpon pad+mas bal mo sh+aakya de ba la bshad /
NK011(da)001:382: de gnyis kas o rgyan gyi rgyal po d+harma ko sha la bshad /
NK011(da)001:383: de nas o rgyan gyi yul na dar zhing rgyas par spyod do //
NK011(da)001:384: bal po sh+ai la many+dzusa smad 'tshong ma sh+ain+tam la bshad /
NK011(da)001:385: des bal po'i rgyal po gu na ta la la bshad /
NK011(da)001:386: de nas bal po'i yul na dar zhing rgyas par spyod do //
NK011(da)001:387: da ni bod yul du ji ltar dar ba'i tshul ni /
NK011(da)001:389: bod kyi rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis bod
NK011(da)001:390: yul du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'dzugs par dgongs
NK011(da)001:391: nas / thugs dam gyi lha khang bsam yas bzhengs
NK011(da)001:392: pa'i sa 'dul ba la slob dpon bo d+hi sa
NK011(da)001:393: t+wa spyan drangs nas sa 'dul mdzad pas bod kyi
NK011(da)001:395: nyin mo mis brtsigs pa nub mo lha 'dres bshigs te ri rdo ri la bskyal /
NK011(da)001:396: klungs rdo klungs la bskyal nas rtsig tu ma ster ba dang /
NK011(da)001:398: e sha slob dpon gyi byin rlabs chung ngam /
NK011(da)001:403: slob dpon gyi zhal nas bdag ting nge 'dzin rtsal shugs chung ba ma yin te /
NK011(da)001:404: byams pa shas ches pas mi ma yin ma thul ba yin /
NK011(da)001:405: o rgyan gyi slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas zhes bya
NK011(da)001:406: ba rdo rje phur pa'i dngos grub thob pa gcig
NK011(da)001:407: bzhugs / de spyan drangs na bar chad zhi bar 'gyur ro gsungs /
NK011(da)001:408: de spyan mi drongs sam zhus pas slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK011(da)001:409: rang re rnams tshe sngon ma'i spun yin pa'i las dang /
NK011(da)001:410: smon pa'i dbang gis byon yong gsungs /
NK011(da)001:411: de ji ltar yin zhus pas /
NK011(da)001:412: spyir sangs rgyas thams cad kyis sems can gyi don mdzad tshul bsam gyis mi khyab pa yin /
NK011(da)001:413: khyad par du 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs kyis sems
NK011(da)001:414: can thams cad 'khor ba nas drangs te lan gsum
NK011(da)001:415: du sangs rgyas kyi sa la bzhag ste /
NK011(da)001:416: da sems can 'khor ba na med dam snyam gzigs pas /
NK011(da)001:417: sngar bas kyang sems can mang zhing nyon mongs pa rags su song 'dug pas /
NK011(da)001:418: slar snying rje skyes te bshums pas /
NK011(da)001:419: mchi ma thigs pa gnyis gtor nas 'di gnyis kyis
NK011(da)001:420: rtsod dus kyi sems can gyi don chen po ma
NK011(da)001:421: 'ongs pa'i dus na 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:423: mchi ma thigs pa gnyis sum cu rtsa gsum du song ba las /
NK011(da)001:424: lha'i bu mo gad+g+aa ma dang /
NK011(da)001:425: gad+g+aa ma chung ngu zhes pa gnyis su skyes /
NK011(da)001:426: de gnyis cher skyes nas skabs su lha'i khrims bsrung ba zhig gi tshe /
NK011(da)001:427: gad+g+aa chung ngus gang+g+aa ma'i ldum ra nas me tog brkus pas lha'i khrims nyams pas tshe 'phos te /
NK011(da)001:428: skye ba phyi ma la mi'i yul du bya rdzi mo bde mchog bya bar skyes /
NK011(da)001:429: bya 'tshos pa'i gla dang rgyags lhag bsags te /
NK011(da)001:430: mchod rten bya rung kha shor kha bya ba bzhengs /
NK011(da)001:431: bum par srog shing ma tshugs tsam la mo shi
NK011(da)001:432: nas dam tshig gi lha mo pra mo ha zhes
NK011(da)001:434: de la bu bzhi yod de /
NK011(da)001:435: dge slong a ba kha du /
NK011(da)001:439: bu de bzhis mchod rten gyi 'phro rdzogs par 'byongs te grub /
NK011(da)001:440: rab gnas byas tshar ba dang /
NK011(da)001:441: bu so sos smon lam 'di ltar btab bo //
NK011(da)001:442: bu che bas bdag cag chos dge ba 'di la
NK011(da)001:443: brten nas skye ba phyi ma la sa bdag gi
NK011(da)001:444: rgyal po chen po gcig tu skye bar gyur cig
NK011(da)001:447: bstan pa srung ba'i sngags 'chang mthu stobs can du skye bar gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:449: mkhan po byang chub sems dpa' gcig tu skye bar gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:451: phu bo gsum po'i bya ba bsgrub pa gcig tu gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:453: de'i dus kyi che ba rgyal po nyid yin /
NK011(da)001:454: de'i 'og ma slob dpon pad+ma yin /
NK011(da)001:456: de'i 'og ma yar lung gi rba mi khri gzher yin gsungs /
NK011(da)001:457: de nas rgyal pos sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms /
NK011(da)001:459: shud bu dpal gyi sed+ge gsum chibs dang bcas nas
NK011(da)001:460: gser phye mang po bskur nas slob dpon spyan 'dren
NK011(da)001:461: la bardzangasa so // de'i dus su slob dpon chen
NK011(da)001:462: po pad ma 'byung gnas rgya gar d+aa h+au la'i
NK011(da)001:463: gtsug lag khang na 'khor pan+di ta lnga brgya la
NK011(da)001:464: rgyud lung man ngag gsum gyi chos kyi 'khor lo
NK011(da)001:466: mngon par mkhyen pas mkhyen te /
NK011(da)001:468: da zla ba gsum na bdag bod kyi rgyal po'i
NK011(da)001:469: bla mchod la 'gro bar 'dug chos rnams myur du
NK011(da)001:471: chos rdzogs pa dang zla ba gsum song ba'i nyin der /
NK011(da)001:472: bod kyi bang phyin pa mi gsum gyis sleb /
NK011(da)001:473: gser gyi pa tra bco brgyad dang /
NK011(da)001:475: mnga' bdag rgyal po'i zhu ba rnams gsol bas /
NK011(da)001:476: sngon gyi smon lam gyi 'brel pa yod pas bod la 'dongs gsungs nas gnang ngo //
NK011(da)001:478: bod kyi mi gsum gyis d+aa h+au la'i gtsug lag
NK011(da)001:479: khang nas bteg ste rim gyis bal yul du phebs
NK011(da)001:480: so // lang lab kyi lo rgyus su ni /
NK011(da)001:481: slob dpon spyan 'dren pa'i bang phyin pa /
NK011(da)001:482: stag tshal gyi lo ts+aa ba brang sti dza ya rak+shi ta dang /
NK011(da)001:483: mang yul gyi lce ku ku r+aa dza gnyis gser phye bskur nas bardzangasa /
NK011(da)001:485: de nas rim gyis mang yul gyi grong khyer khrod ze bya bar phebs /
NK011(da)001:486: de'i dus mang yul na khyim bdun las med /
NK011(da)001:487: rgan mo gsum la gdams pa btab pas skad cig la grol /
NK011(da)001:488: de dus bod kyi lha 'dre rnams kyis nyi ma phyed na nam sros su bcug pas /
NK011(da)001:489: lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas skad cig la nyi ma bkug
NK011(da)001:490: nas zhag bdun du nyi ma ma btang bar lha
NK011(da)001:491: 'dre'i kha gnon du grong khyer khrod ze'i gong kha
NK011(da)001:493: de la de dus mun pa'i lha khang zer ro //
NK011(da)001:494: de'i rtsa ba na chu mig gnyan po sus kyang
NK011(da)001:495: rig mi nus pa gcig yod pa de'i klu btul
NK011(da)001:497: lha khang du thugs rje chen po bzhugs su gsol lo //
NK011(da)001:498: ri gong gcig tu bal po'i lha 'dre phyir 'brangs rnams kyi kha gnon du rdo'i mchod rten bzhengs /
NK011(da)001:499: phur pa gsum rdo la nub par btab nas bzhag /
NK011(da)001:500: de nas ya tshad na khung bu nas rlung 'ong
NK011(da)001:501: ba'i sa de bod la gnod par gzigs nas lha
NK011(da)001:502: khang brtsegs te mang yul byams sprin yin no //
NK011(da)001:503: de nas yar byon te ma chung gi bar du gro gsol /
NK011(da)001:504: der slob dpon la lha 'dres ma tshugs /
NK011(da)001:505: 'khor rnams smyo bas smyon thang du grags so //
NK011(da)001:506: de 'dul ba'i don du mchod rten brgya rtsa brgyad mdzad do //
NK011(da)001:507: yang zhang zhung yul te gu ge la byon /
NK011(da)001:508: de'i gzhi bdag dgra lha dmu tsa med kyis ma bzod nas /
NK011(da)001:509: ri phan tshun 'thab pa'i bar du slob dpon dpon g.yog bcar bar brtsams pas /
NK011(da)001:510: dpon g.yog rnams nam mkha' la gshegs /
NK011(da)001:511: dgra lha dmu tsa med skrag ste bros pa la phyag mtshan rdo rje gsor bas /
NK011(da)001:512: mo drung du lhags te srog snying phul bran du khas blangs te dam la btags so //
NK011(da)001:513: de nas lha yul gung thang du byon /
NK011(da)001:514: dge bsnyen nyi shu rtsa gcig gis cho 'phrul bstan thog phab pas /
NK011(da)001:515: thog me tog gi char du song nas /
NK011(da)001:516: der dge bsnyen rnams dbang du bsdus nas chos kyi srung mar bskos so //
NK011(da)001:517: de nas mang yul kha la'i rong sgo ru brtan
NK011(da)001:518: ma bcu gnyis kyis thog mda' bcu gnyis dus gcig
NK011(da)001:519: la phab pas / sdigs mdzub kyi rtse la blangs te klad la bskor bas /
NK011(da)001:520: sol dum bcu gnyis su nag hrul gyis song bas
NK011(da)001:521: brtan ma skrag ste srog snying phul dam la btags
NK011(da)001:522: / de dus gtso mo gangs dkar ma she'u bza'
NK011(da)001:523: bros te dpal mo lha mtsho'i nang du bros pas
NK011(da)001:524: / / slob dpon gyis dpal mtsho nas chu spar
NK011(da)001:525: bu gang blangs nas dgongs pa gtad pas skad cig
NK011(da)001:526: la spar bu'i chu la rlangs ngad chil gyis byung
NK011(da)001:527: ba dang mtsho yang rlangs pa phyur gyis byung /
NK011(da)001:528: spar bu'i chu de khol ba dang mtsho khol bas mos ma bzod de /
NK011(da)001:529: mtsho la rnyings thon pa dang rus pa dang sha
NK011(da)001:530: so sor bral nas keng rus su song ba la
NK011(da)001:531: / phyag mtshan rdo rje 'phangs pas mig ya gcig bcar te mo skrag nas srog snying phul /
NK011(da)001:535: gnam sman mched lnga'i sgrub skor gsum du phyes /
NK011(da)001:536: sngar brtan ma'i gtso mo yin pa la phyis rang mnyam du bzhag /
NK011(da)001:537: de nas rtsangs lhas stag phug tu bsnyen bskur nas bka' 'bangs su byas te /
NK011(da)001:538: 'di ni chos la dad pas slob dpon la tho ma 'tshams so //
NK011(da)001:539: phug der stag gsum byung ba la rdo rje gsor
NK011(da)001:540: bas stag gsum po phug gcig tu bros song ba
NK011(da)001:541: la / shul snyegs te byon pas rlung 'tshubs gcig tu song ba la phur pa btab pas /
NK011(da)001:542: gsang btsan gyis rang gzugs bstan nas srog snying phul lo //
NK011(da)001:543: phug pa de la stag phug ces da lta yang grags so //
NK011(da)001:544: de rnams su lha 'dre thams cad bstar la brgyus
NK011(da)001:545: pa ltar dam la btags pas chu'i ming yang bstar
NK011(da)001:546: chu zhes grags / de na lha 'dre'i khrom tshogs pas yul gyi ming la khrom pa zer /
NK011(da)001:547: de nas cums pa sbugs nas mar byon /
NK011(da)001:548: phug bdag mo gcig dge bsnyen du btsud /
NK011(da)001:549: de nas byang lam tshur tha nas byon /
NK011(da)001:550: stag mo sdings kyi kha nas grom lha khang gi rab gnas mdzad pas /
NK011(da)001:551: grom pa rgyang du de nas grags zer /
NK011(da)001:552: de nas rim gyis byang phyi khong nas mar la byon /
NK011(da)001:553: 'u yug gre mo 'phrad kyi la kha ru lha srin gyi cho 'phrul byung ba btul /
NK011(da)001:554: de nas 'dam snying grong ngos la byon /
NK011(da)001:555: gnam mtsho dang thang lha'i bar du sbra dkar phub nas bzhugs pas /
NK011(da)001:556: thang lhas thog char pa ltar phab /
NK011(da)001:557: slob dpon gyis sbra dkar rdo rje'i khang par bsgoms pas /
NK011(da)001:558: thog 'dred de mtsho la song bas /
NK011(da)001:559: mtsho khol te chu nang gi srog chags rnams shi bas /
NK011(da)001:560: der ngan song sbyong ba'i cho ga mdzad de sems can shi ba rnams byang chub la bkod /
NK011(da)001:561: de nas sbra dkar btab ste /
NK011(da)001:562: thang lha'i gangs la zhal gzigs nas /
NK011(da)001:563: gangs kyi mgor ram gcig bsgoms pas gangs zhu nas
NK011(da)001:564: rgyun chad de g.ya' brag tu zangs kyis song ba
NK011(da)001:565: dang / kho skrag ste rang gzugs bstan nas srog snying phul /
NK011(da)001:569: bdag ni lha 'dre kun gyi sde dpon yin zer /
NK011(da)001:570: 'o na khyod kyis lha 'dre thams cad khrid shog gsungs pas /
NK011(da)001:571: der khos lha 'dre phal che ba bkug byung ba la srog snying phrog ste dam la btags so //
NK011(da)001:572: de nas gnam gyi shug sdong du dregs pa gnad 'bebs kyi sgrub pa zhag gsum mdzad /
NK011(da)001:573: nam srod la ri rab nyil ba lta bu'i sgra drag po byung ba dang /
NK011(da)001:574: thang lha dmag dpon bzhi 'khor dang bcas pa lhags so //
NK011(da)001:575: der slob dpon gyis khyod la de tsam gyi sgra skad cho 'phrul yod na bzang gi /
NK011(da)001:576: khyod kyi khrod na pho bdud nyi khri bzhi stong dang /
NK011(da)001:577: de'i khrod na mthu chen rtsal drag nyi shu rtsa gcig yod kyi /
NK011(da)001:578: de dag khrid la da lta nga yi drung du shog /
NK011(da)001:579: mi 'ong na khyod thams cad kyi srog snying nga la yod pas /
NK011(da)001:580: ngas thams cad kyi snying 'byin no gsungs pas skrag ste 'dar phril phril 'dug /
NK011(da)001:581: de nas dar cig na bdud la dbang che ba bzhi /
NK011(da)001:582: dmag dpon rnam rol dang lnga /
NK011(da)001:583: shar nas dbang che ba bzhi /
NK011(da)001:585: gnyan la dbang che ba bzhi /
NK011(da)001:586: klu rje thod dkar dang lnga /
NK011(da)001:587: btsan la dbang che ba bzhi /
NK011(da)001:588: yam shud dmar po dang lnga /
NK011(da)001:589: de dag gi las mkhan t+aak+ki nag po dang nyer
NK011(da)001:590: gcig po dbang du bsdus dam nyams sgrol ba'i ging
NK011(da)001:591: du bskos / lha yi dge bsnyen du ming btags /
NK011(da)001:592: phur bu sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi dgongs
NK011(da)001:593: pa sgrub pa dang dpal 'byor dang tshe spel bar
NK011(da)001:595: de nas 'phan yul gong gi la kha nas /
NK011(da)001:596: stod lung la log byon te /
NK011(da)001:597: stod lung gzhong bar chos ston gsol ba la chu med nas /
NK011(da)001:598: kha t+w+aam ga bye ma la rgyab pas chu rka 'go bdun byung /
NK011(da)001:599: da lta gzhong pa lha chu bya bar grags /
NK011(da)001:600: gzhan yang stod lung gi yul rnams su btsan dang /
NK011(da)001:602: the'u rang rnams dam la btags /
NK011(da)001:603: de nas lha sa gram thang du byon nas zhag gcig bzhugs /
NK011(da)001:604: der chibs la r+ts+wa med pa la lha sa'i bye
NK011(da)001:605: ma skad cig la ne'u seng du bsgyur nas chibs
NK011(da)001:607: deng sang yang ne'u seng du yod pa 'di yin /
NK011(da)001:608: de nas skyi chu brgal te ba lam klags kyi la la byon pa dang /
NK011(da)001:609: phyi blon rnams kyis mnga' bdag la /
NK011(da)001:612: nga bod kyi btsad po yin yang /
NK011(da)001:613: slob dpon o rgyan gyi rgyal po'i sras yin /
NK011(da)001:614: sangs rgyas rnams dang mi lab pa bzhin du gsung gleng mdzad pas /
NK011(da)001:615: lha ma srin bran du khol ba la sogs yon
NK011(da)001:616: tan mtha' yas pa yin pas bsu ba la 'gro
NK011(da)001:617: dgos dgongs nas / dbu la zhwa dang /
NK011(da)001:619: na bza' stod g.yogs ber ske rags ma bcings par g.yang lugs su gsol nas byon tsa na /
NK011(da)001:622: dus nam zhig na stod du rgyal khrims zhwa tsam zhig chags par 'dug /
NK011(da)001:623: smad du rgyal khrims lhwam tsam gcig lus par 'dug /
NK011(da)001:624: bar 'di rang kha sil bur sil bur 'gro bar 'dug /
NK011(da)001:625: kyi hud sems can snying re rje /
NK011(da)001:627: dus der phan tshun phyag snyeg res byung bas /
NK011(da)001:628: slob dpon gyis rgyal po la dbu deng mdzad pas /
NK011(da)001:629: rgyal po'i na bza' phyed mes gzhob tu rog par song /
NK011(da)001:630: phyag mkhar dum bu gsum du chag /
NK011(da)001:632: rdzu 'phrul dang yon tan slob dpon lhag mod /
NK011(da)001:633: nga bod ru zhi'i rje yin pas /
NK011(da)001:634: phyag la lan 'ong ngam dgongs pas /
NK011(da)001:635: slob dpon gyis srin lag gi sen mo la gleng
NK011(da)001:636: bzhi gling phran thams cad khongs su bcug nas bstan
NK011(da)001:637: / nga che nga btsan gyi mgur gsungs pas /
NK011(da)001:639: de nas bsam yas kyi sa 'dul mdzad de brtsigs /
NK011(da)001:640: nyin par mi dang mtshan mo lha 'dres brtsigs pas legs par 'byongs te rab gnas mnga' gsol mdzad /
NK011(da)001:641: rgyal po rje 'bangs kyis dga' ston lo bcu gsum du byas so //
NK011(da)001:642: bsam yas 'byongs nas rgyal po dang /
NK011(da)001:643: jo mo mkhar chen bza' dang /
NK011(da)001:644: spyan 'dren mi gsum gyis rdo rje phur pa'i dbang nos /
NK011(da)001:645: rgyud dang sgrub thabs nyan te /
NK011(da)001:646: phur pa rgyal po lugs su grags pa dang /
NK011(da)001:650: jo mo lugs lnga ru byung /
NK011(da)001:651: de rjes rong ban la gnang bas /
NK011(da)001:654: mkhon gyi lugs deng sang sa phur du grags pa 'di byung ba yin la /
NK011(da)001:655: cog ro bzas slob dpon dngos la thug kyang dbang yi dam la zhus pas /
NK011(da)001:656: yi dam slob dpon gyi thugs kar 'dus pas dbang skal chad /
NK011(da)001:657: phyis jo mo mtsho rgyal gyis thugs brtse bas man
NK011(da)001:658: ngag zab dgu gnang bas phur pa lcam lugs zhes
NK011(da)001:660: de'i nang nas 'byung ba'i drag sngags gza' gdong dmar nag ces grags pa /
NK011(da)001:661: gnubs chen dang rje btsun mi la'i mthu chen po de yang /
NK011(da)001:662: phur pa lcam lugs kyi gdams skor yin te deng sang gi bar du lung rgyun yod do //
NK011(da)001:663: de nas brag dmar bsam yas su slob dpon gyis
NK011(da)001:664: phyi nang gi chos rgya chen po gsungs pa'i dus
NK011(da)001:665: / jo mo mkhar chen bza' lha mo l+aa s+ye ma'i sprul pa yin par gzigs /
NK011(da)001:666: rgyal pos kyang gzungs mar phul /
NK011(da)001:667: der slob dpon gyis jo mo la /
NK011(da)001:668: khyod la 'og min gyi zhing khams bstan gyi gsungs
NK011(da)001:669: nas slob dpon dang gnyis 'ja' ltar du yal nas
NK011(da)001:670: song / zhag gsum song ba'i nang bar log nas byung /
NK011(da)001:672: khyod kyi 'og min gyi zhing khams mthong ngam gsungs
NK011(da)001:673: pas bdag gis kun tu bzang po'i zhing khams dang
NK011(da)001:679: de rnams kyi zhing khams mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK011(da)001:680: 'khor lo bsam gyis mi khyab pa bstan te mthong
NK011(da)001:681: / zhus pas mnga' bdag gi zhal nas /
NK011(da)001:682: de mi bden slob dpon gyis 'og min gyi zhing khams la spyod mi nus /
NK011(da)001:683: de nus pa yin na gzugs kyi phung po la mi chags pa yin te /
NK011(da)001:684: slob dpon da rung gzugs kyi phung po la chags 'dug pa gsungs pas /
NK011(da)001:686: bdag gis mthong ba'i zhing khams de rnams kyi bkod pa 'di dang 'di lta bu gda' /
NK011(da)001:688: 'o na de dag bden na sngon bdag gi ma
NK011(da)001:689: gyim shang kong jo mo ma bde spyod rgyal po
NK011(da)001:691: ge sar rgyal po'i lag tu bdag gi ma'i 'phrul
NK011(da)001:692: gyi me long bswe'i phub chung tsam zhig shor nas
NK011(da)001:693: yod kyi / de slob dpon la len du chug cig gsungs /
NK011(da)001:694: jo mos slob dpon la de brjod ma thag tu slob dpon 'od du yal /
NK011(da)001:695: rje'i shel phreng brgya rtsa brgyad bgrangs ma zin pa
NK011(da)001:696: la slob dpon gyis ge sar rgyal pa'i bang mdzod
NK011(da)001:698: de jo mos rje la phul /
NK011(da)001:700: 'o na sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha'i gnas na bya khyung gi sgo nga yod kyi /
NK011(da)001:703: de ma thag slob dpon gyis blangs pa jo mos rje la phul /
NK011(da)001:705: rgya mtsho'i gting na klu'i rgyal po gtsug na rin
NK011(da)001:706: chen gyi bu mo mdzes ldan ma'i lag na yid
NK011(da)001:707: bzhin gyi nor bu yod kyi /
NK011(da)001:709: jo mos de skad brjod ma thag /
NK011(da)001:713: bar snang khams na sbrang kham pa'i rnga ma yod kyi /
NK011(da)001:714: de slob dpon la len du chug gsungs /
NK011(da)001:715: sngar ltar skad cig la blangs /
NK011(da)001:717: zhang po rgya'i yul na sngon bskal pa bzang po'i nas tshad dang /
NK011(da)001:718: tshe lo bcu pa'i bre tshad yod kyi gsungs /
NK011(da)001:719: de yang skad cig la blangs byung /
NK011(da)001:722: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK011(da)001:723: dri ma med pa'i sku'i gdan khri'i bar gyi sa
NK011(da)001:724: 'og na gnam chag pa'i dum bu bya ba dang
NK011(da)001:725: / sa ral pa'i ras ma bya ba'i dum bu rin po che yod kyi /
NK011(da)001:726: de slob dpon la len du chug gsungs /
NK011(da)001:727: jo mos slob dpon la brjod ma thag tu blangs byung ba rje la phul bas /
NK011(da)001:729: slob dpon gyis rdzu 'phrul gyi khung brtag pa yin te /
NK011(da)001:731: slob dpon 'di 'byung ba dang rang sems la dbang thob pa /
NK011(da)001:732: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas las lhag pa gcig 'dug gsungs /
NK011(da)001:733: thugs ches zhabs spyi bor blangs so //
NK011(da)001:734: de'i dus su rgyal po rje 'bangs rnams kyi tshe
NK011(da)001:735: snga ma'i skye ba ji ltar blangs pa'i tshul dang
NK011(da)001:737: blon po khri bzang yab lha khyod //
NK011(da)001:738: skye ba 'di yi snga ma la //
NK011(da)001:739: nya yi lus ni blangs pa'i rtags //
NK011(da)001:740: da lta mchan khung g.yon na nya gshog yod //
NK011(da)001:741: ces sogs gsungs pas kun yid ches /
NK011(da)001:742: da lta rang rang so so'i bsam pa 'di ltar 'gyu tshul dang /
NK011(da)001:743: ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi 'gyur ldog la sogs pa
NK011(da)001:744: dus gsum sa ler gzigs pas chags thogs med par
NK011(da)001:745: lung bstan / dus 'dir lo ts+aa ba brang sti dza ya rak+shi ta dang /
NK011(da)001:746: lce ku ku r+aa dzas byas nas chos mang du bsgyur /
NK011(da)001:747: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug la phur pa gnang bas /
NK011(da)001:748: des rgyud kyi don khong du chud /
NK011(da)001:749: gdan 'dren pa mi gsum gyis kyang rgyud kyi bshad pa rgya cher spel te /
NK011(da)001:750: sna nam gyis gtsang du spel /
NK011(da)001:751: shud bus lho brag tu bshad /
NK011(da)001:752: mchims kyis kong yul mchims kyi steng du spel lo //
NK011(da)001:753: de tsa na bsam yas mchims phur slob dpon pad+ma
NK011(da)001:754: 'byung gnas dang de'i lo ts+aa ba gnyags dz+ny+aa na
NK011(da)001:756: rje 'bangs nyer lngas sgrub chen byas pa la /
NK011(da)001:757: dar bza' byang chub kyis sgrub pa la yal ga bsgrags nas chab gsol dgos zer /
NK011(da)001:758: der blon po rnams kyis btsad po la zhus /
NK011(da)001:759: khyad par ngan lam rta ra klu gong gis slob
NK011(da)001:760: dpon la ngan smras mang du byas pas kho kha
NK011(da)001:761: lkugs / dar bza' byang chub ni sa'i lha mo brtan ma phag se khra la zhon pa /
NK011(da)001:762: lag na lcags kyu thogs pas dar baza'i lce nas
NK011(da)001:763: btab ste gson po sa 'og tu khrid pa kun
NK011(da)001:764: gyis mthong bas / blon po rnams kyis slob dpon la chab gsol ma nus /
NK011(da)001:765: bstan pa ma nub tsam du byung /
NK011(da)001:766: der slob dpon rdzu 'phrul dang mthu stobs che bas /
NK011(da)001:767: bod kyi blon po chos la mi dga' ba rnams yid rab tu skrag ste /
NK011(da)001:768: slob dpon slar rgya gar du 'byon pa'i zhu ba rgyal po la phul /
NK011(da)001:769: sdig blon rnams dbang ches pas rgyal po yang gsan dgos pa byung nas zhal gyis bzhes /
NK011(da)001:771: nga rgya gar du 'gro ba rung mod kyi /
NK011(da)001:772: 'on kyang gsang sngags rnying ma'i bstan pa yongs rdzogs spel ma thub pas glo ba ma dga' /
NK011(da)001:773: bod kyi ri thams cad nags kyis khyab pa /
NK011(da)001:775: bye ma thams cad ne'u sing du bsgyur ba /
NK011(da)001:777: byang thang thams cad zhing la btang ba sogs bya rgyu mang po yod pa la /
NK011(da)001:778: sems can gyi bsod nams la ma shong ba yin /
NK011(da)001:780: bsam yas kyi mtha' skor gyi bye ma la bsnyen
NK011(da)001:781: phur bsgril bas ne'u sing du sngo zhur gyis song
NK011(da)001:782: / gtsug lag khang dang lcags ri'i mtha' la bskor ba mdzad pas /
NK011(da)001:783: zhabs bzhag pa'i sar lcang ma re skyes so //
NK011(da)001:785: bstan pa bsrung ba'i drag sngags brgya rtsa brgyad dang /
NK011(da)001:786: phan bya brgya nyi shu rnams gnang /
NK011(da)001:787: 'dzam bu'i gling gi nor kun bsdus nas rgyal po pe dkar la gtad /
NK011(da)001:788: de bsam yas kyi srung mar bskos /
NK011(da)001:789: de nas slob dpon gshegs khar jo mos zhus pa /
NK011(da)001:790: bdag bud med blo dman pas nyung la bslab par sla ba'i chos shig zhu /
NK011(da)001:791: nyon mongs pa rags pas nyon mongs pa 'joms pa'i chos shig zhu /
NK011(da)001:792: tshe thung bas grub thag nye ba'i chos shig zhu /
NK011(da)001:793: dgra mang bas mthu che ba'i chos shig zhu zhes zhu don bzhi phul bas /
NK011(da)001:794: nyung la 'dus pa phur pa rtsa ba'i dum bu stod las byang chub sgrub pa /
NK011(da)001:795: smad las dmod pa lam du khyer ba man ngag mchog tu gyur pa 'di gnang ngo //
NK011(da)001:796: de nas slob dpon gyis mnga' bdag la gsungs pa /
NK011(da)001:797: da ni bdag srin po'i kha gnon la 'gro ba'i dus la bab pa 'dra'o //
NK011(da)001:798: bdag ni tshe yi rig 'dzin thob pa yin /
NK011(da)001:799: mnga' bdag nyid kyang tshe'i dngos grub 'dod na tshe
NK011(da)001:800: chu 'di 'thung mdzod gsungs nas bdud rtsi bum pa
NK011(da)001:801: gang gnang / der rgyal po'i dgongs pa la /
NK011(da)001:802: slob dpon gshegs par chas pa 'dis ma dgyes nas /
NK011(da)001:803: lho bal gyi zhabs kyis dug btang ba 'dra'ang srid snyam /
NK011(da)001:804: spyang thul 'dabs nas mar pho bas de ma thag sa la chu mig rdol bas /
NK011(da)001:805: deng sang chu rje ne'u sing du grags so //
NK011(da)001:806: de nas slob dpon gshegs pa la mnga' bdag gis ma bzod de /
NK011(da)001:808: rgyal po bdag nyid ma gum bar du bzhugs par zhu zhus pas /
NK011(da)001:809: bsam yas su rgyun du bzhugs pa ma gnang /
NK011(da)001:810: ma 'ongs pa'i 'gro ba skal ldan rnams kyi don
NK011(da)001:811: du bod kyi sgrub gnas rnams su rgyud sde rgya
NK011(da)001:812: mtsho'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs nas sgrub pa mdzad de byin
NK011(da)001:814: bod khams gling dgu'i sa gzhi thams cad zhabs kyis
NK011(da)001:815: bcags te bkra shis shing byin chags par bya ba
NK011(da)001:816: dang / da dung bod kyi gdul bya ma rdzogs pas /
NK011(da)001:817: de dag gi don gyi phyir dben gnas gangs dang ri brag mtsho gling rnams su gnas bcas te /
NK011(da)001:818: rgyal po rje 'bangs kyi don du skabs skabs su 'ong gis /
NK011(da)001:819: nga'i chos kyi 'phro lus pa rnams rgya gar nas
NK011(da)001:820: slob dpon bi ma la mi tra spyan drongs la
NK011(da)001:821: zhus shig gsungs / jo mo mtsho rgyal gyis nye gnas byas te gshegs so //
NK011(da)001:822: de nas sgrub gnas rnams su byon nas sgrub pa mdzad /
NK011(da)001:823: brag la sku dang phyag zhabs kyi rjes bzhag /
NK011(da)001:824: khyad par du mtsho chen po bzhi la phyag rjes
NK011(da)001:825: bzhag pa ni chu ma bskams kyi bar du gnas
NK011(da)001:827: bsam yas kyi rab gnas dang /
NK011(da)001:828: skabs su rgyal po rje 'bangs la chos gsung ba dang /
NK011(da)001:829: btsun mo dmar rgyan baza'i mdze nad bsal ba rnams la byon /
NK011(da)001:831: sras mu ne btsan po yum gyis dug gis bgrongs /
NK011(da)001:832: mu khri btsad po na gzhon /
NK011(da)001:836: khrom la sogs pas bod phung la nye ba na /
NK011(da)001:837: rgyal srid lo gsum bskyangs te bod 'bangs kyi don mdzad /
NK011(da)001:838: mthar rgyal bu la rgyal sa gtad de de nas su yis bshol btab kyang ma gsan te /
NK011(da)001:839: lho nub rnga yab kyi yul du srin po'i kha gnon la gshegs so //
NK011(da)001:840: de ltar bod yul 'dir ji tsam bzhugs snyam na /
NK011(da)001:841: rba bzhed du bshad pa ltar bsam yas kyi sa
NK011(da)001:842: 'dul ba la sogs pa'i bar du zla ba gsum
NK011(da)001:843: bzhugs / de nas rgya gar la gshegs pa ltar
NK011(da)001:844: du sdig blon rnams kyi ngor mdzad nas bod kyi
NK011(da)001:845: dben rtsa rnams su bzhugs te /
NK011(da)001:846: zla ba drug gi bgrod pa re la lo dang
NK011(da)001:847: zhag bco lnga la zla ba re re brtsi ba
NK011(da)001:848: / rgyal po lo chos la sogs pa rgya gar
NK011(da)001:849: gyi rtsis lugs gcig gi dbang du byas pa'i lo
NK011(da)001:851: lo hril po lnga bcu rtsa lnga dang zla ba drug bzhugs pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:852: don 'di nyid thugs su ma chud cing /
NK011(da)001:853: lo rgyus la go ba ma longs pa dag gis
NK011(da)001:854: myang gi gter dpe bee ro'i phyag bris ma las
NK011(da)001:855: / slob dpon pad+mas bod yul du lo brgya dang bcu gcig bzhugs te /
NK011(da)001:856: zhes pas rgyal po'i bla mchod du lo brgya dang /
NK011(da)001:857: sgrub gnas rnams su lo bcu gcig bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:859: rgyal pos dgung lo drug cu rtsa brgyad bzhugs par khas len mod kyi /
NK011(da)001:860: de ltar na lugs de'i lo bcu dgu po de
NK011(da)001:861: la gong gi mdzad pa de rnams rdzogs pa'i yul
NK011(da)001:862: med la / mdzad pa de dag ji ltar mdzad
NK011(da)001:863: pa'i tshul ni deng sang gi bar du phal che
NK011(da)001:864: ba mngon sum du gsal bas shes so //
NK011(da)001:865: spyir slob dpon 'di'i yon tan dang phrin las dang gdul bya 'dul tshul ni /
NK011(da)001:866: 'phags pa sa bcu pa la gnas pa rnams kyis
NK011(da)001:867: kyang bsam par mi nus shing sangs rgyas rnams kyis
NK011(da)001:868: bskal brgya'i bar du gsungs kyang rdzogs mtha' mngon pa
NK011(da)001:869: ma yin par rgya bod kyi pan grub thams cad
NK011(da)001:870: bzhed do // slob dpon de la phur pa'i slob ma mang yang /
NK011(da)001:871: mchog tu bka' babs pa ni jo mo mtsho rgyal yin te /
NK011(da)001:872: des mon kha ne ring seng ge rdzong gi brag
NK011(da)001:873: phug tu phur pa'i dkyil 'khor zhal phyes te bsgrubs
NK011(da)001:874: pas zhag nyer gcig nas phur pa thams cad bzhad
NK011(da)001:875: cing 'od 'phro ba dang bro 'khrab pa byung /
NK011(da)001:876: der jo mo'i dgongs pa la /
NK011(da)001:879: ging po 'grub na las la rbad //
NK011(da)001:880: phur pa 'grub na gdab las bya //
NK011(da)001:882: bdag la bsdo ba'i dgra ni med /
NK011(da)001:883: su la brdeg gam snyam ste bsnyen phur bsgril ba las /
NK011(da)001:884: bdag la dgra med kyang pha mes kyi srog gcod
NK011(da)001:885: pa'i za 'dre la gdab snyam du dgongs pa dang
NK011(da)001:886: / bsnyen phur phyag nas shor te nam mkha' la 'phur bas /
NK011(da)001:887: pha yul gyi khang pa'i ltag na 'dre de gnas
NK011(da)001:888: pa'i skyer phung gcig yod pa la babs te skyer
NK011(da)001:889: phung de rtsa ba nas bsregs shing za 'dre de
NK011(da)001:890: nyid du bsgral / phur pa de dbon brgyud rnams
NK011(da)001:891: kyis bcangs te gdengs pa tsam gyis lha 'dre mang
NK011(da)001:892: nyid du bsgral / po btul bas / mkhar chen
NK011(da)001:893: bza' 'dre 'dul gyi brgyud pa zhes zam ma chad
NK011(da)001:894: nyid du bsgral / po btul bas / par byung
NK011(da)001:895: ngo // jo mo 'dis ni sgrol ba tshad du
NK011(da)001:896: nyid du bsgral / po btul bas / par byung
NK011(da)001:897: ngo // phyin pas / mtshon gyis bsad pa'i mi
NK011(da)001:898: ro yang gson por slong nus pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:899: de nas ji ltar brgyud pa ni /
NK011(da)001:900: jo mos rang gi ming po mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug la bshad /
NK011(da)001:901: des la byid ye shes brtsegs la /
NK011(da)001:902: des lce ston yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK011(da)001:906: des rma chu rab kyi pha rol /
NK011(da)001:907: skye chu rab kyi tshu rol /
NK011(da)001:908: bye ma yug mo sgang du lang lab byang chub rdo rje la bshad de /
NK011(da)001:909: de yan chad chig brgyud kho na yin la /
NK011(da)001:910: phur ba man ngag drug pa zhes bya ba'i brgyud pa yin /
NK011(da)001:911: de nas lang lab kyis bka' babs sna nam shes
NK011(da)001:912: rab tshul khrims bka' brkus ba myang nag dbang gi
NK011(da)001:914: de dus kyi slob dpon so so'i chags sdang gi gtam yin gyi /
NK011(da)001:915: myang nag la bka' bab pa'i lo rgyus 'og tu 'chad do //
NK011(da)001:916: de nas sna nam gyis rgya ston sangs rgyas la bshad /
NK011(da)001:917: des shang gur zhogs khams pa lung du rgya thung shes rab rgyal mtshan la bshad /
NK011(da)001:918: des nag po rmu'i brag phug tu dgon ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan la bshad de /
NK011(da)001:919: 'dis ni sna nam shud bu mchims gsum gyi gdung brgyud la yang thug nas zhus so //
NK011(da)001:920: phur pa la 'di bas mkhas pa ma byung zhes grags /
NK011(da)001:921: des myang dar ma seng ge la bshad /
NK011(da)001:922: des gnubs shes rab ye shes la /
NK011(da)001:923: des rang gi sras gnubs bdud rtsi 'od la /
NK011(da)001:924: des sras phur grags la bshad /
NK011(da)001:925: des sras jo lcam la bshad /
NK011(da)001:939: bla chen chos kyi rgyal po /
NK011(da)001:940: de las bdag gis man ngag drug pa'i dbang dang gdams skor rnams kyi lung nos /
NK011(da)001:941: yang lang lab kyi slob ma kyi ban byang chub rin chen bya ba zhig byung /
NK011(da)001:942: de la pha spun rnams kyis khang zhing dang nor 'phrogs pa la brten nas /
NK011(da)001:943: lang lab la phur pa zhus te bsgrubs pas /
NK011(da)001:944: pha spun gyi mi grong tsho dgu'i mi phyugs sgo khyi tshun chad tshar bcad de /
NK011(da)001:945: mthar dgra 'di tsho shi bas mi chog khang pa'i
NK011(da)001:946: gyang 'di mthong ba dang yang snying na gsungs nas
NK011(da)001:948: gyang kun kyang rmang nas 'gyel te /
NK011(da)001:949: de nas mtshan yang skyi gyang 'gyel du grags /
NK011(da)001:950: de'i slob ma khams pa stong gsum sgom chen mu ne dang /
NK011(da)001:951: thag gdong dkar gyi btsun pa shes rab 'od gnyis
NK011(da)001:952: las mched de shin tu mthu che ba kyi phur
NK011(da)001:954: deng sang ni gdams skor thar bu las /
NK011(da)001:955: yongs su rdzogs pa bzhugs pa'i bka' lung yod pa ma rnyed do //
NK011(da)001:956: yi ge rnying pa las thag btsun shes rab 'od
NK011(da)001:957: kyi slob ma lha rje gnubs chung yin par bshad
NK011(da)001:958: pa ltar na gza' gdong dmar nag skor yongs kyi
NK011(da)001:959: lugs la yod dam snyam mo //
NK011(da)001:971: 'o bran la sogs pa'i rus chen rnams kyi gdung rigs las /
NK011(da)001:972: rdo rje phur pa'i grub pa thob pa ni bod
NK011(da)001:973: yul 'dir shin tu mang zhing brjod kyis mi lang
NK011(da)001:974: la / gsar ma'i sngags rnams ma dar gyi bar
NK011(da)001:975: du bod du yi dam dang bstan srung gi srog
NK011(da)001:976: rtsa yang phur gyis bzung ba yin pas /
NK011(da)001:977: brgyud pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i sngags 'chang de rnams kyi gdung rigs shas che ba las /
NK011(da)001:978: gsar ma'i skyes chen rnams kyang byon pa yin te /
NK011(da)001:979: bstan pa'i bdag po sa skya ba dang /
NK011(da)001:981: phag mo gru pa la sogs pa lta bu ste /
NK011(da)001:982: ji ltar byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK011(da)001:983: so so'i gdung rabs rnams su gzigs par mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:984: bdag cag shes rab chung ba rnams kyis brjod par mi nus so //
NK011(da)001:985: da ni rang lugs la grags pa rong zom lugs kyi lo rgyus cung zad brjod par bya ste /
NK011(da)001:986: de la phur pa'i chos 'di rong zom la ji ltar brgyud pa ni /
NK011(da)001:989: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug /
NK011(da)001:990: don +aa tsar+ya dpal gyi me tog /
NK011(da)001:993: rong ban yon tan rin chen /
NK011(da)001:994: rong ban rin chen tshul khrims kyi bar du brgyud pa las 'ongs pa yin la /
NK011(da)001:996: rong ban yon tan rin chen gyis slob dpon pad+ma dngos la thug /
NK011(da)001:997: des mi yul du lo sum brgya bzhugs te mthar sku lus ma spangs par mkha' spyod du gshegs /
NK011(da)001:998: de'i sras rong ban rin chen tshul khrims kyis kyang lo phyed dang nyis brgya bzhugs /
NK011(da)001:999: de'i sras rong zom yin la /
NK011(da)001:1000: 'dis lo brgya dang bcu dgu mi yul du bzhugs
NK011(da)001:1001: te sku bsgres rgud mi mnga' ba'i ngang nas sku
NK011(da)001:1003: gang ltar yang grub thob bar ma chad pa'i brgyud pa yin la /
NK011(da)001:1005: bod ru bzhi'i nang nas ru lag gtsang smad kyi sa'i cha /
NK011(da)001:1007: sku gzhon nu nas sgra tshad la sogs pa shes
NK011(da)001:1008: bya thams cad la mkhas shing gzhan dag dngos po
NK011(da)001:1009: stobs shugs kyi rigs pas tshar bcad pas /
NK011(da)001:1010: kha cig pan+di ta smri ti'i skye ba yin zer /
NK011(da)001:1011: kha cig pan+di ta phra la ring mo'i skye ba yin zer /
NK011(da)001:1012: phyis jo bo rje dang rong yul lhar mjal rtsod pa byas pas /
NK011(da)001:1013: jo bos rong zom ma thub /
NK011(da)001:1015: khyod rgya gar gyi +aa tsar+ya nag po zhabs chen po spyod pa ba de'i skye ba yin te /
NK011(da)001:1016: kho bos khyod dang chos kyi gtam bya bar ga la thub ces gsungs /
NK011(da)001:1017: ngo mtshar ba'i mdzad pa dang cho 'phrul la thogs pa med pas /
NK011(da)001:1018: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa'i sprul par yang grags la /
NK011(da)001:1019: phal cher mthun par 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa yin zhes pa sngags pa brjod do //
NK011(da)001:1020: 'dis dgung lo bcu gcig la mtshan nyid gsan /
NK011(da)001:1021: bcu gsum yan chad la gsan pa rdzogs te /
NK011(da)001:1023: bslab pa'i shes bya thams cad la yang ma rmongs /
NK011(da)001:1024: dka' ba'i gnas rnams kyang lan re nyan pas mkhyen pa yin te /
NK011(da)001:1026: bdag thos pa chung ba yang ma yin te /
NK011(da)001:1027: chos thams cad la ma thos pa med do //
NK011(da)001:1028: bdag thos pa che ba yang ma yin te /
NK011(da)001:1029: chos thams cad la tshar re las ma dgos so //
NK011(da)001:1031: spyir na dam pa 'di shes rab zab la rgya che ba dri ma med pa dang ldan pas /
NK011(da)001:1032: rgya gar gyi chos su gtogs pa mdo rgyud bstan
NK011(da)001:1033: bcos sngar ma gzigs pa dag la yang tshar re
NK011(da)001:1034: re gnyis gnyis tsam gzigs pas mkhyen nas tshig don
NK011(da)001:1035: ma lus pa thugs su chud cing mi brjed pa'i
NK011(da)001:1037: gzhan yang tsa na ka la sogs pa 'jig rten gyi bstan bcos dang /
NK011(da)001:1041: rig byed kyi bstan bcos gzhan gsum dang /
NK011(da)001:1042: sa brtag pa la sogs pa'i shes bya phra mo mtha' dag la yang mkhas shing /
NK011(da)001:1043: thugs rje chen po mnga' bas chos la mos pa'i mi rnams dang /
NK011(da)001:1045: rdo rje theg pa la zhugs pa dag gi las
NK011(da)001:1046: dang dngos grub sgrub par 'dod pa rnams la phyin
NK011(da)001:1047: ci ma log pa'i gdams pas nan tan du phan
NK011(da)001:1048: thogs pa mdzad / mngon par shes pa'i cha dang
NK011(da)001:1049: ldan zhing sems can 'dul ba'i dus dang tshod la
NK011(da)001:1050: thogs pa mdzad / mkhas / 'gro ba phal pa
NK011(da)001:1051: dang chos kyi bloo bsgyur ba rnams tshe 'di dang
NK011(da)001:1052: phyi ma gnyis ka bde ba la 'god pa'i phyir
NK011(da)001:1053: bstan bcos mang du brtsams shing /
NK011(da)001:1054: de lta bus phan 'dogs pa la dus rtag tu skyo ba mi mnga' /
NK011(da)001:1055: chos kyis blo ma bsgyur ba'i skye bo phal pa
NK011(da)001:1056: la yang ser sna dang gnod sems spangs nas thugs
NK011(da)001:1057: rjes yul du mdzad de zhi bde la 'god /
NK011(da)001:1058: sdom pa dang thugs dam la srog ltar gces spras su mdzad cing /
NK011(da)001:1059: gzhan dag kyang de la sbyor /
NK011(da)001:1060: chos rtsom pa na glegs bam bsdu zhing gzigs pa la sogs pa'i rtsol ba ma mdzad kyang /
NK011(da)001:1061: chos phyogs med la thogs rdugs med pa'i spobs pa spro ba nas /
NK011(da)001:1062: bstan bcos mdzad pa de dag kyang lung dang rig
NK011(da)001:1063: pa dang mi 'gal zhing sgra skyon dang don skyon
NK011(da)001:1064: rnam par bral bas gzhan mkhas pa sus kyang rtsod
NK011(da)001:1065: mi nus / sgra'i tshul dang samskri ta'i skad ma bslab par mkhyen /
NK011(da)001:1066: byis pa'i dus su a tsa ra byung tshad la dgyes shing de dag gi skad la mkhas /
NK011(da)001:1067: byi to'i po ti gzigs pas skad dod kyi bag chags sad pa ltar gyur /
NK011(da)001:1068: tha na dud 'gro'i skad dang brda yang mkhyen /
NK011(da)001:1069: 'khrul pa mi mnga' zhing byin rlabs che bas /
NK011(da)001:1070: des mdzad pa'i gsang sngags kyi yig cha rnams la
NK011(da)001:1071: slob pa'i brgyud du byung ba'i gang zag rnams kyis
NK011(da)001:1072: lung ma thob par yi ge la byung ba bzhin
NK011(da)001:1073: du bsgrub pa la byin rlabs dang dngos grub ma
NK011(da)001:1074: byung ba med / lo ts+aa ba chen po de
NK011(da)001:1075: la dus de'i tshe bod ru bzhi'i mkhas pa mang
NK011(da)001:1077: go rub lo ts+aa ba dge slong chos kyi shes
NK011(da)001:1078: rab ces bya ba chos phyogs med la mkhas pa
NK011(da)001:1079: zhig gis / thog mar bod du skyes pa'i gang
NK011(da)001:1080: zag gis chos mang po brtsams zhes skur pa btab
NK011(da)001:1081: zhig gis / bo // phyis bla ma rong zom
NK011(da)001:1082: gyis mdzad pa'i theg pa chen po'i tshul la 'jug
NK011(da)001:1083: pa'i po ti de mthong bas gus pa chen po
NK011(da)001:1084: zhig gis / bo // skyes te / zang zing
NK011(da)001:1085: mang pos mnyes par byas te nyes pa bshags nas
NK011(da)001:1086: bdag rjes su bzung du gsol zhes zhus pas gnang
NK011(da)001:1087: zhig gis / bo // skyes te / ste /
NK011(da)001:1088: 'jam dpal gsang rgyud la sogs pa chos mang du
NK011(da)001:1089: zhig gis / bo // skyes te / ste /
NK011(da)001:1090: zhus pas gnang / gzhan yang mar pa chos kyi
NK011(da)001:1091: dbang phyug la sogs pa'i lo ts+aa ba dang /
NK011(da)001:1092: mkhas par grags pa'i blo rtsal can mang pos btud
NK011(da)001:1093: cing gsan par gyur te gsan pa po de dag
NK011(da)001:1094: gi slob brgyud thams cad kyang shin tu dad nas
NK011(da)001:1096: gsang rgyud kyi skabs su nyid kyi zhal nas /
NK011(da)001:1097: 'o skol la da lta rgya dpe yod na 'di ltar 'gro ba yin te /
NK011(da)001:1098: rgya dpe med pas da lta bcos su med gsungs pa la /
NK011(da)001:1099: go rub kyis de bzung nas phyis jo bo krish+na
NK011(da)001:1100: pa zhes bya ba'i pan+di ta las rgya dpe byung
NK011(da)001:1102: rong pa chen pos gsungs pa bzhin byung bas shin tu mos te /
NK011(da)001:1103: krish+na pa las byung ba'i dpe gcig rong pa de nyid la phul nas yang gsan skad /
NK011(da)001:1105: pan+di ta many+dzu sh+r+ai wa rma dang /
NK011(da)001:1107: u pa ya sh+r+ai mi tra dang /
NK011(da)001:1108: bud+d+ha +aa ka ra b+ha dra dang /
NK011(da)001:1109: de b+aa ka ri tsan+t+ra dang /
NK011(da)001:1110: sa ra me shwa ra dang /
NK011(da)001:1111: a mo g+ha badz+ra la sogs pa pan+di ta mang po bsten nas /
NK011(da)001:1112: de dag gis lo ts+aa ba mdzad de /
NK011(da)001:1116: bde mchog rtsa rgyud la sogs pa mang du bsgyur /
NK011(da)001:1117: 'gyur shin tu bzang bas phan che bar btags /
NK011(da)001:1118: pan+di ta kun gyi gsung nas kyang /
NK011(da)001:1119: d+harma b+ha dra khyod kyis chos mang po brtsams la 'gro ba rnams skyobs shig /
NK011(da)001:1120: khyod kyi yon tan gzhan lta zhog gi /
NK011(da)001:1121: sgra tshad kyi lugs 'di'i sum cha tsam las mi
NK011(da)001:1122: shes pas kyang rgya gar na chos mang po rtsom
NK011(da)001:1123: pa yin / khyed ci'i phyir chos mi brtsam zhes gsungs /
NK011(da)001:1124: de lta bu'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa dang
NK011(da)001:1125: ldan yang bdag bstod la sogs pa'i dri ma dang
NK011(da)001:1126: bral cing / gzhan gyi chos lugs dang spyod pa dman yang don du 'gyur na ma gtogs /
NK011(da)001:1127: pha rol khyad du gsod pa'i gtam ye mi gsung /
NK011(da)001:1128: brag gzar po'i ngos la gshegs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1130: brag la phur pa 'debs pa la sogs pa'i rdzu 'phrul dang grub rtags la thogs pa mi mnga' /
NK011(da)001:1131: myang smad du 'gar ston tshul khrims bzang po la
NK011(da)001:1132: gsang sngags rnying ma gsan te 'di dgung lo bcu
NK011(da)001:1134: lo bcu gsum pa la mkhas pa mdo ston seng ge rgyal mtshan la yang gsan /
NK011(da)001:1135: mnal lam du gsang ba snying pos zan byas /
NK011(da)001:1136: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyis tshod ma byas gsol ba rmis pa slob dpon la zhus pas /
NK011(da)001:1138: chos de khong du chud pa'i rtags yin no //
NK011(da)001:1139: de gnyis la khyod kyis 'grel pa re gyis gsungs pas 'grel pa mdzad de /
NK011(da)001:1140: bod du yig cha byung ba la bzang /
NK011(da)001:1141: dus phyis bstan bcos mdzad pa ni /
NK011(da)001:1142: bslab pa rin po che gsum la bsten pa'i ched du /
NK011(da)001:1143: gal che ba'i man ngag gsum mdzad de /
NK011(da)001:1144: lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa rgyud la bskyed pa'i phyir dam tshig mdo rgyas mdzad /
NK011(da)001:1145: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pa rgyud la
NK011(da)001:1146: bskyed pa'i phyir 'grel pa tshul bzhi yan lag bco
NK011(da)001:1147: lnga pa mdzad / lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab
NK011(da)001:1148: pa rgyud la bskyed pa'i phyir rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK011(da)001:1150: gzhan yang ngan song spyong rgyud /
NK011(da)001:1151: 'jigs byed dang smra sgo la sogs pa la yang 'grel pa mdzad cing /
NK011(da)001:1152: bstan bcos gzhan yang mang du mdzad do //
NK011(da)001:1153: de'i dus su shab kyi yang khyed bla ma /
NK011(da)001:1161: rgya rgyal tshul khrims la sogs pa bod ru bzhi'i mkhas pa rnams kyis rtsod par brtsam ste /
NK011(da)001:1162: bod du skyes pa'i gang zag gis bstan bcos 'di
NK011(da)001:1163: tsam brtsam par mi rigs so zhes zer zhing sun
NK011(da)001:1165: gsung gleng mdzad pa tsam gyis rtsod pa'i spobs pa bcom /
NK011(da)001:1166: bstan bcos re mthong bas shin tu mos te /
NK011(da)001:1168: zhabs tog mdzad de gtan gyi skyabs gnas su 'dzin par gyur to //
NK011(da)001:1169: de ltar rong zom 'di ni 'khrungs pa tsam nyid
NK011(da)001:1170: nas ngang gis dge ba'i kun spyod can lhun gyis
NK011(da)001:1172: 'jig rten lugs kyi thugs dkyil yang shin tu che
NK011(da)001:1173: zhing rang dang dus mtshungs kyi mkhas pa thams cad
NK011(da)001:1175: phyi nang gi rigs pa'i gnas mtha' dag la mkhas /
NK011(da)001:1176: khyad par sgra tshad la ma rmongs pas /
NK011(da)001:1178: 'di ni don 'di tsam zhig la 'jug go zhes
NK011(da)001:1179: tshig don gyi khyad par phra mo dag kyang gzhan
NK011(da)001:1180: las ches lhag par ston nus /
NK011(da)001:1181: mdo rgyud bstan bcos bod du 'gyur ro cog gi
NK011(da)001:1182: tshig don ma lus pa thugs su chud cing mkhas
NK011(da)001:1183: / tha na 'jig rten pa'i 'tsho tshigs zhing las /
NK011(da)001:1185: dkar she sgrub pa sogs la'ang mkhas pas /
NK011(da)001:1186: de dag ji ltar sgrub pa'i bstan bcos kyang mdzad /
NK011(da)001:1187: bod kyi lha 'dre thams cad kyis kyang chos zhus zhing bsnyen bkur /
NK011(da)001:1191: bstan pa'i bdag por gyur pa yin te /
NK011(da)001:1192: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi chos thams cad kyang mnga' /
NK011(da)001:1193: bee ro tsa na'i chos thams cad kyang /
NK011(da)001:1194: bee ros g.yu sgra snying po /
NK011(da)001:1195: des bla chen dgongs pa rab gsal /
NK011(da)001:1196: des grum shing slag can nas gnubs dpal brtan /
NK011(da)001:1198: des rong zom la bshad de /
NK011(da)001:1199: sems phyogs kyi brgyud pa lugs gcig kyang mnga' ste bstan pa'i bdag por gyur /
NK011(da)001:1200: 'dan klong thang sgrol mar sku 'khrungs pa'i sprul pa'i
NK011(da)001:1201: sku a ro ye shes 'byung gnas kyi gdams pa'i
NK011(da)001:1203: 'di la rgya gar bdun brgyud dang rgya'i h+aa shang bdun brgyud kyi gdams pa yod pa las /
NK011(da)001:1204: a ro'i dngos slob lcog ro zangs dkar mdzod khur
NK011(da)001:1205: dang khams pa ya zi bon ston gnyis ka la
NK011(da)001:1207: de nas brgyud pa tsho la rdzogs chen khams lugs su grags /
NK011(da)001:1208: bi ma la nas brgyud pa rnams kyang myang ting 'dzin bzang po dang /
NK011(da)001:1210: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra nas brgyud pa dag kyang /
NK011(da)001:1211: gnyags dang rma gnyis kas khu byang chub 'od dang /
NK011(da)001:1212: khyung po dbyig 'od las rim par 'ongs te rong zom la mnga' /
NK011(da)001:1213: mdor na 'di'i mkhyen pa dang yon tan ni sus kyang brjod du mi nus shing /
NK011(da)001:1214: bod gangs can gyi rgyud 'dir 'di dang mnyam pa'i mkhas pa ni su yang ma byung la /
NK011(da)001:1215: spyir 'di sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa yin mod kyi /
NK011(da)001:1216: grub pa thob pa ni rdo rje phur pa'i sgo nas yin pas /
NK011(da)001:1217: phur pa'i bstan bcos kyang mang du mdzad de /
NK011(da)001:1218: brgyud pa rnams kyang grub thob zam ma chad par byon pa yin la /
NK011(da)001:1222: dang por rong ban dpal gyi rin yon tan rin chen /
NK011(da)001:1225: de'i sras rong ban rin chen tshul khrims /
NK011(da)001:1226: de'i sras rong zom chos kyi bzang po dang /
NK011(da)001:1228: chos bzang gi sras gzi brjid 'bar dang 'bum 'bar gnyis /
NK011(da)001:1229: gzi brjid 'bar gyi sras ston dar dang ston skyabs gnyis /
NK011(da)001:1230: ston dar la sras ston seng /
NK011(da)001:1231: ston seng gi sras jo sras ra spe /
NK011(da)001:1233: ston skyabs kyi sras jo sras 'od zer /
NK011(da)001:1235: chos bzang gi sras gnyis pa 'bum 'bar la sras chos kyi rgyal mtshan /
NK011(da)001:1237: jo bzang sogs kha yar byung /
NK011(da)001:1238: chos kyi rgyal mtshan gyi sras ru +aa nan+da badz+ra ste /
NK011(da)001:1240: de'i sras slob dpon me dpung /
NK011(da)001:1241: de'i sras chos kyi bshes gnyen dang /
NK011(da)001:1243: rong pa jo bzang gi sras slob dpon jo bkra /
NK011(da)001:1246: dar bzang gi sras slob dpon gser 'od /
NK011(da)001:1247: jo bo rdo rje brtan gyi sras nyi ma seng ge /
NK011(da)001:1248: de'i sras 'od zer 'bum dang 'bum rgod gnyis /
NK011(da)001:1249: rong sgom chen chos 'phags kyi sras slob dpon ston g.yung /
NK011(da)001:1250: de'i sras jo sras lha bsrung /
NK011(da)001:1251: de'i sras slob dpon byams chos pa chen po dar ma brtan /
NK011(da)001:1252: de'i sras slob dpon sra brtan rdo rje yin no //
NK011(da)001:1253: deng sang ni rong zom gyi gdung brgyud chad nas
NK011(da)001:1254: med kyang 'bum rgod kyi dus su rin spungs pa'i
NK011(da)001:1255: zhal ngo nam mkha' rgyal pos sbyin bdag mdzad de
NK011(da)001:1257: de'i nang nas mchog tu gyur pa thang khrom bka' bzhi pa yin te /
NK011(da)001:1259: rong zom chos kyi bzang po'i gdung 'bum dgon pa dkar por spyan drangs /
NK011(da)001:1260: phur pa'i chos skor gnyags kyi gdung brgyud sngags 'chang sle ma ba rnams la gsungs so //
NK011(da)001:1262: spyir dam pa 'di la de dus kyi mkhas grub
NK011(da)001:1263: thams cad kyis zhabs la gtugs pa bsam gyis mi
NK011(da)001:1264: khyab cing / khyad par go rub lo ts+aa ba /
NK011(da)001:1266: 'gos la sogs pa lo ts+aa ba bcu bdun /
NK011(da)001:1267: g.yag rdo rje 'dzin pa sogs pa grub thob chen po sum cu rtsa lnga /
NK011(da)001:1268: ma gcig zha ma'i ming po rje mkhon bu ba
NK011(da)001:1269: la sogs pa sgom chen grub pa thob pa brgya
NK011(da)001:1270: dang brgyad cu / yol dge bsnyen rdo rje dbang phyug dang /
NK011(da)001:1271: yang khyed bla ma sogs ston pa gdugs thob pa
NK011(da)001:1272: lnga brgya la sogs pa mtha' yas te brjod kyis
NK011(da)001:1273: mi lang ba lta bu las /
NK011(da)001:1274: phur pa'i chos skor ji ltar brgyud pa ni /
NK011(da)001:1275: rong zom gyis yol dge bsnyen rdo rje dbang phyug /
NK011(da)001:1288: lo chen bsod nams rgya mtsho /
NK011(da)001:1289: chag lo rin chen chos rgyal /
NK011(da)001:1290: bla ma dam pa rdo rje seng ge /
NK011(da)001:1291: de la bdag gis rong zom gyi dbang lung rdzogs par zhus so //
NK011(da)001:1292: yang phur pa lha nag tu grags pa ni /
NK011(da)001:1293: slob dpon pad+ma yab yum yan chad spyi dang 'dra la /
NK011(da)001:1294: de la 'bre a tsa ra nu ru /
NK011(da)001:1295: 'di ni phur pa'i sgo nas grub pa thob ste
NK011(da)001:1296: tshe'i rig 'dzin brnyes pas deng sang gi bar du
NK011(da)001:1297: 'das grongs med par bzhugs pa yin la /
NK011(da)001:1298: lang lab byang chub rdo rjes grub pa thob tshar ba'i rjes su'ang 'di dang mjal nas /
NK011(da)001:1299: sngar thob pa'i phur pa'i skor la zhus dag byas nas tshar gcig zhus pa yin cing /
NK011(da)001:1301: ngam 'bre a tsa ra sa le yin par byas 'dug pa ni ma nges pa chen po ste /
NK011(da)001:1302: mtsho rgyal dang lang lab kyi bar na mi rabs lnga yod pa ma go ba yin la /
NK011(da)001:1303: gter ma'i lo rgyus gcig na /
NK011(da)001:1304: lang lab lo bdun 'gro ba'i byis pa gcig gis /
NK011(da)001:1305: slob dpon lho nub tu byon khar zhabs la gtugs zer ba snang ste /
NK011(da)001:1306: ma nges pa'i rang bzo kho na'o //
NK011(da)001:1307: phyis 'gro ba'i mgon po chos rgyal 'phags pas /
NK011(da)001:1308: smad las drag po sgrol ba'i dbang 'di gsan par bzhed nas btsal bsam rnyed de /
NK011(da)001:1309: 'khor rnams la 'di lta bu'i dbang thob pa 'dug na sprang po zhig la 'dug kyang khrid shog /
NK011(da)001:1310: de la kho bos zhu'o gsungs nas btsal kyang ma rnyed /
NK011(da)001:1311: phyis bal po nas tshong pa'i skad cha las /
NK011(da)001:1312: jo mo mtsho rgyal gyi slob ma a tsa ra
NK011(da)001:1313: nu lo rgyus gzhan las bal po'i pan+di ta rat+na
NK011(da)001:1314: sh+r+ai yin zer / ru bya ba tshe'i rig 'dzin
NK011(da)001:1315: thob pa zhig la phur pa'i chos rdzogs par zhus
NK011(da)001:1316: sh+r+ai yin zer / / bal po na gsung gi 'dug zer /
NK011(da)001:1317: der bstan pa'i khur chen por dgongs nas /
NK011(da)001:1318: 'o na de bal por yod dam gsungs pas med /
NK011(da)001:1319: bsil ba tshal la sogs pa'i gnas rnams su mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi don mdzad pa yin zer /
NK011(da)001:1320: skabs su skabs su byon nas gdul bya skal ba
NK011(da)001:1321: can rnams la chos bag re gsung bar gda' zer
NK011(da)001:1322: ba las / 'o na de bal por byon na
NK011(da)001:1323: nga la skad thegs par gyis gsungs te gnang sbyin
NK011(da)001:1324: ba las / mang po gnang / de nas lo 'ga' song ba dang /
NK011(da)001:1326: der 'phags pa rin po che chos dang 'jig rten
NK011(da)001:1327: gyi thugs brel gyis g.yengs nas 'byon ma thub nas
NK011(da)001:1328: / glo bo lo ts+aa ba shes rab rin chen
NK011(da)001:1329: la gser la sogs pa'i dngos po mang po bskur
NK011(da)001:1330: / nas bardzangasa / de nas lo ts+aa ba bod
NK011(da)001:1331: du byon pa dang 'phags pa rin po ches drag
NK011(da)001:1333: deng sang gi bar du ma nub pa 'di yang
NK011(da)001:1334: a tsa ra nu ru dang 'phags pa rin po
NK011(da)001:1336: lha nag gi brgyud pa ni /
NK011(da)001:1337: ya 'brog pa go rub yang dag gis rgyud mya
NK011(da)001:1338: ngan las 'das pa zhes bya ba 'di la brten
NK011(da)001:1339: nas lha thams cad nag por mdzad pa las byung
NK011(da)001:1341: de'i gong gi brgyud pa ni /
NK011(da)001:1344: sna nam tshul khrims shes rab /
NK011(da)001:1356: dpal ldan rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK011(da)001:1357: 'di bshad 'bum rdo rje don gsal dang /
NK011(da)001:1358: dbang chog sgrub skor la sogs pa yig sna mang du mdzad /
NK011(da)001:1359: des bla ma tshul rgyal ba /
NK011(da)001:1360: ri gdong pa shes rab rgyal mtshan /
NK011(da)001:1361: slob dpon bsod nams bzang po dang /
NK011(da)001:1362: slob dpon bkra shis rgya mtsho /
NK011(da)001:1364: sems dpal chen po nam mkha'i mtshan can /
NK011(da)001:1365: bla ma chen po rdo rje rgyal po /
NK011(da)001:1367: de la bdag gis zhus so //
NK011(da)001:1368: yang go rub nas brgyud pa'i phur pa lha nag ni /
NK011(da)001:1370: snye mdo pa la babs te phrin las che bar byung ngo //
NK011(da)001:1371: deng sang gi bar du bstan pa'i bdag po dpal
NK011(da)001:1372: sa skya pa rnams phyag len du mdzad pa'i sa
NK011(da)001:1374: dang por mkhon klu dbang srung bas slob dpon pad+ma
NK011(da)001:1375: dngos la zhus nas bsgrubs pas grub pa thob ste
NK011(da)001:1376: 'di'i gcung mkhon rdo rje rin chen ni phur pa
NK011(da)001:1377: la brten nas grub pa thob cing /
NK011(da)001:1378: de'i sras shes rab yon tan /
NK011(da)001:1385: mkhon rog shes rab tshul khrims /
NK011(da)001:1386: 'dis ni lha srin bran du 'khor zhing /
NK011(da)001:1387: yi dam mang po'i zhal gzigs /
NK011(da)001:1388: rnga la zhon te nam mkha' la 'gro ba la
NK011(da)001:1389: sogs pa rdzu 'phrul thogs med du ston nus pa
NK011(da)001:1390: yin la / 'di yan chad du phur pa'i grub pa thob pa sha stag byon no //
NK011(da)001:1391: mkhon rog 'di'i gcung po dkon mchog rgyal po yin te /
NK011(da)001:1392: 'dis 'gro ba'i lung stong chen po zhig la ltad mor byon pas sngags pa 'gas /
NK011(da)001:1393: dbang phyug nyer brgyad kyi 'chams byas pas khrom thog chod /
NK011(da)001:1394: de'i lo rgyus gcen la bsnyad pas /
NK011(da)001:1395: da gsang sngags 'chol ba bya ba'i dus byung bas grub thob mi 'ong /
NK011(da)001:1396: rang re la yod pa'i dpe cha lha rten sngags kyi lag cha kun gter du sbos /
NK011(da)001:1399: mang dkar du 'brog mi lo ts+aa ba la gsang
NK011(da)001:1400: sngags gsar ma nyon shog gsungs nas rnying ma kun
NK011(da)001:1401: gter du sbas / der chos skyong gi cho 'phrul che bas /
NK011(da)001:1402: phur pa'i mngon rtogs skor bsdus pa gcig /
NK011(da)001:1403: yang dag gi dpe tshan gcig /
NK011(da)001:1405: seng ldeng phur pa dkor cha gnyis /
NK011(da)001:1406: dkar mo nyi zlas mkhon rog la dngos su bstan
NK011(da)001:1407: pa'i sgrub skor rnams 'don dgos pa byung ste gcung
NK011(da)001:1408: la gnang / 'di'i sras sa skya pa chen po yin la /
NK011(da)001:1409: de nas rje btsun sku mched sa skya pan+di ta dang /
NK011(da)001:1410: 'phags pa rin po che nas rim par brgyud nas deng sang gi bar du dar rgyas che la /
NK011(da)001:1411: bla chen chos kyi rgyal po'i drung du bdag gis
NK011(da)001:1412: kyang ldong ston gyi yig cha'i steng nas sa phur
NK011(da)001:1413: gyi dbang dang / chos skor sna 'ga' re thos so //
NK011(da)001:1414: yang gsang ba'i rgyud phur pa la brten pa mtha' dag nas btus pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1416: k+ai la ya'i tan+t+ra bcu gnyis nas btus pa gsham sngon gyi skor du grags pa /
NK011(da)001:1417: stod las yang dag la brten nas byang chub sgrub pa'i tshul dang /
NK011(da)001:1418: smad las sras mchog phur pa la brten nas dgra
NK011(da)001:1419: bgegs sgrol ba'i rim pa dang por bal yul yang
NK011(da)001:1420: le shod du slob dpon rnams pa gsum gyis mdzad
NK011(da)001:1421: / bod yul du slob dpon pad+mas bsnams nas byon
NK011(da)001:1422: pa dus der spel ba'i dus la ma babs nas
NK011(da)001:1423: / / byang gi bya mang mtsho'i sa'i char gter
NK011(da)001:1424: du sbas pa dus phyis gter ston byang chub gling
NK011(da)001:1425: pa dpal rgyal mtshan gyis gter nas bton te deng
NK011(da)001:1427: pan chen bi ma la mi tra nas brgyud de
NK011(da)001:1428: dar ba'i tshul ni bod chos kyis skyong ba'i rgyal
NK011(da)001:1429: po khri srong lde'u btsan sku gshegs rjes /
NK011(da)001:1430: btsun mo dmar rgyan bza' me tog dbang che zhing spyod pa ngan pas /
NK011(da)001:1431: sngags kyi lo ts+aa ba kun la sdang zhing gtses pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1434: gnyags la sogs pa bsam yas su ma bzhugs par bas mtha' dang /
NK011(da)001:1435: yul gyi mtha'i dben pa rnams na bzhugs la /
NK011(da)001:1436: khyad par du gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra yar 'brog sgang du bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK011(da)001:1437: rang gi pha spun po gnyags dge la ston gyis
NK011(da)001:1438: 'di mu stegs ngan sngags mkhan yin no zhes yul
NK011(da)001:1440: ban+d+ha zung gcig bswe zhos byug nas dmar por yod pa de gnyis brkus nas /
NK011(da)001:1441: ban+d+ha gri rtses 'drud cing mi rnams la ston /
NK011(da)001:1442: 'dis zog 'di 'dra byed do zer ya ga bsgrags so //
NK011(da)001:1444: dben pa bshig pa'i gros bshams pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1445: slob dpon gyis de dgongs nas /
NK011(da)001:1446: gang du dgongs pa mdzad pa'i sar rin po che gtor zhing bzhag pas /
NK011(da)001:1448: slob dpon gang na dgongs pa mdzad pa'i shul kyang rin po che brul lo //
NK011(da)001:1449: khyod kyis de mi bden no zer ba la /
NK011(da)001:1451: mi bden na 'di red zer zhing yang ban+d+ha gri rtses 'drud cing ston no //
NK011(da)001:1452: der slob dpon yul der ma chags nas g.yog po
NK011(da)001:1453: glal mi 'og btsan bya ba zhig khrid nas kong
NK011(da)001:1454: po mchims yul gyi gting du byon pas /
NK011(da)001:1459: g.yog po na re 'di kun gyis ci 'tshal /
NK011(da)001:1460: ra la bdag po mchis byas pas /
NK011(da)001:1462: lung stong gi ra la bdag po ga na mchis /
NK011(da)001:1463: ded gsungs nas ded phyin pas /
NK011(da)001:1464: ra mchims bya rog gi yin pas /
NK011(da)001:1465: khos mthong nas rkun khag btsugs /
NK011(da)001:1467: ra la bdun 'jal sprad tsa na /
NK011(da)001:1468: ma nyan par dben pa bshig /
NK011(da)001:1469: lcags kyi tho ba thogs nas ded pas slob dpon bros te gtsug lag khang du chud /
NK011(da)001:1471: sgo'i ya lcibs la lcags kyi tho ba chen po gcig brgyab ste /
NK011(da)001:1472: btsun chung gi mgo la lcags tho de'u thob zer ro //
NK011(da)001:1473: der yang bzhugs su ma chags nas /
NK011(da)001:1474: bod yul dbus su byon pas /
NK011(da)001:1475: slob dpon rta gcig chibs nas mas nas byon pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1476: 'bro sras chung sha ba gcig ded nas yas nas byung ba dang thug gis phrad pas /
NK011(da)001:1478: sha ba yang shor bas kho slar byung ste /
NK011(da)001:1479: nyams ban 'dis nga yi sha ba yang shor /
NK011(da)001:1481: rta brdabs kyang 'tshal zer nas ded de gsod par chas ba la /
NK011(da)001:1483: dus de tsa na mnga' bdag gi sras che ba mu ne btsan po la /
NK011(da)001:1484: yum dmar rgyan bzas dug btang ste bgrongs /
NK011(da)001:1485: de'i 'dad kyi tshogs dpon la slob dpon bi ma la rgya nag nas spyan drangs 'dug /
NK011(da)001:1486: der bi ma la'i spyan sngar phyin nas gser phye long mo gang phul /
NK011(da)001:1488: lo ts+aa ba dpon g.yog skyid dam gsungs pa la /
NK011(da)001:1489: yar 'brog sgang du skyid bgyi ru //
NK011(da)001:1490: dge la ston gyi ma ster ro //
NK011(da)001:1491: mchims yul gting du skyid bgyi ru //
NK011(da)001:1492: bya rog dmyal bas ma ster ro //
NK011(da)001:1493: bod yul dbus su skyid bgyi ru //
NK011(da)001:1494: 'bro sras chung gis ma ster ro //
NK011(da)001:1496: bi ma las bstan pa nub kyis dogs nas /
NK011(da)001:1497: phur pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1498: gsham sngon ma bu gnyis thugs nas phyung ste gnang /
NK011(da)001:1499: lho brag mkhar chu sna'i brag phug tu seng ldeng
NK011(da)001:1500: phur pa nyi shu rtsa gcig la brten te bi
NK011(da)001:1501: ma la dang / gnyags lo ts+aa ba gnyis kas
NK011(da)001:1502: bsgrubs pas phur bu 'khrol ba la sogs pa'i mtshan
NK011(da)001:1504: der gnyags kyis thog mar bya rog la'o byas nas phur pa bsgril bas /
NK011(da)001:1505: stong khams kyi bya rog thams cad 'ub 'ub 'dus byung /
NK011(da)001:1506: ma yin te mchims bya rog la'o byas pas /
NK011(da)001:1507: mchims yul steng gi bya rog zung zhig byung /
NK011(da)001:1508: der gnyags khros nas bya rog gcig la btab par brtsams pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1509: bya rog tshub ling gis shi'o //
NK011(da)001:1510: de nas bi ma las da slong la thong byas bas bslang ma thub /
NK011(da)001:1511: der bi ma las bye ma gcig btab ste bslang ste btang /
NK011(da)001:1512: da phyin chad de tsug ma byed sdig che'o gsung nas /
NK011(da)001:1513: gnas lung gi cho ga yang der gnang ngo //
NK011(da)001:1514: de nas mchims lha than tsho g.yag dkar po gcig
