NK011(da)001:1515: tu byas nas byung ba la yang phur pa btab
NK011(da)001:1516: nas bsgral / mchims bya rog kyang der bsgral /
NK011(da)001:1517: bla spyang rab la btab pas rab bskams /
NK011(da)001:1519: tha ma la btab pas tha ma bskams /
NK011(da)001:1523: gnag gi gnyen mtshams yan chod la btab pas rabs bcad de /
NK011(da)001:1524: dam sri'am sku dgra rnam pa gcig der btul lo //
NK011(da)001:1525: dam sri rnam pa gcig ni pha spun po gnyags
NK011(da)001:1526: dge la ston la btab pas slob dpon gnyags nyid
NK011(da)001:1527: snying rje skyes shing chos nyid kyi klong du gyur
NK011(da)001:1529: phur bu'i mtshan dang ldan pa gcig rnyed na thebs te 'ong gsungs /
NK011(da)001:1530: der tshol du phyin pas dus de tsam na mgar ba la sog po zer bas /
NK011(da)001:1531: sog po chen po gcig gis sha gcig dang shing khur gcig khur /
NK011(da)001:1534: bdag gi rus ni khang lags /
NK011(da)001:1535: ming ni stag spyan lags zer /
NK011(da)001:1536: phyi bzhin du 'brang ste phyin pas /
NK011(da)001:1538: der khab nag brdungs gnyis mid pas /
NK011(da)001:1540: khyod kyis chos nus sam gsungs pas bka' bstsal na rngo thogs lags zer /
NK011(da)001:1541: nang par ban+de gzhan gcig mgar tshang du byung ba
NK011(da)001:1542: la skam pas khab tsag brgyab pas a tsha zer
NK011(da)001:1543: / mdang dgongs kyi ben+de des ni /
NK011(da)001:1545: khyod a tsha zer ba ci nyes zer rgod de /
NK011(da)001:1546: bar der chung ma la rngan pa byin nas khyo la gros thob cig byas /
NK011(da)001:1547: de nas kho la bya'am bgyis pas /
NK011(da)001:1548: chung ma la 'adri'o zer dris pas /
NK011(da)001:1550: chos mi bya ba'i tsug ga na 'ong /
NK011(da)001:1551: chos ni dmar srang khri tshos kyang mi khugs zer /
NK011(da)001:1552: der chos sgor zhugs pa la /
NK011(da)001:1553: yo byad med zer ba la /
NK011(da)001:1554: yo byad slob dpon gyis phyung nas chos byin pas /
NK011(da)001:1555: kho dad pa mchog tu skyes te rab tu byung /
NK011(da)001:1556: ming lha dpal gyi ye shes su btags /
NK011(da)001:1557: 'di phur bu'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa ni /
NK011(da)001:1560: mgo bo rgya mdud du 'dril ba /
NK011(da)001:1562: ro stod zur brgyad du 'dug pa /
NK011(da)001:1563: ro smad zur gsum du yod pa /
NK011(da)001:1564: ci la yang thogs pa med pa gcig rnyed /
NK011(da)001:1565: de dang mthun pa 'o bran dpal gyi gzhon nu la yang 'dug pas /
NK011(da)001:1566: sngar gyi slob ma yang yin pas gnyis ka khrid de 'ong ngo //
NK011(da)001:1567: de nas dpon slob gsum gyis bsgrub pa byas nas bsgral /
NK011(da)001:1568: slar yang sog po dpal yes gnyags dge la ston gyi gam du song nas /
NK011(da)001:1569: kho shi 'dug pa'i snying bton nas slob dpon la phul ste /
NK011(da)001:1570: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK011(da)001:1571: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK011(da)001:1572: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul //
NK011(da)001:1573: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:1574: kun kyang gnod pa rnams dang bral //
NK011(da)001:1575: zhes ched du brjod de gnas spar /
NK011(da)001:1576: gnyags lha bya rmangs lcags kyi bya khra gcig tu byas te byung ba yang bsgral /
NK011(da)001:1577: bla spyang rab 'bring tha ma gsum ka la btab ste bskams /
NK011(da)001:1578: bran dang 'og rta sgo khyi gnag gi gnyen mtshams tshun chad bsgral te /
NK011(da)001:1579: dam srid rnam pa gcig der btul lo //
NK011(da)001:1580: de nas 'bro sras chung ne'u thang na rta khyu 'tsho ba las /
NK011(da)001:1581: rnam shes lid+ga la bkug nas phur pa btab ste bsgral /
NK011(da)001:1582: 'bro'i lha spyang ki sngon po gcig tu byas te byung ba yang bsgral /
NK011(da)001:1583: bla spyang rab 'bring tha ma gsum la btab pas bskams /
NK011(da)001:1584: bran dang 'og rta sgo khyi gnag gi gnyen mtshams yan chad la btab nas bsgral te /
NK011(da)001:1585: dam sri rnam pa gcig der btul lo //
NK011(da)001:1586: tshul 'di la lo rgyus la lar /
NK011(da)001:1587: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra la dgra rnam gsum langs pa'i dus su /
NK011(da)001:1588: 'o bran dpal gyi gzhon nus dkor nor dang zhing yul la sogs pa phul /
NK011(da)001:1589: brtul zhugs dang dpal rtsal gyis slob dpon gyi thugs bzung /
NK011(da)001:1590: yab mched po gnyags dge la ston dang gnyags 'phags pa smyug zhu can gnyis kyis /
NK011(da)001:1591: gcen gshes gnyen lha mtsho btson du bzung nas /
NK011(da)001:1592: btson bsrung mi gnyis bzhag pa la /
NK011(da)001:1593: 'o bran gyis brkus nas slob dpon la phul bas mnyes te phur pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1594: gsham sngon can gnyis gnang ba yin zer /
NK011(da)001:1597: btson du bzung ba ni yul nye 'khor gyi mda' dmar zhes par /
NK011(da)001:1598: dmar dang pha spun mi sha chags pa la /
NK011(da)001:1599: chos rgyal bzhugs pas gnyags la rtsod ma nus pa
NK011(da)001:1600: las phyis btsun mos sras dang lo ts+aa ba rnams
NK011(da)001:1602: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra nyid btson du bzung ba /
NK011(da)001:1603: sog po dpal yes srog la ma bltas pas brtson
NK011(da)001:1604: bsrung mi gnyis bkum nas slob dpon brtson nas bton
NK011(da)001:1605: pa yin pas / gcen lha mtsho btson du bcug pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1606: 'don pa po'o bran dpal gyi gzhon nu yin zhes pa nor ba yin la /
NK011(da)001:1607: phur pa phun sum tshogs pa gsham sngon dang bcas
NK011(da)001:1608: pa'i chos skor kyang 'o bran kho na la yod
NK011(da)001:1609: pa las / gzhan la ma grags pa ma yin te /
NK011(da)001:1610: gnyags la dpal gyi slob ma brgyad byung ba'i brgyad
NK011(da)001:1611: ka la yod par phur pa'i lo rgyus kyi yi
NK011(da)001:1612: ge rnying pa dag na gsal lo //
NK011(da)001:1613: dpal gyi slob ma brgyad ni /
NK011(da)001:1616: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug /
NK011(da)001:1617: thag bzang dpal gyi rdo rje /
NK011(da)001:1619: zla lcog dpal gyi seng ge /
NK011(da)001:1620: dar rje dpal gyi grags pa /
NK011(da)001:1621: lha lung dpal gyi rdo rje rnams yin no //
NK011(da)001:1624: mnga' ris su mched pa grangs las 'das pa byung bar bshad /
NK011(da)001:1625: de tsho'i nang nas 'brog mi ral pa can gyis
NK011(da)001:1626: sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che rten dge slong
NK011(da)001:1627: la brgyud pas phrin las che bar grags shing /
NK011(da)001:1628: 'di dag ni slob brgyud shas che'o //
NK011(da)001:1629: gdung brgyud kyis dar rgyas byung ba yang mang ngo //
NK011(da)001:1630: de dag tu ma 'dus pa'i mchog gi slob ma ni /
NK011(da)001:1633: gnyags kyi dbon brgyud rnams yin te phrin las rgya che zhing rgyun mi chad pa byung zhing /
NK011(da)001:1634: khyad par grub thob zam ma chad par byon no //
NK011(da)001:1635: de dag las lung rgyun dbang dang 'brel ba ma chad tsam bdag gis rnyed pa ni /
NK011(da)001:1636: 'o bran dpal gyi gzhon nu sku 'das nas zla ba lnga drug nas /
NK011(da)001:1639: yab mes kyi phyag dpe rnams gzigs pas dad de /
NK011(da)001:1640: lung rgyun rtsad bcad pas ring mo zhig lon pa na /
NK011(da)001:1641: gye re gnyan rtse'i ri khrod na gnubs ston pad+ma dbang rgyal la bzhugs zer /
NK011(da)001:1643: gser srang bco brgyad kyis sna drangs pa'i 'bul ba
NK011(da)001:1644: mang po byas nas lo gnyis la rdzogs par zhus
NK011(da)001:1646: gser gyi 'bul ba med par mi ster bas /
NK011(da)001:1647: 'o bran gyi phur pa gser mgo can du grags shing /
NK011(da)001:1648: gzhan yang gshin rje'i gshed mtheb rgya can gyi skor dang /
NK011(da)001:1649: mdo sgyu sems gsum la sogs pa gnubs pa las brgyud par 'dod do //
NK011(da)001:1650: de nas sras blo gros dbang phyug gis rang gi yab 'o bran pad 'byung la yang gsan /
NK011(da)001:1651: chos 'phro cung zad ma rdzogs pa la yab gshegs
NK011(da)001:1652: pas gnubs kyi slob ma gnyags pad 'byung gi sras
NK011(da)001:1653: / gnyags pad+ma rgyal po la rdzogs par gsan te brgyud pa gnyis ldan du byed do //
NK011(da)001:1654: de nas sprul sku ri rab dam pa'i bar du 'o bran gyi gdung brgyud rnams la brgyud cing /
NK011(da)001:1655: ri rab dam pas rin po che don grub dpal 'byor ba la gnang /
NK011(da)001:1656: de nas rim par brgyud de /
NK011(da)001:1657: yongs 'dzin dam pa rdo rje seng ges bdag la
NK011(da)001:1658: phur pa phun sum tshogs pa gsham sngon dang bcas
NK011(da)001:1659: pa thugs brtse bas gnang ngo //
NK011(da)001:1660: de nas phur pa gzhan la ma grags pa jo
NK011(da)001:1661: bo lang lab kyi khyad chos ji ltar byung ba
NK011(da)001:1662: ni / lang lab kyi bla ma ngam 'bre sa le yan chad ni gong du bstan zin la /
NK011(da)001:1663: jo bo lang lab ni sku gzhon nu nas pha ma grongs /
NK011(da)001:1664: pha spun rnams kyis pha ma'i kha chems la ma nyan te /
NK011(da)001:1665: lang lab ma bu la khang pa smig gu gang dang zhing chung gcig las ma byin pas /
NK011(da)001:1666: ngam 'bre sa le'i thugs kyis ma bzod de /
NK011(da)001:1667: khyad par 'phags pa phur pa'i gdams pa 'di gnang ste /
NK011(da)001:1668: lang lab kyis sgrub pa byas te dgra thams cad tshar bcad /
NK011(da)001:1669: snyan grags kyi phyogs kun tu khyab kyang sbyin 'bras chung bas phongs te /
NK011(da)001:1670: 'khor re na lug rdzi byed cing yod tsa na /
NK011(da)001:1671: de dus dge bshes rwa lo ts+aa ba rdo rje grags sku bsod dang /
NK011(da)001:1672: mthu che bas bod kyi mi che dgu dang /
NK011(da)001:1673: bla ma slob dpon dge ba'i bshes gnyen thams cad
NK011(da)001:1674: kyis phyag dang zhe sa bkur sti 'bul dgos pa
NK011(da)001:1675: yin la / gal te ma byas na gshin rje'i
NK011(da)001:1676: gshed kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis skad cig la sgrol
NK011(da)001:1677: yin la / ba yin te / khong la zhe
NK011(da)001:1678: sa ma byas pas mar pa'i sras dar ma mdo
NK011(da)001:1679: sde la sogs pa sa thob pa'i byang chub sems
NK011(da)001:1681: gnyan lo ts+aa ba dar ma grags la sogs par
NK011(da)001:1682: rang mnyam gyi lo ts+aa ba bcu gsum la sogs
NK011(da)001:1683: pa mang po bsgral ba yin cing /
NK011(da)001:1684: khong de tsa na grwa pa khri tshos bskor te 'khor re ru chos 'khor la byon /
NK011(da)001:1685: 'khor re btsad po la sogs pas chos gzhis zla ba bzhi btegs /
NK011(da)001:1686: de dus rwa lo ts+aa ba la lang lab kyi phyag ma btsal ba la /
NK011(da)001:1687: mi blun pa gcig yin 'ong dgongs pa las /
NK011(da)001:1688: slar mi rnams kyis khong sku mthu che zhing phur pa la mkhas pa yin kyang /
NK011(da)001:1689: sku bsod chung bas da lta gzhan gyi lug rdzi byed dgos pa lags byas pas /
NK011(da)001:1690: 'o na kho nga rgyal gyis khong sbos nas nga la phyag mi byed pa yin 'ong ste /
NK011(da)001:1691: kho la do nub kyi tshe las med kyi sgur sdod cig gsungs /
NK011(da)001:1693: rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi gsod pa'i sbyor ba bzhi'i bca' gzhi mdzad de /
NK011(da)001:1694: khyad par sbyin sreg gi skabs su rwa lo ts+aa
NK011(da)001:1695: ba nyid rdo rje 'jigs byed dngos kyi skur gyur
NK011(da)001:1696: nas / lid+ga la lang lab dgug gzhug gi bden brdar lan gsum byas te /
NK011(da)001:1697: dus der lang lab ni lug 'tsho ba nyid las gzhan ci yang mi byed mod kyi /
NK011(da)001:1698: dgug 'dren dang po'i dus der dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor na gnas pa'i rtsang phur rnams phyung ste /
NK011(da)001:1699: char du babs nas tho phyi'i grwa pa rnams smas /
NK011(da)001:1700: bar pa la za gsod dang khro bo bcu'i lcags
NK011(da)001:1701: phur gyi char babs nas 'khor rnams khyim kyi phug
NK011(da)001:1703: tha ma'i tshe nam mkha'i khams me dpung dang 'ur sgras gang ste /
NK011(da)001:1704: der steng du bltas pa na /
NK011(da)001:1705: rdo rje gzhon nu ri dil chad pa tsam lcags bsregs las grub pa /
NK011(da)001:1706: stod khro bo smad phur pa /
NK011(da)001:1707: thugs ka na phur pa drag tu bsgril zhing /
NK011(da)001:1708: h'u phata kyi sgra sgrog pa gcig rwa lo ts+aa ba'i thog tu 'bab la khad /
NK011(da)001:1709: za za rngam rngam 'cha' 'cha' ltar du 'dug pas rab tu skrag ste /
NK011(da)001:1710: de nyid du bzod par gsol /
NK011(da)001:1711: lang lab la gus 'dud byed par dam bcas pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1713: de nas de'i nub lang lab spyan drangs te /
NK011(da)001:1714: phyag dang zhe sa bsnyen bkur ba dang /
NK011(da)001:1716: dus der mi rnams na re /
NK011(da)001:1717: gshin rje mkhan po phur pa la rdugs /
NK011(da)001:1718: zhes pa'i gtam yang rgya cher grags skad /
NK011(da)001:1719: de lta bu'i slob dpon lang lab 'di bas lhag
NK011(da)001:1720: pa'i phur pa'i grub thob ni bod yul 'dir su
NK011(da)001:1722: slob ma yang kha yar byung zhing /
NK011(da)001:1723: mchog tu gyur pa ni bzhi yin te /
NK011(da)001:1724: 'khor re brgyal thang gi sna nam shes rab tshul khrims /
NK011(da)001:1726: rong gi sprangs phur bu mgo /
NK011(da)001:1727: 'o yug rol po'i nyang nag dbang gi shes rab dang bzhi'o //
NK011(da)001:1729: dbang dang gdams ngag med zer ba yang chags sdang gi gtam yin gyi /
NK011(da)001:1731: de ltar byin rlabs dang cho 'phrul phun sum tshogs
NK011(da)001:1732: pa phur pa'i chos 'di la dang po nyid nas
NK011(da)001:1733: / bdag cag gi bla ma'i bar du byin rlabs
NK011(da)001:1734: kyi rtags mtshan zam ma chad par byung ba yin
NK011(da)001:1735: / te / de yang slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas
NK011(da)001:1736: kyis rgya gar du tsan+dana gyi nags tshal la me
NK011(da)001:1737: / te / shor te / zhag mang por me ma shi nas nags tshal kun zad du nye /
NK011(da)001:1738: sems can mang po shi zhing la la shi la khad pa la /
NK011(da)001:1739: seng ldeng gi phur pa sor brgyad pa gcig btab pas /
NK011(da)001:1740: me shi ste nags tshal sngar las phun sum tshogs pa skyes /
NK011(da)001:1741: sems can shi ba dang shi la khad pa rnams gsos /
NK011(da)001:1742: tsan+dana nags la thebs zer yang /
NK011(da)001:1743: 'byung ba me la thebs pa yin /
NK011(da)001:1744: slob dpon 'di'i dben sa ni bal yul yang le shod kyi brag phug /
NK011(da)001:1745: slob dpon gyi gsang mtshan ni bde ba'i myu gu'o //
NK011(da)001:1746: slob dpon bi ma la mi tras chu bo gad+g+aa la thebs te /
NK011(da)001:1747: slob dpon gyis chu bo gang+ga'i 'gram du sgrub pa
NK011(da)001:1748: mdzad pas de'i sngags kyi zer phyogs de'i klu chen
NK011(da)001:1749: po gcig gis ma bzod nas phyi'i rgya mtsho chen
NK011(da)001:1751: slob dpon la skyin thang drag po phab /
NK011(da)001:1752: chu bo gad+g+aa lud de lung par mi shong bar byas byung ba las /
NK011(da)001:1753: slob dpon gyis phur pa sor brgyad pa gcig btab pas /
NK011(da)001:1754: gad+g+aa yar mar du chad de bar du lam dod de phyin chog pa byung /
NK011(da)001:1755: 'di ni gad+g+aa la btab zer yang /
NK011(da)001:1758: bal bo sh+ai la many+dzusa man+da la'i mkhar gong la thebs te /
NK011(da)001:1759: man+da la'i mkhar gong la brag srin mo gdug pa
NK011(da)001:1760: can cig gnas pa des slob dpon gyi dgongs pa
NK011(da)001:1761: la bar chod brtsams pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1762: phur pa bsgril bas man+da la'i mkhar gong gi brag nas tsam sran tsam du nyil lo //
NK011(da)001:1763: 'di ni brag mkhar gong la thebs zer te /
NK011(da)001:1764: brag srin mo la thebs pa'o //
NK011(da)001:1765: lo rgyus gzhan dag na ni /
NK011(da)001:1766: rgya gar du phyi nang gnyis ma 'cham pa na rgyal pos /
NK011(da)001:1767: zhag gsum na rtsod pa gyis shig /
NK011(da)001:1768: su rgyal ba dang rdzu 'phrul su che ba de'i zhabs nas 'degs so zer /
NK011(da)001:1769: der rtsod pa'i dus su slob dpon gyis /
NK011(da)001:1770: brjod rgyu thams cad tha snyad mtha' la gnas //
NK011(da)001:1771: don ma mthong bar grol bar ga la 'gyur //
NK011(da)001:1772: mu stegs 'chal ba'i gtam gyis ci zhig bya //
NK011(da)001:1773: chos kyi rgyal mtshan chen po 'dzugs par bya //
NK011(da)001:1774: zhes gsungs nas phur pa bsgril bas /
NK011(da)001:1775: man+da la zhes bya ba'i grong khyer chen po gcig
NK011(da)001:1776: gi rgyab na mkhar gong gi brag chen po gcig
NK011(da)001:1777: yod pa las / brag de nyil te mu stegs kyi grong khyer thams cad bcom /
NK011(da)001:1778: mu stegs rnams la la khrag skyugs te shi /
NK011(da)001:1780: la la mig 'bras brul nas thams cad tshar bcad de /
NK011(da)001:1781: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i bstan pa dar bar byas so //
NK011(da)001:1782: mkhas gang mthu yis bcad ces grags //
NK011(da)001:1784: bod yul du byung ba ni /
NK011(da)001:1785: jo mo mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal gyis dben pa'o yug mkhar ba sna ru mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK011(da)001:1786: byang phyogs kyi bye ma spyang ki 'dra ba la thebs /
NK011(da)001:1787: de yang byang phyogs nas yar ldong stong gi tshong pa mang po yong ba las /
NK011(da)001:1788: tshong dpon nam tshong lha rgyal po shel ging gis byed ba las /
NK011(da)001:1790: byang spyang bcu bzhis rta bong rnams nyal gsod /
NK011(da)001:1791: tha ma mi la za ru byung ba las tshong pas lha 'dre'i rdzur yin par shes te /
NK011(da)001:1792: yul na byin rlabs che ba su yod dris pas /
NK011(da)001:1793: mkhar ba sna na jo mo bzhugs zer te /
NK011(da)001:1794: der jo mo'i drung du phyin nas zhus pas /
NK011(da)001:1795: jo mos de rnams bstan pa mchod pa'i sbyin bdag yin par mkhyen nas /
NK011(da)001:1796: spyang ki rnams kyi rjes sa khyer shog gsungs pas /
NK011(da)001:1797: bye ma la rjes sa 'dug pa blangs te phul bas /
NK011(da)001:1799: bag phye la gzugs bcu bzhi byas nas phur pa btab pas /
NK011(da)001:1800: spyang ki bcu bzhi po dngos su mkhar ba sna'i
NK011(da)001:1801: gnya' na mar la hril li li 'gril nas lhung
NK011(da)001:1802: byung / spyang ki la thebs zer yang /
NK011(da)001:1803: rgyal po shel ging la thebs so //
NK011(da)001:1806: 'di'i slob ma mi nub rgyal ba'i snying po yin te /
NK011(da)001:1807: 'dis jo mo la dkor nor sna re la /
NK011(da)001:1808: nor sna khri tsho re ri ba bdun phul /
NK011(da)001:1809: dar gyi dge tsho'i steng nas jo mos bshad /
NK011(da)001:1810: mthing shog la gser gyis bris te glegs bam du byas /
NK011(da)001:1811: dben sa gar zha mkha' 'gro'i gling /
NK011(da)001:1815: de yang phreng ba na baza'i khar bzhag ste dbu skra bsil bas /
NK011(da)001:1816: bya rog gis phreng ba khyer ba la brtags pas
NK011(da)001:1817: bya rog bdud nag po bkrag med kyi sprul pas
NK011(da)001:1818: bar chod byed par mkhyen nas /
NK011(da)001:1819: bya rog gi grib ma la phur pa btab pas /
NK011(da)001:1820: bya rog sa la lhung nas shi'o //
NK011(da)001:1821: bya rog la thebs zer yang /
NK011(da)001:1823: de'i slob ma lo dpal gyi blo gros yin te /
NK011(da)001:1824: dben sa spa gro stag tshang sed+ge phug /
NK011(da)001:1825: gsang mtshan rdo rje grags pa rtsal /
NK011(da)001:1827: de yang slob dpon mon na bzhugs dus dmag gis dgon pa bshig /
NK011(da)001:1829: de nas dgongs rgyud rtsa 'grel tsho bsnams te spa gro stag tshang du byon /
NK011(da)001:1830: bsnyen pa byas pas rdo rje gzhon nu zhal gzigs /
NK011(da)001:1831: lho'i rba'i khyim la dmigs phur ba btab pas /
NK011(da)001:1832: dngos su rba'i khyim la phur pa gcur gcur byung
NK011(da)001:1833: nas mon pa rnams kyi snying la phur pa re
NK011(da)001:1834: thar thar zug nas kun bsgral lo //
NK011(da)001:1835: lho'i rba khyim la thebs zer yang /
NK011(da)001:1837: de'i slob ma ngam 'bre klu'i rgyal mtshan /
NK011(da)001:1838: dben sa nyang stod srin mo ri'i co to /
NK011(da)001:1839: gsang mtshan bdud 'dul grags pa rtsal /
NK011(da)001:1840: dgra la btab pas bgegs la thebs /
NK011(da)001:1841: yang slob dpon 'dis phur pa grub pas dgra bgegs gnyis la ngang ngam shugs kyi thebs /
NK011(da)001:1842: nyon mongs dug lnga la thebs te lta sgom phul du phyin /
NK011(da)001:1843: bar chod dgra bgegs thams cad bsgral nas dgung lo dgu bcu rtsa dgu la sku 'das te /
NK011(da)001:1844: pur sbyangs pas gdung rus ci yang ma byung ste /
NK011(da)001:1845: rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku zhal gsum phyag drug pa mkhyud gang ba gcig dang /
NK011(da)001:1846: k+ai la ya 'bur dod cig phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin thob pa'i rtags su byung ngo //
NK011(da)001:1847: de'i sras ngam 'bre sa le shes rab dbang phyug ste /
NK011(da)001:1848: 'dis bla ma la 'bul ba chen po byas te /
NK011(da)001:1849: rma gtsang gi gtsang 'gram du zhus /
NK011(da)001:1850: dben sa gong ma dang gcig la /
NK011(da)001:1851: gsang mtshan bgegs rigs 'joms pa rtsal /
NK011(da)001:1853: de yang srin mo ril sgrub pa la bzhugs dus /
NK011(da)001:1854: nub gcig 'od chen po cig byung /
NK011(da)001:1855: 'od de la phur pa btab pas /
NK011(da)001:1856: tho rang mi dkar po gcig byung ba na re /
NK011(da)001:1857: slob dpon gyi bka' 'khor la ngas gnod pa mi byed kyi /
NK011(da)001:1859: der kho la mna' bsgag nas phur pa bton no //
NK011(da)001:1862: bla ma 'di nam mkha' la 'gro ba dang /
NK011(da)001:1863: chu la mi bying ba la sogs pa dngos grub du ma la dbang 'byor ba yin no //
NK011(da)001:1864: 'di'i slob ma lang lab byang chub rdo rje yin te /
NK011(da)001:1865: rma chu rab kyi pha rol skyi chu rab kyi tshu rol bye ma yug mor zhus /
NK011(da)001:1866: phyis gser srang brgyad las byas pa'i 'jam dpal gyi sku gcig phul /
NK011(da)001:1867: des sna drangs te nor sna bdun phul /
NK011(da)001:1868: lang lab kyi dben sa 'khor re'i rdo rje rtse 'dus /
NK011(da)001:1869: gsang mtshan phrin las mthar phyin rtsal /
NK011(da)001:1870: 'dis spyir dgra bgegs kun la thebs /
NK011(da)001:1871: khyad par rkun ma la thebs te /
NK011(da)001:1872: lang lab kyi nor rku la shor ba las /
NK011(da)001:1873: rku ma'i rjes la phur pa btab pas /
NK011(da)001:1874: 'bri grags po bya ba zhag gsum na shi ste /
NK011(da)001:1875: shul mi rnams kyis nor bskyal lo //
NK011(da)001:1876: slob dpon 'di'i sgrub pa mdzad pa la phur pa rnams 'phar ba dang /
NK011(da)001:1879: du ba la sogs pa byung /
NK011(da)001:1880: lcags phur cig brag gi ngos la btab pa la
NK011(da)001:1881: phyugs rdzi dang shing 'thu ba dag gi lag pa
NK011(da)001:1882: 'jus te spyan drangs la dbyug pa sogs rtsed mo
NK011(da)001:1884: 'di yan chod du phur pa chig brgyud yin no //
NK011(da)001:1885: 'di las gong du bstan pa dar ba'i slob ma mang du byung la /
NK011(da)001:1887: sna nam tshul gyis thugs zin pas /
NK011(da)001:1888: phrin las dang lag len man ngag tu dril nas gnang /
NK011(da)001:1889: rgyud 'grel che ba rnams ma gnang la /
NK011(da)001:1890: rtsa ba'i rgyud rdo rje khros pa'i dum bu gnang /
NK011(da)001:1891: 'di rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma yin zer /
NK011(da)001:1892: man ngag phrin las bzhi'i don 'di la gnang ba rnams shin tu zab par byed do //
NK011(da)001:1894: yul mi rnams kyis nor phyugs khang zhing thams cad phrogs pa la brten nas /
NK011(da)001:1895: lang lab kyi rtsar byon nas gdams pa zhus pas zla ba dgu lha bsnyen gyis la /
NK011(da)001:1896: de nas bswe lcags shel gsum la zla ba gnyis sgrubs shig /
NK011(da)001:1898: de ltar bsgrubs pas lus drod tshad du phyin /
NK011(da)001:1899: de nas gyang gi drung na mi mang po nyi
NK011(da)001:1900: ma la 'de zhing 'dug pas thams cad dgra ru
NK011(da)001:1902: gong khug nas phur pa phyungs te /
NK011(da)001:1904: gyang 'gyel ba'i thibs 'og tu mi kun shi bas skyi nag gyang 'gyel du grags /
NK011(da)001:1907: 'di shes rab che bas rgyud 'grel man ngag thams cad gnang ngo //
NK011(da)001:1908: sprangs phur bu mgo ni sngar nas phur pa mang po shes /
NK011(da)001:1910: 'di kun kha mthun par jo mo mkhar chen baza'i
NK011(da)001:1911: thugs dam gyi phur pa jo bo lang lab la
NK011(da)001:1912: yod zer bas / nas bong khal drug /
NK011(da)001:1915: chang rkyal pa gang rnams khyer te 'khor rer 'ongs /
NK011(da)001:1916: der lang lab bza' mi gnyis la sras ni mi mnga' /
NK011(da)001:1917: nor rdzas srab mo las med pas /
NK011(da)001:1918: khang pa'i sgo glegs dang shing cha btsongs nas za ba las /
NK011(da)001:1919: sprangs phur bu mgo bong khal ded nas phyi sgo
NK011(da)001:1920: med pas khang pa'i nang du tsangs kyis byung ba
NK011(da)001:1921: dang / lang lab kyis jo bo sngags pa 'di
NK011(da)001:1922: mgron khang ma lags sgo nor ba ma yin nam
NK011(da)001:1924: ma lags 'di khar chos kyi bka' drin zhur mchis lags /
NK011(da)001:1927: gtam mthun sbyor mang po btang /
NK011(da)001:1931: phur pa jo mo lugs zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK011(da)001:1932: da 'o na zla ba phyed nas shes par bya gsungs nas gnang ste /
NK011(da)001:1933: dpa' bo gcig par sgrub pa'i don zab tu gnang ngo //
NK011(da)001:1934: de nas sprangs kyis rong du slob ma mang du bsdus /
NK011(da)001:1935: khong rang gis phur pa phyi rgyud mang po shes pas /
NK011(da)001:1936: de tsho nas btus kyin sgrub thabs mang du brtsams /
NK011(da)001:1937: 'di jo mo mkhar chen baza'i thugs dam yin /
NK011(da)001:1938: lang lab byang chub rdo rje'i phyag nas 'ongs zer zhing /
NK011(da)001:1939: slob ma rnams la so sor mi 'dra ba mang po bstan pas /
NK011(da)001:1940: phur pa rtsa dum gyi chos skor 'cha' mgo zug /
NK011(da)001:1941: so sor mi 'dra ba mang bas sprangs kyi slob
NK011(da)001:1942: ma rnams kyang nga'i 'di jo mo lugs yin zer
NK011(da)001:1943: zhing / gcig la gcig mi mgu /
NK011(da)001:1944: da ltar jo mo lugs kyi sgrub thabs mi 'dra ba mang po byung ba yang de yin /
NK011(da)001:1946: bdag gis ni sprangs kyis byas pa'i yig cha ma
NK011(da)001:1947: mthong bas 'thad mi 'thad spro bar mi nus so
NK011(da)001:1948: // da ni slob ma bzhi pa nyang nag dbang
NK011(da)001:1949: gi shes rab kyi lo rgyus brjod par bya ste
NK011(da)001:1950: // / de yang lang lab yab yum gnyis zas nor gyis phongs par yod pa la /
NK011(da)001:1951: nyang nag gis 'o yug rol po gong mar spyan drangs nas zhabs tog byas /
NK011(da)001:1952: der lo gsum song ba dang /
NK011(da)001:1953: jo mo de khar bzhag nas slob dpon sdong kha
NK011(da)001:1954: smad na mar rnyed pa tshol bar byon nas zla
NK011(da)001:1955: ba dgu'i bar du ma byon /
NK011(da)001:1956: der jo mo skyo zhing yid chad nas /
NK011(da)001:1957: nang ma gcig jo mos nyang nag bos nas slob
NK011(da)001:1958: dpon 'di bas snying thag ring bar ma byung gi
NK011(da)001:1959: / khyed rang chos 'dod na ngas sbyin no zer /
NK011(da)001:1960: 'o na da bdag dga' byas pas /
NK011(da)001:1961: 'o na sgro ba nag po kha phyes shig zer nas /
NK011(da)001:1962: slob dpon lang lab kyi la rgya yod pa bcag nas kha phyes /
NK011(da)001:1963: dbang ma thob pa la dgongs rgyud bris pas /
NK011(da)001:1964: nyang nag la bkra mi shis pa byung ste /
NK011(da)001:1965: gnag phyug mang po la gnag nad byung ste phal cher shi /
NK011(da)001:1968: slob dpon gshegs pa'i phyogs kyi ri mtho sar phyin
NK011(da)001:1969: te gtor tshogs mang po bshams nas bshags pa byas
NK011(da)001:1970: / slob dpon spyan drangs nas nor rdzas kyi phyed 'bul bar byas pas /
NK011(da)001:1971: gnag nad dang bkra mi shis pa kun chad /
NK011(da)001:1972: slob dpon spyan 'dren pa btang ngo //
NK011(da)001:1973: der slob dpon byon pa dang /
NK011(da)001:1974: sngar jo mos gsungs pa la sogs pa'i lo rgyus bsnyad pas /
NK011(da)001:1975: slob dpon na re e he he lha'i khug mar srin gyi lag pa btsangs ang gsungs /
NK011(da)001:1976: der gong gi dam bcas pa'i nor rdzas tsho phul
NK011(da)001:1977: nas chos zhu 'tshal byas pas slob dpon na re
NK011(da)001:1978: / 'o na sngon la khyod pha spad dbang cig thob pa bya dgos gsungs nas /
NK011(da)001:1979: yab yum sras ga sum la chos kyi dbang rdzogs par bskur te /
NK011(da)001:1980: 'di ltar dbang phyi nang gsang gsum bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:1981: der sras che ba de snga bu yin pas yab dang ma yar sdang zhing dbang chung bar 'dug /
NK011(da)001:1982: bu chung ba ni gces phrug byed de de'i ming tshul le zer ba yin /
NK011(da)001:1983: che ba la gnang de zer ste 'di rig pa can sngags kyi snod dang ldan par gzigs nas /
NK011(da)001:1984: lang lab kyis ming spos nas /
NK011(da)001:1986: de nas slob dpon lang lab kyi zhal nas /
NK011(da)001:1987: nged rgas 'khogs gnyis kyis nor 'di tsho'i nya ra mi yong bar gda' yis /
NK011(da)001:1988: 'di tsho khyed rang yab sras mdzod la /
NK011(da)001:1989: nged bza' mi gnyis ma shi bar mi sdug pa cig zhu gsungs /
NK011(da)001:1990: der nyang nag dbang gi shes rab thugs ma bde ste /
NK011(da)001:1991: slob dpon khyad par can 'di la gdung brgyud gcig byung na bstan pa dang sems can la'ang phan /
NK011(da)001:1992: nga'i bu tsha brgyud rnams kyis phyag mchod pa 'bul sa gcig kyang dgos par 'dug snyam nas /
NK011(da)001:1993: jo mo bsgres mo lo lnga bcu nga brgyad lon pa de la rgyu mtshan smras te /
NK011(da)001:1994: nga la bsam mno 'di 'dra zhig bdog /
NK011(da)001:1995: nor rdzas 'di tsho'i bdag po gcig dgos par gda'
NK011(da)001:1996: bas jo mo gcig blangs na rung ngam byas pas
NK011(da)001:1997: / jo mos de shin tu legs so gsungs /
NK011(da)001:1998: de nas slob dpon la zhus pas mi byed gsungs /
NK011(da)001:1999: der gong gi rgyu mtshan tsho zhib tu brjod de /
NK011(da)001:2000: jo mos ni gnang lags byas pas /
NK011(da)001:2001: rgan mo la mi dga' ba mi 'dug gam gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2002: jo mo dgos pa gda' lags zhus pas /
NK011(da)001:2004: der rus 'o phya bza' yin pa'i bu mo gcig
NK011(da)001:2005: blangs nas jo bo la phul bas sras gnyis byung
NK011(da)001:2006: ste / che ba la grags chung zer /
NK011(da)001:2007: nu bo la grags pa dbang phyug tu btags /
NK011(da)001:2008: de tsa na nyang nag dbang gi shes rab kyis chos thams cad khong du chud /
NK011(da)001:2009: bla ma yab yum gyi zhabs tog kyang 'di nyid kho na bzang ba yin no //
NK011(da)001:2010: de nas skabs shig tu nyang nag gis shog bu mang po sbyar nas yod pa la /
NK011(da)001:2013: rgyud 'grel zhal bshu ba lags byas pas /
NK011(da)001:2015: bdag ni nyi ma rgas kha 'dra /
NK011(da)001:2016: chos kyi bdag po nyid lags kyi /
NK011(da)001:2017: bla dpe zhal ma bshu bar tshags mdzod cig gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2018: bla dpe sras gnyis la dgos mod byas pas /
NK011(da)001:2019: byis pa gnyis gsang sngags kyi snod du rung zhing mthar phyin pa'i nges pa med /
NK011(da)001:2020: de ltar byung na de dus su gdams pa byin pas chog mod gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2021: bla dpe po ti bswe glegs can bya ba /
NK011(da)001:2022: dgongs rgyud kyi glegs shing la bswe'i lha mo bzhi bris pa'i pu sti gnang ngo //
NK011(da)001:2024: nyang ro 'khor re ru lang lab byang chub rdo rje rabs chad /
NK011(da)001:2025: 'o yug phu ru sras gnyis skyes /
NK011(da)001:2027: phyis sras gnyis po chos par ma song /
NK011(da)001:2028: phyug po chen po gnyis byung /
NK011(da)001:2029: grags chung la bu gnyis las /
NK011(da)001:2030: che ba yon bdag ldong rtse /
NK011(da)001:2031: 'dis gsung rab mang po bzhengs so //
NK011(da)001:2033: jo mos la rgya bcag pa'i gtam 'di la brten te /
NK011(da)001:2037: nyang nag gis bka' brkus zer te /
NK011(da)001:2038: phyis nyang nag sras kyi thu bor gyur pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:2039: byin rlabs dang nus mthu yang phul du byung ba'i gtam rgyud mang la /
NK011(da)001:2040: dben sa ni 'o yug sgo mo'i snyam sa snyam gyi brag phug zer /
NK011(da)001:2041: rgyab snyam bzang gi brag phug tu'o //
NK011(da)001:2042: gsang mtshan rdo rje gshog rgod rtsal /
NK011(da)001:2043: snyam bzang phug par sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK011(da)001:2044: phur pa nam mkha' la lding nas 'od dang sgra dang bcas pa byung /
NK011(da)001:2045: dgra bgegs thams cad btul ba yin no //
NK011(da)001:2046: 'dis dgung lo brgyad cu rtsa lnga bzhes nas 'da' khar sras tshul le la zhal chems gsungs pa /
NK011(da)001:2047: sh+aakya rgyal mtshan gyis ni man ngag thams cad shes /
NK011(da)001:2048: khos dpe cha kun khyer 'ong ngo //
NK011(da)001:2049: 'og khang gi ka gzhu'i steng na po ti bswe glegs can yod de /
NK011(da)001:2050: bu rang tshags gyis la sbos shig gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2051: de 'og khang na sh+aakya rgyal mtshan yod pas tshor te /
NK011(da)001:2052: yi chad nas po ti bswe glegs can yod pa khyer nas bros phyin /
NK011(da)001:2053: snye phu'i gnas bya ba na yab kyi slob ma
NK011(da)001:2054: gnang h'u ka ra bya ba zhig yod pa de'i
NK011(da)001:2055: sar phyin te yab ni grongs su cha ba yod
NK011(da)001:2056: / tshul le la zhal chems gsungs pas yi chad pa'i tshul smras pas /
NK011(da)001:2057: gnang h'u ka ra ha las te slob dpon grongs su cha na /
NK011(da)001:2058: po ti khyer nas bros na dam tshig nyams nas 'gro bas nangs par rang re gnyis ka 'dong /
NK011(da)001:2059: chos nu bo la yang sbyin dgos zer /
NK011(da)001:2060: nangs par phyin tsa na yab grongs nas 'dug /
NK011(da)001:2061: der gnang h'u ka ras spun gnyis mthun par byas so //
NK011(da)001:2062: de nas dus re zhig na bshags pa mang po byas /
NK011(da)001:2063: tshogs kyi 'khor lo mang po bskor /
NK011(da)001:2064: de nas dben sa ru mched gnyis kyis bsnyen sgrub mdzad pas /
NK011(da)001:2065: rtags dang mtshan ma mang po ni byung /
NK011(da)001:2066: nub cig mar me mi gsal /
NK011(da)001:2067: sgra snyan mang po grags pa dang /
NK011(da)001:2068: sh+aakya rgyal mtshan spyan mi gsal bas /
NK011(da)001:2069: tshul le la mar me de 'chos dang gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2070: tshul les mar me 'chos par phyin pas /
NK011(da)001:2071: sgra snyan mang po thos shing /
NK011(da)001:2072: dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i lha phur tsho bro pa
NK011(da)001:2073: do rar zhugs pa bzhin cod pan zang zing 'khrab
NK011(da)001:2075: gcen la 'di ltar gda' byas pas /
NK011(da)001:2076: rung gsungs nas zangs nag chen po gcig bsnams nas /
NK011(da)001:2077: phyag tu rba mkhar dngul mgo bsnams nas sa la btsugs te /
NK011(da)001:2078: mched gnyis kyis bstod pa mdzad de dngos grub blangs so //
NK011(da)001:2080: slob dpon sh+aakya rgyal mtshan gyis tshong pa mang po'i dpon mdzad de ldong kha na phar byon pas /
NK011(da)001:2081: 'dar nag po'i rta pa nyi shu rtsa gcig gis tshong pa thams cad bcom /
NK011(da)001:2082: der rting ris gshegs nas gzigs pas nom pa bgo ba mthong nas ber sngon po de phud nas /
NK011(da)001:2083: lha bos klu bos nas brdabs pas /
NK011(da)001:2084: mi rgan gcig gdong du byung nas lung pa 'di'i sa gnyan rdo gnyan de tshugs ma byed zer /
NK011(da)001:2085: gnyan sa kho na 'dong mi rung ba kho na 'dong gsung /
NK011(da)001:2086: de'i nub mo mi nyal tsam pa'i dus tshod la ngu co dir ba gcig byung nas /
NK011(da)001:2088: nangs par nyan tsa na tshong dpon gyi bu'i mgo
NK011(da)001:2089: la slob dpon gyi rta yis 'phra rgyab ste shi
NK011(da)001:2091: der slob dpon 'khor bcas kyis nub mo bros nas phyin /
NK011(da)001:2092: phyi de lo dus na rta pa bcu dgu shi'o //
NK011(da)001:2093: gnyis kyis slob dpon can du 'ongs nas 'bangs byas so //
NK011(da)001:2094: der nyang nag ber sngon can zhes phyogs kun tu grags so //
NK011(da)001:2095: dben sa snyam snyam brag phug /
NK011(da)001:2096: gsang mtshan rdo rje gshog rgod rtsal /
NK011(da)001:2097: brdabs pa ber sngon po brdabs pas /
NK011(da)001:2098: thebs pa 'dar nag po la thebs so //
NK011(da)001:2099: 'di'i slob ma lhan gyi slob dpon drag po /
NK011(da)001:2100: dben sa lhan gyi stag lung grogs po /
NK011(da)001:2101: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde chen rtsal /
NK011(da)001:2102: thebs pa zhang po nyang nad la thebs /
NK011(da)001:2103: de yang gnubs yul rong gi sa'i cha 'grogs bya bar 'khrungs /
NK011(da)001:2104: mi rmang po nye ris med pa gcig yin /
NK011(da)001:2105: chung ngu la pha ma shi nas /
NK011(da)001:2106: zhang po nyang nad kyis ris ban+de 'phan po mang
NK011(da)001:2107: po yod pas de rnams kyi nor rdzas thams cad
NK011(da)001:2108: phrogs nas sprang du btang ngo //
NK011(da)001:2109: der slob dpon sh+aakya rgyal mtshan dang mjal /
NK011(da)001:2110: lo bco brgyad nas sum cu'i bar du bla ma'i gnag rdzi'u byas /
NK011(da)001:2111: bla mas gsang sngags kyi snod du rung bar gzigs /
NK011(da)001:2112: shes rab che bas phyugs skyong rin la man ngag thams cad gnang /
NK011(da)001:2113: phyag bzhes thams cad la mkhas pa'i phul du phyin /
NK011(da)001:2115: da ni ngas kyang lo brgyad cu gya lnga lon /
NK011(da)001:2118: der slob dpon drag po la yul na nor bag tsam yod pas der 'abri'am zhus pas /
NK011(da)001:2120: 'dir bu gnyis po phrag dog skyes pa srid do gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2121: der pu sti kun gnang nas yul du 'bri gin yod tsa na /
NK011(da)001:2122: slob dpon gyi sras che ba chos tshul bya ba byon nas /
NK011(da)001:2123: a pho drag po yab ni grongs nas med /
NK011(da)001:2124: po ti bswe glegs can yang mi 'dug /
NK011(da)001:2125: de su la 'dug pa gcig la mgo skyel pa la zer /
NK011(da)001:2126: slob dpon grongs pas mi dga' /
NK011(da)001:2128: pu sti bswe glegs can su la 'dug pa la
NK011(da)001:2129: mgo skyel zer bas yang dang yang du ma dga'
NK011(da)001:2130: / pu sti nga la yod zer ni ma phod /
NK011(da)001:2131: der bla dpe slob dpon drag po la lus so //
NK011(da)001:2132: de tsa na bla ma drag po'i zhang po nor
NK011(da)001:2133: 'phrog mi kun gyis slar yang 'di nyang nag ber
NK011(da)001:2134: sngon can gyi mthus bsnyems pa yin nam /
NK011(da)001:2135: khyod la zo zhig ci nus pa rems shig zer kha smras byed do //
NK011(da)001:2136: de nas slob dpon gyis lhan du byon te /
NK011(da)001:2137: bud med gcig la yul zhing bsten thub tsam cig 'dug pas /
NK011(da)001:2139: der lhan gyi stag lung grogs por dben sa byas
NK011(da)001:2140: te sgrub pa mdzad pas rtags mtshan mang du byung
NK011(da)001:2141: / zhang po dregs pa can de kun gyis bsdums byed du ma 'dod pa'i khar /
NK011(da)001:2142: zla ba gcig na slob dpon drag po mthus bkrongs kyis btang gis zer /
NK011(da)001:2143: g.yas ru gtsang po'i 'gram rtsa na brag phug yod
NK011(da)001:2144: pa der nyang nad ban+de bcu gsum zhugs nas mthu
NK011(da)001:2145: byed do // slob dpon gyis kyang stag lung grogs por drag las byas pas /
NK011(da)001:2146: de nas zla ba gsum na nyang nad ban+de bcu gsum po la glo tshad thebs nas kun shi'o //
NK011(da)001:2147: phyis 'grogs lung par ltad mo chen po gcig byung
NK011(da)001:2148: ba la slob dpon drag pos zang nag chen po
NK011(da)001:2149: zhig gyon / dre'u gcig la chibs /
NK011(da)001:2150: 'khor mang pos bskor te ltad mo la byon pas /
NK011(da)001:2151: zhang ne mo kun gyis sa gtor te /
NK011(da)001:2152: zhang mi rmang po ngan pa byung ngo zer zhing 'a tsi 'a tsi zer ba la /
NK011(da)001:2154: 'a tsi bya ba khyed rang yin mod /
NK011(da)001:2156: bar du bsdums mi byed par mthu byed /
NK011(da)001:2157: tha ma ban+de bcu gsum po srog dang bral nas phung /
NK011(da)001:2158: 'a tsi bya ba khyed rang tsho yin mod zer zhing ya ga bsgrags so //
NK011(da)001:2159: slob dpon drag po 'dis dgongs rgyud skor la mi mkhyen pa med cing /
NK011(da)001:2160: mthu dang sku bsod che bas dbus gtsang gi mkhas btsun thams cad kyis zhabs la gtugs so //
NK011(da)001:2161: 'di mar pa lo ts+aa dang dus mtshungs yin /
NK011(da)001:2162: de tsa na sna nam shes rab tshul khrims la
NK011(da)001:2163: sras gnyis yod pa'i che ba sna nam 'bre ban
NK011(da)001:2164: la sku dgra gcig byung nas /
NK011(da)001:2165: dgra de dag gi mthu bzlog pa la gnubs zam
NK011(da)001:2166: nag stong pa'i jo bo stag ram spyan drangs so
NK011(da)001:2167: // lan gcig sna nam 'bre ban dang /
NK011(da)001:2168: gnubs stag ram zam kha gcig tu mjal ba dang /
NK011(da)001:2169: sna nam gyis jo bo stag ram la phyag byas
NK011(da)001:2170: te dge bshes pa mi 'di pas bdag la mi
NK011(da)001:2171: 'tshams pa'i las mang po bgyis pas /
NK011(da)001:2172: thugs dam la dgongs la 'di pa'i bsrung ba mi mdzad par zhu byas pas /
NK011(da)001:2173: gnubs stag ram gyi zhal nas /
NK011(da)001:2174: lang lab byang chub rdo rje'i phur thung res sbos pa /
NK011(da)001:2177: sna nam khros nas gos brdabs /
NK011(da)001:2178: ngas ma nyes ma yo byas so //
NK011(da)001:2180: gnyis ka phug tu zhugs pas /
NK011(da)001:2181: zla ba gsum na gnubs stag ram khrag skyugs te shi'o //
NK011(da)001:2182: gshin rje mkhan po phur pa la rdugs /
NK011(da)001:2183: bya ba dus der yang grags la /
NK011(da)001:2184: der sna nam gyis chang mang po btsos te /
NK011(da)001:2185: nyang ro'i ban+de phur pa shes tshad spyan drangs te tshogs 'khor byas so //
NK011(da)001:2188: rdo rje gzhon nu'i gzhu mo la //
NK011(da)001:2190: khro bo pha bcu'i mda' smyug la //
NK011(da)001:2191: khro mo ma bcu'i sgro yis sgron //
NK011(da)001:2192: phur pa sras mchog gi made'u btsug /
NK011(da)001:2193: dam can rnam gsum gyi rgyus pas dkris //
NK011(da)001:2194: bswe lcags shel gsum gyi ngar cig blud //
NK011(da)001:2195: 'phang ni zangs nag gi phyogs su 'phangs //
NK011(da)001:2196: phog pa jo bo stag ram la phog /
NK011(da)001:2197: mda' tshabs mi chung che bar gda' //
NK011(da)001:2199: de nas dar ches pas phur pa rtsa dum 'chal ches te /
NK011(da)001:2200: nyang ro'i rgyal khams tsam du lad do //
NK011(da)001:2202: bdag cag la ni cha med la /
NK011(da)001:2203: de ji ltar lad 'chad pa na sna nam shes
NK011(da)001:2204: tshul gyi slob ma rgya ston sangs rgyas bya bas
NK011(da)001:2205: / shangs kyi lung par phur pa rgyud 'grel gzhan
NK011(da)001:2206: bkab nas rtsa dum la brten pa'i sgrub thabs mang
NK011(da)001:2207: / po brtsams / jo mo mkhar chen baza'i gdams
NK011(da)001:2208: ngag can gyis bltas pa na bsres kyang mi 'dres
NK011(da)001:2209: / po brtsams / skad do // gdams ngag dang
NK011(da)001:2210: mi ldan pas ni bsres pa dang bslad pa mi
NK011(da)001:2211: / po brtsams / skad do // shes / rgya
NK011(da)001:2212: ston sangs rgyas kyi slob ma rgya rtsags shes rab
NK011(da)001:2213: rgyal mtshan gyis kyang rtsa dum gyi sgrub gzhung mang
NK011(da)001:2214: / po brtsams / skad do // shes / po brtsams / shangs pa dgon ston gyis kyang brtsams /
NK011(da)001:2215: de'i slob ma sgro ston dar rtsug gis kyang sgrub thabs mang du byas /
NK011(da)001:2216: la la gsang skor gyis bslad /
NK011(da)001:2217: la la mdo skor gyis bslad /
NK011(da)001:2218: de dag gi sgrubs thabs kyi ming ni man ngag drug pa dang /
NK011(da)001:2221: bskyed pa sku'i thems yig dang /
NK011(da)001:2225: phur pa 'dul bzhi la sogs pa mtshams gyi rnam grangs mang po btags skad /
NK011(da)001:2226: dus der tsa na jo bo ston pa kun na re /
NK011(da)001:2227: nga'i 'di jo mo mkhar chen baza'i thugs dam yin /
NK011(da)001:2229: gcig la gcig mi mgu skad /
NK011(da)001:2230: spyir dang por sprangs phur bu mgos sgrub gzhung mang po brtsams /
NK011(da)001:2231: bar du rgya ston sangs rgyas la sogs pas shangs lung bar gzhung mang po brtsams /
NK011(da)001:2232: tha mar gang zag shes rab can rnams kyis legs
NK011(da)001:2233: su re bas mang po byas nas ming phur pa
NK011(da)001:2234: rtsa dum du btags nas mi 'dra ba grangs las
NK011(da)001:2235: 'das / bka' dang brgyud pa man ngag ma chad
NK011(da)001:2236: pa chos ma bslad pa man ngag thob pa gcig
NK011(da)001:2237: gis bltas na 'chal ba yin par shes /
NK011(da)001:2238: bod du bsgyur ba'i chos la phur pa rtsa dum 'chal che skad /
NK011(da)001:2239: phur pa rtsa dum lhad med yod pa slob dpon drag po yin /
NK011(da)001:2242: gong gi de dag lang lab kyi khyad chos jo
NK011(da)001:2243: mo mkhar chen baza'i thugs tig 'di ma grags pa
NK011(da)001:2244: yin gyi / de dag gi brgyud pa rnams la
NK011(da)001:2245: gang zag bzang po sha stag byon pa yin pas
NK011(da)001:2246: yin gyi / / rang rang gi sgrub gzhung de
NK011(da)001:2247: dag la 'chal ba'i skyon yod par mi sems la
NK011(da)001:2248: yin gyi / / / yang sgrub thabs kha cig ni sbyor dngos rjes gsum ma tshang ba dang /
NK011(da)001:2250: nor ba la sogs pa kha yar snang mod kyi /
NK011(da)001:2251: deng sang nub nas nyams len byed pa mi 'dug pas /
NK011(da)001:2253: slob dpon drag po la slob ma mang yang /
NK011(da)001:2254: thugs kyi sras su gyur pa ni gnyis yin te /
NK011(da)001:2255: nyang ro rgyan mkhar gyi se ston khri rgyal dang /
NK011(da)001:2256: nyang ston gyi lce ston sh+aakya rgyal mtshan gnyis so //
NK011(da)001:2257: de la lce ston sh+aakya rgyal mtshan ni /
NK011(da)001:2258: ston pa chen po gcig yin pas /
NK011(da)001:2259: 'khor mang pos bskor te gdugs spur te byon te /
NK011(da)001:2260: slob dpon drag po mjal bas mkhyen pa la thugs
NK011(da)001:2261: mnyes nas rgyud 'grel thams cad gnang yang ston pa
NK011(da)001:2262: 'di sku bsod che bas lag len ma lobs te
NK011(da)001:2263: mi mkhas / rgyud 'grel gyi bshad pa ni mkhas so //
NK011(da)001:2264: phyis lag len dang man ngag zhu bsam ste byon
NK011(da)001:2265: tsa na slob dpon drag po ni grongs nas mi
NK011(da)001:2266: bzhugs / slob dpon gyi jo mo skyid gu rang
NK011(da)001:2267: gi yul du spyan drangs nas dbyangs tsho tshod tsam
NK011(da)001:2268: bzhugs / byung / man ngag gi brgyud pa ma zin no //
NK011(da)001:2269: lce ston gyi slob ma skyi chung pa shes rab
NK011(da)001:2270: grags pa bya ba shes rab can zhig gis dgongs
NK011(da)001:2271: rgyud bcos nas la stod du mang po spel /
NK011(da)001:2272: 'go ba bya yes kyang rgyud la bcos skad /
NK011(da)001:2273: der dgongs rgyud la gnyis byung /
NK011(da)001:2274: lce ston gyis man ngag med par rgyud 'grel gzhan gyis bslad nas mang du bshad do //
NK011(da)001:2275: slob dpon drag po'i chos brgyud zin pa'i slob ma ni se ston khri rgyal kho na yin te /
NK011(da)001:2276: rgyu 'grel man ngag kun la mkhas /
NK011(da)001:2277: dben sa rgyan mkhar gyi ngo dmar brag phug /
NK011(da)001:2278: gsang mtshan rdo rje gter sgrub rtsal /
NK011(da)001:2279: rtags dang mtshan ma phul du phyin /
NK011(da)001:2280: phur pa dgra bgegs gnyis la thebs so //
NK011(da)001:2281: 'di'i slob ma lha rje phur ston ring mo yin te /
NK011(da)001:2282: zhabs tog gis bla ma mnyes pa mang po mdzad de gdams pa ma lus pa thob /
NK011(da)001:2283: sku gzhon nu'i tshe slob dpon drag po la yang rtsa ba tshar gnyis zhus /
NK011(da)001:2284: dben sa khra ri'i rdo rje gnam rdzong /
NK011(da)001:2285: gsang mtshan rdo rje las rab rtsal /
NK011(da)001:2288: bka' shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa sras
NK011(da)001:2289: yum bcu bdun bzhengs pa la sogs dge ba'i las
NK011(da)001:2290: rgya che mdzad / khra ri gnam rdzong bya ba de la stod rgyal gyi rtsibs ri'i byang nas /
NK011(da)001:2291: rgyangs tsam song ba'i ri la brag seng ge gnam du mchong ba 'dra ba gcig yod /
NK011(da)001:2292: de'i steng na rdzong bar snang la ling nge 'dra ba zhig yod /
NK011(da)001:2293: de ru bsgrubs pas rtags dang mtshan ma thob bo //
NK011(da)001:2294: de'i slob ma rgya ston nam mkha' rgyal pos khra
NK011(da)001:2295: ri gnam rdzong du bla ma mnyes par byas nas
NK011(da)001:2296: gdams pa man ngag tshang bar zhus kyang dbang ma
NK011(da)001:2297: thob pas / phyis rang gi gcen smyos ston nyi
NK011(da)001:2298: ma rdo rje bya ba lha rje phur gyi thugs
NK011(da)001:2299: thob pas / sras la zhus / dben sa ding
NK011(da)001:2300: ri brag nye'i dbang steng dgon bar bla ma smyos
NK011(da)001:2301: thob pas / sras la zhus / dang / rgya
NK011(da)001:2302: ston gnyis kas bsgrubs pas rtags dang mtshan ma mtha'
NK011(da)001:2303: thob pas / sras la zhus / dang / ru
NK011(da)001:2304: phyin / gsang mtshan gnyis ka mthun par rdo rje
NK011(da)001:2305: thob pas / sras la zhus / dang / ru
NK011(da)001:2306: phyin / drag po rtsal / dgra bgegs gnyis ka
NK011(da)001:2307: thob pas / sras la zhus / dang / ru
NK011(da)001:2308: phyin / drag po rtsal / la thebs / de
NK011(da)001:2309: ltar gnyis kas lha rje phur la thug kyang dbang
NK011(da)001:2311: lha rje smyos ston nyi ma rdo rje /
NK011(da)001:2312: rgya ston nam mkha' rgyal po zhes 'dod do //
NK011(da)001:2313: nam mkha' rgyal po'i slob ma rang gi sras gnyis las /
NK011(da)001:2314: sras chung ba nyi ma rgyal mtshan pa la rgyud 'grel gdams ngag tshang bar gnang /
NK011(da)001:2315: chung ngu nas yab kyi drung du phyag phyir lag
NK011(da)001:2316: len mang pa mdzad pas lag len dbyangs dang bcas
NK011(da)001:2318: yab kyis bsnyen sgrub la bcug pas rtags dang mtshan ma mang po brnyes /
NK011(da)001:2319: dgra bgegs gnyis ka la thebs /
NK011(da)001:2320: dngos grub rlabs can du grags so //
NK011(da)001:2321: de'i slob ma nyang ban shu mngas lung pa chen po yin te /
NK011(da)001:2322: bla ma la dbang dang rgyud 'grel man ngag tshang bar zhus /
NK011(da)001:2323: dben sa rong rgyan mkhar gyi thog phug /
NK011(da)001:2324: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbang 'dus rtsal /
NK011(da)001:2326: de'i slob ma 'dzam gling pan+di ta nag po /
NK011(da)001:2327: 'di ni mi che bas nyang stod kyi bya chos
NK011(da)001:2328: mkhar po che la sogs pa mkhar gsum gyi bdag
NK011(da)001:2329: por gyur / rong du rmu bsam gling gi lha khang bzhengs /
NK011(da)001:2330: dben sa mon mo gtsug rum /
NK011(da)001:2331: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'dus pa rtsal dang /
NK011(da)001:2333: lha 'dre bran du 'khol ba la sogs pa'i yon tan mnga' 'o //
NK011(da)001:2334: de'i slob ma shangs rdo rje gling pa bla chen rdo rje rin po che yin te /
NK011(da)001:2335: 'di ni mkhas btsun bzang po'i yon tan du ma dang ldan /
NK011(da)001:2336: sku la tshul khrims kyi dri 'phro /
NK011(da)001:2337: bla ma 'dzam gling pa rang gi dgon par spyan drangs nas dbang dang gdams pa zhus /
NK011(da)001:2340: de'i slob ma chu bar nyi phug pa chen po yin te /
NK011(da)001:2341: dben sa brel phu bsam gtan phug /
NK011(da)001:2342: gsang mtshan rdo rje thog 'bebs rtsal /
NK011(da)001:2345: de'i slob ma gtsang nya ri ban grong gi ston pa gsang sngags rdo rje yin te /
NK011(da)001:2346: dus phyis byon pa'i sngags pa la mkhyen pa dang nus mthu gnyis ka che /
NK011(da)001:2347: slob dpon pad+mas mchims rdo rje spre'u chung gi skye bar lung bstan /
NK011(da)001:2348: bod la phan pa'i rten 'brel mang po 'dug pa /
NK011(da)001:2349: mnga' ri rdzong kha'i chos rgyal gyi gdung brgyud rnams
NK011(da)001:2350: kyis mthun rkyen sbyar te sna 'ga' re yang grub
NK011(da)001:2351: / rdzong kha rgyal po'i sku rim gyi nub re'i
NK011(da)001:2352: thun gtor 'phangs pa'i tshe me dngos su 'gro ba
NK011(da)001:2353: skye bo kun gyis mthun snang du grub pa sogs
NK011(da)001:2354: mthu'i nus pa'i grags pa thon /
NK011(da)001:2355: rdzong khar yi dam mang po'i zhal gzigs /
NK011(da)001:2356: 'dis sku gzhon nu'i dus su sgro phug gi dus
NK011(da)001:2357: su dben sar phur pa'i sgrub pa zhag bdun mdzad
NK011(da)001:2358: pas / rdo rje gzhon nu zhal gzigs /
NK011(da)001:2359: phur pa dgra bgegs gnyis ka la thebs so //
NK011(da)001:2360: de la mang yul skyid grong gi thugs rje chen
NK011(da)001:2361: po dngos dang mtshungs pa 'phags pa wa ti bzhugs
NK011(da)001:2363: bdag cag gi bla ma dam pa grub pa'i dbang phyug chen po des gsan pa yin te /
NK011(da)001:2364: 'di ni chu pho rta'i lo la mi nyag 'ga' dang nye ba'i sar sku 'khrungs /
NK011(da)001:2365: dgung lo bco brgyad lon pa'i tshe sa g.yos kyi
NK011(da)001:2366: 'jigs pas nang mi dang grong pa kun shi bas
NK011(da)001:2367: thugs skyo ste dbus gtsang du chos la byon /
NK011(da)001:2368: der yar klugs btsan thang du gong ma grags pa
NK011(da)001:2369: 'byung gnas pas dmar ston rgyal mtshan 'od zer spyan
NK011(da)001:2370: drangs btsan thang ma mo cher grags pa'i chos 'khor
NK011(da)001:2371: bskor ba dang thug ste sngags gsar ma'i dbang bka'
NK011(da)001:2373: rje 'gos lo ts+aa ba la sbyor drug gi khrid
NK011(da)001:2374: gsan pas zla ba drug bsgoms pa la yon tan
NK011(da)001:2375: thams cad rdzogs pas rje nyid shin tu dgyes te
NK011(da)001:2376: / khyod chos 'di la bag chags sad pa gcig 'dug gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2377: skabs der rdo rje'i zam pa gnang ba dang thug
NK011(da)001:2378: pas sngags rnying ma'i chos skor la dad pa mchi
NK011(da)001:2380: chos thams cad thob pa zhig bya dgos snyam pa shar /
NK011(da)001:2382: dbu ru na zhogs thar pa gling bya ba na sangs rgyas dbon po la yod zer /
NK011(da)001:2383: der byon te rdzogs pa chen po bka' gter phal cher gsan /
NK011(da)001:2384: 'bri gung du chos rje kun dga' rin chen la 'bri gung pa'i skor yongs rdzogs gsan /
NK011(da)001:2385: chos rje'i sku mdun du gsang phu ba'i ka bcu pa bstan gsal bya bas /
NK011(da)001:2386: dgong gcig la dgag pa mang po byas pa la /
NK011(da)001:2388: chos rje dang bka' bcu pa gnyis ka dgyes /
NK011(da)001:2390: khams pa khyod 'di 'dra'i shes rab che ba la
NK011(da)001:2391: mdo phyogs bslab na sa skya pan+di ta 'dra ba
NK011(da)001:2393: der ban sgar pa 'jam dpal bzang po 'bri gung du byin /
NK011(da)001:2394: khong la pan chen nags rin gyi chos skor zhus /
NK011(da)001:2396: khyed la bka' brgyud kyi bstan 'dzin cig re bas stag lung du song gsung /
NK011(da)001:2398: stag lung ngag dbang grags pa la /
NK011(da)001:2399: bo dong pa'i chos bka' tsam las bka' brgyud ma thob kyang /
NK011(da)001:2400: lo bzhi bzhugs te thugs rtsis che /
NK011(da)001:2401: slar 'bri gung du byon pa na chos rje gshegs /
NK011(da)001:2402: dbon po kun rin pa rten bzhengs kyi 'bul sdud
NK011(da)001:2403: la myang long la byon song 'dug pas yar klungs
NK011(da)001:2404: su byon / 'on mthing ma ba sngags 'chang g.yu
NK011(da)001:2405: 'brug rdo rje la mdo dbang dang sems phyogs gsan
NK011(da)001:2406: su byon / / de nas spa gro stag tshang
NK011(da)001:2407: du kahthoga pa ye shes 'bum pa la rgyud 'bum
NK011(da)001:2408: su byon / / gyi lung dang / bka' ma'i chos bka' mang po zhus /
NK011(da)001:2409: rat+na gling pa'i dri lan mdzad kyin 'dug pas de
NK011(da)001:2410: khyer nas lho brag shar du rat+na gling pa la
NK011(da)001:2411: phul / khong gi gter chos yongs rdzogs dang /
NK011(da)001:2413: phur pa bka' ma kha yar thob /
NK011(da)001:2414: de nas la stod byang du byon /
NK011(da)001:2415: rgyal mkhar se ston pa la zhi khro phur gsum gyi skor dang /
NK011(da)001:2418: sgang shar sogs ma mo'i rgyud lung mang po dang /
NK011(da)001:2422: gshin rje dmar po la sogs pa khong la bzhugs tshad kyi chos gsan bas /
NK011(da)001:2423: pu sti phyed dang sum brgya tsam gyi dbang lung thob /
NK011(da)001:2424: bla ma 'dis lto gos chos gsum ka gnang /
NK011(da)001:2425: lhag par bstan pa'i khur che bas 'di bas lhag pa'i bla ma med gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2426: lo rgyus gsungs pa na'ang spyan chab 'byin /
NK011(da)001:2430: ko ta la sogs pa'ang gzigs par byon /
NK011(da)001:2431: la stod lhor sngags 'chang nam bkras pa la bka' brgyad bka' gter mi gcig pa bdun dang /
NK011(da)001:2432: rdzogs chen a ro'i skor phal che ba dang /
NK011(da)001:2436: grub snying a ma ra na si ka ra'i skor /
NK011(da)001:2437: do ha mdzod 'jam dbyangs rdo rje'i chos bskor la sogs pa mang po gsan /
NK011(da)001:2438: de nas yar klungs su byon /
NK011(da)001:2439: khrus khang lo ts+aa ba la rngog dkyil bdun gyi skor gsan /
NK011(da)001:2440: chag lo rin chen chos rgyal la ste'u ra'i chos skor rdzogs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:2441: chos rje nam bkras pa la bka' gdams kyi skor mang po gsan /
NK011(da)001:2442: zhwa dmar ba bzhi pa la karma pa'i chos skor mtha' dag dang /
NK011(da)001:2443: yab tu byang sems chen po la zhi byed skor /
NK011(da)001:2444: gtsang smyon la ras chung pa'i snyan brgyud la sogs pa mang po dang /
NK011(da)001:2445: zing pa stag mgor sangs rgyas rgyal mtshan pa la kun mkhyen klong chen pa'i chos skor /
NK011(da)001:2446: dol ba sgrub chen ma la gcod yul dang /
NK011(da)001:2447: bla ma dgongs 'dus la sogs pa sangs rgyas gling pa'i chos skor ma lus pa dang /
NK011(da)001:2448: bsam gtan gling pa la khong re'i a ti skor dang /
NK011(da)001:2450: lam 'bras la sogs pa mang po dang /
NK011(da)001:2451: rgyal dbang chos rje kun dga' dpal 'byor ba la 'brug phyogs mtha' dag thob cing /
NK011(da)001:2452: shangs 'ba' ra nam mkha' rgyal mtshan pa la stod 'brug dang 'ba' chos mtha' dag dang /
NK011(da)001:2453: 'jag pa la shangs pa bka' brgyud skor dang /
NK011(da)001:2454: sku drung nyi zla ba la kun skyong gling pa'i chos skor dang /
NK011(da)001:2455: ngor du chos rje 'dren mchog la lam 'bras dang /
NK011(da)001:2457: zhwa lu ba dkon mchog bzang po la yo ga dang zhwa lu pa'i chos bka' phal cher gsan /
NK011(da)001:2458: chos rje byang chen pa la 'chims nas brgyud pa'i
NK011(da)001:2459: dbu ma'i khrid sogs snar thang pa'i chos skor dang
NK011(da)001:2460: / gtum shul du mnga' bdag gi gdung dang slob
NK011(da)001:2461: brgyud rnams la nyang lugs kyi chos mang po dang
NK011(da)001:2462: / / gnas rnying bsam gtan sgang pa la chos
NK011(da)001:2463: dbang rin po che'i gter chos sogs mang du gsan
NK011(da)001:2464: / / cing / mdor na bod du dar ba'i
NK011(da)001:2465: chos la ma gsan pa med pa lta bu yod
NK011(da)001:2466: kyang bdag gis kyang brjod par mi nus so //
NK011(da)001:2467: de nas gra thang du zhwa lu lo ts+aa ba'i drung du byon pas /
NK011(da)001:2469: gsang 'dus rim lnga'i khrid zhu gsung ba la /
NK011(da)001:2470: rim lnga zhus pas rlung lnga'i kha dog so sor gzigs /
NK011(da)001:2471: mnal lam bzung nas zhing khams mang po bsgrod /
NK011(da)001:2472: bar srid thogs med du gzigs /
NK011(da)001:2473: slob ma dang yon bdag dam tshig gtsang ba rnams
NK011(da)001:2474: kyi bde sdug mkhyen pa'i mngon par shes pa mnga'
NK011(da)001:2475: ba sogs yon tan du ma byung bas /
NK011(da)001:2476: sna 'ga' re gsungs pa la brten nas mi kun
NK011(da)001:2477: gyis kyang bsnyen bkur dang 'bul ba rgya chen byas
NK011(da)001:2478: shing / thugs dam brtags pa zhu ba mang bas g.yengs pa la thugs sun zhing /
NK011(da)001:2479: tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas bsgrub par dgongs nas bya bral la bzhugs te /
NK011(da)001:2480: mon yul du bros nas 'tsho ba ngan ngon la brten te tshe dang sgrub pa mnyam pa dang /
NK011(da)001:2481: snod ldan gyi slob ma byung na chos kyi sbyin pa lhug par stsol ba'i dam bca' mdzad /
NK011(da)001:2482: mkhar chur lo bdun sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK011(da)001:2483: zhwa lu lo ts+aa ba la sku tshe'i bar chad
NK011(da)001:2484: drug cu rtsa gcig gi dgung stengs su 'dug pa
NK011(da)001:2485: de / nyid kyi phur pa'i bsnyen sgrub mdzad na /
NK011(da)001:2486: slar sum cu'i bar phyir nur te dgung lo dgu cu rtsa gcig bzhes par 'gyur zhes /
NK011(da)001:2487: re ma tis lung bstan byung ba la /
NK011(da)001:2488: de'i nangs par rang dkyil 'khor bzhengs nas zla ba dgu sgrub pa la bzhugs /
NK011(da)001:2489: de dus bsnyen phur gyi zhal nas me stag 'phro 'phro byung ba dang /
NK011(da)001:2490: nga la dgra cig yod na bsgral chog pa la dgra med dgongs pa byung /
NK011(da)001:2491: yang sgu chul la phyug po la bsod snyoms kyi nas bcol ba ma sprad pa'i khar /
NK011(da)001:2493: yon bdag kun dang phra ma bcug pa de thugs kyis dran pas phur pa ldeg ldeg pa dang /
NK011(da)001:2495: du ba sngo phyur phyur byung /
NK011(da)001:2496: der nga'i bla ma'i sku tshe 'thud yod dam /
NK011(da)001:2497: phur pa ni grub byung dgongs nas /
NK011(da)001:2498: thug sdor gyi phag sha skam po tshal pa gcig yod pa de tshogs 'khor byas /
NK011(da)001:2499: gtor ma rgyas par bsngosa nas /
NK011(da)001:2501: dkyil 'khor gyi nang nas yin bsam pa la /
NK011(da)001:2502: yang re sgrub khang nas yin bsam pa'i bud med
NK011(da)001:2503: rta pa mang pos shing gi phur pa dkar po
NK011(da)001:2504: dang / grod pa mang po khur nas sgu chul
NK011(da)001:2505: gzhis kar song nas grod pa nas khrag mang po
NK011(da)001:2507: de nas zhwa lu lo ts+aa ba'i drung du byon
NK011(da)001:2508: tsa na 'bul ba cang med nas sku phrag myul
NK011(da)001:2509: bas a ru ra rlon pa sum cu so gcig
NK011(da)001:2510: byung ba bla ma la phul bas /
NK011(da)001:2511: shin tu dgyes te phyag tu bzhes /
NK011(da)001:2512: gcig tshur gnang nas nga rang gi khar bcug pa rmis /
NK011(da)001:2515: nga la gcig gnang ba des lo gcig gis nyung ngu song ba 'dra snyam pa byung ste /
NK011(da)001:2516: phyis de ka rang byung ste dgung lo dgu bcu bzhugs pa yin /
NK011(da)001:2517: de nas zla ba gcig tsa na sgu chul ba
NK011(da)001:2518: tsho la bshal rims byung nas rang re la sems
NK011(da)001:2519: gnag tshad shi / dug gtong mi phyug po tshang gi grong rkang stongs /
NK011(da)001:2520: phur pa 'dis nga'i bla ma'i sku tshe 'thud de /
NK011(da)001:2521: nga ngan song du de'i skyur /
NK011(da)001:2526: gtsug gtor dri med rnams kyi sgrib sbyong la lo re re ste lo lnga la mtshams bsdom /
NK011(da)001:2527: mi che chung lnga bcu tsam shi ba 'grongs e yod yin te skyon che gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2528: spyir bla ma 'di'i mkhas btsun bzang gsum /
NK011(da)001:2530: thos bsam sgom gsum la thugs rtsom mdzad lugs sogs
NK011(da)001:2531: ni sems can gyi blor shong ba dka' zhing yon
NK011(da)001:2532: tan de dag gi cha shas tsam yang bdag lta
NK011(da)001:2533: bus brjod par mi nus la /
NK011(da)001:2534: rnam thar mdo tsam zhig 'dri bar zhus pas ma gnang /
NK011(da)001:2535: phag tu zin bris btab pa zhig yod pa de yang mngon shes kyis dgongs nas long shog gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2537: khyed rang dang dad pa che ste /
NK011(da)001:2538: dus ngan gyi sems can tsho sdig pa gsog lugs 'dis chog pa 'dug pa la /
NK011(da)001:2539: nga la brten nas sdig pa theb gsog tu ma 'jug /
NK011(da)001:2540: ma dad pa skyes na sdug ge tsho dmyal bar skye /
NK011(da)001:2541: nga la yon tan yod tshul su la yang ma lab gsungs nas zin bris me la btab /
NK011(da)001:2542: bka' rgya dam pas brjod du yang med la /
NK011(da)001:2543: phyis sku thim par nye ba na /
NK011(da)001:2544: da lo'i 'brum nad 'di la nga thag ring gcig la bros 'gro gsungs nas /
NK011(da)001:2545: skabs shig tu gar song cha med du song /
NK011(da)001:2546: de nas me tog gi char dang /
NK011(da)001:2547: nam mkha' la 'ja' dang sa g.yo ba dang nyi ma bdun bstud mar byung /
NK011(da)001:2548: shar phyogs su sgra chen po grags pa sogs kyi ltas la brten nas /
NK011(da)001:2549: slob ma re gnyis dang yon bdag chos nyams ldan
NK011(da)001:2550: pa dag ni sku ma spangs par mkha' spyod du
NK011(da)001:2552: de ltar yongs 'dzin dam pa ni dgung lo ji tsam bzhes zhes zhus pa na /
NK011(da)001:2553: brgya cu rtsa lnga tsam a mi lon /
NK011(da)001:2554: da rgas nas brjed de mi gda' /
NK011(da)001:2555: zhes thams cad la gsungs pa zhig yin mod kyi /
NK011(da)001:2558: dmar ston sogs kyi drung du chos gsan pa dang thog mtshungs pa yin pas /
NK011(da)001:2559: mi yul du lo nyis brgya lhag tsam bzhugs pa 'dra zhing /
NK011(da)001:2560: yon tan gzhan rnams smra ru med kyang /
NK011(da)001:2561: rdo rje phur pa la brten nas dngos grub brnyes
NK011(da)001:2562: tshul phur pa brgyud pa'i lo rgyus 'dir med na
NK011(da)001:2563: mi rung bas cung zad bris pa la dpal ldan
NK011(da)001:2564: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin rgyal mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang
NK011(da)001:2565: bcas pas gnang ba bstsal te bdag cag gi lam
NK011(da)001:2566: dang dngos grub kyi gegs su mi 'gyur bar byin
NK011(da)001:2568: de ltar lha mchog phur pa'i sgor zhugs pas //
NK011(da)001:2569: rig 'dzin grub thob rim par byon pa'i tshul //
NK011(da)001:2570: rgya bal bod du bgrang gis mi lang la //
NK011(da)001:2571: sngon byung lo rgyus ji bzhin 'chad nus pa'i //
NK011(da)001:2572: blo gros spobs pa bdag la ma mchis mod //
NK011(da)001:2573: de lta na yang rang gis thos pa tsam //
NK011(da)001:2574: yi ge'i lam du gsal bar ma byas na //
NK011(da)001:2575: deng sang rgyud gzhung mkhyen pa smos ci dgos //
NK011(da)001:2576: gtam tsam rna bar sgrog pa mi snang bas //
NK011(da)001:2577: nub par 'phangs nas dge ba'i sems kyis bkod //
NK011(da)001:2578: nongs na bla ma lha la bzod par gsol //
NK011(da)001:2579: e ma rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin po che //
NK011(da)001:2580: sngon chad bod 'dir dar la rgya che zhing //
NK011(da)001:2581: bstan 'dzin mkhas grub tshad mar gyur pa dang //
NK011(da)001:2582: nyams len mdzad pa'i gang zag bsam mi khyab //
NK011(da)001:2583: deng sang dus na nam langs skar ma bzhin //
NK011(da)001:2584: bstan la phan pa thams cad zhing gzhan gshegs //
NK011(da)001:2585: gsang sngags 'dzin par 'dod pa 'ga' zhig kyang //
NK011(da)001:2586: 'phral dgos za chog slob par mi nus na //
NK011(da)001:2587: rgya chen rgyud 'grel lag len lta ci smos //
NK011(da)001:2588: ming dang rtags tsam 'dzin pa nyid du gyur //
NK011(da)001:2589: thos bsam sgro 'dogs gcod pa'i blo med cing //
NK011(da)001:2590: bsnyen sgrub mtha' ru 'don pa'i 'dun pa bral //
NK011(da)001:2591: bzang bardzu 'ug pa sbos pa ltar 'gying ba'i //
NK011(da)001:2592: gang zag mthong bas rang sems lhag par skyo //
NK011(da)001:2593: phyi tshul bzang po'i gos kyis rnam spud cing //
NK011(da)001:2594: nang du khyim pa'i sems dang mi 'bral la //
NK011(da)001:2595: bstan dang 'gro ba'i don la rgyab kyis phyogs //
NK011(da)001:2596: 'di 'dra'i bstan 'dzin mthong tshe snying nas skyo //
NK011(da)001:2597: 'dzum pa'i zhal nas bstan pa spel zhes lo //
NK011(da)001:2598: kha bgrad mig tshums sems can snying rje skad //
NK011(da)001:2599: zhe nas lag len rang gi bsnyen bkur bsgrub //
NK011(da)001:2600: bstan 'gro'i bya ba bshol 'di snying nas skyo //
NK011(da)001:2601: mang pos bkur ba'i zas nor gyis ci bya //
NK011(da)001:2602: rang gi sems la rang gis mi khrel ba'i //
NK011(da)001:2603: slob gnyer bsnyen sgrub lam rtags thon tsam re //
NK011(da)001:2604: med na rang la rang gis ma bslus sam //
NK011(da)001:2605: bdag ni 'dod pa'i lha yi bdud dbang gis //
NK011(da)001:2606: nyin mtshan dal med grong chog bon ltar rgyug /
NK011(da)001:2607: dkor gyi phung pos shes rgyud sgrib pas non //
NK011(da)001:2608: yon tan gsar du skye ba lta ci zhig /
NK011(da)001:2609: sngar shes skyabs 'gro tsam yang brjed de thal //
NK011(da)001:2610: dal 'byor don med rnam g.yengs dbang du song //
NK011(da)001:2612: da ni dben par don gnyis bsgrub par smon //
NK011(da)001:2613: 'di ltar snod bcud nyams pa'i dus dbang gis //
NK011(da)001:2614: sangs rgyas bstan dang skye rgu'i bde skyid rnams //
NK011(da)001:2615: rang dang gzhan gyi spyod tshul mtha' dag la //
NK011(da)001:2616: bsam bzhin bsam bzhin skyo ba gting nas skyes //
NK011(da)001:2617: da ni gzhan skyon sems brjod nyes dmigs che //
NK011(da)001:2618: rang skyon 'don pa dam pa'i spyod pa lags //
NK011(da)001:2619: de phyir rang drin rang la che ba'i thabs //
NK011(da)001:2620: legs nyes yin min kha 'khyams mi smra bar //
NK011(da)001:2621: thos bsam sgom gsum brtson pa'i lam zhugs te //
NK011(da)001:2622: ring por mi thogs rang btsan zin par smon //
NK011(da)001:2623: rang don bslu ba'i gzhan don ltar snang 'dis //
NK011(da)001:2624: sngar yang don med bya ba mang du byas //
NK011(da)001:2625: da ni sol ba 'bad de mi bkru bar //
NK011(da)001:2626: skal ldan srid na de don byed par smon //
NK011(da)001:2627: yun ring srid par 'gro don brtson pa dang //
NK011(da)001:2628: khyad par dam chos nyams pa de gso ba'i //
NK011(da)001:2629: lugs 'di rgyal sras rnams kyi spyod pa lags //
NK011(da)001:2630: de phyir chos rnams ci nus spel bar smon //
NK011(da)001:2631: des na mdo rgyud man ngag rgya mtsho dang //
NK011(da)001:2632: khyad par lam bzang rdo rje phur pa'i gzhung //
NK011(da)001:2633: ma lus mi nub gsal bar ston nus par //
NK011(da)001:2634: skye ba 'di dang brgyud mar 'gyur bar smon //
NK011(da)001:2635: 'on kyang dman pa bdag 'dra'i spyod tshul gyis //
NK011(da)001:2636: rgya chen lam bzang snang bar ma nus na //
NK011(da)001:2637: de slad rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs rje yis //
NK011(da)001:2638: 'gro kun sngags kyi snod du 'gyur bar shog /
NK011(da)001:2639: kun kyang mang du thos pa'i mthar son te //
NK011(da)001:2640: bsam pas don rig sgom pas dngos grub thob //
NK011(da)001:2641: rig 'dzin rnam bzhi rim gyis mngon 'gyur te //
NK011(da)001:2642: skyob pa pad+ma rgyal po de mtshungs shog /
NK011(da)001:2643: mar gyur drin can mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK011(da)001:2644: las dang dus kyi sbyor ba las byung ba'i //
NK011(da)001:2645: mi mthun rgud pa mtha' dag nyer zhi nas //
NK011(da)001:2646: bskal pa rdzogs ldan bzhin du bde bar shog /
NK011(da)001:2647: rdo rje phur pa'i chos tshul nyi 'od kyis //
NK011(da)001:2648: bstan dgra mun tshogs mtha' dag drung phyung ste //
NK011(da)001:2649: srid pa bdun gyi sbyor ba las gyur pa //
NK011(da)001:2650: chos kyi bar chad ma lus zhi bar shog /
NK011(da)001:2651: rta gdong kun nas tsha ba'i me dang ni //
NK011(da)001:2652: gang g+aa'i klung dang pak+shu'i rgyun bzhin du //
NK011(da)001:2653: rgyun mi chad pa srid pa ji srid bar //
NK011(da)001:2654: dam pa'i chos ni mi nub dar bar shog /
NK011(da)001:2655: thub dbang bstan pa'i gzhi ma dge 'dun te //
NK011(da)001:2656: de yang bdag rkyen byed la rag lus pas //
NK011(da)001:2657: gang zhig bstan pa mchod pa'i sbyin bdag yang //
NK011(da)001:2658: tshe ring nad med bde skyid ldan par shog /
NK011(da)001:2659: 'dis mtsho na bdag gis ji srid sangs rgyas par //
NK011(da)001:2660: dge tshogs ji snyed gang zhig thob gyur pa //
NK011(da)001:2661: shel dang zla ba kun+da ltar dkar ba //
NK011(da)001:2662: des ni 'gro 'dis phur pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:2663: dpal ldan rdo rje phur pa'i chos kyi byung tshul
NK011(da)001:2664: lo rgyus ngo mtshar rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs zhes bya
NK011(da)001:2665: ba / rang dang skal ba mnyam pa rnams kyi brjed byang du /
NK011(da)001:2666: sh+aakya'i btsun pa nam mkhar spyod pa zhes bya bas
NK011(da)001:2667: sa mo bya'i lo dbo'i nya ba'i gang ba dang
NK011(da)001:2668: po'i tshes la rdzogs par sbyar ba 'dis kyang rgyal
NK011(da)001:2669: ba'i bstan pa phyogs dus kun tu rgyas pa dang
NK011(da)001:2670: / 'gro ba rnams bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa'i dpal la dus kun tu spyod par gyur cig //
NK011(da)001:2672: /// dpal rdo rje phur pa'i las byang chog khrigs chos
NK011(da)001:2673: 'byung dang las byang 'di gnyis jo mo lugs dang
NK011(da)001:2674: rong zom lugs gnyis kar 'jug gsungs /
NK011(da)001:2676: dngos grub rgya mtsho zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:2678: gu ru badz+ra k+ai la ya man+da la de wa
NK011(da)001:2679: b+h+yah mi gnas mi dmigs chos sku dag pa las
NK011(da)001:2680: // bdud 'dul khro rgyal 'jigs pa'i skur bzhengs pa //
NK011(da)001:2681: 'jig rten gsum las rgyal ba he ru ka /
NK011(da)001:2682: 'bar ba'i gar mdzad de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:2683: yi dam lha la bdag gis phyag btsal nas //
NK011(da)001:2684: bstan pa bsrung ba'i phrin las mngon spyod 'di //
NK011(da)001:2685: dpyang thag chad pa thugs rjes bzung slad du //
NK011(da)001:2686: sgrub thabs 'di ni bdag gis bshad par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:2687: de la dang po rten dang mchod pa tshul bzhin du bshams nas /
NK011(da)001:2689: sems bskyed pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK011(da)001:2690: rang lha'i nga rgyal gyis bgegs gtor byin gyis brlabs la /
NK011(da)001:2691: sarba big+h+n+aana na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi
NK011(da)001:2692: shwa mu khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra
NK011(da)001:2693: na i mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)001:2694: lan gsum gyis bsngosa la gzhan du bskrad do //
NK011(da)001:2695: de nas mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK011(da)001:2696: rang nyid khro bo gnod mdzes rdo rje'i tho ba dang lcags kyu 'dzin par bskyed la /
NK011(da)001:2699: thugs ka nas ma dmar po 'phros /
NK011(da)001:2701: zhes pas nyi ma'i gdan du gyur /
NK011(da)001:2702: sh+r+ai h'u k+aa ra badz+ra man+da la h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2704: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dbus su ni //
NK011(da)001:2705: dbyar gyi 'char sprin lta bu'i mdog /
NK011(da)001:2706: bskal pa'i me dpung bzhin du 'bar //
NK011(da)001:2707: dor stabs tshul du zhabs bgrad cing //
NK011(da)001:2708: smin mtshams khro gnyer 'bar ba can //
NK011(da)001:2709: zhal gsum mche gtsigs rnam par gyur //
NK011(da)001:2710: phyag gnyis h'u gi rgya bcings nas //
NK011(da)001:2711: rdo rje dang ni dril bu dang //
NK011(da)001:2712: g.yas gnyis lcags kyu ral gri dang //
NK011(da)001:2713: g.yon gnyis dgra s+t+wa zhags pa bsnams //
NK011(da)001:2714: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams mnyan par byos //
NK011(da)001:2716: khro bo rdo rje gnod mdzes kyis h'u k+aa ra
NK011(da)001:2717: la phyogs bcur khro bcu'i gdan bshams pa'i bka' bsgos
NK011(da)001:2718: te thugs ka nas tho ba dang lcags kyu spros
NK011(da)001:2719: te h'u k+aa ra la gtad par bsam /
NK011(da)001:2720: sh+r+ai h'u tak+ki r+aa dza badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2721: 'dod rgyal sngo skya g.yas dkar g.yon dmar zhal //
NK011(da)001:2722: phyag drug dang pos rang gi phyag rgya bcings //
NK011(da)001:2723: bar pa gnyis kyis lcags kyu zhags pa dang //
NK011(da)001:2724: phyag g.yas tha ma mda' gzhu 'dzin la brtson //
NK011(da)001:2725: phyag g.yon tha ma nyi ma'i gdan bsnams gyur //
NK011(da)001:2728: 'dod rgyal gyi thugs ka nas ma bcu phyogs bcur 'phros pas nyi ma'i gdan bcur gyur /
NK011(da)001:2730: khro bo'i rgyal po 'di dag ni //
NK011(da)001:2731: bgegs kyi tshogs rnams kun nas bshig /
NK011(da)001:2732: blo ldan rab tu sbyar ba yi //
NK011(da)001:2733: cho ga bzhin du phur bus gdab //
NK011(da)001:2735: khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal po phyogs bcur phyin te
NK011(da)001:2736: phyogs skyong bcu lcags kyus bzung tho bas brdungs te
NK011(da)001:2737: phyogs bcu'i nyi gdan gyi steng du bsnol nas bzhag
NK011(da)001:2739: gdan steng khro rgyal chen po rnams //
NK011(da)001:2740: zhe sdang rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:2741: khro chen rngams brjid sprul pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:2742: nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:2743: zhes pas khro bo bcu spyan drangs te /
NK011(da)001:2744: 'dod rgyal h'u k+aa ra la thim //
NK011(da)001:2745: de nas h'u k+aa ras h'u bcu brjod la /
NK011(da)001:2747: khro bo bcu dag byung nas ni //
NK011(da)001:2748: h'u las bskyed pa'i nyi ma'i gdan //
NK011(da)001:2749: smad ni rtse mo'i rnam par bsam //
NK011(da)001:2750: phyogs bcu'i dkyil 'khor phyogs rnams su //
NK011(da)001:2751: rim pa bzhin du kun tu 'khod //
NK011(da)001:2752: bgegs rnams thams cad bshig pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:2753: gnod mdzes bka' byung phur pas btab //
NK011(da)001:2754: g+ha g+ha g+h+aa ta ya g+ha ta ya /
NK011(da)001:2755: sarba dush+tam m+aa ra ya phata phata /
NK011(da)001:2756: k+ai la ya k+ai la ya sarba p+aa bam phata phata /
NK011(da)001:2757: h'u h'u badz+ra k+ai la ya badz+ra d+ha rod a dz+ny+aa pa ya ti /
NK011(da)001:2758: sarba big+h+nana k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai la ya h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2762: tho ba phyag na bsnams pa'i mchog /
NK011(da)001:2763: gnod mdzes rgyal po'i rnam par bsam //
NK011(da)001:2764: h'u brjod 'bar ba'i blta ba yis //
NK011(da)001:2765: bgegs kyi tshogs rnams bshig pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:2766: gnod mdzes bka' stsal phur pas thob //
NK011(da)001:2771: khro bo'i rgyal po 'jigs byed bcu //
NK011(da)001:2772: rdo rje phur bu nyid gnas pa //
NK011(da)001:2775: lte ba man chad chos rnams ni //
NK011(da)001:2776: rtse mo lta bu'i rnam pa la //
NK011(da)001:2777: sku stod khro bo chen po ste //
NK011(da)001:2778: zhal gsum pa la phyag drug pa //
NK011(da)001:2779: bgegs kyi tshogs rnams 'og tu gzir //
NK011(da)001:2780: de yi sngags ni brjod byas nas //
NK011(da)001:2781: rdo rje phur pa nges btab na //
NK011(da)001:2782: bgegs lus shin tu mi gayo'o //
NK011(da)001:2783: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u /
NK011(da)001:2785: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza h'u /
NK011(da)001:2786: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2787: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h'u /
NK011(da)001:2788: da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2789: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h'u /
NK011(da)001:2790: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2791: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya ya a tsa la h'u /
NK011(da)001:2793: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h'u /
NK011(da)001:2794: hu lu hu lu h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2795: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h'u /
NK011(da)001:2797: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da l+ai h'u /
NK011(da)001:2799: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h'u /
NK011(da)001:2801: h'u badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK011(da)001:2804: de nas khro bo rnams rim pa bzhin phyogs bcu'i phyogs skyong rnams kyi snying gar babs pas /
NK011(da)001:2805: lus phug ste 'og gi nyi ma'i gdan la sbrags par bsam la /
NK011(da)001:2806: bstod cing phyogs bcing ba ni /
NK011(da)001:2808: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi steng 'og bcu'i //
NK011(da)001:2809: khro bo'i rgyal po'i bdud chen rnams //
NK011(da)001:2810: kun kyang zhal gsum phyag drug ste //
NK011(da)001:2811: ya mtshan che ba'i dbu rgyan can //
NK011(da)001:2812: dbu skra kham nag ral pa ni //
NK011(da)001:2814: spyan dmar glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK011(da)001:2815: mche ba zangs yag rnon po gtsigs //
NK011(da)001:2816: rkan sgra gtogs pas khams gsum 'khrugs //
NK011(da)001:2817: bdud rgyal rnams kyis zhabs la btud //
NK011(da)001:2818: mdzes pa'i lha mo mang po yis //
NK011(da)001:2819: snyan pa'i glu dbyangs du mas bstod //
NK011(da)001:2820: bcom ldan 'das kyi sprul pa ste //
NK011(da)001:2821: yang sprul grangs med phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK011(da)001:2823: lho phyogs gshin rje zhabs kyis gnon //
NK011(da)001:2824: nub phyogs klu yi gdon rnams gzir //
NK011(da)001:2825: byang phyogs gnod sbyin brlag par mdzad //
NK011(da)001:2826: shar lho me lha zil gyis gnon //
NK011(da)001:2827: lho nub srin po gdan du bting //
NK011(da)001:2828: nub byang rlung lha 'ching mdzad cing //
NK011(da)001:2829: byang shar dbang ldan gnon pa'i bdag /
NK011(da)001:2830: steng gi lha rnams dbang du bsdus //
NK011(da)001:2831: 'og gi sa bdag rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:2832: phyogs mtshams phur pas gtams byas nas //
NK011(da)001:2833: steng 'og yang dag byin gyis rlobs //
NK011(da)001:2834: bgegs kyi sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK011(da)001:2835: badz+ra kro d+ha rak+sha rak+sha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2836: yang rang gi thugs ka nas mtshon cha sna tshogs
NK011(da)001:2837: pa'i char 'phros te srid pa gsum gyi bgegs rnams
NK011(da)001:2838: bcom ste / tshur 'dus pas khro bo rnams kyi
NK011(da)001:2839: phyi rol du mtshon cha'i gur ra bar gyur par
NK011(da)001:2841: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:2842: khro bo'i byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK011(da)001:2843: rdo rje 'khor lo phur pa dang //
NK011(da)001:2844: tho ba ral gri la sogs pa'i //
NK011(da)001:2845: mtshon cha rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK011(da)001:2846: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK011(da)001:2847: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)001:2848: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed /
NK011(da)001:2849: badz+ra yu d+ha rak+sha rak+sha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2851: bdud dpung nges par bsreg byed pa'i //
NK011(da)001:2852: sa dang nam mkha' yongs gang ba //
NK011(da)001:2853: 'bar ba me yi phung por gyur //
NK011(da)001:2854: badz+ra dz+wa la ram rak+sha rak+sha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2855: 'jigs byed 'bar ba nga yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)001:2856: 'dod chags 'joms pa'i me ni dmar nag 'bar //
NK011(da)001:2857: zhe sdang 'joms pa'i me ni dkar nag 'bar //
NK011(da)001:2858: gti mug 'joms pa'i me ni mthing nag 'bar //
NK011(da)001:2859: nga rgyal 'joms pa'i me ni ser nag 'bar //
NK011(da)001:2860: phrag dog 'joms pa'i me ni ljang nag 'bar //
NK011(da)001:2861: dbang drag gdug rtsub me ni smug nag 'bar //
NK011(da)001:2862: 'bar ba me yi mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK011(da)001:2863: badz+ra ag+ne ye dz+wa la ram rak+sha rak+sha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2864: ces pas de'i phyi rol du me dpung gi gur du gyur par bsam /
NK011(da)001:2866: mtshams bcad nang 'di tshun chad du //
NK011(da)001:2867: su yang 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK011(da)001:2868: gal te 'da' par gyur pa na //
NK011(da)001:2869: tho ba lcags kyu 'khril ba yis //
NK011(da)001:2870: snying nas drangs te brdung bar bya'o //
NK011(da)001:2871: badz+ra am ku sha ya dzah badz+ra mud+ga ra a ko t+aa ya +aa ko t+aa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:2872: rang gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od 'phros /
NK011(da)001:2873: bla ma yi dam sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa'
NK011(da)001:2874: mkha' 'gro chos skyong thams cad rang bzhin gyi gnas
NK011(da)001:2875: nas spyan drangs nas mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa
NK011(da)001:2876: la / yan lag bdun pa 'bul zhing dam bca' ba ni /
NK011(da)001:2877: rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya dang /
NK011(da)001:2878: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK011(da)001:2879: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:2880: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK011(da)001:2881: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK011(da)001:2882: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK011(da)001:2883: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK011(da)001:2884: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:2885: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK011(da)001:2886: phyogs bcu'i 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK011(da)001:2887: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK011(da)001:2888: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK011(da)001:2889: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK011(da)001:2890: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK011(da)001:2891: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK011(da)001:2892: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK011(da)001:2893: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK011(da)001:2895: / rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po mthar phyin pa //
NK011(da)001:2896: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rje'i dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK011(da)001:2897: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gyur cig pu pa //
NK011(da)001:2898: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:2900: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK011(da)001:2901: rnal 'byor mchog gi grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK011(da)001:2902: lha dang lha min gsang sngags dam tshig can //
NK011(da)001:2903: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:2905: bdag ni mtho ris rgyal srid longs spyod dang //
NK011(da)001:2906: 'dod pa'i yon tan sgrub pa ma lags te //
NK011(da)001:2907: 'gro la snying brtse kho nas don brtson pa //
NK011(da)001:2908: 'di la kun mkhyen khyod nyid dpang du gyur //
NK011(da)001:2910: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK011(da)001:2911: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyod kyis mkhyen //
NK011(da)001:2912: khyed kyi spyan sngar khas blangs dam bcas pa //
NK011(da)001:2913: sun par mi bgyid mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK011(da)001:2915: bdag ni deng nas khe dang grags la sogs //
NK011(da)001:2916: g.yo dang zang zing sems ni gtan spangs nas //
NK011(da)001:2917: bdag don gcig pu sems la mi bzhag ste //
NK011(da)001:2918: rnams 'byor spyod pa rlabs chen bdag gis brtsam //
NK011(da)001:2920: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
