NK011(da)001:2921: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK011(da)001:2922: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK011(da)001:2923: deng nas tshul bzhin bdag gis bslab par bgyi //
NK011(da)001:2925: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK011(da)001:2926: dum bu stong du bdag lus gtubs na yang //
NK011(da)001:2927: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK011(da)001:2928: yi dam rgyal ba khyod ni yongs mi spong //
NK011(da)001:2930: rdo rje'i dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni //
NK011(da)001:2931: rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral dang //
NK011(da)001:2932: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la zhugs pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:2933: 'di dag srog gi phyir yang ci nus bzung //
NK011(da)001:2935: 'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la //
NK011(da)001:2936: bdag ni 'jigs pa ci yang ma mchis te //
NK011(da)001:2937: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK011(da)001:2938: phyi mthar thug gi bar du byed par spro //
NK011(da)001:2940: gzhan don spyod cing 'khor bar gnas pa na //
NK011(da)001:2941: byang chub spyod pa rlabs chen bdag gis spyad //
NK011(da)001:2942: rgyu drug sems can kun la phan slad du //
NK011(da)001:2943: rang gi dbang du skye ba bdag gis blang //
NK011(da)001:2945: bdag ni yongs su dag pa'i 'jig rten du //
NK011(da)001:2946: sangs rgyas rings shing spro bas ma mchis te //
NK011(da)001:2947: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK011(da)001:2948: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK011(da)001:2950: srid par yun ring 'gro don brtson pa ni //
NK011(da)001:2951: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi spyod pa lags //
NK011(da)001:2952: ci srid ngan song stongs par ma gyur bar //
NK011(da)001:2953: de srid bdag gis skyo ba'i sems mi bskyed //
NK011(da)001:2955: shes rab thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don byed pa //
NK011(da)001:2956: snying rje'i longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK011(da)001:2957: dmyal sems yi dwags gshin rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK011(da)001:2958: lha yi dga' tshal lta bur blta bar bgyi //
NK011(da)001:2960: 'gro la thugs brtses dpal gyi mgur nas gsung //
NK011(da)001:2961: rnal 'byor theg chen dam chos bdud rtsi mchog /
NK011(da)001:2962: bdag gis 'jig rten thug pa ma mchis kyang //
NK011(da)001:2963: 'jig rten 'tshams pa bzhin du rgyas par bagyi'o //
NK011(da)001:2965: srid par las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur te //
NK011(da)001:2966: gang du dam chos 'jigs pa de dang der //
NK011(da)001:2967: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK011(da)001:2968: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bsrung //
NK011(da)001:2970: bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK011(da)001:2971: sgrub pa mchog la zhugs pa'i skyes bu la //
NK011(da)001:2972: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i mthu rtsal ci mchis kyis //
NK011(da)001:2973: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu skong //
NK011(da)001:2975: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub la gegs byed pa //
NK011(da)001:2976: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK011(da)001:2977: bdag gis zhi khro'i thabs tshul sna tshogs kyis //
NK011(da)001:2978: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par gzhom par bgyi //
NK011(da)001:2980: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla na med //
NK011(da)001:2981: dpal mchog h'u mdzad khyod la brten nas ni //
NK011(da)001:2982: sangs rgyas zhing sbyong 'gro la phan don du //
NK011(da)001:2983: byang chub snying po bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK011(da)001:2985: bdag gis 'phags mchog phyag rgya mngon sprul te //
NK011(da)001:2986: gal te skal med 'chi ba'i dus babs na //
NK011(da)001:2987: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK011(da)001:2988: khyed kyi sku gsung thugs ni myur du bsab //
NK011(da)001:2990: srid par sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK011(da)001:2991: dmyal tshogs me dpung zhi bar bgyid la sogs //
NK011(da)001:2992: sems can don la myur bar bdag brtson na //
NK011(da)001:2993: dam pa rnams kyis nges pa'i mthu rtsal stsol //
NK011(da)001:2995: zhes dam bcas la tshogs zhing rnams rang la thim par bsam /
NK011(da)001:2996: dzahmh'u bam hoh de nas byin dbab pa ni /
NK011(da)001:2998: gdal ba chen po chos dbyings pho brang nas //
NK011(da)001:2999: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal sangs rgyas 'dus pa'i rje //
NK011(da)001:3000: byin rlabs 'dod rgu'i char chen 'bebs mdzad pa //
NK011(da)001:3001: phur ba grub pa'i rig 'dzin brgyud par bcas //
NK011(da)001:3002: rdo rje gzhon nu'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyis //
NK011(da)001:3003: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyi //
NK011(da)001:3004: mthu dbang byin rlabs dngos grub stsol ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:3005: dbyings nas 'dir gshegs dkyil 'khor byin phob cig /
NK011(da)001:3006: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sa ba ri w+aa ra badz+ra a be sha ya a a a /
NK011(da)001:3007: mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK011(da)001:3008: a mri tas bdud rtsi gtor ba'i rtse la khro bo spros pas bgegs bskrad /
NK011(da)001:3010: rang nyid lha yi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)001:3012: yam las rlung byung bag chags gtor //
NK011(da)001:3016: h'u sngon spros te rnam rtog sbyangs //
NK011(da)001:3019: h+r+aihyiga kha dog lnga ldan spros te zhu //
NK011(da)001:3020: lha rnams dgyes pa'i rdzas su gyur //
NK011(da)001:3022: thod pa snang srid kun khyab gzhal yas su //
NK011(da)001:3023: rigs lnga yab yum sbyor ba'i byang sems 'khyil //
NK011(da)001:3025: bdud rtsi bkug thim lha rnams bdud rtsir zhu //
NK011(da)001:3026: de las chu bur tshul du rta mgrin dbang //
NK011(da)001:3027: yum bzhir bcas pa dag tu gyur pa yang //
NK011(da)001:3028: zhu bas kha dog dri dang ro ldan zhing //
NK011(da)001:3029: nus mthu phun tshogs bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho che //
NK011(da)001:3030: chos dbyings nam mkha'i khams kun gang bar gyur //
NK011(da)001:3031: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aah a /
NK011(da)001:3032: b+han+d+ha stong gsum khyab pa'i snod nang du //
NK011(da)001:3033: nyon mongs 'gro ba bsgral ba'i rak+ta dang //
NK011(da)001:3034: rten 'brel bcu gnyis m+au la rak+ta dang //
NK011(da)001:3035: mkha' dbyings rnam dag pad+ma rak+ta dang //
NK011(da)001:3036: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i khrag chen rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK011(da)001:3037: ra las byung ba'i lha mo rak+ta mo //
NK011(da)001:3038: 'bru gsum sbyor bas zhu nas bdud rtsir brlab //
NK011(da)001:3039: +aahmh'u ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u h+r+aihth+aah a /
NK011(da)001:3040: snang ba snod kyi 'jig rten ka p+aa lar //
NK011(da)001:3041: sha lnga bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin ri ltar spungs //
NK011(da)001:3042: yi ge gsum gyis bzhu bas bdud rtsi'i mtsho //
NK011(da)001:3043: chos dbyings nam mkha'i mtha' klas gang bar gyur //
NK011(da)001:3044: +aahmh'u ma h+aa ba ling ta te dzo ba ling+ta
NK011(da)001:3045: ba la ba te gu h+ya sa ma ya h'u
NK011(da)001:3046: h+r+aihth+aah mchod yon zhabs bsil bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor 'khyil
NK011(da)001:3047: // lha rdzas me tog sa dang bar snang khyab //
NK011(da)001:3048: spos kyi dud sprin gnam sa bar kun 'khrigs //
NK011(da)001:3049: mar me'i phreng ba stong gsum 'od kyis 'bar //
NK011(da)001:3050: spos chu'i rdzing bu snang srid kun tu bskyil //
NK011(da)001:3051: zhal zas bdud rtsi'i bcud kyis stong khams bkang //
NK011(da)001:3052: lha mi'i rol mo sgra snyan srid gsum 'khrol //
NK011(da)001:3053: kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin gyi phung por gyur //
NK011(da)001:3061: badz+ra shap+da pra t+ai ts+tsha hoh khams gsum rnam dag dur khrod gnas mchog tu //
NK011(da)001:3062: dbang po lnga yi me tog ri ltar spungs //
NK011(da)001:3063: gsur chen dud pa'i sprin phung kun tu 'khrigs //
NK011(da)001:3064: zhun chen mar me dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK011(da)001:3065: mchog chen zhag gi byug ba'i mtsho ru bskyil //
NK011(da)001:3066: sha chen bdud rtsi'i zhal zas 'jig rten gang //
NK011(da)001:3067: srid gsum khyab pa'i keng rus brag ltar 'tsher //
NK011(da)001:3068: go ro tsa na nam mkha'i rgya khyon bkang //
NK011(da)001:3069: rkang gling thod rnga'i sgra dbyangs stong gsum sgrog /
NK011(da)001:3070: dpag yas nang gi mchod pa bla na med //
NK011(da)001:3071: rol pa'i ye shes rdzas su byin gyis brlab //
NK011(da)001:3072: ma h+aa rak+ta kim ni ri ti ma h+aa pany+tsa
NK011(da)001:3073: p+au dza hoh sgrol mchod kyi phyir lid+ga la dgra
NK011(da)001:3074: bgegs dgug gzhug bya ste mchod pa byin gyis brlab
NK011(da)001:3075: pa'i rim pa'o // de yan chad ni sngon 'gro yin la //
NK011(da)001:3077: slob dpon chen pos rtsa ba las /
NK011(da)001:3078: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis chos nyid kyi don gtan la phab /
NK011(da)001:3079: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin gyis khyab pa'i snying rje bskyed /
NK011(da)001:3080: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sems kyi 'bras bu btsal /
NK011(da)001:3081: dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor lngas 'byung ba lnga cha mnyam /
NK011(da)001:3082: b+h+r+aum dang ba dang e las ye shes lha'i bzhugs gnas dang /
NK011(da)001:3086: ting nge 'dzin gsum ni dbyangs dang bcas te don dran bzhin pas /
NK011(da)001:3088: chos rnams stong zhing bdag med pa //
NK011(da)001:3089: nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang nyid las //
NK011(da)001:3090: bde chen spros med thig le che //
NK011(da)001:3091: ma rtogs rang la rang 'khrul pa'i //
NK011(da)001:3092: 'gro drug sems can snying re rje //
NK011(da)001:3093: stong snyid snying rje'i ngang can des //
NK011(da)001:3094: 'gro don rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:3095: rgyu yi rig pa h'u du shar //
NK011(da)001:3097: stong pa chen po'i ngang du gyur //
NK011(da)001:3098: e yam ram kham su kem ba b+h+r+aum /
NK011(da)001:3101: pho brang gzhal yas khang gi gnas //
NK011(da)001:3102: nam mkha' sngo skya gru gsum par //
NK011(da)001:3103: rlung nag rdo rje rgya gram gtams //
NK011(da)001:3104: thams cad 'degs pa'i shugs dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:3106: khrag gi rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrug /
NK011(da)001:3107: zhing chen smug po'i sa gzhi brdal //
NK011(da)001:3108: keng rus chen po'i ri rab la //
NK011(da)001:3109: rdo rje'i brag chen sra ba'i steng //
NK011(da)001:3110: ba las dur khrod rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK011(da)001:3111: dbus su ye shes gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)001:3112: phyogs bcur rgya yongs ma chad pa //
NK011(da)001:3113: phyi dang nang med kun tu nang //
NK011(da)001:3114: rtsig pa pha gu d+r+wa phyed dang //
NK011(da)001:3115: shar bu dang ni mda' yab mdzes //
NK011(da)001:3116: stegs bu 'dod yon lha mos gang //
NK011(da)001:3117: gru chad bzhi dang ldan pa ste //
NK011(da)001:3118: gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs mdzes //
NK011(da)001:3119: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:3120: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi zlas brjod //
NK011(da)001:3121: rgyan rnams kun gyi legs par brgyan //
NK011(da)001:3123: phyi nang gnyis su mi dmigs kyang //
NK011(da)001:3124: 'gag med ye shes rang snang la //
NK011(da)001:3125: nang ni dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)001:3126: thod pa skam rlon rtsig pa la //
NK011(da)001:3127: kun kyang mig nas me 'bar zhing //
NK011(da)001:3128: sna nas dud pa'i sprin phung 'thul //
NK011(da)001:3129: kha nas khrag gi zham chu 'bab //
NK011(da)001:3130: bar mtshams sha chen 'jim zhal byas //
NK011(da)001:3131: sa bdag pho mo'i ka gdan la //
NK011(da)001:3132: mchog chen brgyad kyi ka ba byas //
NK011(da)001:3133: nyi zla 'bar ba'i ka gzhu la //
NK011(da)001:3134: tshangs pa'i gdung bzhi mig mang bris //
NK011(da)001:3135: zhing chen zhing chung gral lcam byas //
NK011(da)001:3136: zhing lpags thog dang bla bres la //
NK011(da)001:3137: rgyu rlon lda ldi don snying 'phyang //
NK011(da)001:3138: keng rus thod tshal d+r+wa bas brgyan //
NK011(da)001:3139: sgo bzhi sbrul nag re gzhi la //
NK011(da)001:3140: nam mkha' lding dang rus sbal gyi //
NK011(da)001:3141: ya them ma them rab tu brjid //
NK011(da)001:3142: chu srin gdug pa'i lcib khung du //
NK011(da)001:3143: zhing gi lpags pas sgo glegs byas //
NK011(da)001:3144: zhing chen rgyal mtshan phyogs bzhir sgreng //
NK011(da)001:3145: g.yang gzhi rlon pa'i ba dan phyar //
NK011(da)001:3146: rgyu ma'i dar dpyangs phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK011(da)001:3147: tsit+ta rlon pa'i tog gis mtshan //
NK011(da)001:3148: ye shes lnga yi me dpung 'bar //
NK011(da)001:3149: rdo rje 'bar ba'i ra bas bskor //
NK011(da)001:3150: 'jigs pa'i dur khrod chen po brgyad //
NK011(da)001:3151: gsar dang rnying pa ro yis gang //
NK011(da)001:3152: ro langs mang po gar byed cing //
NK011(da)001:3153: keng rus me 'bar rgyug cing mchong //
NK011(da)001:3154: gsal shing dag gis phug pa'i ro //
NK011(da)001:3155: shing la dpyangs dang rengs pa dang //
NK011(da)001:3156: rus dang myags dang mes 'tshig dang //
NK011(da)001:3157: mgo dang sha rus lhu dum 'thor //
NK011(da)001:3158: dur bya gshog brdab lce spyang 'khrug /
NK011(da)001:3159: phyogs skyong zhing skyong lha dang klu //
NK011(da)001:3160: 'dre dang sha za srin po dag /
NK011(da)001:3161: 'jigs pa'i ca co cher sgrog cing //
NK011(da)001:3162: me chu shing dang mchod rten sprin //
NK011(da)001:3163: khrag mtsho khol ma dag dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:3164: mkha' 'gro ma yis bdag byas shing //
NK011(da)001:3165: rab 'jigs kun tu skyi g.ya' ba //
NK011(da)001:3166: grub pa'i rnal 'byor rgyu ba'i gnas //
NK011(da)001:3167: 'bar ba brgyad kyis bskor ba yi //
NK011(da)001:3168: dkyil 'khor chen po lhun gyis grub //
NK011(da)001:3169: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+hany+dza dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aam /
NK011(da)001:3170: de dbus mthing nag gru gsum e //
NK011(da)001:3171: zla gam khrag mtsho gsum dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:3173: mu khyud thod pa'i ra bar bcas //
NK011(da)001:3175: thugs ka nas khro bo lcags kyu dang tho ba thogs pa mang po 'phros nas /
NK011(da)001:3177: phyogs skyong rnams kyi snying ga nas lcags kyus bzung /
NK011(da)001:3178: tho bas nyal gyis brdungs nas dbus dang rtsibs bcur bzhag par bsam la /
NK011(da)001:3179: dzah bdag nyid dpal gyi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)001:3181: lha chen dregs pa khyo shugs dang //
NK011(da)001:3182: phyogs skyong 'byung po gdan du bting //
NK011(da)001:3186: ma h+aa de wa dzah u ma de wi dzah
NK011(da)001:3187: brah+ma dzah in+d+ra dzah ag+he dzah ya ma dzah nee
NK011(da)001:3188: ri t+ye dzah wa ru na dzah wa ya we
NK011(da)001:3189: dzah ku bee ra dzah i shwa na dzah b+h+au
NK011(da)001:3190: mi ba ti dzah m+aa ra dzah zhes pas ma
NK011(da)001:3191: h+aa de wa pho mo dbus su gtso bo'i gdan
NK011(da)001:3192: dang / phyogs skyong rnams rtsibs steng du khro bo rnams kyi gdan du bting la /
NK011(da)001:3193: de nas bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)001:3195: cho ga rnam pa gsum gyis bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK011(da)001:3198: chos nyid stong pa'i rang sgra las //
NK011(da)001:3199: rgyu yi ting 'dzin yi ge h'u //
NK011(da)001:3200: rdo rje h'u gis mtshan par gyur //
NK011(da)001:3201: de nyid dbus kyi gdan steng babs //
NK011(da)001:3203: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+nam bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3204: snang stong rdo rje'i chos kyi sku //
NK011(da)001:3205: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK011(da)001:3206: mthing nag dkar dmar 'jigs pa'i zhal //
NK011(da)001:3207: rdo rje rtse dgu rtse lnga dang //
NK011(da)001:3208: me dpung dang ni kha t+w+aam thogs //
NK011(da)001:3209: ri rab brjid pa'i phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:3210: rab 'jigs srin po khros pa'i gzugs //
NK011(da)001:3211: dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:3212: rdo rje'i gshog pa nam mkhar gdengs //
NK011(da)001:3213: dkar dmar ljang nag sbrul chen gyis //
NK011(da)001:3214: dbu rgyan se ral sked chings dang //
NK011(da)001:3215: phyag dang zhabs rnams rnam par spras //
NK011(da)001:3216: dbu la rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:3217: zhabs bzhi dor stabs dregs pa bardzisa //
NK011(da)001:3218: ye shes bskal pa'i me klong bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:3219: gar dgu'i nyams ldan dpa' bo che //
NK011(da)001:3220: thugs kar rang 'dra'i sems dpa' ni //
NK011(da)001:3221: smug nag 'bar ba tshon gang ba'i //
NK011(da)001:3222: thugs kar rdo rje h'u dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:3223: mtha' mar k+ai la ya yis bskor //
NK011(da)001:3224: thugs ni rin chen zur brgyad pa //
NK011(da)001:3225: zla gam gnam sgo gcig pa yi //
NK011(da)001:3226: sgo srung rta mgrin rgyal por gsal //
NK011(da)001:3227: bdag gi phung khams skye mched dang //
NK011(da)001:3228: skra dang ba spu bcas pa kun //
NK011(da)001:3229: rang 'dra'i rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK011(da)001:3230: k+ai la ya yi sgra sgrog cing //
NK011(da)001:3231: go mtshams med par gtams par gyur /
NK011(da)001:3232: tip+ta tsakra ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3235: gzig sham phyag rgya lnga yis spras //
NK011(da)001:3236: thod skam dbu rgyan do shal 'phyang //
NK011(da)001:3237: khro mo'i chas rnams rdzogs par gsal //
NK011(da)001:3239: snod bcud gzhal yas lha ru gyur //
NK011(da)001:3241: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK011(da)001:3242: srid pa rdo rje sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:3245: slar yang thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis //
NK011(da)001:3246: ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs te //
NK011(da)001:3247: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK011(da)001:3248: ye shes khro bo 'grub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:3249: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahmh'u
NK011(da)001:3250: bam hoh zhes pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK011(da)001:3251: rdo rje phur pa'i lha tshogs kyi rnam par byon
NK011(da)001:3252: nas / bcud kyi sems can lha dang lha mor
NK011(da)001:3253: gsal ba de dag la bstim pas snod bcud dag
NK011(da)001:3255: rang gi ye shes spyan drangs pa ni //
NK011(da)001:3257: bdag gi gnas gsum 'bru gsum las //
NK011(da)001:3259: sku gsung thugs kyi lha rnams kun //
NK011(da)001:3260: ma lus spyan drangs thim pa las //
NK011(da)001:3261: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rjer gyur //
NK011(da)001:3263: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK011(da)001:3264: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings las //
NK011(da)001:3265: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NK011(da)001:3266: sku yi dbyig tu bdag bskyed cig /
NK011(da)001:3267: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK011(da)001:3268: de bzhin du sbyar te w+aa ka /
NK011(da)001:3271: yab kyi gsang gnas mi dmigs pad zla nyir //
NK011(da)001:3272: rdo rje h'u dang rwa la 'bru lngas mtshan //
NK011(da)001:3273: yum gyi mkha' gsang nyi zla pad+ma'i steng //
NK011(da)001:3274: gru gsum mthing nag e yis mtshan par gyur //
NK011(da)001:3279: rigs lnga mkha' la spyan drangs te //
NK011(da)001:3280: ma h+aa sarba p+au dza hoh mchod pa chen pos dgyes byas nas //
NK011(da)001:3282: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK011(da)001:3283: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK011(da)001:3284: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK011(da)001:3285: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsol cig /
NK011(da)001:3286: badz+r+ai b+ha wa a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK011(da)001:3287: ye shes chu yis dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:3288: dri ma sbyor ste lud pa las //
NK011(da)001:3289: rigs lnga yab yum he ru kas //
NK011(da)001:3290: dbu la rab tu brgyan par gyur //
NK011(da)001:3291: h'u t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam /
NK011(da)001:3292: sh+r+ai he ru ka kro ti shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK011(da)001:3293: zhes pas bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK011(da)001:3294: gnyis pa phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)001:3296: h'u zung bcus phyogs bcu'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsam /
NK011(da)001:3298: yum gyis sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK011(da)001:3300: yab kyis sa ma ya hoh zhes pa dang /
NK011(da)001:3303: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK011(da)001:3304: byang sems sprin 'phros 'gro rnams bde la bkod //
NK011(da)001:3305: tshur 'dus gdan thog bcu ru thig le bcu //
NK011(da)001:3306: thugs ka'i h'u las h'u yig bsgrigs ma bcu //
NK011(da)001:3307: 'phros nas thig le bcu yi nang du zhugs //
NK011(da)001:3308: khro bcu yab yum sprul par bcas pa gsal //
NK011(da)001:3310: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba las //
NK011(da)001:3311: byung ba'i phyogs bcu'i khro bo ni //
NK011(da)001:3312: thams cad zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NK011(da)001:3313: spyan dgu zhabs kyang bzhi pa ste //
NK011(da)001:3314: dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas kyi brgyan //
NK011(da)001:3315: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis dag gis ni //
NK011(da)001:3316: rdo rje dung dmar dkrug cing gsol //
NK011(da)001:3317: mtha' gnyis ri rib phur pa bsgril //
NK011(da)001:3319: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra h'u /
NK011(da)001:3322: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra zhes pas khro bo yab dang /
NK011(da)001:3324: gardza gardza zhes pas phra men gnyis bskyed la /
NK011(da)001:3325: h'u phata ces pas de dag bskul te gdan la
NK011(da)001:3326: 'khor par bsam pa ste 'og ma rnams la'ang sbyar
NK011(da)001:3327: ro // steng phyogs khro bo h'u mdzad sngo //
NK011(da)001:3328: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar sgra 'byin yum //
NK011(da)001:3329: bar pa phyag gnyis mda' gzhu 'gengs //
NK011(da)001:3330: sprul pa phag dang rtsangs pa'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:3331: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u /
NK011(da)001:3332: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3333: shar phyogs khro bo rnam par rgyal //
NK011(da)001:3334: dkar dmar sngo zhing snyems ma yum //
NK011(da)001:3336: sprul pa stag dang bya rgod mgo //
NK011(da)001:3337: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h'u /
NK011(da)001:3338: da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3339: shar lho khro bo dbyug sngon sngo //
NK011(da)001:3340: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar sder mo yum //
NK011(da)001:3341: bar pa dbyug to me da bal bsnams //
NK011(da)001:3342: sprul pa g.yag dang bya rog mgo //
NK011(da)001:3343: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h'u /
NK011(da)001:3344: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3345: lho ru gshin rjee gshed po mthing //
NK011(da)001:3346: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dur khrod yum //
NK011(da)001:3347: bar pa dgra s+t+wa dbyug to 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3349: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK011(da)001:3351: lho nub khro bo mi g.yo smug /
NK011(da)001:3352: g.yas dkar g.yon ljang gtum khung yum //
NK011(da)001:3353: bar pa ral gri zhags pa 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3354: sprul pa gzig dang khwa ta'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:3355: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai ba h'u /
NK011(da)001:3356: hu lu hu lu h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3357: nub tu khro bo rta mchog dmar //
NK011(da)001:3358: g.yas dkar g.yon mthing gtum mo yum //
NK011(da)001:3359: bar pa ral gri sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3360: sprul pa byi la pu shud mgo //
NK011(da)001:3361: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h'u /
NK011(da)001:3363: nub byang khro bo 'dod rgyal dmar //
NK011(da)001:3364: g.yas dkar g.yon ljang mda' snyems yum //
NK011(da)001:3365: bar pa dbyug to rnga yab 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3366: sprul pa spyang ki khra yi mgo //
NK011(da)001:3367: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da l+ai h'u tshin+d+ha tshin+d+ha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3368: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang //
NK011(da)001:3369: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar rlung 'byin yum //
NK011(da)001:3370: bar pa rgya gram dbyug to 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3371: sprul pa seng ge pha wang mgo //
NK011(da)001:3372: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h'u /
NK011(da)001:3374: byang shar khro bo bgegs 'dul ser //
NK011(da)001:3375: g.yas mthing g.yon ljang gsod byed yum //
NK011(da)001:3376: bar pa rdo rje tri shul 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3377: sprul pa dred dang sre mong mgo //
NK011(da)001:3378: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK011(da)001:3379: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3380: 'og phyogs stobs chen dud kha'i mdog /
NK011(da)001:3381: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar rigs byed yum //
NK011(da)001:3382: bar pa tho ba gtun shing 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3383: sprul pa dom dang byi ba'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:3384: yab rnams cha lugs gtso dang mthun //
NK011(da)001:3385: rang rang yum rnams sku mdog dang //
NK011(da)001:3386: cha lugs gtso mo dag dang mtshungs //
NK011(da)001:3387: phyag mtshan dril bu dung dmar 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3388: sprul pa lcam dral sku mdog ni //
NK011(da)001:3389: g.yas g.yon zhal gyi kha dog 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3390: phyag mtshan sna tshogs phur bu thogs //
NK011(da)001:3391: rngam brjid 'bar ba'i sku ru bskyed //
NK011(da)001:3392: dzah shar gyi sgo ba pu shud mgo //
NK011(da)001:3393: mthing nag g.yas pas lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3395: lho yi sgo ba skya ka'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:3396: ser mo g.yas pas zhags pa 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3398: nub kyi sgo ba srin bya'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:3399: dmar nag g.yas pas lcags sgrog 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3400: hoh byang gi sgo ba khra yi mgo //
NK011(da)001:3401: ljang nag g.yas pas dril bu 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3402: kun kyang g.yon pas phur bu thogs //
NK011(da)001:3403: rgyan dang cha lugs rdzogs par bskyed //
NK011(da)001:3404: de nas dam can 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed de //
NK011(da)001:3405: pho brang gzhal yas phyi rol du //
NK011(da)001:3406: khrag khyams zhing skam gdan steng du //
NK011(da)001:3407: dbang phyug chen po nyi shu brgyad //
NK011(da)001:3408: smug nag ser nag dmar nag dang //
NK011(da)001:3409: ljang nag bdun nyid phyogs bzhir bskyed //
NK011(da)001:3410: khrag khyams phyi rol lha snam gnyis //
NK011(da)001:3411: mi ro rta ros gang ba'i steng //
NK011(da)001:3412: nang ngos phur srung bcu gnyis dang //
NK011(da)001:3413: phyi rol ming po ging rnams gsal //
NK011(da)001:3414: shar sgor dung gi skyes bu dang //
NK011(da)001:3415: lho sgor lcags kyi skyes bu dang //
NK011(da)001:3416: nub sgor bswe yi skyes bu dang //
NK011(da)001:3417: byang sgor ta ki nag po bskyed //
NK011(da)001:3418: gzhan yang bar khyams 'khor yug la //
NK011(da)001:3419: mkha' 'gro chen po sum cu gnyis //
NK011(da)001:3420: ging chen pho mo bco brgyad dang //
NK011(da)001:3421: 'bar ba'i pho nya ma mo bdun //
NK011(da)001:3422: sring bzhi brtan ma bcu gnyis dag /
NK011(da)001:3423: dge bsnyen nyi shu rtsa gcig rnams //
NK011(da)001:3425: de nas phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)001:3427: phrin las rnam bzhi'i phur pas phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor bsam //
NK011(da)001:3429: gzhan gsum logs su blta la /
NK011(da)001:3432: bdag gi thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis //
NK011(da)001:3434: srid gsum gdug pa bkug nas ni //
NK011(da)001:3435: gan rkyal kha sbub bsgyel bar gyur //
NK011(da)001:3436: zhes pas phur gdan e las bskyed la /
NK011(da)001:3437: der dgra bgegs n+ri tri las bskyed de dgug gzhug bya /
NK011(da)001:3438: byin gyis brlab pa la don brgyad de /
NK011(da)001:3439: sku gsum du byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK011(da)001:3440: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lngar byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK011(da)001:3442: thugs ye shes rtse gcig pa dang /
NK011(da)001:3443: rigs so so'i khro bo byin gyis brlab cing dbang bskur ba dang /
NK011(da)001:3444: phur pa bdag nyid chen por byin gyis brlab cing dbang bskur ba dang /
NK011(da)001:3445: bdag nyid chen por yongs su rdzogs par byin gyis brlab cing dbang bskur ba dang /
NK011(da)001:3446: rdzas kyis byin gyis brlab cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK011(da)001:3447: dang po ni don dran bzhin pas /
NK011(da)001:3449: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK011(da)001:3450: byang chub sems kyi phur pa ste //
NK011(da)001:3451: phur pa'i rang bzhin gdon nas dag /
NK011(da)001:3452: blo bral chos kyi sku ru gsal //
NK011(da)001:3454: skye med 'gags pa med pa'i rang rtsal las //
NK011(da)001:3455: h'u las skyes pa'i drag po'i phur pa ste //
NK011(da)001:3456: rgya mdud dang po b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)001:3457: 'bru lnga yongs gyur khrag 'thung rigs lnga la //
NK011(da)001:3458: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod sprin rgya mtshos mchod //
NK011(da)001:3459: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:3461: ji ltar shel la tshon gyis bsgyur ba ltar //
NK011(da)001:3462: longs spyod rdzogs las thugs rjes sprul pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:3463: khro rgyal 'dus pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)001:3464: sku stod khro bo smad phur gshog pa can //
NK011(da)001:3465: kham nag ral pa zur gsum stabs su sgreng //
NK011(da)001:3466: sbrul chen 'jigs pas thod rlon bcings shing spras //
NK011(da)001:3467: spyan gsum sdang mig rab bgrad phyogs bcur gzigs //
NK011(da)001:3468: gtum rngams mche gtsigs me dpung klong na bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:3469: phyag bzhi'i g.yas na s+t+wa re ltag par 'phyar //
NK011(da)001:3470: 'og ma rdo rje ri rab gnon stabs 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3471: kha t+w+aam 'khrol bas khams gsum 'jigs par mdzad //
NK011(da)001:3472: phur bu btab pas ngan song gsum po 'jig /
NK011(da)001:3473: khyod kyi nus mthu stobs dang drag rtsal ni //
NK011(da)001:3474: khro bo thams cad 'dus pa bas kyang che //
NK011(da)001:3475: brtag pa chen po sprul skur byin brlabs pa'i //
NK011(da)001:3476: gnas lngar dpa' bo 'bru lngas mtshan par bsam //
NK011(da)001:3478: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lngar byin gyis rlabs pa'o //
NK011(da)001:3479: yang na de yi spyi mgrin rtse mo ru //
NK011(da)001:3480: dang h+r+aihdang phata kyis mtshan pa las /
NK011(da)001:3482: sku dang gsung dang thugs su byin gyis brlab //
NK011(da)001:3483: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK011(da)001:3484: dbal gsum phata gsum ngos gsum h'u gsum mtshan //
NK011(da)001:3485: thugs rje ye shes rtse mor gcig par brlabs //
NK011(da)001:3486: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis //
NK011(da)001:3487: rigs kyi khro bo thams cad spyan drangs te //
NK011(da)001:3488: ma h+aa p+au dza hoh zhes yid kyis rgyas par mchod nas //
NK011(da)001:3489: mchod pas dgyes mdzod 'di la dbang bskur stsol //
NK011(da)001:3490: h'u t+r+aam trih+aah sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha badz+ra rat+na pad+ma karma a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK011(da)001:3491: de nas rol pa khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK011(da)001:3492: phyogs bcur sprul pa 'phros te tshur 'dus nas //
NK011(da)001:3493: h'u phata 'jigs pa'i gad rgyangs cher sgrog cing //
NK011(da)001:3494: phur pa la thim dbang dang byin rlabs rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:3495: rigs so so'i khro bos dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK011(da)001:3497: bdag nyid rtsa ba'i phyag g.yas ma las nyi steng h'u /
NK011(da)001:3498: g.yon par a las zla steng yi ge +aah g.yas sor lnga la nyi dkyil re re'i steng //
NK011(da)001:3499: h'u t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah mthe bong nas brtsams yig 'bru re rer gsal //
NK011(da)001:3500: g.yon sor lnga la zla dkyil re re la //
NK011(da)001:3502: mthe bong nas brtsams yig 'bru re re gsal //
NK011(da)001:3503: de dag yongs gyur rigs lnga yab yum bcu //
NK011(da)001:3504: sku mdog cha lugs rgyan rnams rdzogs par gyur //
NK011(da)001:3505: de nas thal mo mnyam par sbyar la /
NK011(da)001:3508: sor mo cung zad bsnol la /
NK011(da)001:3510: sor mo rgyab tu bsnol ba bsdams la /
NK011(da)001:3512: phur pa blangs la changs bar bcug /
NK011(da)001:3513: lag pa'i rting pa'i mkhrig ma bsnyal te mtho bong
NK011(da)001:3514: gnyis dang srin lag dang mathe'u chung gi bar du
NK011(da)001:3515: phur pa gzhug / mthe bong cung zad bsgul bas 'dril la /
NK011(da)001:3516: badz+ra a be sha ya a +aa /
NK011(da)001:3517: phyogs bcu dus gsum rgyal sras 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:3518: sngon gyi thugs dam sdong grogs rjes dgongs nas //
NK011(da)001:3519: bu yug 'tshubs ltar gshegs nas phur par thim //
NK011(da)001:3520: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid chen por brlabs //
NK011(da)001:3521: phur pa bdag nyid chen por byin gyis brlabs shing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK011(da)001:3522: de nas sor mo rgyab tu bsnol la /
NK011(da)001:3523: gung mo gnyis gshib nas bsgrengs pa'i bar du phur pa bcug la /
NK011(da)001:3525: de nas sor mo pug pug bor byas la /
NK011(da)001:3526: lag pa'i rting pas phur pa bzung la /
NK011(da)001:3528: de nas sor mo rgyab tu bsnol te mthe bong gshibs nas phur pa bzung ste /
NK011(da)001:3529: tshin+d+ha tshin+d+ha ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3532: bdag nyid che rnams thams cad kyang //
NK011(da)001:3533: gnyis med sbyor ba'i gzi byin rnams //
NK011(da)001:3534: phur pa la ni zhugs pa yis //
NK011(da)001:3535: stong khams gang ba'i me stag 'phros //
NK011(da)001:3536: dmigs pa'i las rnams nges 'grub pa'i //
NK011(da)001:3537: dbang chen ldan par byin gyis brlabs //
NK011(da)001:3538: zhes don dran bzhin pas mdun gyi e steng du bzhugs su gsol /
NK011(da)001:3539: de nas yungs kar rgyal po gtor la /
NK011(da)001:3540: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha tshal pa h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3542: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya d+h+au pe ta li ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3543: gu gul sbyar mas nus pa bskyed //
NK011(da)001:3544: rak+ta rnam pa gsum gtor la /
NK011(da)001:3545: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa
NK011(da)001:3546: la man+da la dgra bgegs m+aa ra ya h'u phata
NK011(da)001:3550: mthing nag gcer bu ral pa can //
NK011(da)001:3551: sku stod khro bo chen po la //
NK011(da)001:3552: lte ba man chad phur pa'i dbal //
NK011(da)001:3554: dbu la rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:3555: thugs la rdo rje gzhon nu 'bar //
NK011(da)001:3556: ye shes me dpung klong na bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:3557: drag por gyur pa'i phur pa ste //
NK011(da)001:3558: btab na lha yang brlag gyur na //
NK011(da)001:3559: gnod byed rnams la smos ci dgos //
NK011(da)001:3560: dgra bgegs snying la k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)001:3564: 'di ni byin rlabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK011(da)001:3565: dgos pa ni dngos grub myur du 'byung ba dang /
NK011(da)001:3567: phrin las myur du 'grub pa dang /
NK011(da)001:3568: bar chad sel nus pa'i phyir gal shin tu che'o //
NK011(da)001:3569: rgyun gyi las byang nar ma la 'dis chog la /
NK011(da)001:3570: lha phur tshang ba'i byin rlabs ni sgom khog tu blta'o //
NK011(da)001:3571: de ni phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK011(da)001:3573: ye shes kyi 'od zer gyis dkyil 'khor gsum la srog ye shes su dbang bskur zhes pas /
NK011(da)001:3575: phur pa rdzas la ni sngar gyi des go chod pas mi dgos la /
NK011(da)001:3576: khro bcu yab yum khra thabs sgo ma dang bcas
NK011(da)001:3577: pa rnams kyi gnas gsum du +aahmh'u dkar dmar mthing
NK011(da)001:3578: gsum bsam zhing / dang po spyan drangs te rtsa ba las /
NK011(da)001:3579: don gyi man ngag gis man ngag gi 'khrugs bsdebs /
NK011(da)001:3581: de yang bdag bskyed gtso 'khor rnams kyi thugs ka'i
NK011(da)001:3582: h'u gi 'od zer gyis rang zhin gyi gnas nas
NK011(da)001:3584: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis
NK011(da)001:3585: bskor ba phur pa'i lha tshogs kyi rnam par spyan
NK011(da)001:3587: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK011(da)001:3588: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:3590: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK011(da)001:3591: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor ba //
NK011(da)001:3592: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK011(da)001:3593: snying po'i dkyil 'khor lhu na gyis rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:3594: srid pa phur par sgrub pa dang //
NK011(da)001:3595: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:3596: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:3597: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:3598: rtags dang mtshan ma ston pa dang //
NK011(da)001:3599: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:3600: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dam tshig pas ye shes pa la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK011(da)001:3601: srid gsum gdug pa 'dul ba dang //
NK011(da)001:3602: nga rgyal zhen pa gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:3603: rdo rje srin po 'khor bcas la //
NK011(da)001:3604: rtse gcig gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:3605: a ti pu hoh pra t+ai ts+tsha hoh zhes phyag bya'o //
NK011(da)001:3606: sh+r+ai badz+ra he ru ka sa pa ri w+aa ra p+aa d+yam pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)001:3608: zhes pas zhabs bsil zhing gdan la bzhugs /
NK011(da)001:3609: ma h+aa p+au dza hoh zhes mchod pa thams cad kyis mchod la /
NK011(da)001:3610: dzahmh'u bam hohs gnyis su med par bstim /
NK011(da)001:3611: bdag gi thugs kyi ye shes las //
NK011(da)001:3612: sprul pa'i rigs lnga he ru ka /
NK011(da)001:3613: bum pa thogs te 'di skad du //
NK011(da)001:3615: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK011(da)001:3616: rje btsun ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:3617: sku gsung thugs su byin rlabs shing //
NK011(da)001:3618: ye shes lnga yi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:3620: 'khor gyi lha rnams thams cad la //
NK011(da)001:3621: gtso bo yis ni dbu brgyan cing //
NK011(da)001:3622: dam can phur srung tshogs rnams la //
NK011(da)001:3623: dbang rtags rdo rjes mtshan par gyur //
NK011(da)001:3625: dag cing dri med mchod yon dam pa dang //
NK011(da)001:3626: me tog bdug spoos snang gsal byug pa dang //
NK011(da)001:3627: zhal zas sgra snyan la sogs mchod pa'i sprin //
NK011(da)001:3628: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa //
NK011(da)001:3629: chos dbyings nam mkha'i khams rnams yongs bkang ste //
NK011(da)001:3630: zag med bde bskyed kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin //
NK011(da)001:3631: srid pa ji srid 'byung bar byin brlabs te //
NK011(da)001:3632: rdo rje phur pa'i dkyil 'khor lha la 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3633: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham sogs kyis mchod /
NK011(da)001:3634: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'dod yon gyi lha mo
NK011(da)001:3635: dpag tu med pa byung ste sa dang nam mkha'i
NK011(da)001:3636: rgya khyon gang bas mchod par bsam la /
NK011(da)001:3638: gzugs kyi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)001:3639: dkar mo mdzes ma me long 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3641: spyan gyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:3642: sgra yi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)001:3643: ser mo dbyangs snyan pi wam 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3645: snyan gyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:3646: dri yi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)001:3647: sngon mo mdzes ma spos phor 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3649: shangs kyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:3650: ro yi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)001:3651: dmar mo mdzes ma zhal zas 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3653: ljags kyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:3654: reg bya'i lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)001:3657: sku yi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:3658: chos kyi lha mo yid 'ong ma //
NK011(da)001:3661: thugs kyi mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:3662: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sa pa ri w+aa ra /
NK011(da)001:3668: d+har+m+aa k+aa ma gu na p+au dza hoh de nas phyag rgya'i mchod pa ni //
NK011(da)001:3669: phyag rgya rnams rim par bsgyur zhing //
NK011(da)001:3671: khrag 'thung rgyal po gar la dgyes //
NK011(da)001:3672: sku mdog zhal ni rab bsgyur zhing //
NK011(da)001:3673: sku yi gar stabs glog 'gyu bas //
NK011(da)001:3674: 'bar ba'i khro bo mnyes bya ste //
NK011(da)001:3675: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3676: zhes lha rnams kyi sku mdog phyag mtshan lam gyis gsal bas rung la /
NK011(da)001:3677: cung zad rgyas par byed na /
NK011(da)001:3679: khro bo rgyal po'i phyag rgya ni //
NK011(da)001:3680: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK011(da)001:3681: mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum pa //
NK011(da)001:3682: rdo rje rtse dgu med dpung 'bar //
NK011(da)001:3683: rdo rje rtse lnga kha t+w+aam ka /
NK011(da)001:3684: tha ma ri rab phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:3685: brkyang bskum gyad kyi dor thabs bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:3686: 'di ni khro bo rgyal po yi //
NK011(da)001:3687: phyag rgya yin par dpa' bos bshad //
NK011(da)001:3688: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK011(da)001:3689: h'u k+aar mthing skya mda' gzhu 'gengs //
NK011(da)001:3691: dbyug sngon dbyug to me dbal bsnams //
NK011(da)001:3692: gshin rje dgra s+t+wa dbyug pa 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3693: mi g.yo ral gri zhags pa thogs //
NK011(da)001:3694: rta mgrin ral gri sbrul zhags bsnams //
NK011(da)001:3695: 'dod rgyal dbyug to rnga yab thogs //
NK011(da)001:3696: bdud rtsi rgya gram dbyug to 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3698: stobs chen tho ba gtun shing 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:3699: kun kyang dang po rdo rje b+han dmar dkrug /
NK011(da)001:3700: g.yas g.yon tha ma ri rab phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:3701: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3702: khro mo yum rnams phyag rgya ni //
NK011(da)001:3703: g.yas pas dril bu gtso la 'khyud //
NK011(da)001:3704: g.yon pas dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK011(da)001:3705: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3706: za byed yab kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK011(da)001:3707: phag gi mgo can rdo rje thogs //
NK011(da)001:3708: g.yon pas drag po'i phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:3709: stag gi mgo can lcags kyu thogs //
NK011(da)001:3710: g.yon pa'i phyag gis phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:3711: g.yag gi mgo can dbyug to thogs //
NK011(da)001:3712: g.yon pa'i phyag gis phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:3713: sha ba'i mgo can rdor dbyug thogs //
NK011(da)001:3714: g.yon pa'i gzigs gi mgo can ral gri thogs //
NK011(da)001:3715: g.yon pa'i byi la'i mgo can pad+ma thogs //
NK011(da)001:3716: g.yon pa'i lce spyang mgo can rdo rje thogs //
NK011(da)001:3717: g.yon pa'i seng ge'i mgo can rgya gram thogs //
NK011(da)001:3718: g.yon pa'i dred kyi mgo can rdo rje thogs //
NK011(da)001:3719: g.yon pa'i dom gyi mgo can tho ba thogs //
NK011(da)001:3720: g.yon pa'i phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3721: gsod byed yum gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK011(da)001:3722: rmig bu'i mgo can dril bu bsnams //
NK011(da)001:3723: g.yon pa'i bya rgod mgo can rnga yab thogs //
NK011(da)001:3724: g.yon pa'i bya rog mgo can me dpung thogs //
NK011(da)001:3725: g.yon pa'i 'ug pa'i mgo can dgra s+t+wa thogs //
NK011(da)001:3726: g.yon pa'i khwa ta'i mgo can zhags pa thogs //
NK011(da)001:3727: g.yon pa'i pu shud mgo can sbrul zhags bsnams //
NK011(da)001:3728: g.yon pa'i khra yi mgo can 'khor lo thogs //
NK011(da)001:3729: g.yon pa'i pha wang mgo can be con thogs //
NK011(da)001:3730: g.yon pa'i sre mong mgo can rtse gsum thogs //
NK011(da)001:3731: g.yon pa'i byi ba'i mgo can gtun shing thogs //
NK011(da)001:3732: g.yon pa'i phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3733: shar gyi sgo ma lcags kyu thogs //
NK011(da)001:3734: lho yi sgo ma zhags pa thogs //
NK011(da)001:3735: nub kyi sgo ma lcags sgrog thogs //
NK011(da)001:3736: byang gi sgo ma dril bu thogs //
NK011(da)001:3737: kun kyang g.yon pas phur pa 'debs //
NK011(da)001:3738: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3739: a la la te mchod pa bzhes //
NK011(da)001:3742: rdo rje phur pa'i lha tshogs la //
NK011(da)001:3744: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK011(da)001:3745: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par mchod //
NK011(da)001:3746: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK011(da)001:3747: a nu r+aa ga ya hoh a nu r+aa ga ya mye /
NK011(da)001:3748: dzahmh'u bam hoh h'u bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK011(da)001:3750: thugs ka nas spros pa'i lha mo ro rdo rje
NK011(da)001:3751: mas thod pa bdud rtsis bkang nas mchod pa byed
NK011(da)001:3753: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK011(da)001:3754: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK011(da)001:3755: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK011(da)001:3756: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK011(da)001:3757: rgyud lnga sems can kun grol phyir //
NK011(da)001:3758: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK011(da)001:3759: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad dang //
NK011(da)001:3760: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen por //
NK011(da)001:3761: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK011(da)001:3762: bzhes nas 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:3763: rgyal ba kun dngos rtsa ba'i bla ma dang //
NK011(da)001:3764: rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad dang //
NK011(da)001:3765: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum la //
NK011(da)001:3766: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3767: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:3768: 'jigs byed chen po khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK011(da)001:3769: za byed gsod byed khra thabs bcu phrag gnyis //
NK011(da)001:3770: pho brang srung ba'i sgo ma bzhi rnams la //
NK011(da)001:3771: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3772: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:3773: las bzhi'i phrin las mdzad pa'i pho brang du //
NK011(da)001:3774: sras mchog phur pa'i lha tshogs thams cad la //
NK011(da)001:3775: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bus //
NK011(da)001:3776: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub rtsol //
NK011(da)001:3777: phyi nang mkha' 'gro 'khor bcas thams cad dang //
NK011(da)001:3778: dam can bcu gnyis ging dang bcas pa dang //
NK011(da)001:3779: ging chen bco brgyad ging phran 'bum rnams dang //
NK011(da)001:3780: dge bsnyen nyer gcig brtan ma bcu gnyis sogs //
NK011(da)001:3781: phur pa'i srung ma zhal bzhes thams cad la //
NK011(da)001:3782: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3783: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:3784: sdom la gnas shing rig 'dzin sgrub ba po //
NK011(da)001:3785: lha dang lha min phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor la //
NK011(da)001:3786: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:3787: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:3788: lce yi dam tshig rdo rje la //
NK011(da)001:3789: rdo rje can gyi h'u bsgoms te //
NK011(da)001:3790: bdud rtsi lnga las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK011(da)001:3791: zos pas dngos grub gsum thob 'gyur //
NK011(da)001:3792: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta sid+d+hi pha la hoh rak+ta 'bul ba ni /
NK011(da)001:3794: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK011(da)001:3795: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK011(da)001:3797: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK011(da)001:3798: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK011(da)001:3801: ma lus bzhes nas bsnams su gsol //
NK011(da)001:3802: sarba dush+tam ru tra m+aa ra ya kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:3804: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK011(da)001:3805: khams gsum ma lus za ba dang //
NK011(da)001:3806: gdul dka' rab tu 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:3807: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK011(da)001:3809: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK011(da)001:3810: 'khor ba'i ra bar chags pa yi //
NK011(da)001:3811: dmar chen khrag gi ar+g+ham la //
NK011(da)001:3813: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sa pa ri w+aa ra /
NK011(da)001:3818: ma h+aa go ro tsa na /
NK011(da)001:3819: ma h+aa kim ni ri ti kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:3820: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh kha kha kha le le le /
NK011(da)001:3821: h'u b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:3824: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:3825: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:3826: bdag nyid chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:3827: sa bdag chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:3828: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:3829: bsgral bar bya ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:3830: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK011(da)001:3831: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i //
NK011(da)001:3832: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK011(da)001:3833: gnod byed gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK011(da)001:3834: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:3835: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:3836: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK011(da)001:3837: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK011(da)001:3838: lus ngag rdul du bshig nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:3839: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK011(da)001:3840: lam h'u lam s+t+wam b+ha ya nan /
NK011(da)001:3841: mo ha g+ha ta ya b+ha ga w+aan /
NK011(da)001:3842: sh+ai kri bi kri badz+ra h'u k+aa ra h'u /
NK011(da)001:3843: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh sarba big+h+n+aam badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3844: bdud dang bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:3845: sdug bsngal sems la mnyam sbyar ba'i //
NK011(da)001:3847: zungs shig chings shig rnam par chings //
NK011(da)001:3848: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:3849: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK011(da)001:3850: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:3851: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:3852: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par gyis //
NK011(da)001:3853: h'u pa ra bid dan tshin+d+ha tshin+d+ha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3856: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3858: t+r+aa sa ya t+r+aa sa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3859: ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra h+r+aihdan+da h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3860: sh+r+ai kri +aa na ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3861: dz+wa la ya dz+wa la ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3862: a be sha ya a be sha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3863: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:3864: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:3865: sngon chad ji ltar khas blangs ba //
NK011(da)001:3866: mngon spyod phrin las tshul bzhin mdzod //
NK011(da)001:3874: ka ta ya ka ta ya /
NK011(da)001:3878: m+aa ra s+ya na pra ma rta na ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3879: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK011(da)001:3880: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK011(da)001:3881: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK011(da)001:3882: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK011(da)001:3883: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)001:3884: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK011(da)001:3885: h'u ma ma pa sham ku ru ma tam nya
NK011(da)001:3886: ka ra i nan d+ha d+hi ma ma sh+r+ai g+h+ram
NK011(da)001:3888: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:3889: zungs shig lha min lha yang rung //
NK011(da)001:3890: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:3891: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par byos //
NK011(da)001:3893: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:3894: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK011(da)001:3895: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK011(da)001:3896: rdo rje me dbal snying bsregs nas //
NK011(da)001:3897: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du brdung //
NK011(da)001:3898: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK011(da)001:3899: rdo rje tho bas brdungs byas nas //
NK011(da)001:3900: lha yang rung ste brlag par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:3901: kha tam kha tam kha tam h'u h'u h'u phata phata phata /
NK011(da)001:3902: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:3903: ha ha h'u h'u phata phata /
NK011(da)001:3904: ces bsgral la gtor mar sbran dmar sbreng //
NK011(da)001:3910: go ro tsa na kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:3912: lha rnams kyi ljags 'od zer gyi sbu gus gtor ma gsol bar bsam zhing /
NK011(da)001:3913: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:3914: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK011(da)001:3915: 'dod pa'i yon tan mang pos rab brgyan te //
NK011(da)001:3916: thugs dam bzhin du ci bder bzhes nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:3917: bdag la dngos grub ma lus stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)001:3918: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka i dam /
NK011(da)001:3924: p+au dza hoh pra t+aits+tsha kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:3926: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:3927: lha thams cad dgyes nas ha ha zhes bzhad /
NK011(da)001:3928: h'u h'u zhes gsungs nas bdag la byin gyis brlabs /
NK011(da)001:3929: phata phata ces gsungs nas dgra bgegs bsgral te chos nyid du gnas spar bar bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:3932: dpal ldan che ba'i che mchog lha yi lha //
NK011(da)001:3933: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK011(da)001:3934: phrin las thams cad rdzogs pa'i dpal chen po //
NK011(da)001:3935: he ru ka dpal khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:3936: 'jigs byed 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK011(da)001:3937: sku gsum rdzogs pa'i khro rgyal phur pa'i lha //
NK011(da)001:3938: srid rtsi'i bdag 'dzin ru tra sde gsum 'dul //
NK011(da)001:3939: rtsal chen phrin las rdzogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:3940: gtum chen brjid pa 'gying zhing sgeg pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:3941: bdud tshogs sde bcas 'dul ba'i dpa' bo che //
NK011(da)001:3942: mi sdug srin po khros 'dra'i cha lugs kyis //
NK011(da)001:3943: srid gsum gdug pa 'dul mdzad khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:3944: bzhad sgra 'brug stong ldir 'dra'i gad rgyangs can //
NK011(da)001:3945: drag shul chen pos ri rab thal bar brlag /
NK011(da)001:3946: 'jigs rung rtsal gyis khams gsum dus gcig sgrol //
NK011(da)001:3947: dpal chen khro bo'i dbang phyug khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)001:3948: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig chen po yis //
NK011(da)001:3949: 'gro kun byang chub snying por 'dren mdzad cing //
NK011(da)001:3950: thugs rje'i dbyings nas khros pa'i rngams stabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:3951: 'khor ba gtan nas rlag byed khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)001:3952: gdug can drag pos 'dul bar nyer dgongs nas //
NK011(da)001:3953: 'bar ba'i khro tshul du ma'i gar mdzad kyang //
NK011(da)001:3954: chos dbyings zhi ba'i ngang las mi g.yo ba //
NK011(da)001:3955: dpal chen mngon rdzogs rgyal po khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)001:3956: nam mkha'i khams kun yongs su khyab pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:3957: gling bzhi ri rab nyi zla gza' skar yang //
NK011(da)001:3958: sku yi rgyan du che ba'i dpal chen po //
NK011(da)001:3959: che btsan 'gran zla bral ba khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)001:3960: gnyen po ye shes gzhom gzhig mi mnga' bas //
NK011(da)001:3961: nyon mongs rtog pa'i bdud tshogs tshar gcod phyir //
NK011(da)001:3962: phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse dgu 'phyar ba yis //
NK011(da)001:3963: ri rab chen po kun kyang thal bar rlog /
NK011(da)001:3964: bdud dang 'byung po kun gyi klad pa 'gems //
NK011(da)001:3965: srid pa'i 'gong po spun dgu rdung du rlog /
NK011(da)001:3966: 'gro rnams theg pa dgu yi lam la 'dren //
NK011(da)001:3967: bar pa rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams pa yis //
NK011(da)001:3968: nyon mongs dug lnga gtan nas brlag byed cing //
NK011(da)001:3969: don dam spros med byang sems rnam pa lngas //
NK011(da)001:3970: rgyud lnga'i sems can thar pa'i lam la sbyor //
NK011(da)001:3971: bdud dang dam sri nag po'i phyogs rnams kun //
NK011(da)001:3972: kun tu bsdigs shing thal bar brlag bya'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:3973: dus mtha'i me ltar rab tu cher 'bar ba'i //
NK011(da)001:3974: ye shes med dpung 'bar ba'i sdigs mdzub gdengs //
NK011(da)001:3975: srid gsum gdug pa mtha' dag tshar bcad nas //
NK011(da)001:3976: dug gsum sku gsung thugs su sgrol byed cing //
NK011(da)001:3977: 'khor ba'i g.yul ngo gtan nas pham mdzad pa'i //
NK011(da)001:3978: dpa' bo rgyal rtags kha t+w+aam rtse gsum thogs //
NK011(da)001:3979: khro rgyal ma lus 'dus pa'i rtsal 'chang zhing //
NK011(da)001:3980: mi bzad stong khams bsreg pa'i me stag 'phro //
NK011(da)001:3981: btab na ye shes lha yang thal bar rlog /
NK011(da)001:3982: 'bar ba'i phreng ba 'khrigs pa'i 'od zer can //
NK011(da)001:3983: ri rab brjid pa'i phur pa drag tu 'dril //
NK011(da)001:3984: khams gsum yongs sgrol dpa' bo che la bstod //
NK011(da)001:3985: gar gyi dbang phyug rnam par 'gyur ba'i sku //
NK011(da)001:3986: dpal dang dur khrod chas rnams yongs rdzogs shig /
NK011(da)001:3987: zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum gyad kyi dor stobs kyis //
NK011(da)001:3988: dregs pa lha chen gnon mdzad khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)001:3990: mche ba zangs yag gtsigs pa'i za byed che //
NK011(da)001:3992: khro gnyer glog stong 'khyug 'dra'i rngams stabs can //
NK011(da)001:3993: mi bzad sku yi dngos po shin tu 'gyur //
NK011(da)001:3994: rngams pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir ba bzhin //
NK011(da)001:3995: thug chom ri rab 'bum phrag bsnyil ba'i skad //
NK011(da)001:3996: gad rgyangs drag pos 'jig rten g.yo zhing 'degs //
NK011(da)001:3997: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung kun tu g.yengs ba che //
NK011(da)001:3998: hoh khro bo shes rab ye shes me bo che //
NK011(da)001:3999: ye shes chen po'i 'od zer kun tu gsal //
NK011(da)001:4000: 'bar ba'i ye shes ma rig mun pa 'joms //
NK011(da)001:4001: snying po ye shes sna tshogs thig le che //
NK011(da)001:4002: hoh ye shes dkyil 'khor khro bo'i sprin chen po //
NK011(da)001:4003: 'phros pas dkyil 'khor kun gyi char chen 'bebs //
NK011(da)001:4004: phyogs bcu'i dkyil 'khor yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK011(da)001:4005: rnam pa sna tshogs ye shes thig le che //
NK011(da)001:4006: hoh bdud rnams kun gyi bdud de bdud chen po //
NK011(da)001:4007: 'jigs byed 'jigs pa'i tshogs kyang 'jigs par byed //
NK011(da)001:4008: srid zhi'i 'ching ba thams cad 'joms mdzad pa //
NK011(da)001:4009: dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:4011: 'jigs pa'i btsun mo 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma //
NK011(da)001:4012: kun tu bzang mo dkyil 'khor kun gyi yum //
NK011(da)001:4013: gdug pa 'dul phyir srin mo khros pa'i gzugs //
NK011(da)001:4014: srid pa'i 'khor lo ye shes rgya yis 'debs //
NK011(da)001:4015: gnyis med don ldan yab la dgyes par 'khril //
NK011(da)001:4016: phyag g.yas 'khor los bdud kyi mgo lus gshog /
NK011(da)001:4017: g.yon pas thod khrag 'khor 'das dbang du sdud //
NK011(da)001:4018: 'jigs pa'i sku la phyag rgya lnga yis spras //
NK011(da)001:4019: drag po'i nga ros 'jig rten g.yo zhing 'khrugs //
NK011(da)001:4020: rgyud lnga'i sems can thugs rjes dbyings su sgrol //
NK011(da)001:4021: srid gsum gdug pa'i tshogs rnams thal bar rlog /
NK011(da)001:4022: mkha' 'gro yongs kyi gtso mo khyod la bstod //
NK011(da)001:4024: phyogs bcu dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan steng na //
NK011(da)001:4025: ye shes bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i sku //
NK011(da)001:4026: 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i khro rgyal chen po bcu //
NK011(da)001:4027: mi dge bcu spangs dge bcu rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:4028: kun kyang zhal gsum phyag drug gtum la rngams //
NK011(da)001:4029: phyogs skyong dregs pa pho mo thams cad 'dul //
NK011(da)001:4030: dbu skra ral pa srid pa'i rtse mor 'bar //
NK011(da)001:4031: mi sdug khro gnyer smin mtshams g.yo ba can //
NK011(da)001:4032: spyan gsum dmar zlum sdang mig phyogs bcur gzigs //
NK011(da)001:4033: log par lta ba rtsad nas gcod cing sgrol //
NK011(da)001:4034: mche ba zangs yag skye shi rtsad nas gcod //
NK011(da)001:4035: gdug pa 'dul mdzad 'bar ba'i phyag mtshan bsnams //
NK011(da)001:4036: dur khrod chas brgyad sku yi rgyan du che //
NK011(da)001:4037: rdo rje rin chen gshog pa nam mkhar gdengs //
NK011(da)001:4038: rngams pa'i zhal gdangs ljags 'dril rkan sgra rdeb //
NK011(da)001:4039: kun kyang phur pa 'dril zhing phyogs bcur 'debs //
NK011(da)001:4040: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med yum dang 'khril //
NK011(da)001:4041: g.yas g.yon dag tu sprul pa'i khra thabs ni //
NK011(da)001:4042: mgo brnyan mche gshog rdzu 'phrul mthu stobs ldan //
NK011(da)001:4043: 'bar ba'i khro rgyal ma bcos rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:4044: sgra las 'das pa grags stong h'u sgra gsung //
NK011(da)001:4045: bsam dang bral ba sgrol byed snying po'i ngang //
NK011(da)001:4046: yon tan phrin las thams cad rdzogs pa'i dpal //
NK011(da)001:4047: sprul pa chen po'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:4049: gnyis med sku la 'khril ba'i gzungs mchog ma //
NK011(da)001:4050: rngams brjid 'jigs pa khro mo'i cha lugs can //
NK011(da)001:4051: pha rol phyin pa bcu yi ngo bo nyid //
NK011(da)001:4052: bdud 'dul yum gyi tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:4054: rdo rje gdong mo pho nya mgyogs ma bzhi //
NK011(da)001:4055: dgra bgegs gdug pa 'gug 'ching sdom zhing rdeg /
NK011(da)001:4056: shar lho nub byang sgo srung drag shul can //
NK011(da)001:4057: sgo ma chen mo bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:4059: mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:4060: dpal gyi sras mchog 'jigs byed k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)001:4061: mthing nag khros pa zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa //
NK011(da)001:4062: phyag g.yas dang pos s+t+wa re ltag par 'phyar //
NK011(da)001:4063: 'og mas rdo rje ri rab gnon stabs 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:4064: g.yon pa'i phyag na kha t+w+aam ga 'khrol zhing //
NK011(da)001:4065: 'og mas phur bu dgra bgegs snying la 'debs //
NK011(da)001:4066: rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan thugs srog h'u du 'bar //
NK011(da)001:4067: snyan nas 'brug sgrog spyan nas me 'od 'phro //
NK011(da)001:4068: shangs nas rlung 'tshubs zhal nas thog ser 'bebs //
NK011(da)001:4069: mche ba gtsigs shing ag tshom me ltar 'bar //
NK011(da)001:4070: khyod kyi lte ba man chad chas rnams ni //
NK011(da)001:4071: lcags phur zur gsum me stag phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK011(da)001:4072: dgra bgegs gdug pa'i tshogs rnams skad cig sgrol //
NK011(da)001:4073: mi g.yo che mchog sku gsung thugs kyi ngang //
NK011(da)001:4074: khro rgyal 'dus pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)001:4075: srid par 'khyams pa'i sems can thams cad kun //
NK011(da)001:4076: thabs kyis bsgral ba'i skal dang mi ldan yang //
NK011(da)001:4077: shugs kyis sgrol ba'i phrin las mdzad slad du //
NK011(da)001:4078: dbyer med sku gsung thugs su sgrol mdzad pa //
NK011(da)001:4079: sras mchog k+ai la ya la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:4082: sgrub thabs ltar 'phro 'du'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pas /
NK011(da)001:4083: gtso bo la stong rtsa brgyad dang //
NK011(da)001:4085: srung ma la nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK011(da)001:4086: dbang mo la b+h+yo bdun phrag bzhi sogs ci rigs bzlas so //
NK011(da)001:4087: de nas skabs 'gar pho nya 'gug 'dren gyi 'phyong gtong bar 'dod na /
NK011(da)001:4089: steng gi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs 'gug pa //
NK011(da)001:4090: h'u mdzad sgra 'byin phag dang rmig bu'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:4091: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NK011(da)001:4092: steng gi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs drongs shig /
NK011(da)001:4094: shar gyi phyogs nas dgra dang rnam rgyal snyems ma stag dang bya rgod mgo //
NK011(da)001:4095: dbu gsum phyag drug shar gyi phyogs nas dgra lho
NK011(da)001:4096: yi phyogs nas gshin rje dur khrod sha ba 'ug
NK011(da)001:4097: pa'i mgo // dbu gsum phyag drug lho yi phyogs
NK011(da)001:4098: nas dgra nub kyi phyogs rta mgrin gtum mo byi
NK011(da)001:4100: dbu gsum phyag nub kyi byang gi bdud rtsi rlung 'byin seng ge pha wang mgo //
NK011(da)001:4101: dbu gsum byang gi shar lho mtshams dbyug sngon sder mo g.yag dang bya rog mgo //
NK011(da)001:4102: dbu gsum shar lho lho nub mtshams mi g.yo gtun khung gzig dang khwa ta'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:4104: lho nub nub byang mtshams 'dod rgyal mda' snyems spyang ki khra yi mgo //
NK011(da)001:4105: dbu gsum nub byang byang shar mtshams bgegs 'dul gsod byed dred dang sre mong mgo //
NK011(da)001:4106: dbu gsum byang shar 'og gi phyogs nas stobs chen bskyod byed dom dang byi ba'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:4107: dbu gsum 'og gi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs drongs shig /
NK011(da)001:4108: shar gyi sgo ba pu shud mgo bo can //
NK011(da)001:4109: dam nyams dgra bgegs lcags kyus 'debs shing 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:4110: shar gyi phyogs kyi dgra dang bgegs drongs shig /
NK011(da)001:4111: lho yi sgo ba skya ka'i mgo bo can //
NK011(da)001:4112: dam nyams dgra bgegs zhags pas 'ching bar byed //
NK011(da)001:4113: lho yi nub kyi sgo ba srin bya'i mgo bo can //
NK011(da)001:4114: dam nyams dgra bgegs sgrog gis sdom par byed //
NK011(da)001:4115: nub byang gi sgo ba khra yi mgo bo can //
NK011(da)001:4116: dam nyams dgra bgegs dril bus myos shing 'phul //
NK011(da)001:4117: byang gi phyogs kyi dgra dang bgegs drongs shig /
NK011(da)001:4119: tshogs byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK011(da)001:4120: bdud rtsi tshogs la gtor la /
NK011(da)001:4121: bdud rtsi'i zer las khro bo spros te bgegs bskrad cing /
NK011(da)001:4122: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4123: bi shud+d+he a mri te h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4124: d+harma a mri te h'u phata kyis bsang /
NK011(da)001:4126: tshogs kyi yo byad rnams kyi steng //
NK011(da)001:4127: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor h'u mthing mtshan //
NK011(da)001:4128: de gnyis 'od zhu thim pa las //
NK011(da)001:4129: dag pa chos dbyings ngang du brlab //
NK011(da)001:4131: pad+ma'i steng du am dmar po //
NK011(da)001:4132: 'od zhu thim pas bdud rtsir gyur //
NK011(da)001:4135: 'dod yon lnga yis gang bar gyur //
NK011(da)001:4138: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro dang //
NK011(da)001:4139: rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum sras //
NK011(da)001:4140: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas pa //
NK011(da)001:4141: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:4142: lha dang lha min rnal 'byor pa //
NK011(da)001:4143: thugs dang mthad pa'i gnas mchog 'dir //
NK011(da)001:4144: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4145: kun bzang mchod sprin rol par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4146: dam tshig bzhin du ci bder bzhes //
NK011(da)001:4147: ma h+aa sarba p+au dza hoh h'u /
NK011(da)001:4148: phyogs bcu dus gsum rgyal ba mchod pa dang //
NK011(da)001:4149: rnal 'byor dbang phyug thugs dam bskang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:4150: sgo gsum g.yo sgyu med cing gus ldan pas //
NK011(da)001:4151: yo ga gsang ba'i mchod pa'i rnam grangs 'bum //
NK011(da)001:4152: snang srid chos dang rgyal srid rin po che //
NK011(da)001:4153: phyag rgya bzhi dang nyon mongs rnam pa lnga //
NK011(da)001:4154: ting 'dzin chos dang bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NK011(da)001:4155: 'dod pa'i yon tan mang po glu dang gar //
NK011(da)001:4156: rtog med don gyi mchod pa la sogs 'bul //
NK011(da)001:4157: pho brang bzhugs gnas zhing khams thams cad du //
NK011(da)001:4158: mchod pa'i sprin gyis gtibs shing rgyas gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:4159: snang srid tshogs kyi mchod par bsngo ba ni //
NK011(da)001:4161: ye shes khro bo rol pa'i zhal chen por //
NK011(da)001:4162: snod bcud ma lus mchod pa chen por sbyor //
NK011(da)001:4163: dbyings dang ye shes rol pa'i mchod pa ru //
NK011(da)001:4164: so sor phyes te snod bcud mchod par 'bul //
NK011(da)001:4165: kun tu dbyer med pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK011(da)001:4167: rgyal ba ma lus ye shes khro bo'i sku //
NK011(da)001:4168: dwangs snyigs mi phyed gnyis med mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK011(da)001:4169: dug gsum skyon bral dbyings kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:4170: 'du 'bral med pa srid gsum mchod par rol //
NK011(da)001:4171: thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi mchod pa ni /
NK011(da)001:4172: mtha' dang dbus med mnyam pa'i mchod pa ni //
NK011(da)001:4173: nga dang bdag med mkha' ltar dag pa yi //
NK011(da)001:4174: ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:4175: gnyis med bde chen mnyam pa'i mchod par rol //
NK011(da)001:4177: snying po byang chub rol pa longs spyod sprul pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:4178: 'dod pa'i yon tan lha mo'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:4179: snang srid ma lus 'dod rgur bsgyur byas te //
NK011(da)001:4180: mkha' ltar dag pa'i dbyings su ye shes rol //
NK011(da)001:4181: de nas tshogs gsum du bcad la //
NK011(da)001:4184: rang byung ma bcos dbyibs dang kha dog bral //
NK011(da)001:4185: rnam par rtog pa'i nyon mongs cir snang yang //
NK011(da)001:4186: gdod nas dag pas 'khor ba dbyings su rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:4187: ye shes khro rgyal thugs dam bskang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:4188: khams gsum ma lus 'dus pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:4189: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs zhal du bstab po bzhes //
NK011(da)001:4190: bla ma rig 'dzin yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' /
NK011(da)001:4191: dpa' bo mkha' 'gro dam can srung mi'i tshogs dang
NK011(da)001:4192: bcas pa thams cad kyi zhal du ma h+aa ga
NK011(da)001:4194: ma h+aa dza gad kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:4195: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK011(da)001:4200: ma h+aa kim ni ri ti /
NK011(da)001:4201: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:4202: ma h+aa sarba p+au dza hoh bar pa bshags pa ni /
NK011(da)001:4203: thog med dus nas da lta thug gi bar //
NK011(da)001:4204: ma rig dbang gis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK011(da)001:4205: lus kyis sdig byas spyod pa ngan du spyad //
NK011(da)001:4206: ngag gis tshig 'khyal smra ba ngan du brjod //
NK011(da)001:4207: sems kyi bloo nor log par bsam la sogs //
NK011(da)001:4208: 'dod khro gti mug dbang gis nongs bgyis pa //
NK011(da)001:4209: bkra ba'i lha tshogs rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK011(da)001:4210: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK011(da)001:4211: de yi 'khor du gtogs pa'i dam can rnams //
NK011(da)001:4212: mi yi skyon mthong tsam na chad pas gcod //
NK011(da)001:4213: 'gal 'khrul nongs pa ci mchis mthol lo bshags //
NK011(da)001:4214: bzod par bzhes nas tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)001:4215: zhes pa dang yi ge brgya pa tshul bzhin bzlas so //
NK011(da)001:4217: lid+ga la dgra bgegs dgug gzhug byas la /
NK011(da)001:4220: bco lnga la sogs pa mdun du bkod la /
NK011(da)001:4221: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra la sogs pa'i sngags kyis spyi bor h'u k+aa ra /
NK011(da)001:4222: rgya mdud gong ma la phyogs kyi khro bo /
NK011(da)001:4223: 'og ma la mtshams kyi khro bo /
NK011(da)001:4225: chu srin kha la stobs po che /
NK011(da)001:4226: dbal la dam can bskyed la /
NK011(da)001:4227: de rnams kyi gnas gsum gyi yi ge gsum las 'od 'phros /
NK011(da)001:4229: mchod pas mchod la bstim zhing /
NK011(da)001:4231: rdo rje thal mos phur pa 'dril zhing dpral bar bzung la /
NK011(da)001:4232: ha na ha na tip+ta tsakra /
NK011(da)001:4234: sh+r+ai badz+ra k+ai la ya +aah snying gar bzung la /
NK011(da)001:4235: badz+ra sat+wa r+aa dza h'u gis rim pa bzhin du
NK011(da)001:4236: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi sgo nas khams gsum
NK011(da)001:4237: sgrol ba'i mthu dang ldan par bsam la /
NK011(da)001:4238: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya be ta li man+da la rak+sha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4239: phur pa la yungs kar gtor zhing mthu dang ldan par bsam /
NK011(da)001:4241: ma gu ta la pra ta la ash+thi ma h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4242: gu gul gyis bdug cing gzi mdangs dang ldan par bsam /
NK011(da)001:4244: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4245: rak+ta gtor la chags pa dang ldan par bsam /
NK011(da)001:4246: de nas dkyil 'khor gsum dang dam can gyi bstod bskul rgyas bsdus gang rigs bya /
NK011(da)001:4247: de nas pho nya 'gug pa'i 'phyong btang /
NK011(da)001:4248: gser skyems sngags drug phyag drug gis byin gyis brlabs la /
NK011(da)001:4249: hoh bdud rtsi phud kyi mchod pa 'di 'bul zhing bsngo ba'i gnas su gyur pa ni /
NK011(da)001:4250: kun tu bzang po nas rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar
NK011(da)001:4251: gyi rtsa brgyud bla ma rnams kyi zhal du +aahmh'u
NK011(da)001:4252: / sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum gyi zhal du +aahmh'u /
NK011(da)001:4253: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas /
NK011(da)001:4254: yab dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu /
NK011(da)001:4256: 'jigs pa'i khro bo yab yum nyi shu /
NK011(da)001:4257: sprul pa stag gi mgo can la sogs pa mche ba can gyi tshogs /
NK011(da)001:4258: bya rgod kyi mgo can la sogs pa'i gshog pa can gyi tshogs /
NK011(da)001:4262: ging chen dge bsnyen rnams kyi zhal du gzhan yang zhi ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK011(da)001:4263: 'bar ba khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK011(da)001:4278: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin rnams kyi zhal du gzhan yang bya ba'i rgyud /
NK011(da)001:4281: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud la sogs pa
NK011(da)001:4282: gsang sngags rig sngags gzungs sngags snying po phyag rgya'i
NK011(da)001:4283: lha tshogs rnams kyi zhal du mi mthun pa'i phyogs
NK011(da)001:4285: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK011(da)001:4286: gzhan yang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi mgon po sogs dang /
NK011(da)001:4293: rgyal chen sde bzhi la sogs pa mgon po bdun
NK011(da)001:4294: cu rtsa lnga'i zhal du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NK011(da)001:4295: srungs shig / dkon mchog gi dbu 'phang bstod cig /
NK011(da)001:4296: khyad par du yang bstan pa spyi'i dgra /
NK011(da)001:4298: dam tshig can gyi sdang dgra /
NK011(da)001:4300: sems can yongs la 'tshe ba'i dgra bgegs gdug pa can 'di bsgral ba'i phrin las mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:4301: gzhan yang sde brgyad sde bcu gzhi bdag sogs kyi
NK011(da)001:4302: zhal du khyed rnams la phur pa'i dbal mi ston
NK011(da)001:4305: drag po'i pho nya mi 'gyed pas /
NK011(da)001:4306: mtho ba rnams ko long dang phrag dog ma byed /
NK011(da)001:4307: dma' ba rnams ma 'jigs ma skrag par rang rang so so'i gnas su 'dug la /
NK011(da)001:4308: rnal 'byor pa'i sdong grogs gyis la dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:4309: mthu dang stobs med na chos thams cad bsam pa'i
NK011(da)001:4310: khyad par yin pas bsam pa byang chub kyi sems
NK011(da)001:4312: gzhan yang khams gsum rigs drug gi sems can thams cad la bsngo'o //
NK011(da)001:4314: bar 'dir gzu dpang bya ba ni logs su gsal lo //
NK011(da)001:4315: de nas dngos gzhi sprul pa spro ba ni /
NK011(da)001:4316: h'u bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata ha la ha la h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4317: bdag gi thugs las 'phros pa'i pho nya ni //
NK011(da)001:4318: khro bo 'chol ba dpag tu med pa byung //
NK011(da)001:4319: srid pas gar khyab gnam sa bar snang kun //
NK011(da)001:4320: ras bal rlung gis gtor bzhin khyab par gyur //
NK011(da)001:4324: gab pa'i sngags drug gis bsad pa'i las bya /
NK011(da)001:4325: sbas pa'i 'phyong drug gis drag po'i las gzhung bsrang /
NK011(da)001:4326: tshe lung dang khrus lung gis dgongs pa phul du byung /
NK011(da)001:4327: gnod pa'i dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK011(da)001:4328: phur pa btab la khams gsum dus gcig tu bsgral ba'i mchod pa bya /
NK011(da)001:4329: ye shes kyi lha dgyes pa bskyed ba'i phyir /
NK011(da)001:4330: kha t+w+aam gyi phyag rgyas sha khrag zhal du bstab
NK011(da)001:4331: cing kho'i rnam shes bdag la bsdus la skur 'don
NK011(da)001:4332: / byang chub kyi sems rnam pa gsum bcas bskyed rdzogs rnam gsum gyis dgra bgegs gnas bstab /
NK011(da)001:4333: don chos nyid las mi 'da' ba'i phyir /
NK011(da)001:4334: chos nyid kyi bden pa bdar /
NK011(da)001:4336: dang po ngan sngags drug gis dgug gzhug bya ba ni drug ste /
NK011(da)001:4337: rdzas dang lha dang smon lam dang //
NK011(da)001:4338: bskul dang sngags dang ting 'dzin te //
NK011(da)001:4339: kun la 'dres te sum cu drug /
NK011(da)001:4340: ces pas dang po rdzas ni gu gul gyis bdug
NK011(da)001:4341: cing lha mo'am sras mchog gang rung 'don pa bsgyur
NK011(da)001:4343: sras mchog gu gul phyag na bsnams //
NK011(da)001:4344: dgra bgegs 'go ba'i lha dang phrol //
NK011(da)001:4345: skyob pa'i grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:4346: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4347: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4348: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4349: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4350: bdag nyid chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4351: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4352: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4353: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4354: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK011(da)001:4355: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK011(da)001:4356: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK011(da)001:4357: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK011(da)001:4358: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:4359: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)001:4360: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK011(da)001:4361: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:4362: dzahmh'u bam hoh mo ha ga ya /
NK011(da)001:4363: che ge mo ha sa ya ra ha sa ya ra /
NK011(da)001:4365: m+aa ra se nya pra mar+d+ha na ye sarba big+h+n+aam bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4366: sras mchog de yi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)001:4367: rang 'dra dpag med thon nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:4368: gu gul sbyar ma'i dud sprin gyis //
NK011(da)001:4369: dgra bgegs 'go ba'i lha kun byer //
NK011(da)001:4370: kho rang gcig pur 'khyams par gyur //
NK011(da)001:4371: gnyis pa gzugs la dbab pa la drug las /
NK011(da)001:4372: rdzas ni lcags kyu thogs pa'am phyag rgya bcas la /
NK011(da)001:4374: sras mchog phyag na lcags kyu thogs //
NK011(da)001:4375: dgra bgegs rnam shes rten la phob //
NK011(da)001:4377: rdo rje gsang ba'i sogs tshig drug gi mjug tu /
NK011(da)001:4378: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:4379: tri yam dzah n+ri yam dzah badz+ra k+ai li k+ai
NK011(da)001:4380: la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh mo ha ga ya ch+gee
NK011(da)001:4381: mo sh+ai kri ka ra ya m+aa ra se na
NK011(da)001:4382: pra mar+d+ha na ye sarba big+h+n+aam bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4383: sras mchog de yi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)001:4384: rang 'dra dpag med thon nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:4385: h'u dang phata kyi sgra sgrog cing //
NK011(da)001:4386: lcags kyus bzung zhing mtshon chas bsdigs //
NK011(da)001:4387: skad cig yud la bkug nas bstim //
NK011(da)001:4390: gsum pa byang du gzhug pa la drug gi dang po rdzas ni tshon skud thogs la /
NK011(da)001:4392: sras mchog phyag na zhags pa thogs //
NK011(da)001:4393: dgra bgegs lus ngag dam du sdom //
NK011(da)001:4394: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4395: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4396: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4397: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4398: bdag nyid chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4399: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4400: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4402: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK011(da)001:4403: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK011(da)001:4404: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK011(da)001:4405: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK011(da)001:4406: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:4407: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)001:4408: zugs shig chings shig rnam par sdoms //
NK011(da)001:4409: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ch+gee mo sh+ai kri a na ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4410: sras mchog de yi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)001:4411: rang 'dra dpag med thon nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:4412: nyams pa'i dgra bgegs lus kyi cha //
NK011(da)001:4413: gru gu thul du bcings par gyur //
NK011(da)001:4414: bzhi pa smyo ru gzhug pa la drug gi dang po rdzas ni dug thun thogs la /
NK011(da)001:4416: sras mchog phyag na dug thun thogs //
NK011(da)001:4417: dgra bgegs smyo zhing 'bog tu chug /
NK011(da)001:4420: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK011(da)001:4421: badz+ra ka li ki la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh mo ha ga ya ch+gee mo dz+wa la pa ya /
NK011(da)001:4422: dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4423: dgra bgegs smyo zhing 'bog nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:4424: ci byas thol thol smra bar gyur //
NK011(da)001:4425: lnga pa brdung ba la drug gi dang po rdzas ni tho gtun thogs la /
NK011(da)001:4426: h'u sras mchog phyag na tho ba thogs //
NK011(da)001:4427: dgra bgegs lus ngag rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:4430: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du brdung //
NK011(da)001:4431: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh mo
NK011(da)001:4432: ha ga ya ch+gee mo ta th+aa ya ta th+aa
NK011(da)001:4433: ya h'u phata / sras mchog tho ba thogs pa yis //
NK011(da)001:4434: dgra bgegs nyil nyil 'dres par brdung //
NK011(da)001:4435: drug pa rdul du byas la 'bul ba ni /
NK011(da)001:4436: phur gdab byas pa'i rjes su 'brel bas 'og tu ston no //
NK011(da)001:4437: bsgral ba dngos la drug gi /
NK011(da)001:4438: dang po kun gzhi rtsad nas bcad de bsgral ba dang /
NK011(da)001:4439: nyon mongs pa skye ba'i sgo lnga dag par bsgral ba dang /
NK011(da)001:4440: tshogs brgyad dag par bsgral ba dang /
NK011(da)001:4441: dge sdig cha mnyam du bsgral ba dang /
NK011(da)001:4442: ma bdud kyi dmod pas bsgral ba dang /
NK011(da)001:4443: gtun du brdung ste bsgral ba dang drug go //
NK011(da)001:4445: bdag nyid gsal ba gsum dang ldan pas /
NK011(da)001:4446: bstod bskul nas dgug gzhug gi bar byed pa de phyag srol la 'dug pas slar yang bya zhing /
NK011(da)001:4447: rngam stabs 'chams tshul brub 'chams ltar rdzogs par byas la /
NK011(da)001:4450: srid pa phur par bsgrub pa dang //
NK011(da)001:4451: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:4452: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4453: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:4454: rtags dang mtshan ma ston pa dang //
NK011(da)001:4455: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:4457: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK011(da)001:4458: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i //
NK011(da)001:4459: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK011(da)001:4460: gnod byed gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK011(da)001:4461: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:4462: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:4463: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK011(da)001:4464: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK011(da)001:4465: lus ngag rdul du bshig nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:4466: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4467: lam h'u lam s+t+wam b+ha ya n+aam mo ha ga ta ya b+ha ga w+aan /
NK011(da)001:4468: sh+ai kri bi kri badz+ra h'u k+aa ra h'u h'u phata phata /
NK011(da)001:4469: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh sarba big+h+n+aam /
NK011(da)001:4470: badz+ra k+ai la ya h'u h'u phata phata badz+ra h'u k+aa ra h'u a /
NK011(da)001:4471: zhes phur pa snying gar btab /
NK011(da)001:4472: yod na byabs phur gyis kyang btab cing /
NK011(da)001:4473: sdigs phur gyis btab la bsdig /
NK011(da)001:4474: dbang phur btab nas dbang du byas /
NK011(da)001:4476: de nas tshe lung khrus lung gi dgongs pa ni /
NK011(da)001:4478: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi gnas gsum a dkar las //
NK011(da)001:4479: a dkar 'od zer phra mo grangs med 'phros //
NK011(da)001:4480: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad spyan drangs te //
NK011(da)001:4481: a yi rang bzhin nyid du thams cad zhu //
NK011(da)001:4482: bdag dang khro bo phur pa la thim pas //
NK011(da)001:4483: lus ngag yid kyi shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK011(da)001:4484: phyag rgya chen por gsal te bdag gi khrus //
NK011(da)001:4486: bdag gi gnas gsum a las 'od 'phros pas //
NK011(da)001:4487: rgyal ba mchod cing 'gro drug sdig sgrib sbyangs //
NK011(da)001:4488: srid gsum a yi rang bzhin byang chub sems //
NK011(da)001:4489: 'od kyi gong bur gsal te snang srid khrus //
