NK011(da)001:4491: thams cad byang sems gyur te 'od gsal ba //
NK011(da)001:4492: mtha' nas rim gyis 'dus te gzas po yi //
NK011(da)001:4493: sgo gsum thim nas lus ngag yid sgrib sbyangs //
NK011(da)001:4494: a yi rang bzhin byang chub sems su zhu //
NK011(da)001:4495: 'od kyi gong bur gyur te gzas po'i khrus //
NK011(da)001:4496: de ltar khrus lung rnam pa gsum po rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:4497: de nas tshe lung 'di ltar gsal btab te //
NK011(da)001:4499: gzas po'i snying dkyil pad+ma 'dab bzhir gyes pa yi //
NK011(da)001:4500: bzhi mdor rtsa yi dwangs ma 'dus de'i nang //
NK011(da)001:4501: khrag gi dwangs ma bye'u yi ni mgo bo tsam //
NK011(da)001:4502: de la dbugs dang 'od kyi dwangs ma chags shing gnas //
NK011(da)001:4503: 'od kyi thag pa tshe tshad dang mnyam ring thung gis //
NK011(da)001:4504: ba thag lta bur d+r+wa bas bstums te gnas pa la //
NK011(da)001:4505: de rnams dbus na rnam shes rten ni 'od du gnas //
NK011(da)001:4506: de yang pad 'dab bzhi ni nyon mongs rnam shes thams cad 'byung ba'i gzhi ste de las ni //
NK011(da)001:4507: rtsa bzhir gyes pa'i chos nyid rang byung rtsa ni
NK011(da)001:4508: rtsa yi dwangs ma la brgyud kun gzhi'i rnam shes
NK011(da)001:4509: rgyu ba'i rtsa'o // gnyis med chos kyi rtsa ni
NK011(da)001:4510: dbugs kyi dwangs ma la brgyud de la yid kyi
NK011(da)001:4511: rgyu ba'i rtsa'o // rnam shes rgyu / glo bur
NK011(da)001:4512: rgyud 'dzin rtsa ni khrag gi dwangs ma la brgyud
NK011(da)001:4513: de la nyon mongs can yid rgyu //
NK011(da)001:4514: skyon yon dbang po dwangs byed rtsa ni dbang po dwangs ma la brgyud sgo lnga'i rnam shes rgyu'o //
NK011(da)001:4515: de rnams mdo ni rtsa'i dwangs ma 'dus nas gnas pa kha dog dar dkar skud pa bzhin //
NK011(da)001:4516: sbom phra dag ni rta rnga bcur bkas tsam gyi tshad la nyon mongs zhe sdang rgyu ba'o //
NK011(da)001:4517: de'i nang na khrag gi dwangs ma bye'u len pa'i
NK011(da)001:4518: mgo tsam sbal pa'i dbyibs can nang na 'dod chags
NK011(da)001:4519: rgyu // drod dang dbugs kyi dwangs ma gnas kyang
NK011(da)001:4520: kha dog rdzas su grub pa med pa nyid du
NK011(da)001:4521: rgyu // gnas pa ste // sa 'og gser bcug
NK011(da)001:4522: rlangs pa tsam gnas de la nyon mongs phrag dog
NK011(da)001:4523: rgyu // gnas pa ste // rgyu'o // de la
NK011(da)001:4524: 'od kyi dwangs ma chags te sna tshogs 'od ni
NK011(da)001:4525: sems kyi yul la khyab par gnas //
NK011(da)001:4526: de la tshe yi rten nyid gnas te sdom thag dbyibs can dkar po dag la gti mug rgyu //
NK011(da)001:4527: de dbus sems ni 'od lnga ldan pa che chung
NK011(da)001:4528: ma nges pa ste thams cad de las phyung rigs
NK011(da)001:4529: bya // zhes de ltar phur pa btab pa'i yul nges par byas la /
NK011(da)001:4530: lam gyi sngags kyis phur pa snying gar btab la ting 'dzin gsal te 'di ltar bsgom par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:4532: phur pa'i 'od kyis pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi //
NK011(da)001:4533: bya sgro mer bcug lta bur thul gyis bsregs //
NK011(da)001:4534: 'byung ba bzhi la btab pa zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)001:4535: rtsa bzhi chon thag bsdus pa bzhin du gyur //
NK011(da)001:4536: de ni 'byung ba'i rgyu bzhir btab pa'o //
NK011(da)001:4537: rtsa bzhi'i dwangs ma 'dus pa phur rtse la //
NK011(da)001:4538: sbrul 'khyud lta bu hril gyis 'dril gyur nas //
NK011(da)001:4539: de ni rgyu bzhi'i dwangs ma zhe sdang bcad //
NK011(da)001:4540: de yi dbugs rta drod kyi dwangs ma de //
NK011(da)001:4541: me la chu blugs bzhin du zhi gyur cing //
NK011(da)001:4542: dbugs kyi rta bsgral phrag dog rtsad bcad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:4543: de la 'od kyi dwangs ma chags pa de //
NK011(da)001:4544: khab len rdo bzhin phur pa la 'dus pas //
NK011(da)001:4545: rdo tshan kha ba babs ltar bskam par bsam //
NK011(da)001:4546: sems kyi yul phyung nga rgyal rtsad bcad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:4547: de yi khrag gi dwangs ma sbal pa'o //
NK011(da)001:4548: lcags bsregs chu thig phog bzhin bskam par bsgom //
NK011(da)001:4549: dwangs ma gnas sleb 'dod chags rtsad bcad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:4550: tshe skud ba thag d+r+wa bas bstums pa de //
NK011(da)001:4551: rtsa spur me lce 'phrad pa lta bur tshig /
NK011(da)001:4552: tshe yi rten phral gti mug rtsad bcad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:4553: de rnams dbus kyi tshe yi rten gyur pa //
NK011(da)001:4554: a zhes brjod pas ar gyur phur rtser sbyar //
NK011(da)001:4556: bo d+hi tsit+ta +aah bo d+hi tsit+ta h'uh bdag la bstim /
NK011(da)001:4557: bdag la bstims pas bdag nyid lhag par yang //
NK011(da)001:4558: sku gsung thugs kyi gzi byin cher rgyas te //
NK011(da)001:4559: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas pa ni //
NK011(da)001:4560: bkrag mdangs 'phrog pa bdag gi tshe lung ngo //
NK011(da)001:4561: kho yi rnam shes bdag gi thugs ka ru //
NK011(da)001:4562: a ru gnas pa tshigs pa'i lam las phyungs //
NK011(da)001:4563: rlung sgrom shangs nas dung khang gzhal yas song //
NK011(da)001:4564: rgal tshigs rta brgyud rdo rje'i lam nas phyungs //
NK011(da)001:4565: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs yum gyi mkha' ru babs //
NK011(da)001:4566: h'u gsum gyur pa phata gsum gyis 'phangs pas //
NK011(da)001:4567: 'og min rgyal ba rigs lnga'i sbyor mtshams thim //
NK011(da)001:4568: h'u de rdo rje de las rdo rje sems //
NK011(da)001:4569: ye shes rang bzhin gnas pa kho'i tshe lung //
NK011(da)001:4571: rnam shes ye nas dag pa rgyal ba'i sras //
NK011(da)001:4572: dug lnga gnas su dag pa ye shes lnga //
NK011(da)001:4573: de kho na la kho yi tshe lung bstan //
NK011(da)001:4575: de nas thun gsum gyis brab /
NK011(da)001:4577: phur pa la bdud rtsi'i skyems phul la ling ga la btab la bzhag go //
NK011(da)001:4578: gnyis pa nyon mongs pa skye ba'i sgo lnga dag par bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)001:4579: phur pa gzhan yod na rim pas blangs /
NK011(da)001:4580: med na gcig po blangs la btab ste /
NK011(da)001:4581: dngos grub bar chad pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:4582: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:4583: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK011(da)001:4584: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:4585: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK011(da)001:4586: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:4587: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:4588: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par gyis //
NK011(da)001:4593: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4595: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4596: ha sa ya ra hri ta na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4597: sh+r+ai kri na a na ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4598: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4599: +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4600: bin+d+ha ya bin+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4601: ces pa phur pa gcig snying gar btab ste dran pa skye ba'i sgo bkag /
NK011(da)001:4602: dpral bar btab ste tshe skye ba'i sgo bkag /
NK011(da)001:4603: de bzhin du mgul pa dang /
NK011(da)001:4608: srid par skye ba'i sgo bkag go //
NK011(da)001:4609: gsum pa tshogs brgyad dag par bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)001:4610: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:4611: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4612: sngon chad ji ltar dam bcas pas //
NK011(da)001:4613: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4621: ka tang ka ye dza ye bi dza ye /
NK011(da)001:4624: m+aa ra se na pra mar+d+ha na ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4625: ces dbang po mig dang rna ba dang sna dang lce dang lus kyi gzhi lte ba /
NK011(da)001:4628: yid kyi rnam shes snying rtsa g.yas su btab bo //
NK011(da)001:4629: bzhi pa dge sdig cha mnyam ste bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)001:4630: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa yi //
NK011(da)001:4632: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:4633: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par byos //
NK011(da)001:4635: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4636: spyi bo nas gsang bar thal phyung du btab /
NK011(da)001:4637: rkang mthil gnyis nas spyi bor thal phyung du btab bo //
NK011(da)001:4638: lnga pa ma bdud kyi dmod pas bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)001:4639: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK011(da)001:4640: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK011(da)001:4641: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK011(da)001:4642: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK011(da)001:4643: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK011(da)001:4644: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK011(da)001:4645: h'u ma ma pa sham ku ru ma tang nya
NK011(da)001:4646: ka ra i dan d+ha ti ma ma sh+ai krang
NK011(da)001:4648: ces dpral ba nas ltag par thal phyung du btab /
NK011(da)001:4650: rna ltag g.yas nas g.yon du /
NK011(da)001:4651: g.yon nas g.yas su thal phyung du btab ste /
NK011(da)001:4652: dbang po thams cad kyi rten med par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:4653: drug pa de nas rdul du bya ba ni /
NK011(da)001:4654: phur pa khro bo rnams kyi tho bar dmigs shing /
NK011(da)001:4655: e khro mo rnams kyi mkha' dbyings su dmigs nas lhag ma med par brdungs te /
NK011(da)001:4657: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK011(da)001:4658: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK011(da)001:4659: rdo rje me dbal snying bsregs nas //
NK011(da)001:4660: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du brdung //
NK011(da)001:4661: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK011(da)001:4662: rdo rje tho bas brdungs byas nas //
NK011(da)001:4663: lha yang rung ste brlag par bya //
NK011(da)001:4664: kha tam kha tam kha tam /
NK011(da)001:4668: kha t+w+aam gyi phyag rgyas kyang mnan no //
NK011(da)001:4669: de nas rdo rje gnod sbyin gyis bza' bar bya ste /
NK011(da)001:4670: de'i steng du mche ba'i phyag rgya bca' zhing /
NK011(da)001:4671: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:4676: bdag rdo rje gzhon nu rdo rje gnod sbyin du
NK011(da)001:4677: snang ba 'khor dang bcas pas phung po sha khrag
NK011(da)001:4678: ma lus pa gsol zhing lha tshogs dgyes pa'i sgra
NK011(da)001:4679: sgrogs / bdag la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol /
NK011(da)001:4680: dgra bgegs kyi rnam shes dkyil 'khor gsum gyi thugs
NK011(da)001:4681: kar 'phangs te dbyer med du gyur par bsam la
NK011(da)001:4682: / ling ro gtor ma la bstab cing /
NK011(da)001:4683: sras mchog gis dgra bgegs kyi sha rus thogs pa bstab par bsam la /
NK011(da)001:4686: 'bar ba chen po'i zhal hom du //
NK011(da)001:4687: bstan pa 'jig pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK011(da)001:4688: ngas bstab khyod kyis yud la rol //
NK011(da)001:4689: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK011(da)001:4690: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur bas //
NK011(da)001:4691: mi rtag mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:4692: za byed khro bo zhal phyes shig /
NK011(da)001:4693: lhag ma med par bzhes nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:4694: dgra bgegs bag chags kun byang ste //
NK011(da)001:4695: nam mkha'i khro bo za byed che'i //
NK011(da)001:4696: zhal gyi dbyings su stong khams thim //
NK011(da)001:4698: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:4699: bcom ldan dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK011(da)001:4700: gnyis med yum chen 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma //
NK011(da)001:4701: ye shes thabs kyi sprul pa khro bo bcu //
NK011(da)001:4702: shes rab dbyings las shar ba'i khro mo bcu //
NK011(da)001:4703: za byed gsod byed phra men mche gshog tshogs //
NK011(da)001:4704: mthar byed chen mo ye shes sgo ma bzhi //
NK011(da)001:4705: gdug pa sgrol ba'i sras mchog phur bu'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:4706: gnam sa gdangs pa lta bu'i zhal phyes la //
NK011(da)001:4707: zla gam glog dmar 'khyug 'dra'i ljags rkyongs te //
NK011(da)001:4708: gangs ri'i phreng ba lta bu'i tshems 'dor la //
NK011(da)001:4709: bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra bgegs zhal du bstab //
NK011(da)001:4710: zhal du bstab po bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK011(da)001:4711: dkyil 'khor de yi phyi rim bar khyams nas //
NK011(da)001:4712: dbang phyug chen po nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang //
NK011(da)001:4713: gsod pa'i las mdzad srung ma bcu gnyis dang //
NK011(da)001:4714: ging chen ging phran dge bsnyen nyer gcig sogs //
NK011(da)001:4715: phur pa'i srung mar zhal bzhes thams cad kyang //
NK011(da)001:4716: rngams pa'i zhal gdangs 'bar ba'i ljags rkyongs la //
NK011(da)001:4717: skye 'gro rtsad nas gcod pa'i tshems 'dor la //
NK011(da)001:4718: bstan pa 'jig pa'i dgra bgegs zhal du bstab //
NK011(da)001:4719: zhal du bstab po bzhes shig kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK011(da)001:4720: 'dod chags khrag la ljib ljib dgyes par rol //
NK011(da)001:4721: zhe sdang rus la hrum hrum dgyes par rol //
NK011(da)001:4722: gti mug sha la chem chem dgyes par rol //
NK011(da)001:4723: nga rgyal mkhris pa'i phung po'i mchod par bzhes //
NK011(da)001:4724: phrag dog glo snying rol cig kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK011(da)001:4725: dug lnga bsgral ba'i mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:4726: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyis //
NK011(da)001:4727: dngos grub thams cad dus 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)001:4728: ma h+aa m+aam sa la kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:4732: ma h+aa kim ni ri ti /
NK011(da)001:4733: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:4735: bee d+aur sngon po'i rin chen ri rab la //
NK011(da)001:4736: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer gdal ba ltar //
NK011(da)001:4737: sems dpa' sngon po 'od kyi dkyil 'khor 'bar //
NK011(da)001:4738: dpal chen gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:4739: 'od phung stug po sprin ltar 'khrugs pa'i dbus //
NK011(da)001:4740: 'jigs byed rngams stabs brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:4741: za byed bskal pa'i me dpung bzhin du 'bar //
NK011(da)001:4742: gdug pa thams cad rdo rje'i zhal du 'dren //
NK011(da)001:4743: mi bzad mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK011(da)001:4744: srid gsum za bar byed pa'i rkan sgra can //
NK011(da)001:4745: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gyi sdang mig gis //
NK011(da)001:4746: bgegs dpung bsregs par mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:4747: ces che ba'i yon tan gyis bstod do //
NK011(da)001:4748: de nas rnga gdeng pa re dang bcas pas //
NK011(da)001:4750: gsang sngags kyi byin brlabs so //
NK011(da)001:4752: zhes chos nyid kyi bden pa brdar ro //
NK011(da)001:4753: de nas tshogs la longs spyod pa ni /
NK011(da)001:4755: 'og min lte ba'i gzhal yas su //
NK011(da)001:4756: dkyil 'khor lha rnams spyan drangs nas //
NK011(da)001:4757: ye shes chen po'i me sbar te //
NK011(da)001:4758: hom gzar lag pas mchod rdzas bstab //
NK011(da)001:4759: ha ha ru lu bzhes su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4760: zhes gsal btab cing lha mchod par bsam la rol lo //
NK011(da)001:4761: de nas lhag ma bsdus la kha chus bran te /
NK011(da)001:4762: ya rkan la ni rta mgrin tshon gang ba //
NK011(da)001:4763: ma rkan gtun khung yum gsal byang sems rgyun //
NK011(da)001:4764: mu tig ltar bsgom dza gad mkhur bkang gis //
NK011(da)001:4765: lan gsum bran pas bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho che //
NK011(da)001:4766: 'dod yon sprin 'phro mi zad gter du bsam //
NK011(da)001:4767: gu ru tra ha ka sa ma ya bag sha
NK011(da)001:4768: su gan su tri shi tri la tish+tha thangs la
NK011(da)001:4771: bcom ldan dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yis //
NK011(da)001:4772: las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur nas //
NK011(da)001:4773: lhag ma kha chu'i dam tshig mnga' mdzad rnams //
NK011(da)001:4774: dam tshig tshul bzhin mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4775: rta mgrin gyi phyag rgyas dbang du bsdus la /
NK011(da)001:4776: 'dar phri li li bka' nyan par bsam la /
NK011(da)001:4777: dzahmh'u bam hoh badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai +aa kak+sha ya h'u dzah e +aa ral+li hrim hrim /
NK011(da)001:4788: sarba badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai nam /
NK011(da)001:4789: h+r+ai da yam h'u dzahmh'u bam hoh d+aa ki n+ai
NK011(da)001:4790: h'u dzah bdag dpal gyi sku'i gzi byin gyi zil
NK011(da)001:4791: gyis mnan la / badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba dush+tam sa ma ya mu tra /
NK011(da)001:4793: bi t+wan sa ma ya hoh b+ha ga wan /
NK011(da)001:4794: bud+d+ha k+she tra pra t+aits+tsha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4795: ban+d+ha pa ta mu kha +aa kar+sha ya /
NK011(da)001:4810: badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lid+ta h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:4811: bud+d+ha d+aa kin+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lid+ta phata /
NK011(da)001:4812: rat+na d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lid+ta s+w+aa phata /
NK011(da)001:4813: pad+ma d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba lid+ta +aam phata /
NK011(da)001:4814: karma d+aa ki n+ai pra t+aits+tsha mam ba ling+ha h+aa phata /
NK011(da)001:4817: gu ru kro d+ha ha kha rat+na sa ma ya
NK011(da)001:4818: bri sha ka kha la b+hak+sha su ka na bud+d+ha
NK011(da)001:4819: k+she tra pra ti ti pa la kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:4822: rnam dag chos dbyings zhi ba las //
NK011(da)001:4823: thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa 'byung //
NK011(da)001:4824: thabs shes zla gsang thig le las //
NK011(da)001:4825: yal gam can rnams 'du bar mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4827: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK011(da)001:4828: yi dwags rta la yang dag zhon //
NK011(da)001:4829: gdug pa'i sems kyis bsdig byed cing //
NK011(da)001:4830: dpa' bo brjid pa'i gzugs 'dzin pa //
NK011(da)001:4831: skal ldan rang gi lag char ldan //
NK011(da)001:4832: sha khrag dang ni rgyu ma dang //
NK011(da)001:4833: rkang dang tshil bu za zhing byon //
NK011(da)001:4834: dga' bar byed dang 'dren byed ma //
NK011(da)001:4835: gzi brjid che dang 'bar byed ma //
NK011(da)001:4836: 'joms byed ma dang bong bu'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:4837: chags byed ma dang chags bral ma //
NK011(da)001:4839: sna tshogs lus dang bsrung ba'o //
NK011(da)001:4840: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsrung bar byed //
NK011(da)001:4841: gnod sbyin mo ste yang dag 'phrog /
NK011(da)001:4842: bya rog gdong ste mig 'bru zhing //
NK011(da)001:4844: sna tshogs mchog gi gdong 'dzin cing //
NK011(da)001:4845: lag na gri dang mkhar gzhong thogs //
NK011(da)001:4846: bzhad dang 'ug pa'i gdong rigs can //
NK011(da)001:4847: khros pas khyi dang phag gi gdong //
NK011(da)001:4848: gsus po che la lto 'phyang ma //
NK011(da)001:4849: rnga mong bong bu'i gzugs 'dzin cing //
NK011(da)001:4850: khros pas ra dang byi la'i gdong //
NK011(da)001:4851: rgyu ma'i mgo nas za byed cing //
NK011(da)001:4852: keng rus dkar mo 'dzin pa ste //
NK011(da)001:4853: khros pas rus pa'i phreng bas klubs //
NK011(da)001:4854: phan tshun 'thab cing rtsod pa ste //
NK011(da)001:4855: lce spyang khro gtum rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:4856: 'jigs byed gdong ni mche ba gtsigs //
NK011(da)001:4858: shar nyid du ni bum sna ma //
NK011(da)001:4859: nub tu d+ha sha g+h+ri ba'o //
NK011(da)001:4860: lho ru rnam par 'joms ma ste //
NK011(da)001:4861: byang nyid du ni 'bod sgrogs so //
NK011(da)001:4862: kun kyang smug nag ral gri dang //
NK011(da)001:4863: ban+d+ha khrag bkang lag na thogs //
NK011(da)001:4864: mdor na ye shes las grub pa'i //
NK011(da)001:4865: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ma rnams //
NK011(da)001:4866: don gyi sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK011(da)001:4867: sgrub pa po la phan gdags phyir //
NK011(da)001:4868: bran gyi tshul du khas blangs pa //
NK011(da)001:4869: sngon gyi thugs dam brtser dgongs la //
NK011(da)001:4870: 'dir gshegs mchod kyi phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4871: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi zhal du ma h+aa sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:4873: ma h+aa ba lid+ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:4875: dpa' bo'i tshogs kyi las rnams kun byed pa //
NK011(da)001:4876: khro bo chen po badz+ra ging ka ra //
NK011(da)001:4877: khro mo chen mo khams gsum dbugs sdud bcas //
NK011(da)001:4878: ta na ga na'i phrin las dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:4879: rdo rje gnod sbyin rdo rje srin po dang //
NK011(da)001:4880: rdo rje 'byung po rdo rje spyang ki dang //
NK011(da)001:4881: rdo rje gshin rje rdo rje ro langs dang //
NK011(da)001:4882: rdo rje 'chi bdag rdo rje dus mtshams bsrung //
NK011(da)001:4883: dbang sdud lcags kyus 'dren pa chen mo dang //
NK011(da)001:4884: gar gyi glog stong 'gyur ba chen mo dang //
NK011(da)001:4885: gzugs med rlung ltar rgyu ba chen mo dang //
NK011(da)001:4886: khams gsum g.yab mos 'debs pa chen mo dang //
NK011(da)001:4887: rbod gtong len par byed pa chen mo dang //
NK011(da)001:4888: rna nyan phra ma zer ba chen mo dang //
NK011(da)001:4889: khams gsum snying rjes bsgral ba chen mo dang //
NK011(da)001:4890: tshogs kyi phyag tshang mdzad pa chen mo dang //
NK011(da)001:4891: rdo rje byi nub pho mo 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:4892: kun kyang sngo skya ral gri lcags kyu thogs //
NK011(da)001:4893: khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad rnams //
NK011(da)001:4894: ta na ga na'i tshogs kyi gnas chen 'dir //
NK011(da)001:4895: sngon gyi tha tshig tshul bzhin gshegs nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:4896: bdud rtsi lnga yi mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:4897: dgyes pa'i gar gyis rol cing phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4898: badz+ra ging ka ra ha ha b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:4901: lha dbang brgya byin bu mo ste //
NK011(da)001:4902: 'bar ma nyi ma'i zhags pa can //
NK011(da)001:4903: 'dzin byed chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4904: me lha drang srong bu mo ste //
NK011(da)001:4905: 'bar ma me khyer glog ma srin //
NK011(da)001:4906: bskul byed chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4907: gshin rje'i rgyal po'i bu mo ste //
NK011(da)001:4909: za byed chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4910: srin po'i rgyal po'i bu mo ste //
NK011(da)001:4911: 'bar ma khyung gi khram thogs ma //
NK011(da)001:4912: gsod byed chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4913: gnod sbyin rgyal po'i bu mo ste //
NK011(da)001:4914: 'bar ma gnod sbyin ba lang sna //
NK011(da)001:4915: thogs med chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4916: rlung lha'i rgyal po'i bu mo ste //
NK011(da)001:4917: 'bar ma rlung nag ral gri'i skra //
NK011(da)001:4918: sgrol byed chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4919: tshogs kyi bdag po'i bu mo ste //
NK011(da)001:4921: 'joms byed chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4922: klu yi rgyal po'i bu mo ste //
NK011(da)001:4924: snying 'gems chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4925: 'bar ma chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK011(da)001:4926: bka' yi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK011(da)001:4927: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4929: pho nya chen mo thams cad kyang //
NK011(da)001:4930: shar gyi phyogs na 'byung ba ni //
NK011(da)001:4931: shel gyi ma mo drug cu dang //
NK011(da)001:4932: lho yi phyogs na 'byung ba ni //
NK011(da)001:4933: mchong gi ma mo drug cu dang //
NK011(da)001:4934: nub kyi phyogs na 'byung ba ni //
NK011(da)001:4935: bswe yi ma mo drug cu dang //
NK011(da)001:4936: byang gi phyogs na 'byung ba ni //
NK011(da)001:4937: g.yu yi ma mo drug cu dang //
NK011(da)001:4938: steng gi phyogs na 'byung ba ni //
NK011(da)001:4939: lcags kyi ma mo drug cu dang //
NK011(da)001:4941: gser gyi ma mo drug cu ste //
NK011(da)001:4942: pho nya sum brgya drug cu rnams //
NK011(da)001:4943: bye ba phrag khrig 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:4944: bka' yi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:4945: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4947: rgya mtsho chen po'i klong dkyil nas //
NK011(da)001:4948: dpal ldan shugs sgrol gtso mo ste //
NK011(da)001:4949: nag mo chen mo ral pa can //
NK011(da)001:4950: ri rab bsnyil ba'i rngams stabs can //
NK011(da)001:4951: kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho skems //
NK011(da)001:4952: rdo rje kun grags gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4953: khro mo chen mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:4956: kun tu bzang mo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4958: nam mkha' stong la dbang sgyur mo //
NK011(da)001:4959: bdud dpung dregs snyems kun 'dul ma //
NK011(da)001:4960: rdo rje dregs snyems gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4961: dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:4962: pho nya mo ni drug cu'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:4963: sha chen khrag la longs spyod cing //
NK011(da)001:4964: gdug pa ma lus kun 'dul ma //
NK011(da)001:4965: rdo rje mo ste ye shes mchog /
NK011(da)001:4966: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4967: khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:4968: khro mo gtum chen za byed ma //
NK011(da)001:4969: rdo rje d+r+wa ba'i phreng thogs ma //
NK011(da)001:4971: rdo rje 'od chags gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4972: dbang phyug chen mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:4974: dam tshig nyams pa'i snying bsreg ma //
NK011(da)001:4976: rdo rje g.yu sgron gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4977: ma mo chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK011(da)001:4978: kun kyang nag mo ral pa can //
NK011(da)001:4979: kun kyang kha nas me 'bar ma //
NK011(da)001:4980: kun kyang mig nas khrag 'dzag ma //
NK011(da)001:4981: nag mo ral gri thod khrag 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:4982: gser sbrul mang po'i khri steng nas //
NK011(da)001:4983: dam tshig can la brtser dgongs la //
NK011(da)001:4984: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:4985: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4987: gling bzhi mgyogs ma lha yi sring //
NK011(da)001:4988: shar gyi mgyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4989: mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK011(da)001:4990: lho yi mgyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4991: dmar mo g.yag thod klu yi sring //
NK011(da)001:4992: nub kyi mgyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4993: nag mo sder chen gnod sbyin sring //
NK011(da)001:4994: byang gi mgyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:4995: sring mo bzhi yang gnas 'dir byon //
NK011(da)001:4996: dam dgongs mchod do phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:4998: a pa ra lan ta b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:5003: dbang phyug chen po nyi shu brgyad //
NK011(da)001:5004: snying rje byams pa'i spyod yul can //
NK011(da)001:5005: tshangs ma la sogs ma srin tshogs //
NK011(da)001:5006: 'jig rten khams kyi srin mo te //
NK011(da)001:5007: lag na glo snying nang khrol dang //
NK011(da)001:5008: mkhal ma khrag rnams snyim par thogs //
NK011(da)001:5009: spu gri'i so la sgra g.yengs ma //
NK011(da)001:5010: mche ba gtsigs shing 'bru tshugs blta //
NK011(da)001:5011: gad rgyangs sgra 'byin dur khrod myul //
NK011(da)001:5012: gsod pa'i las rnams kun la brtson //
NK011(da)001:5013: rgyal mo blon mo ded dpon che //
NK011(da)001:5014: g.yog mo dang ni yang g.yog mo //
NK011(da)001:5015: bran dang yang bran 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:5016: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yi //
NK011(da)001:5017: bka' yi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK011(da)001:5018: da lta khyod kyi gzugs mchog rnams //
NK011(da)001:5019: mngon du bstan la sid+d+hi phul //
NK011(da)001:5020: ji srid sid+d+hi ma phul bar //
NK011(da)001:5021: khyed rnams mngon par ma gyur gyi //
NK011(da)001:5022: bar du brten pa'i gnas 'di ru //
NK011(da)001:5023: 'dug la las rnams kun gyis shig /
NK011(da)001:5024: ma mo chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK011(da)001:5026: de'i tshe dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NK011(da)001:5027: spyan sngar khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5029: ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:5030: sgrub pa po yi las bya zhes //
NK011(da)001:5031: dam las ma 'da' phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:5032: b+h+yo nyer brgyad kyi rjes su /
NK011(da)001:5033: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:5035: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:5037: dam can chen mo bcu gnyis dang /
NK011(da)001:5038: ging chen ging phran 'bum phrag tshogs //
NK011(da)001:5039: dge bsnyen chen po nyi shu gcig /
NK011(da)001:5040: de sogs phur srung dam can rnams //
NK011(da)001:5041: 'dir byon lhag ma'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK011(da)001:5042: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:5043: gti mug sha yi lhu dum nyi li li //
NK011(da)001:5044: 'dod chags khrag gi rgya mtsho khyi li li //
NK011(da)001:5045: zhe sdang rus pa'i phung po khra la la //
NK011(da)001:5046: 'dod yon sprin phung rdza ltar nyil li li //
NK011(da)001:5047: rmad byung mchod pa rgya mtsho bzhes nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5048: yid la brnag pa'i 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:5049: ma h+aa pany+tsa sogs kyis mchod de /
NK011(da)001:5051: bar 'dir phur srung mchod pa ni logs su blta'o //
NK011(da)001:5052: de nas rig 'dzin bskul ba dang /
NK011(da)001:5053: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams bskul te logs su blta'o //
NK011(da)001:5054: de nas gtor ma phyir btegs te brtan ma skyong ba ni /
NK011(da)001:5055: thugs ka'i 'od kyis mgron de dag bkug la /
NK011(da)001:5056: dzahmh'u bam hoh d+aa ki n+ai h'u dzah e a ra l+li hring hring /
NK011(da)001:5057: zhes khyung gshog gi phyag rgyas dgug cing zil gyis mnan /
NK011(da)001:5059: bka' yi tshogs dang bcas nyid du //
NK011(da)001:5060: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK011(da)001:5061: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //
NK011(da)001:5062: 'dir byon dam dgongs phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:5063: bdag nyid chen mo rdo rje kun grags ma //
NK011(da)001:5064: dpal ldan ha ri rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong //
NK011(da)001:5065: gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje kun tu bzang //
NK011(da)001:5066: 'grog chen 'khor 'dul rdo rje bgegs kyi gtso //
NK011(da)001:5067: bdud mo chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK011(da)001:5068: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:5069: sil snyan rol mo'i sgra dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:5070: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:5071: 'dir gshegs dam dgongs phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:5072: sha med gangs dkar rdo rje g.yu sgron ma //
NK011(da)001:5073: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum //
NK011(da)001:5074: gser chen mkha' lding rdo rje rlung mo dang //
NK011(da)001:5075: rma ri rab 'byams rdo rje drag mo rgyal //
NK011(da)001:5076: gnod sbyin chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK011(da)001:5077: lhab lhub mang po'i sil snan rol mo'i bran g.yog
NK011(da)001:5078: mang po'i 'dir gshegs dam dgongs kong btsun de mo
NK011(da)001:5080: btsan la la rol rdo rje sman gcig ma //
NK011(da)001:5081: g.yu yi dril bu rdo rje zu le ma //
NK011(da)001:5082: sman btsun ug chos rdo rje dbyar mo bsil //
NK011(da)001:5083: sman btsun chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK011(da)001:5084: lhab lhub mang sil snyan rol bran g.yog mang po'i 'dir gshegs dam dgongs h'u /
NK011(da)001:5085: brtan ma chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK011(da)001:5087: bshes gnyen rlangs chen dpal seng ges //
NK011(da)001:5088: lag tu rdo rje byin nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5089: a mri ta ni lce la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:5090: thar pa thob pa'i ming yang btags //
NK011(da)001:5091: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK011(da)001:5092: bod du mu stegs rtag chad kyi //
NK011(da)001:5093: chos log ma gtong khyed kyi srungs //
NK011(da)001:5094: gsang sngags spyod pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NK011(da)001:5095: bar chad ma btang khyed kyis srungs //
NK011(da)001:5096: bod yul gling dgu'i ljongs 'di ru //
NK011(da)001:5097: mtha' dmag ma gtong khyed kyis srungs //
NK011(da)001:5098: dbus gtsang nang 'khrug zhi bar bsgyur //
NK011(da)001:5099: bod khams rtag tu bde ba dang //
NK011(da)001:5100: bdag cag rnal 'byor yon mchod la //
NK011(da)001:5101: ci las gyur pa'i gdon dang nad //
NK011(da)001:5102: yud tsam gyis ni zhi ba dang //
NK011(da)001:5103: dgra bgegs gnod pa bzlog par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:5106: rdo rje gnod sbyin khro bo yis //
NK011(da)001:5107: snying gi dkyil nas khrag drangs te //
NK011(da)001:5109: de bas dam tshig thub par srungs //
NK011(da)001:5110: bka' yi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK011(da)001:5111: bcol pa'i las rnams 'grub par gyis //
NK011(da)001:5119: ma ma sring 'gro ma h'u b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:5121: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:5123: de nas gtor ma dgra phyogs su 'phangs te /
NK011(da)001:5125: snang srid lha srin sde brgyad rnams //
NK011(da)001:5126: mtho ba rnams ni zhabs skums shig /
NK011(da)001:5127: dma' ba rnams ni dbu chums shig /
NK011(da)001:5128: bar pa rnams ni sku bzur cig /
NK011(da)001:5129: phyogs 'dir zor gyi lam phyes shig /
NK011(da)001:5130: gtor zor khyed la mi 'phen no //
NK011(da)001:5131: bdag gi gtor zor gnyan po 'di //
NK011(da)001:5132: gang la babs kyang gcod cing sgrol //
NK011(da)001:5133: dgra bgegs gdug pa'i snying la 'phen //
NK011(da)001:5134: dgra bgegs srog la gtor zor rgyob //
NK011(da)001:5135: mi nor phyugs la gtor zor rgyob //
NK011(da)001:5136: bdun brgyud rtsad nas chod cig yam //
NK011(da)001:5137: dgu brgyud rlung la skur cig yam //
NK011(da)001:5139: d+ha ti'i sngags bzlas la 'phangs pas dgra bgegs kha phung du brlag par bsam /
NK011(da)001:5141: bar 'dir phur pa gso bar gsungs kyang /
NK011(da)001:5142: da ni dgra bgegs bsgral zin nas bya ba yin gyis /
NK011(da)001:5143: sngas na phrin las mi 'grub pas brtags te shes par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5144: phrin las rnam pa bzhi mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir /
NK011(da)001:5146: zhes pas nang du log la gtor gzhong kha sbub pa'i 'og tu dgra bgegs 'gugs gzhug byas la /
NK011(da)001:5147: h'u ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK011(da)001:5148: dzahmh'u bam hoh sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)001:5151: skad cig yud la dbang du bsdus //
NK011(da)001:5152: dbang mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:5153: w+aa sham ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)001:5154: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad bdag rdo rje ch+gee mo'i dbang du gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:5155: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)001:5156: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:5158: shin tu gdug pa'i sems can la //
NK011(da)001:5159: zhe sdang chen po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK011(da)001:5160: skad cig nyid la brlag mdzad de //
NK011(da)001:5161: brlag par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK011(da)001:5162: brlag mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:5170: gdon stong phrag brgyad cu la sogs pa'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad brlag par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:5171: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)001:5172: gti mug rdo rje 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:5174: shin tu rmongs pa'i sems can la //
NK011(da)001:5175: gti mug chen po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK011(da)001:5176: skad cig yud la zhi mdzad de //
NK011(da)001:5177: zhi bar ma gyur gang yang med //
NK011(da)001:5178: zhi mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:5179: phyi'i dgra bgegs thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:5180: nang gi nyon mongs dug lnga zhi bar gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:5181: sh+aan+tinga ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)001:5182: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)001:5183: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:5185: shin tu dregs pa'i sems can la //
NK011(da)001:5186: nga rgyal chen po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK011(da)001:5187: skad cig yud la rgyas mdzad de //
NK011(da)001:5188: rgyas par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK011(da)001:5189: rgyas mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:5190: bdag cag rnams kyi tshe dang bsod nams dpal dang
NK011(da)001:5191: 'khor dang longs spyod dang zag pa med pa'i ye
NK011(da)001:5192: shes thams cad rgyas par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:5193: push+tinga ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)001:5194: de nas dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK011(da)001:5196: rdo rje phur pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dgongs //
NK011(da)001:5197: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyi //
NK011(da)001:5198: byin rlabs dbang dang dngos grub ma lus stsol //
NK011(da)001:5199: drag po'i stobs kyis dgra bgegs bsgral ba dang //
NK011(da)001:5200: dngos grub thams cad dus 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)001:5204: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje phur pa'i lha
NK011(da)001:5205: tshogs kyis dpal ldan bla ma dam pas gtsor mdzad
NK011(da)001:5206: / sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'dzin pa'i dge ba'i
NK011(da)001:5207: bshes gnyen rnams kyi sku tshe dang phrin las kyi
NK011(da)001:5208: bar du gcod pa thams cad nye bar zhi bar
NK011(da)001:5209: / mdzad du gsol / bdag dang sems can thams
NK011(da)001:5210: cad kyi sdig pa dang sgrib pa dam tshig nyams
NK011(da)001:5211: pa thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK011(da)001:5212: mtho ris dang thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa'i lam gyi bar du gcod pa /
NK011(da)001:5215: shes bya'i sgrib pa thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK011(da)001:5216: gnas skabs su las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis 'byung ba'i gnod pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5217: sdug bsngal gyi bye brag gdon chen po bco brgyad dang /
NK011(da)001:5218: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu dang /
NK011(da)001:5223: pha rol gyi rigs sngags las gyur pa'i gnod pa thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK011(da)001:5226: sa g.yo ba la sogs pa 'byung ba las gyur pa'i gnod pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5227: lo nyes dang dgra'i gnod pa la sogs pa 'jigs pa chen po bcu drug dang /
NK011(da)001:5231: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi dang /
NK011(da)001:5233: dus ma yin par 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK011(da)001:5234: de dag gi rgyu bsam sbyor ngan pa thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK011(da)001:5235: khyad par du yang ch+gee mo zhes bya ba'i sngon gyi las las gyur kyang rung /
NK011(da)001:5236: 'phral gyi rkyen las gyur kyang rung ste /
NK011(da)001:5237: phyi nang gi nye bar 'tshe ba lus sems la gnod par byed pa'i gdon bgegs dang /
NK011(da)001:5238: nad la sogs pa lus kyi sdug bsngal ba thams cad dang /
NK011(da)001:5239: sems kyi yid mi bde ba dang /
NK011(da)001:5247: dge ba sgrub pa'i bar du gcod pa thams cad zhi bar mdzad du gsol /
NK011(da)001:5248: 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir dus kyi 'khrugs pa zhi ba dang /
NK011(da)001:5249: mtshon gyi bskal pa nyams pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5250: mtha'i dmag dpung bzlog pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5251: lo phyugs rtag tu legs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5252: char chu dus su 'bab par mdzad du gsol /
NK011(da)001:5253: mdor na bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi gnas
NK011(da)001:5254: skabs su mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad nye bar
NK011(da)001:5255: zhi nas / 'og min gyi mthar thug gi 'jig rten pa'i dngos grub mtha' dag 'grub pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5256: mthar thug sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas zhi ba'i
NK011(da)001:5257: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub myur du
NK011(da)001:5258: 'grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK011(da)001:5259: phan bde'i 'byung gnas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin
NK011(da)001:5260: po che sgo thams cad nas dar zhing rgyas par
NK011(da)001:5261: mdzad du gsol / 'khor 'das kyi dpal dang phun
NK011(da)001:5262: sum tshogs pa thams cad bdag gi dbang du 'du
NK011(da)001:5264: bdud dang dgra bgegs nag po'i phyogs thams cad da
NK011(da)001:5265: lta nyid du thal bar brlag par mdzad du gsol
NK011(da)001:5268: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs
NK011(da)001:5269: 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su
NK011(da)001:5270: gsol / bdag cag so so'i skye bor gyur pas
NK011(da)001:5271: sems can nyon mongs pa can du gyur nas lus
NK011(da)001:5272: ngag yid gsum gyi spyod pa nyon mongs pa dang
NK011(da)001:5273: 'dres te bag med par gyur pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5274: rnal 'byor la dbang ma thob pas bying ba dang
NK011(da)001:5275: rgod pa'i dbang du gyur te ting 'dzin mi gsal
NK011(da)001:5276: ba dang / snyigs ma lnga'i dus kyi dbang gis
NK011(da)001:5277: nye bar mkho ba'i yo byad ma 'byor pas mchod
NK011(da)001:5278: rdzas ma tshang zhing ngan pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5280: shes bzhin ma yin pa'i dbang du gyur nas /
NK011(da)001:5281: cho ga la lhag pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5283: ser sna'i dbang gis mchod pa ngan zhing chung ba dang /
NK011(da)001:5284: gti mug gi dbang gis rgyud sde nas byung ba'i
NK011(da)001:5285: cho ga bzhin du ma lcogs pa la sogs pa
NK011(da)001:5286: 'khrul zhing nongs pa thams cad bzod par bzhes nas
NK011(da)001:5287: bdag cag gi lam dang dngos grub kyi bar chad
NK011(da)001:5288: du mi 'gyur bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK011(da)001:5289: yi ge brgya pa lan gsum brjod la /
NK011(da)001:5290: so so'i skye bor gyur gang dang //
NK011(da)001:5291: rnal 'byor ma thob dbang gis dang //
NK011(da)001:5292: nye bar mkho ba med pa dang //
NK011(da)001:5293: brjed dang shes bzhin ma yin pas //
NK011(da)001:5294: cung zhig cho ga nyer ma tshang //
NK011(da)001:5295: de dag bkru zhing bzod par gsol //
NK011(da)001:5298: don chos nyid las mi 'da' ba'i phyir sku mchog shin tu legs pa brtan /
NK011(da)001:5300: ye shes lha rnams gshegs su mi gsol te //
NK011(da)001:5301: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lha rnams h'u gsum gyur //
NK011(da)001:5302: phata sgra gsum gyis de las 'od 'phros te //
NK011(da)001:5303: don gnyis byas 'dus h'u yig gsum la thim //
NK011(da)001:5304: gnyis po bdag nyid rtsa ba'i h'u la thim //
NK011(da)001:5305: de yang zhabs nas n+aa da'i bar du thim //
NK011(da)001:5306: n+aa da chos dbyings dag pa'i ngang du thim //
NK011(da)001:5307: de yang slob dpon chen pos rtsa ba rnal 'byor lam gyi rim pa las /
NK011(da)001:5308: rang bzhin sems kyi chos nyid ni //
NK011(da)001:5309: ma bcos lhug par gnas pa'i don //
NK011(da)001:5310: rtag chad dngos po'i mtha' spangs shing //
NK011(da)001:5311: brjod bral mu bzhi las 'das pa //
NK011(da)001:5312: rtsol med gnas pa'i chos nyid de //
NK011(da)001:5313: phur pa zhes ni de la bya //
NK011(da)001:5314: zhes gsungs pa'i don la gnas par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5316: rtag pa chen po rgyun gyi ting 'dzin bsgom //
NK011(da)001:5317: zhes pas de lta bu'i chos nyid kyi ngang nas //
NK011(da)001:5318: h'u h'u zhes pas h'u yig bsgrig mar gyur //
NK011(da)001:5319: 'od 'phros don byas 'dus nas h'u yig gnyis //
NK011(da)001:5320: gtso bo yab yum gyur pa'i spyi bo ru //
NK011(da)001:5321: zla steng ha bsam rgya gram phyag rgya bcings //
NK011(da)001:5323: rang lus rdo rje'i go chas gtams par bsam //
NK011(da)001:5324: mdzub mo gnyis la nyi dal re re'i steng //
NK011(da)001:5325: rdo rje gnod sbyin sngon po mche ba 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:5326: bdud rtsi thabs sbyor dmar po rgya gram bsnams //
NK011(da)001:5327: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi yak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK011(da)001:5328: mdzub mo lte bar btud pas khro bo gnyis //
NK011(da)001:5329: rgyab sprod bzhugs nas bar chad bsrung bar mos //
NK011(da)001:5330: drug mdo snying ga sog pa mtshog ma ltag /
NK011(da)001:5331: reg cing khro bo rgyab sprod bzhugs par bsam //
NK011(da)001:5333: rin chen phyag rgya mgo bo'i gnas lngar gtug /
NK011(da)001:5334: rin po che yi dbu rgyan nyid du bsam //
NK011(da)001:5335: tush+ya ho zhes dgyes pa'i thal mo brdab //
NK011(da)001:5336: le brgan dmar mthing gis ni dbang bskur bsam //
NK011(da)001:5337: +aa li k+aa li dang yi ge brgya pa brjod la lhag chad bskang /
NK011(da)001:5338: 'dir bla ma jo lcam la sogs pa slob dpon snga rabs pa dag /
NK011(da)001:5339: rtag pa chen po rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin zhes
NK011(da)001:5340: pa de lus bsrung ba la 'dod pa ltar bris
NK011(da)001:5341: pa yin la / rang lugs la ni lus bsrung ba dang /
NK011(da)001:5342: de'i rjes bsngo ba'i bar zin pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5344: snod kyi 'jig rten rdo rje phur pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK011(da)001:5345: bcud kyi sems can thams cad rdo rjee gzhon nu yab yum /
NK011(da)001:5346: sgra grags thams cad k+ai la ya'i rang sgra /
NK011(da)001:5347: sems kyi dran rtog thams cad stong gsal rjen pa ste /
NK011(da)001:5348: rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs su lam du khyer ba la 'dod pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:5350: phur pa zhe sdang yongs su dag pa'i rgyud le'u bcu bdun pa las /
NK011(da)001:5351: khrag 'thung rigs su skyes nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5352: mnyam med rdo rje gzhon nu ston //
NK011(da)001:5353: snying rje ldan zhing bla mar gus //
NK011(da)001:5354: skye zhing skye bar 'gyur bar shog /
NK011(da)001:5355: lag na rdo rje phur bu 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:5356: zab mo'i chos ni klog pa dang //
NK011(da)001:5357: btsun mo'i khu ba mnyam zas can //
NK011(da)001:5358: skye zhing skye bar 'gyur bar shog /
NK011(da)001:5360: dge ba 'di yis bdag dang sems can kun //
NK011(da)001:5361: bdud las nam rgyal bar chad kun zhi zhing //
NK011(da)001:5362: rdo rje gzhon nu mya ngan 'das pa'i sar //
NK011(da)001:5363: 'bras bu byang chub nges par brnyes gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:5365: de nas bkra shis rgyas par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5366: de ltar dpal ldan rdo rje phur bu yi //
NK011(da)001:5367: las byang chob khrigs gsal bar bkod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:5368: o rgyan chen po'i rtsa ba la brten cing //
NK011(da)001:5369: jo lcam gyis phyung lang lab sna nam dang //
NK011(da)001:5370: khyad par mkhas ba'i mkhas pa rong zom gyis //
NK011(da)001:5371: gzhung las btus te yi ger bkod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:5372: tshul 'dir mos pa'i ban+de ma tis sbyar //
NK011(da)001:5373: dge ba 'di yis bdag dang 'gro ba kun //
NK011(da)001:5374: lam mchog rdo rje'i thig le'i sgor zhugs te //
NK011(da)001:5375: rgyal ba dgyes pa'i phrin las mthar dbyung nas //
NK011(da)001:5376: rdo rje gzhon nu'i go 'phang myur thob shog /
NK011(da)001:5377: rdo rje phur pa'i las kyi byang bu 'bring por bkod pa dngos grub rgya mtsho zhes bya ba /
NK011(da)001:5378: rig pa 'dzin pa'i dge slong nam mkhar spyod pas
NK011(da)001:5379: yos bu'i lo mchu nya ba'i tshes nyer lnga la
NK011(da)001:5381: 'dis kyang rgyal ba'i bstan pa phyogs dus kun tu rgyas pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5382: sems can thams cad bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK011(da)001:5383: dpal la dus kun tu longs spyod par gyur cig
NK011(da)001:5385: // /// dpal rdo rje phur pa'i gzhung phyogs gcig gi bkol byang lugs gcig bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:5386: phur bu sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor ba rnams kyi bya ba rnam pa gsum ste /
NK011(da)001:5390: de la bsnyen pa'i tshe dang po dbang dang dam tshig mnos te /
NK011(da)001:5391: de nas dus sam grangs sam mtshan ma la dam bca' ste /
NK011(da)001:5392: de yang dus la 'cha' na rang gi nus pa dang sbyar nas /
NK011(da)001:5393: lo zla'i grangs tshad 'di tsam zhig tu bsnyen pa bya'o zhes dam bcas la /
NK011(da)001:5394: khas ji ltar blangs pa las cung zad kyang ma nyams par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5395: de'i dus su nyin zhag re la mchod pa dang
NK011(da)001:5396: bzlas brjod ting nge 'dzin gsum yang dang po nus
NK011(da)001:5397: thang gi tshad gcig bzung la de las ma nyams
NK011(da)001:5398: par bya'o // gal te grangs las dam 'cha' na
NK011(da)001:5399: sa ya man chad nas bye ba phrag gcig gam
NK011(da)001:5400: par bya'o // / gal te dngos grub chen po
NK011(da)001:5401: 'dod na dbye ba phrag lnga'i bar du bzlas so
NK011(da)001:5402: par bya'o // / zhes 'byung ngo // mtshan ma la dam 'cha' na /
NK011(da)001:5404: phyi rol gyi rtags gcig ma thon bar du bsnyen pa mi btang ba ste /
NK011(da)001:5405: 'di ni gang zag rab kyi spyod yul lo //
NK011(da)001:5406: de dag gi dus su yang mchod pa dang ting nge 'dzin dang bcas pa'o //
NK011(da)001:5407: de ltar bsnyen pa rdzogs nas sgrub pa la 'jug par bya ste /
NK011(da)001:5408: dur khrod dam ri bo 'dus pa'i rtse la sogs
NK011(da)001:5409: pa bkra shis pa'i gnas su dus tshod dang sbyor
NK011(da)001:5410: ba bzang po la dkyil 'khor tshul bzhin bris te
NK011(da)001:5411: / dbus su phur pa bkod nas dang por mchod pa chen por byas te /
NK011(da)001:5412: de nas bzlas brjod ting nge 'dzin 'ba' zhig la
NK011(da)001:5413: zhugs nas zla ba drug tu g.yeng ba med par
NK011(da)001:5414: bzlas pa bya'o // de nas nub tha ma'i tho rangs skya rengs shar tsa na /
NK011(da)001:5415: gal te dngos grub rab tu thob na ni phur pa 'phar zhing me ltar 'bar bar 'gyur te /
NK011(da)001:5416: de'i tshe yid gnyis med par byas te /
NK011(da)001:5417: rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag btsal nas rang gi
NK011(da)001:5418: lus phul te phur pa lag pa g.yas par blang
NK011(da)001:5419: bas rig 'dzin gyi rgyal por 'gyur te /
NK011(da)001:5420: sangs rgyas rnams kyi zhal mthong ba la sogs par 'gyur ro //
NK011(da)001:5421: gal te du ba byung na ni mi snang ba la sogs pa thob bo //
NK011(da)001:5422: gal te dro bar gyur na ni rkang mgyogs la sogs pa thob bo //
NK011(da)001:5423: gal te grub par ma gyur na yang las phra mo 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK011(da)001:5424: zhi ba dang rgyas pa dang dbang dang drag po
NK011(da)001:5425: la sogs pa btab pa tsam gyis 'grub par 'gyur
NK011(da)001:5426: ro // dngos grub 'dod pa rnams kyi ni dang
NK011(da)001:5427: po grub par ma gyur kyang spogs pa'i cho ga
NK011(da)001:5428: lan gsum du bskyar bas 'byung ngo //
NK011(da)001:5431: dngos grub thob pa rnams kyi ni bsam pa tsam dang /
NK011(da)001:5432: phur pa btab pa tsam gyis ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin 'gyur ro //
NK011(da)001:5433: las phra mo grub pa rnams kyis ni dang po lha la mchod pa bya ste /
NK011(da)001:5434: de nas sngags brgya rtsa brgyad dam /
NK011(da)001:5436: 'bum yan chad bzlas te bsgrub bya'i gzugs brnyan la
NK011(da)001:5437: phab pas zhi ba dang drag po la sogs pa'i
NK011(da)001:5439: tshul 'di rnams ni bka' bzhin byed nus pa'i gang zag gi dbang du byas pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:5440: da ni gang zag dman pa rnams kyi bya ba bshad pa ste /
NK011(da)001:5441: de la gang zag nus pa chung ba yun ring por sgrub mi nus pa rnams kyi ni /
NK011(da)001:5442: dang por bsnyen sgrub go chu rub tu bya ste
NK011(da)001:5443: dbang dang dam tshig mnos pa'i rjes la lo zla
NK011(da)001:5444: ji tsam nus pa gcig tu nyin zhag re la
NK011(da)001:5445: yi dam nar ma nas 'byung ba bzhin du sgom
NK011(da)001:5446: pa dang mchod pa dang bcas bzlas brjod ji ltar
NK011(da)001:5447: nus pa'i grangs tshad bzung la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5448: de'i dus su dkyil 'khor dang phur bu ni lhag par rten du btsugs kyang nyes skyon med la /
NK011(da)001:5449: 'byor na rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor steng du sku
NK011(da)001:5450: gzugs bkram ste mdun du phur bu bkod na yang
NK011(da)001:5452: de ltar dam bcas pa rdzogs nas /
NK011(da)001:5453: gal te dgra bgegs lta bu 'dul du yod na
NK011(da)001:5454: ni de nyid kyi rjes la las la sbyar bar
NK011(da)001:5455: bya'o // gdug pa 'dul du med na ni de'i nub tha ma la dngos grub blangs te /
NK011(da)001:5456: phur pa lag tu blangs nas de nas sa la
NK011(da)001:5457: mi bzhag par dar mthing ga la sogs pa gos
NK011(da)001:5458: bzang pos dril te gab tse la sogs pa snod
NK011(da)001:5460: gnas gnyan ris su bzhag nas phyis don chen po'i las la sbyar bar byas te /
NK011(da)001:5461: bya ba phran tshegs la mi spyod do //
NK011(da)001:5462: bzlas brjod kyi sngags 'phral gyi bya ba phran tshegs
NK011(da)001:5463: la spyad na don chen po la mthu chung bar
NK011(da)001:5464: 'gyur ro // sgrub pa'i lha dang bsnyen pa'i srung
NK011(da)001:5465: ma rnams kyang bya ba phra mo mang po la
NK011(da)001:5466: bskul na don chen po la mthu chung bar 'gyur
NK011(da)001:5467: 'gyur ro // ro // 'di ni dngos po rnams kyi ngo bo nyid yin te /
NK011(da)001:5468: sgrub pa'i rjes la yang yi dam nar mar bzung ste bsrung ba dang gso ba'i cho ga bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5469: da ni dngos grub ma thob cing dman pa rnams kyi las la sbyor ba'i cho ga bshad de /
NK011(da)001:5470: de la drag po phrin las kyi gnas ni /
NK011(da)001:5471: sngon g.yul chen po bcas shing skye bo mang po bsad pa'i gnas sam /
NK011(da)001:5472: sngon gyi lam rgya gram mam /
NK011(da)001:5475: ma mo'i gnas la sogs pa 'byung po gnas pa'i sa dang /
NK011(da)001:5476: gnam sa'i dbyibs kyang gru gsum dang /
NK011(da)001:5477: lto ral dang gcan gzan gdug pa'i kha 'dra ba
NK011(da)001:5478: la sogs pa rnams su sbra gur la sogs pa
NK011(da)001:5479: bcas te bya'o // yang na de'i nye 'khor gcig tu las la sbyar bar bya ste /
NK011(da)001:5480: der mnan pa byas na yang btub bo //
NK011(da)001:5481: de la las kyi go rim ni /
NK011(da)001:5482: dang por gnas der bcas te /
NK011(da)001:5483: mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang sbyin gtor dang /
NK011(da)001:5484: chang phud rin po che dang bcas pa bshams te 'phags pa mchod pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5485: 'gro ba spyir sbyin gtong ba dang /
NK011(da)001:5486: bgegs rigs la spyi gtor bsngo ba dang /
NK011(da)001:5487: bsgrub bya'i pho lha dang srog lha sogs lha rnams la sbyin gtor bsngosa te /
NK011(da)001:5488: ma nyes pa'i dpang gzugs shing bsgrub bya'i stong grogs mi byed par bka' basgo'o //
NK011(da)001:5489: gnas de'i bgegs la yang khyad par du sbyin gtor mang po stsal te bden pa brdar la /
NK011(da)001:5490: khyod kyi gnas 'di ni dus tshod 'di tsam zhig tu bdag la g.yar dgos kyi /
NK011(da)001:5491: de'i bar du bdag la phrag dog ma byed par bdag gi las kyi grogs gyis shig /
NK011(da)001:5492: las grub ma thag tu rang gi gnas myur du sbyin no zhes basgo'o //
NK011(da)001:5493: de nas las sgrub spyi dang mthun par rgyal po chen po bzhi la phyi mtshams bcol ba dang /
NK011(da)001:5494: nang mtshams dag ci rigs bgyis /
NK011(da)001:5495: sa byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5496: dkyil 'khor chag chag btab pa yan chad spyi dang mthun par ci nus bgyis /
NK011(da)001:5497: de la dal bri ba'i dus ni /
NK011(da)001:5498: dus nub mo bri zhes 'byung na'ang gnas dang dus skabs kyis sbyar /
NK011(da)001:5500: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad khams gcig sgo dang bcas pa'i thig btab /
NK011(da)001:5502: dbus kyi ma lte ba nag po bya ste /
NK011(da)001:5503: dbus su dmar nag gru gsum gcig bya /
NK011(da)001:5504: 'khor lo rtsibs rigs dang bstun la /
NK011(da)001:5505: dkyil du dmar nag gru gsum re gru chad du bya /
NK011(da)001:5506: dbal ka dmar po bya ste /
NK011(da)001:5507: de la yang dmar nag gru gsum re bya /
NK011(da)001:5508: gru chad rak+ta'i rgya mtsho bris /
NK011(da)001:5511: phyi rol la lcags ri dang me ri bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5512: de nas phyag rgya dgod pa ni /
NK011(da)001:5513: yum rnams kyi phyag rgya ni dmar nag gru gsum
NK011(da)001:5514: nyid yin pas gud du dgod mi dgos zhes bshad
NK011(da)001:5515: / yab nyi shu rtsa gcig dang sgo ma bzhi'i
NK011(da)001:5516: phur pa la dar le brgan gyi cod pan btags
NK011(da)001:5517: / te / de la dbus su gtso bo'i phur pa dgod /
NK011(da)001:5518: rtsibs brgyad la phyogs kyi khro bo'i phur pa dgod /
NK011(da)001:5519: dbal kha brgyad la phyogs kyi za byed kyi phur pa bkod /
NK011(da)001:5520: steng 'og gi khro bo za byed dang bcas pa
NK011(da)001:5521: ni shar nub kyi rtsibs lte ba'i mdun rgyab tu
NK011(da)001:5522: dmar nag gru gsum re'i steng du bkod /
NK011(da)001:5523: shar lhor byabs phur te bya rgod kyi gshog zur gyi phur pa bkod /
NK011(da)001:5524: lho sgor bsdigs phur te skyer phur bkod /
NK011(da)001:5525: nub sgor dbang phur te zangs sam shing dmar po'i phur pa bkod /
NK011(da)001:5526: byang du sgrol phur te mchog phur bkod /
NK011(da)001:5527: khyams la phur bu'i srung ma rnams kyi rten bkod
NK011(da)001:5528: de lhag par yang bswe'i lha mo rnams kyi rten
NK011(da)001:5529: bswe phor bzhi'i nang du mtshams bzhir khrag dang zhag
NK011(da)001:5530: dang mar khu dang 'o ma rnams so sor bkang
NK011(da)001:5531: ste bzhag go // lcags ri la dbang phyug ma'i rtsang bkod kyang nyes pa med de /
NK011(da)001:5532: spyir dpal gyi 'khor gyi mkha' 'gro ma mo'i gtso mo yin pas so zhes kyang bshad /
NK011(da)001:5533: phur bu'i dal gyi lhar ma smros pas lhag par ma bkod kyang nyes pa med /
NK011(da)001:5534: phyag rgya 'di rnams bkod pa so so'i dal gyi snying po brjod cing dgod pa'am /
NK011(da)001:5535: lha bzhugs su gsol ba'i skabs nas 'byung ba'i tshig dang /
NK011(da)001:5536: sngags kyis dgod pa ci dgar bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5537: lid+ga dang brub khung bca' ba ni /
NK011(da)001:5538: gang du mnan pa'i sa nyid du gnas bcas pa yin na ni /
NK011(da)001:5539: dang po dal byed pa'i tshe /
NK011(da)001:5540: dal gyi dbus su dang po gru gsum khru gang pa cig brkos te /
NK011(da)001:5541: de la kha khyer btags pa de la bskor te 'khor lo'i lte ba bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5542: gzhan du gnon na ni snga ma bzhin du bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5543: lho nub kyi grar brub khung gcig bya ste /
NK011(da)001:5544: der tshogs mchod kyi dus su bstab pa'i las bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5545: lid+ga'i rgyu yang rnam pa gnyis yin te /
NK011(da)001:5546: mnan pa'i lid+ga ni phun sum tshogs pa nas 'byung
NK011(da)001:5547: ba bzhin du bya ste dkar nag gis btags nas
NK011(da)001:5548: / dbus kyi e'i steng mgo lho nub tu bstan
NK011(da)001:5549: kha sbub du bzhag ste mgo bo ging phur la
NK011(da)001:5550: / gtad do // nang nub tshogs mchod kyi dus su bstab pa'i lid+ga ni /
NK011(da)001:5551: gro ga'am shing lo'am shog shog la sogs par bris te lho nub kyi brub khung du bcug la /
NK011(da)001:5552: tshogs mchod re re zhing lid+ga gsar pa re re
NK011(da)001:5553: la 'gugs 'dren bya zhig phur pa gzhan gyi btab
NK011(da)001:5554: ste / mjug thon khar gtor ma cha gcig sbyin sreg byed pa'i skabs su hom du bsreg go //
NK011(da)001:5556: nub tha ma la sgrub phur nyi shu rtsa gcig
NK011(da)001:5557: btab ste phur pa dang bcas nas mnan pa byas
NK011(da)001:5558: la / de yang stabs bde na mnan pa byas pa'i sa nyid du dkyil 'khor bya ste /
NK011(da)001:5559: de'i dkyil du gru gsum byas pa'i nang du dang po kha sbub tu bzhag pa de /
NK011(da)001:5560: nub tha ma la 'debs khar gan rkyal du bzhag ste phur pa btab la /
NK011(da)001:5561: de nyid du phur pa dang bcas nas phun sum
NK011(da)001:5562: tshogs pa nas 'byung ba bzhin du mnan pa byas
NK011(da)001:5563: te bzhag go // nam rtags 'byung ba dang slar phyung ste gso ba'i cho ga bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5564: dam rdzas ni bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga dang /
NK011(da)001:5566: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang /
NK011(da)001:5567: spyi'i yo byad ji ltar 'byor pa bzhin du bsham mo //
NK011(da)001:5568: dam tshig gi srung ma rnams kyi khyad par gyi rdzas 'byor yang bzang ngo //
NK011(da)001:5569: de ltar spyi'i las made'u brkoos tsam bstan nas /
NK011(da)001:5570: cho ga la 'jug pa'i rim pa bstan te /
NK011(da)001:5572: dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK011(da)001:5574: mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5575: mchod pa dal du bkod pa rnams spyi'i cho ga
NK011(da)001:5576: yin pas ji ltar nus shing 'tshams pa ltar bgyis
NK011(da)001:5577: pa'i rjes la cho ga gzhung la zhugs te bdag
NK011(da)001:5579: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dal bskyed pa'i rjes la lcags sna lnga las byas pa'am /
NK011(da)001:5580: seng ldeng ngam shing gdug pa la byas pa'i phur
NK011(da)001:5581: pa sor bcu gnyis pa nyi shu rtsa gcig shing
NK011(da)001:5582: shun nam ban+de'i dbus su bzhag ste /
NK011(da)001:5583: byin gyis brlab pa phun sum tshogs pa nas 'byung
NK011(da)001:5584: ba bzhin du bya ste tshon skud kyis bcings la
NK011(da)001:5585: / dbus kyi e'i nang gi lid+ga'i steng du rtse
NK011(da)001:5586: mo cung zad ma reg pa tsam du byas te
NK011(da)001:5587: / bzhag go // de nas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs te /
NK011(da)001:5589: de nas tshogs kyi mchod pa phul te /
NK011(da)001:5590: tshogs la rol khar tshogs de yang bsgrub byar byin
NK011(da)001:5591: gyis brlabs la bsgral la phud bkrol te cha gsum
NK011(da)001:5592: du bcad la / dang po mchod par 'bul /
NK011(da)001:5594: cha gsum lho nub mtshams kyi brub khung du blug ste /
NK011(da)001:5595: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis pho nya drag tu bskul zhing 'gug 'dren byas la /
NK011(da)001:5596: phur pa tha mal pa gzhan gyis lid+ga dang zas su bcas pa la bstab /
NK011(da)001:5597: de nas phur pa phyungs te lid+ga'i dum bu brub
NK011(da)001:5598: khung du bzhag la zas rnams phyungs te gtor mar
NK011(da)001:5599: bstab par bya'o // de nas rnal 'byor pa rnams tshogs la rol te /
NK011(da)001:5600: rjes chad dbugs phyung ba dang gtor ma mtshams sbyar te /
NK011(da)001:5601: snga ma btang phyi ma dal du phul la /
NK011(da)001:5602: gtor ma btang ba la lhag ma'i mchod sbyin bzang por sbyar te /
NK011(da)001:5603: gtor ma'i mgron gyi gnas rnams re re la yang dmar gyi ar+g+ha sbreng zhing spyan drangs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5606: phrin las bcol ba rnams bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5607: phrin las la yang pho nya dgug cig gtor ma la yang bsgrub bya bstim pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5610: smon lam btab pa rnams 'tshams par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5611: de ltar nyin zhag phrug gcig la dus mtshams bzhir mchod pa bzhi bya /
NK011(da)001:5612: nam gyi mthar gtor ma re btang /
NK011(da)001:5613: srod dang snga dro la dbus kyi sgrub phur nyi
NK011(da)001:5614: shu rtsa gcig la byin rlabs thebs re bya ste
NK011(da)001:5615: / gu gul sbyar mas bdug cing snga ma bzhin du dbus su bzhugs su gsol /
NK011(da)001:5616: de ltar zhag gsum mam lnga byas pa'i nub tha
NK011(da)001:5617: ma la tshogs kyi mchod pa la lho nub mtshams
NK011(da)001:5618: kyi bstab pa dang btab pa bya mi dgos te
NK011(da)001:5619: / dbus kyi sgrub phur rnams blangs te byin rlabs snga ma bzhin bgyis la /
NK011(da)001:5620: rdo rje khros pas zhe sdang gcod //
NK011(da)001:5622: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK011(da)001:5623: zhes pa nas mar gzhung bsrang //
NK011(da)001:5624: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:5625: ces pas thugs dam drag tu bskul zhing /
NK011(da)001:5626: shar sgo'i byabs phur sgril zhing bskor te pho nya drag tu bskul /
NK011(da)001:5629: sgrol phur btab la mngags gzhugs kyi las rdzogs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5630: sgrub phur nyi shu rtsa gcig gzhung bzhin btab /
NK011(da)001:5631: de nas de nyid du mnan pa byed na mnan pa yan chad rdzogs par bya ste /
NK011(da)001:5633: mnan pa gzhan du byed na phur pa btab pa'i
NK011(da)001:5634: rjes la tshogs la rol la gtor ma bskyal ba
NK011(da)001:5635: dang / mnan pa dus gcig tu bya /
NK011(da)001:5636: de ltar tshogs la rol zin nas gtor ma btang ba ni 'grub na cha gcig gter du sba /
NK011(da)001:5637: cha gcig la sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5638: cha gcig la mkha' 'gro ma bskyang ngo //
NK011(da)001:5639: ma 'grub na gnyis su bcad de gter du sba mi dgos so //
NK011(da)001:5640: sbyin sreg gi dus su lho nub mtshams kyi brub
NK011(da)001:5641: khung gi lid+ga'i sman dum rnams bsdus te hom du
NK011(da)001:5643: yang ma grub na ni gtor mas mkha' 'gro ma bskyang ba tsam byas la /
NK011(da)001:5644: lid+ga'i sman de rnams dbus kyi lid+ga dang lhan cig tu mnan pa byas te bzhag go //
NK011(da)001:5645: phrin las 'di'i dus su e ka tsa ti'i zor
NK011(da)001:5646: thun dang bswe mo bzhi'i zor thun dag byas te
NK011(da)001:5648: de ltar las rdzogs pa'i rjes la dal bsdu ba'i tshe /
NK011(da)001:5649: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i phur pa la sogs pa'i
NK011(da)001:5650: lha dal du bkod pa'i lha'i rten gyi phur pa
NK011(da)001:5651: nyi shu gcig bsdus te bdag gi thugs kar bzung
NK011(da)001:5652: la / lha rnams bdag gi thugs kar bsdus te dal bsdu'o //
NK011(da)001:5653: de nyid ni dngos grub blang ba'ang yin no //
NK011(da)001:5654: bsnyen sgrub dang las kyi bzlas brjod kyi ting 'dzin
NK011(da)001:5655: ni phur pa ma bkod pa'i dus su gsang phreng
NK011(da)001:5656: bzhin nam / yang na thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la bzlas pa'i yi ge bsgoms te bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5657: ting 'dzin gsal na 'phro 'du dang bcas pa bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5658: phur pa dal du bkod nas ni phun sum tshogs pa ltar bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5659: de tshe 'phro ba'i gzhi ni rtsa ba'i dal dang /
NK011(da)001:5660: dbang phyug khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK011(da)001:5661: bsdu ba'i gnas ni phur pa rdzas kyi dal te dbus kyi sgrub phur nyi shu rtsa gcig go //
NK011(da)001:5662: nyi shu rtsa gcig kyang btab pa'i gnas kyi dbye ba tsam ste /
NK011(da)001:5664: rdo rje gzhon nu'i phyag tha ma'i phur pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no //
NK011(da)001:5665: phur bu'i gzhung phyogs gcig gi bkol byang rdzogs so //
NK011(da)001:5667: // 'di'i cha rkyen du med du mi rung ba ni /
NK011(da)001:5668: las byang nar ma chung ngu dang 'bring po tsam /
NK011(da)001:5669: mjug bstab pa'i phrin las dang gsum yin no //
NK011(da)001:5670: 'debs pa'i tshe thugs dam bskul zhing pho nya btang ba ni /
NK011(da)001:5671: phur pa spyi'i cho ga la ltos su rung ngo //
NK011(da)001:5674: spyi'i las made'u rnams ni las sgrub spyi la ltos pas chog go //
NK011(da)001:5675: e ka dz+aa ti dang bswe mo'i thun ni so
NK011(da)001:5676: so'i sgos sgrub nas 'byung ba'i thun zor la ltos
NK011(da)001:5678: 'di bla ma mkhas grub rong zom gyis mdzad do //
NK011(da)001:5681: // // rdo rje phur pa'i bsnyen sgrub las gsum gyi tho byang rong zom gyis mdzad pa bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:5682: phrin las rdo rje gzhon nu'i sgrub thabs 'di la spyi don gsum ste /
NK011(da)001:5686: de yang bsnyen pa'i skabs su bid+yot+ta ma las /
NK011(da)001:5687: gling bzhi pa yi b+hany+dza la //
NK011(da)001:5688: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad e dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:5689: phur bu spungs la bsnyen pa bya //
NK011(da)001:5690: bskyed dang spyan drangs bzhugs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:5691: mchod bstod la sogs rdzogs par bya //
NK011(da)001:5692: de nas rtsa ba'i snying po la //
NK011(da)001:5693: gsum gyi bsnyen pa gang yang rung //
NK011(da)001:5694: gcig gi dam bcas rdzogs pa dang //
NK011(da)001:5695: sgrub pa chen po brtsams pa ni //
NK011(da)001:5696: gong gi sa chog bzhi rjogs nas //
NK011(da)001:5697: gnas tshod sbyar la man+dala brtsigs //
NK011(da)001:5698: lnga yi go ye gnyis kyi thig /
NK011(da)001:5699: tshon lnga 'bru lngas byin gyis brlabs //
NK011(da)001:5700: de nas dkyil 'khor bri ba ni //
NK011(da)001:5701: e khram 'khor lo rtsibs khyams bcas //
NK011(da)001:5702: nyis brtsigs sgo dang ldan par bri //
NK011(da)001:5703: 'dod yon pha gu d+r+wa ba dang //
NK011(da)001:5704: dar bu kad dang ldan par bri //
NK011(da)001:5705: rta babs gdugs dang bcas pa dang //
NK011(da)001:5706: ra ba me sogs ldan par bri //
NK011(da)001:5707: de ltar dkyil 'khor rdzogs nas ni //
NK011(da)001:5708: lha grangs tshang ba'i phur pa la //
NK011(da)001:5709: bdun gnyis gsum gyi las rdzogs nas //
NK011(da)001:5710: dkyil 'khor nyid du dgod par bya //
NK011(da)001:5711: mda' dang mtshon gyis bri bar bya //
NK011(da)001:5712: dar dang me long ral gri dang //
NK011(da)001:5713: rgyan la sogs pa tshang bar bkram //
NK011(da)001:5714: de nas mchod pa'i yo byad ni //
NK011(da)001:5715: tshe gal sogs pa'i ba ling dang //
NK011(da)001:5717: de nas bya ba rdzogs nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5718: slob ma phyir la bzhag nas ni //
NK011(da)001:5719: snga ba'i lha la mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:5720: 'dres pa bsre ba zin nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5721: ma 'dres pa rnams bsre ba ni //
NK011(da)001:5722: phyi ru bum khrus byas nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5723: dar la sogs pas mig bkab ste //
NK011(da)001:5724: de nas drangs pa'i cho ga bya //
NK011(da)001:5725: dor bas gar babs lha yang sbyin //
NK011(da)001:5726: dam tshig bsgrags la dam chu blud //
NK011(da)001:5727: gsang mtshan btags te gral du bzhag /
NK011(da)001:5728: des kyang de la gtang rag gtong //
NK011(da)001:5729: de nas sdig bshags la sogs bgyis //
NK011(da)001:5730: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bskyed nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5731: mchod bstod la sogs rdzogs par bya //
NK011(da)001:5733: so so'i bskul dang bcas pa yi //
NK011(da)001:5734: gtso nas 'khor du rkang thon du //
NK011(da)001:5735: bshags dang bcas te rdzogs par bya //
NK011(da)001:5736: dngos grub dam pa blangs bar bya //
NK011(da)001:5737: dbang yang rim pa bzhin du bskur //
NK011(da)001:5738: sgrub pa chen po rdzogs nas ni //
NK011(da)001:5739: las la sbyar ba brtsam par bya //
NK011(da)001:5740: dang po drug gi 'khor lo bskor //
NK011(da)001:5741: khri khri thon nas smon lam btab //
NK011(da)001:5742: 'khor lo rdzogs nas btab pa ni //
NK011(da)001:5743: go ye thig dang tshon brlabs pa //
NK011(da)001:5744: dang po dag dang mthun pa'o //
NK011(da)001:5745: de nas dkyil 'khor bri ba ni //
NK011(da)001:5746: e khram bcu gnyis gcig dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:5747: khyams dang sgor ni ldan par bri //
NK011(da)001:5748: de nyid yum gyi mkhar byin rlabs //
NK011(da)001:5749: de la sras mchog bzhugs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:5750: 'khor lo ling ga de dbus gtod //
NK011(da)001:5751: bskyed mchod la sogs gong dang mthun //
NK011(da)001:5752: pho nyas dus bzhir dag tu dgug /
NK011(da)001:5753: de re la yang gzir mnan bya //
NK011(da)001:5754: rtsa sngags 'dus pa bzhi yi sngags //
NK011(da)001:5755: bzlas shing bsgrub bya nyid la btab //
NK011(da)001:5756: de ltar bzlas pa tshang nas ni //
NK011(da)001:5757: nyi shu rtsa gcig phur bu yis //
NK011(da)001:5758: nyi shu rtsa gcig gnad la btab //
NK011(da)001:5759: gtubs dang brdungs sogs rdzogs nas ni //
NK011(da)001:5760: de nyid dum bu gsum du bcad //
NK011(da)001:5761: cha gcig bstab pa bya bar gsungs //
NK011(da)001:5763: cha gcig mnan pa'i las bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5764: po de bzhi dang ldan pa yi //
NK011(da)001:5765: gso ba gsum gyi cho ga bya //
NK011(da)001:5766: lha gshegs bsdus la mi dmigs pa'i //
NK011(da)001:5767: ngang du bsgoms te ma dal bsdus //
NK011(da)001:5768: yi ge brgya pa'i bshags pa bya //
NK011(da)001:5769: de nas stong pa'i ngang las ni //
NK011(da)001:5770: mthing nag h'u du bsgom par bya //
NK011(da)001:5771: de las zhe sdang rdo rjer bdag /
NK011(da)001:5772: bskyed la rgyun gyi yi dam bya //
NK011(da)001:5773: bsnyen sgrub gsum gyi tho byang 'di //
NK011(da)001:5774: gang zag blo dman rnams la phan phyir brtsams //
NK011(da)001:5775: nyes 'gal nongs par gyur pa ci mchis pa //
NK011(da)001:5776: 'phags dang mkhas pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen la //
NK011(da)001:5777: bzod par gsol lo tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)001:5782: yi ge 'bru dgu don mang na yang skabs 'dir /
NK011(da)001:5783: sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing dngos grub blang ba'i skabs 'dir /
NK011(da)001:5784: don rnam pa gsum gyis bstan te /
NK011(da)001:5785: phra mo'i ting 'dzin phyag rgya gsal tsam nyid nas chos nyid las ma g.yengs par /
NK011(da)001:5786: rig pa yid la gsal bas rang gi gnas sbyangs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5787: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i 'phro 'dus ye shes kyi lha nye bar bsnyen pa dang /
NK011(da)001:5788: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dngos kun gzhi byang chub sems /
NK011(da)001:5789: grub yum gyi mkha' las blangs pa'o //
NK011(da)001:5790: de la rang gi gnas sbyangs pa ni /
NK011(da)001:5791: bdag gis mi gnas pa'i ye shes phyag rgya gsal ba tsam nyid na rang bzhin med pa /
NK011(da)001:5792: kyi dpal chen po'i sku phyag rgya chen po bsgoms la /
NK011(da)001:5793: thugs kar rin po che zla ba rgyas pa'i dkyil
NK011(da)001:5794: na ye shes kyi he ru ka tshon gang ba
NK011(da)001:5795: gcig / de'i thugs kar gzhal yas khang ga'u zur brgyad /
NK011(da)001:5796: dbus dang dgu na nyi ma'i dal sran ma zlum po tsam dgu'i steng na /
NK011(da)001:5816: yi ge 'bru dgu po de bzlas brjod kyi dus
NK011(da)001:5817: na gcig la gcig 'phro zhing 'du bar bsgom pa
NK011(da)001:5818: ni / drod gsum las ting 'dzin gsal ba'i drod ces bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5819: 'phro 'du gsal zhing las su rung ba'i dus na'o //
NK011(da)001:5820: dpal chen por lhang nger shin tu gsal bar bsgoms
NK011(da)001:5821: pa de'i ljags kyi dkyil du pam las pad+ma 'dab
NK011(da)001:5822: ma brgyad pa dbus kyi lte ba dang dgu na
NK011(da)001:5823: yi ge 'bru dgu gong ma ltar bkod do //
NK011(da)001:5824: de'i don yid la bya ba'i phyir 'di skad do //
NK011(da)001:5825: skye med dbyings las 'bar ba'i skur snang ba //
NK011(da)001:5826: 'jigs byed chen po dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NK011(da)001:5827: thugs kyi dpal be'u rin chen ga'u las //
NK011(da)001:5828: yi ge 'bru dgu don gyi phra bkod pa //
NK011(da)001:5829: gug skyed klad kor tsheg bar zur phyin te //
NK011(da)001:5830: ljags la pad+ma'i 'bru dgu gsal bar bsgom //
NK011(da)001:5831: rnam gsum dus gcig yid la gsal la gyur pa //
NK011(da)001:5832: bdag ye shes sems dpa' k+ai la ya 'bru dgu /
NK011(da)001:5833: ra ri kha khol med par dran gsal zhing //
NK011(da)001:5834: chos nyid rdo rje gsung gi glu blangs pas //
NK011(da)001:5835: a ni ma skyes don gyi gsung du rig /
NK011(da)001:5836: yid kyi sngags tshig bar chad med par bzlas //
NK011(da)001:5837: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aam bam h'u h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:5839: tsit+ta rin chen zur brgyad kyi //
NK011(da)001:5840: gsang chen thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:5841: byang chub sems yig 'bru dgu po //
NK011(da)001:5842: gu h+ya gsang ba'i lam du byung //
NK011(da)001:5843: yang gsang dbugs kyi rlungs gis bskyod //
NK011(da)001:5845: gsang ba'i yi ge h'u gis drangs //
NK011(da)001:5846: klad pa dung gi gzhal yas su //
NK011(da)001:5848: shangs kyi rlung sgrom chen po nas //
NK011(da)001:5849: rdo rje h'u ring sgra las drangs //
NK011(da)001:5851: thugs ka'i 'od dang ljags kyi 'od bsnol mar bstim nas yang 'di skad do //
NK011(da)001:5852: rin chen gser gyi de yang h'u las dang po spros /
NK011(da)001:5854: yi ge 'bru dgu'i phra brgyus pas //
NK011(da)001:5855: dril bu'i sgra ltar rgyun mi chad //
NK011(da)001:5856: phar spros pas ni thugs dam bskul //
NK011(da)001:5857: tshur 'dus pas ni tshogs chen rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:5858: dpal chen thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:5859: ye shes yi ge 'bru dgu po //
NK011(da)001:5860: ljags las gsal bar pa phra bkod nas //
NK011(da)001:5861: mkhur ba dbugs kyi rlung gis bskyed //
NK011(da)001:5862: klad pa gzhal yas khang du spro //
NK011(da)001:5863: rigs lnga dpal gyi sku la thim //
NK011(da)001:5865: yi ge 'bru dgus stong khams gang //
NK011(da)001:5866: slar bsdus pas ni thugs kar 'dus //
NK011(da)001:5867: thugs ka'i dpal be'u zur brgyad kyi //
NK011(da)001:5870: gnas kyi bsnyen pa zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)001:5871: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ye shes lha rnams bsnyen pa ni //
NK011(da)001:5872: bdag nyid dpal gyi skur bsgoms nas //
NK011(da)001:5873: de yi thugs kyi dkyil 'khor na //
NK011(da)001:5874: ye shes sems dpa' he ru ka /
NK011(da)001:5875: khro bo'i tshul du gsal bar bsgoms //
NK011(da)001:5876: de yi thugs kyi dkyil 'khor na //
NK011(da)001:5877: dpal be'u rin chen zur brgyad la //
NK011(da)001:5878: yi ge 'bru dgu phra bkod de //
NK011(da)001:5879: spro zhing bsdu ba'i 'od zer ni //
NK011(da)001:5880: gser gyi ba thag gzengs pa bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5881: spros pas mer mer stong khams gang //
NK011(da)001:5882: phar 'phros pas ni thugs dam bskul //
NK011(da)001:5883: slar bsdus pas ni dpal be'u bkang //
NK011(da)001:5884: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:5885: dpal be'u rin chen zur brgyad las //
NK011(da)001:5887: phar 'phros pas ni thugs kar thim //
NK011(da)001:5888: ye shes lung gis bskyed nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5889: shangs kyi rlung sgrom chen por 'byung //
NK011(da)001:5890: slar 'dus pas ni dpal be'u bkang //
NK011(da)001:5891: mgal me klad la bskor ba bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5894: yid bzhin rin chen zur brgyad las //
NK011(da)001:5896: lcags kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa brdabs pa bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5897: ljags kyi rtse la gtor nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5898: phar 'phros pas ni ljags la thim //
NK011(da)001:5899: slar 'dus pa ni thugs ka'i dkyil //
NK011(da)001:5900: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar thim //
NK011(da)001:5902: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la bdag nyid dpal chen skur bsgoms te //
NK011(da)001:5903: de yi thugs kyi da la ru //
NK011(da)001:5904: ye shes sems dpa' he ru ka /
NK011(da)001:5905: de yi thugs kyi da la ru //
NK011(da)001:5906: yid bzhin rin chen zur brgyad pa //
NK011(da)001:5907: yi ge 'bru dgu phra bkod de //
NK011(da)001:5908: ljags kyi pad+ma'i da la ru //
NK011(da)001:5909: yang nas yang du phar 'phros pas //
NK011(da)001:5910: spros pas mer mer stong gsum gang //
NK011(da)001:5914: de yi thugs kyi da la nas /
NK011(da)001:5915: don gyi yi ge 'bru dgu po //
NK011(da)001:5916: ljags kyi rtse la gtor nas ni //
NK011(da)001:5917: lcags kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa brdabs pa bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5918: bdag nyid dpal gyi thugs ka nas //
NK011(da)001:5919: ye shes yi ge 'bru dgu po //
NK011(da)001:5921: phar spro ba dang tshur bsdu ba //
NK011(da)001:5922: gser gyi ba thag gzings pa'am //
NK011(da)001:5923: mgal me klad la bskor ba bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5924: 'od zer spro bsdu rgyun mi chad //
NK011(da)001:5925: thugs nas ljags kyi dkyil du spro //
NK011(da)001:5926: 'brug gi sgra ltar rab bsgrags pas //
NK011(da)001:5927: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams zil gyis gnon //
NK011(da)001:5929: bsnyen pa'i dus ni rgyang ma ring //
NK011(da)001:5930: sgrub pa'i dus ni mthu ma chung //
NK011(da)001:5931: yang bsnyen yang ni yang bsnyen na //
NK011(da)001:5932: ye shes sems dpa' he ru ka /
NK011(da)001:5933: dam tshig sems dpa'i sku la thim //
NK011(da)001:5934: ye shes sems dpa'i yum rnams kyang //
NK011(da)001:5935: dam tshig sems dpa'i yum la thim //
NK011(da)001:5936: ye shes sems dpa'i 'khor rnams kyang //
NK011(da)001:5937: dam tshig sems dpa'i 'khor la thim //
NK011(da)001:5938: gnyis su med par gyur pa ni //
NK011(da)001:5940: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la byang chub sems ni dngos grub mchog /
NK011(da)001:5941: de rig byang chub rig pas rig /
NK011(da)001:5942: chags pa'i bdag nyid dpal gyi yum //
NK011(da)001:5943: yum gyi mkha' la blang ba ni //
NK011(da)001:5944: ra ni r+aa ga'i sgra drangs nas //
NK011(da)001:5945: skye shi len pa'i khrag yin te //
NK011(da)001:5946: ra ni r+aa ga'i sgra drangs nas //
NK011(da)001:5947: 'dod pa'i dbang mo yum gyi mkha' //
NK011(da)001:5948: sangs rgyas kun gyi skyed mos tshal //
NK011(da)001:5949: gru gsum dgyes pa'i pho brang mchog /
NK011(da)001:5950: a las zla ba'i dal la ru //
NK011(da)001:5951: byang chub sems ni +aam dmar du snang //
NK011(da)001:5952: spros pa med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK011(da)001:5953: mi gnas ye shes dpal chen po //
NK011(da)001:5954: nyi ma'i da la gsang sbubs gang //
NK011(da)001:5955: ye shes rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NK011(da)001:5956: byang chub sems ni dkar po //
NK011(da)001:5957: ga bur shel gyi da la ste //
NK011(da)001:5958: gsang ba brda yis mtshon nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:5959: dang lam gyis byin rlabs nas //
NK011(da)001:5960: dkar dmar bsnol mar bstim pa las //
NK011(da)001:5962: badz+ra ka'i li k+ai la ya gnyis med 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya las //
NK011(da)001:5964: mgal me klad la bskor ba bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5965: rdo rje rtse lnga'i gsang sbubs nas //
NK011(da)001:5967: sku yi gsang brgyud shangs g.yon nas phyung //
NK011(da)001:5968: thabs chen yab kyi shangs g.yas su thim //
NK011(da)001:5969: sku klad pa'i rgyas su phyung /
NK011(da)001:5970: mchog phyag rgya'i gsang du drangs //
NK011(da)001:5971: ye shes rdo rje'i lam du phyungs //
NK011(da)001:5972: pad+ma'i gzhal yas khang du spro //
NK011(da)001:5973: mgal me klad la bskor ba bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5974: rgyun mi chad par bsgom par bya //
NK011(da)001:5975: gnyis su med pa'i dbyings nyid las //
NK011(da)001:5977: dbang phyug khro bo yab yum gyi //
NK011(da)001:5978: mdun gyi nam mkhar zla gam 'bar ba'i gzhal yas
NK011(da)001:5979: khang na dpal khrag 'thung gi tshogs sprin phung 'khrigs
NK011(da)001:5980: pa ltar / sbyor ba'i mtshams su thim nas spros //
NK011(da)001:5981: khro mo gsar ba'i dbyings su thim //
NK011(da)001:5982: ye shes sku yi gsang du phyung //
NK011(da)001:5983: rdo rje lnga'i lam du drangs //
NK011(da)001:5984: khro mo'i gsang ba'i dbyings su thim //
NK011(da)001:5985: bde gshegs kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)001:5986: yi ge 'bru dgu'i phyag rgyar gsal //
NK011(da)001:5987: phyag rgya'i da la sprin phung bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5988: yi ge 'bru dgu'i dbyings su thim //
NK011(da)001:5989: yi ge phyag rgya 'od du spros //
NK011(da)001:5990: yab yum gsang ba'i dbyings su thim //
NK011(da)001:5991: mu tig phreng ba brgyus pa bzhin //
NK011(da)001:5992: gsal shing 'tsher bar gyur pa dang //
NK011(da)001:5993: dngos grub rnams gsum tshul bzhin blangs //
NK011(da)001:5994: zla gam ljags kyi da la ru //
NK011(da)001:5995: dam tshig phyag rgya'i dngos grub blangs //
NK011(da)001:5996: pad+ma r+aa ga'i 'od kyi da la nas //
NK011(da)001:5997: yi ge 'bru dgu gru gsum phyag rgya'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:5998: ge sar stong gis brgyan pa'i da la na //
NK011(da)001:5999: dpal chen he ru ka'i thugs rin po che //
NK011(da)001:6000: thams cad ma lus bde chen dbyings su rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:6001: mtshan ma'i spros bral bde chen dbyings su thim //
NK011(da)001:6003: gsang ba'i dbang la sogs pa rim par blang ngo //
NK011(da)001:6005: bar 'dir 'dzab dbyangs zhes pa zhig gsan yig la
NK011(da)001:6006: bzhugs kyang dpe rgyun 'di la ma byung bas 'di
NK011(da)001:6007: rigs dpe rgyun rnyed na gal che ba yin no
NK011(da)001:6008: //// phur pa'i tshe chog slob dpon pad+mas mdzad pa bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:6009: phur pa'i tshe 'gugs pa'i las bya na /
NK011(da)001:6010: dkyil 'khor 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa byas la der lha rnams bkod de /
NK011(da)001:6013: rin po che sna tshogs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:6014: 'bru sna tshogs pa mar rnying pa dang bsres la /
NK011(da)001:6015: sku gsung thugs kyi ril bu gsum byas la rin
NK011(da)001:6016: po che'i bum pa'i nang du bstsal la kha dar
NK011(da)001:6017: tshon sna lngas gzungs thag btags la de dal gyi
NK011(da)001:6019: sman phud dang gtor ma dang rak+ta dang me tog dang /
NK011(da)001:6021: de nas rdo rje khros pa nas mar gzhung bsrangs la bskyed pa'i rim pa zin pa dang /
NK011(da)001:6022: spyan drangs ba dang phyag dang mchod bstod la sogs pa rdzogs par byas la /
NK011(da)001:6023: ting nge 'dzin dang bcas pas 'dzab bgrang ste /
NK011(da)001:6024: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aam bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:6026: ru ru spu ru dz+wa la tish+tha lo tsa ni
NK011(da)001:6027: h'u sarba ar+tha sid+d+hi ni shang ka ri shang ka
NK011(da)001:6029: de nas tshe'i pho nya bskul ba ni /
NK011(da)001:6031: dbus kyi phyogs nas tshe 'gugs pa //
NK011(da)001:6032: bcom ldan rdo rje gzhon nu ste //
NK011(da)001:6033: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK011(da)001:6034: lha chen gdan la yang dag bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:6036: g.yas pas tshe yi bum pa bsnams //
NK011(da)001:6037: g.yon pa tshe 'gugs lcags kyu bsnams //
NK011(da)001:6038: ma chags mdangs kyis gtso la 'khril //
NK011(da)001:6039: yab yum rol pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK011(da)001:6041: dbus kyi phyogs nas tshe khug cig /
NK011(da)001:6042: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:6043: do nub tshe 'gug phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:6044: tshe dbang thams cad 'dir stsol cig /
NK011(da)001:6045: bkra shis rgyal po tshe yi yab //
