NK011(da)001:7733: nyi shu rtsa gcig zhal du bstab //
NK011(da)001:7734: man ngag gsum gyi khog sdebs la //
NK011(da)001:7735: 'chi kha ma yi man ngag snying la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:7736: las kyi rtag pa bsgom par bya //
NK011(da)001:7737: rdo rje bdud 'joms bdag gis kyang //
NK011(da)001:7738: bla ma'i gdams ngag steng nas bkrol //
NK011(da)001:7739: dbang dang dam tshig yongs su mnos //
NK011(da)001:7740: bsnyen sgrub yan lag mtha' ru dbyung //
NK011(da)001:7742: de ltar sems la bzhag par rigs //
NK011(da)001:7745: // gab pa'i sngags dgu'i gsal byed yod do //
NK011(da)001:7746: de la gab pa'i sngags dgu ni tshig tu yang 'di skad do //
NK011(da)001:7747: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs nas /
NK011(da)001:7750: gtogs la thal bar lhogs shig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:7751: ha sa ya ra hri da na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7752: gang yin pa sdong grogs phrol gcig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:7753: sh+ai kring a na ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7754: rings par khug la ching shig go //
NK011(da)001:7755: dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7756: smra zhing smyo ru chug go //
NK011(da)001:7757: a be sha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7758: gzugs dang ris mo la phob cig go //
NK011(da)001:7760: dbang du bsdus la thal phyungs shig go //
NK011(da)001:7761: m+aa ra se na sod la khrag tu skyug tu chug cig go //
NK011(da)001:7762: pra mar ta ni phur pa sus kyang mi phyin pa'i don no //
NK011(da)001:7763: sarba a na ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7764: nye bar 'ongs pa thams cad bka' nyon cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:7766: gab pa'i sngags dgu'i dbyibs sdom sngags zhes bya bas bstan te /
NK011(da)001:7767: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u pa ra bid
NK011(da)001:7768: t+wan tshina d+ha tshina d+ha m+aa ra ya h'u phata
NK011(da)001:7769: / badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya pa ra bid
NK011(da)001:7770: t+wan bina d+ha bina d+ha m+aa ra ya h'u phata
NK011(da)001:7771: / / badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya pa ra
NK011(da)001:7772: bid t+wan gri h+na grih+na m+aa ra ya h'u phata
NK011(da)001:7773: / / / badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya pa
NK011(da)001:7774: ra bid t+wan ha na ha na m+aa ra ya
NK011(da)001:7775: / / / h'u phata / badz+ra k+ai li k+ai
NK011(da)001:7776: la ya pa ra bid t+wan bna d+ha bna d+ha
NK011(da)001:7778: ma ra se na pra marta na ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7788: a tsi te a pa r+aa tsi te /
NK011(da)001:7789: sngags kyi 'phyong drug gong bzhin thogs shig /
NK011(da)001:7790: su ru mu ru sprel ba la yang sngags 'phyong drug gong bzhin thogs /
NK011(da)001:7791: h'u ma ma p+aa sham ka ru'i tshan la yang gong bzhin btags /
NK011(da)001:7792: ta th+aa ya bcug nas snga ma'i gnas su 'byin
NK011(da)001:7793: pa la sngags kyi 'phyong drug gong bzhin thogs shig
NK011(da)001:7797: // // gab pa'i sngags dgu'i gsal byed bzhugs /
NK011(da)001:7798: gter chen gsan yig tu mi snang /
NK011(da)001:7799: mi g.yo rengs par dgug pa ste //
NK011(da)001:7800: bna d+ha rnams ni brjod byas la //
NK011(da)001:7801: pho nya gang yin khug par bya //
NK011(da)001:7802: stobs chen btags pa'i las shis te //
NK011(da)001:7803: ta th+aa ya zhes rab brjod la //
NK011(da)001:7804: gtun du lan gcig brdung bar bya //
NK011(da)001:7805: dbyug pa sngon pos dbye bar bya //
NK011(da)001:7806: ha sa zhes brjod gu gul bdug /
NK011(da)001:7807: rnam par rgyal bas bzung ba ste //
NK011(da)001:7808: bina d+ha zhes brjod bsgrub bya bzung //
NK011(da)001:7809: ma mo rnams kyis bcing bar bya //
NK011(da)001:7810: sh+ai kring zhes brjod byad du gzhug /
NK011(da)001:7811: gshin rje gshed pos bsdig pa ste //
NK011(da)001:7812: dz+wa la pa zhes smra ru gzhug /
NK011(da)001:7813: rta mgrin rgyal pos dbang bsdus te //
NK011(da)001:7814: grih+na zhes brjod dbang du bsdu //
NK011(da)001:7815: gzhan gyis mi thub gzir ba ste //
NK011(da)001:7816: ha na ha nas gzir bar bya //
NK011(da)001:7817: bdud rtsi 'khyil bas btab pa ste //
NK011(da)001:7819: khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba yis //
NK011(da)001:7821: bsgo ba'i bka' 'di nyan par gyis //
NK011(da)001:7822: 'di rnams brub khung las kyi lha //
NK011(da)001:7823: sgrub pa'i dus su bkod pa ste //
NK011(da)001:7824: thugs kyi sprul pa bcu gcig ste //
NK011(da)001:7825: rgyud las gab pa'i don 'dir phyung //
NK011(da)001:7826: gang na gnas kyang brub khung lha //
NK011(da)001:7827: sgo bzhi'i phur pa bzhi po dang //
NK011(da)001:7828: zangs phur tsan+dana phur pa yang //
NK011(da)001:7829: grogs kyi phur par shes par bya //
NK011(da)001:7832: dam can gnad la dbab pa dang /
NK011(da)001:7833: rtsa bas khams gsum bsgral ba dang /
NK011(da)001:7834: gzir mnan drag pos brdung ba dang /
NK011(da)001:7835: bsgral nas mchod par bstab pa dang /
NK011(da)001:7836: snying po drag tu bzlas pa dang /
NK011(da)001:7837: gab pa'i sdom pa bzung ba dang drug go //
NK011(da)001:7838: dam can gnad la dbab pa ni /
NK011(da)001:7839: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:7841: rtsa bas khams gsum bsgral ba ni /
NK011(da)001:7842: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:7844: gzir mnan drag pos brdung ba ni /
NK011(da)001:7845: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtan bya ba nas mar ro //
NK011(da)001:7846: bsgral nas mchod par bstab pa ni /
NK011(da)001:7847: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kh+aa hi bya ba nas mar ro //
NK011(da)001:7848: snying po drag tu bzlas pa ni /
NK011(da)001:7849: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas pa nas mar ro //
NK011(da)001:7850: gab pa'i sdom pa bzung ba ni /
NK011(da)001:7852: zhes bya ba nas mar ro //
NK011(da)001:7855: // de lta bu'i man ngag zab mo la gsang ma thub na bka' rkun dam nyams pa yin pas /
NK011(da)001:7856: khro bo med dbal gyis lus dang rnam par shes pa tshig pas nyen rab tu che'o //
NK011(da)001:7857: snod ma yin pa la mi spel lo //
NK011(da)001:7858: man ngag gsang ba'i mdzod ces bya ba rdzogs so //
NK011(da)001:7861: // // gdab las kyi made'u kha gsal byed bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:7862: nub dang po la zangs phur la sogs pa rdo
NK011(da)001:7863: rje gzhon nu'i skur bskyed la sku gsung thugs su
NK011(da)001:7864: dbang bskur / lcags ri'i nang du rim pas btsugs la /
NK011(da)001:7865: de nas cho ga gzhung bsrangs te 'dzab thon pa dang /
NK011(da)001:7866: las kyi sbyor kha las 'byung ba bzhin du pho nyas khug par byas la zangs phur sgril zhing /
NK011(da)001:7868: rdo rje gzhon nu 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK011(da)001:7869: pho nya dang yang sprul dang bcas pa'i bka' bden
NK011(da)001:7870: pa dang / thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK011(da)001:7871: bdag cag gi dgra bo dang dam nyams pa che
NK011(da)001:7872: ge mo 'di zangs phur gyis rnam par shes pa
NK011(da)001:7873: gnas nas khug par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:7874: ces brjod de sngags bzlas pas /
NK011(da)001:7875: ting nge 'dzin gyi phur pa rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur gsal ba las /
NK011(da)001:7876: sprul pa lcags kyu thogs pa 'jig rten gyi khams
NK011(da)001:7877: gang bar 'phros pas gzas po'i snying gar gzung nas
NK011(da)001:7878: brub khung gi khar dngos su 'ong bar bsam mo
NK011(da)001:7879: // de nas tsan+dana gyi phur pa sgril zhing bden pa bdar la /
NK011(da)001:7880: bdag gis dgra bo dam nyams pa'i bla 'di bdag gi dbang du 'dus par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:7882: phur pa'i skur gsal ba la phyag rgya bzhi'i sprul
NK011(da)001:7883: pa grangs med pa 'phros pas bla gang yin pa
NK011(da)001:7884: khug ste brub khung gi khar 'ong bar bsam mo
NK011(da)001:7885: // de nas rtsa bas bskul te /
NK011(da)001:7886: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:7887: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:7888: zung zhig rnam par gtogs par gyis //
NK011(da)001:7890: ta th+aa ya'i sngags kyis btab pas nus pa rmas par bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:7892: bdag cag gis dgra bo che ge mo 'di'i nus pa rmas par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:7893: ces phyag rgya bcas te sngags brjod pas gzugs dang bla nus pa rmas par bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:7895: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:7896: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:7897: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:7899: dbye ba'i rdzas lnga sbyar zhing grub pa'i rdzas //
NK011(da)001:7902: ch+gee mo'i srung ba'i pho lha dang dgra lha la
NK011(da)001:7903: sogs pa sdong grogs byed pa rnams dang phrol cig
NK011(da)001:7904: / ces brjod la byabs phur gyis gyen du byabs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:7906: ting 'dzin phur pa rdo rje gzhon nur gsal ba
NK011(da)001:7907: las sprul pa'i lha mo gu gul ma 'phros pas
NK011(da)001:7908: / kho'i stong grogs byed pa'i lha dpag tshad bgrang
NK011(da)001:7909: ba las 'das pa'i pho rol tu bskyal nas lha
NK011(da)001:7911: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:7912: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:7913: zungs shig chings shig rnam par chings //
NK011(da)001:7914: 'khril byed chen mos da khril cig /
NK011(da)001:7915: la sogs pas las bcol lo //
NK011(da)001:7917: sh+ai kring a na ya brjod de zhags pa'i phyag rgya dang bden pa brjod /
NK011(da)001:7918: ch+gee mo 'di byad du chug cig byas la sngags bzlas /
NK011(da)001:7919: ting nge 'dzin ye shes kyi zhags pa sngon dmar
NK011(da)001:7920: gyis cag ta dkris su bcings nas byad du bcug
NK011(da)001:7921: nas rkang pa'i mtha'i bar du bcings nas mi 'chor
NK011(da)001:7922: bar bsam mo // dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:7923: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:7924: rings par khug la rnam par phob //
NK011(da)001:7925: a be sha ya a be sha ya a /
NK011(da)001:7926: brub khung na byad bzhin gsal bar 'dug bar bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:7928: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:7929: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:7930: gzir cig rnam par smrar chug cig /
NK011(da)001:7932: ch+gee mo 'di skyer phur gyis bsdigs pas bred cing skrag basngangasa par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:7933: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya zhes bsgril bas skyer phur skur gsal ba las /
NK011(da)001:7934: rdo rje gzhon nur gsal bas rkang pa g.yas pas mnan pa ltar bya zhing btab tshul bstan pas /
NK011(da)001:7935: gzas pa po bred cig 'dar yed yed 'dug par bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:7936: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:7937: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:7938: nga yi dbang du gyur nas ni //
NK011(da)001:7939: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par gyis //
NK011(da)001:7942: ch+gee mo 'di mchog phur gyis dbang du 'dus par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:7944: zhes bzlas te bdag gis dgra bo dbang du 'dus par bsam /
NK011(da)001:7945: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK011(da)001:7946: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:7947: mnan cing rnam par gzir bar gyis shig byas la dang po lcags phur bsgril /
NK011(da)001:7948: phur pa skur gsal ba las 'od 'byung bas gzir
NK011(da)001:7949: zhing zil gyis mnan nas gar yang 'bros pa'i nus
NK011(da)001:7950: pa med de de nyid na 'dug par bsam mo
NK011(da)001:7951: // lam h'u lam gi dgongs pas zil gyis mnan pa gzhan du blta'o //
NK011(da)001:7952: de nas drag po'i phrin las la sbyor nas las kyi bzlas pa bya ste /
NK011(da)001:7957: rim pa bzhin du gnas nyi shu rtsa gcig tu dkyus las 'byung ba bzhin byas te btab /
NK011(da)001:7958: de yan chad ni bsam rgyud de /
NK011(da)001:7959: gzugs brnyan bca' ba'i rgyu ni don bsdus pa'i zhabs su shes par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:7961: ta th+aa ya spyi bo la'o //
NK011(da)001:7966: b+hina da ya gsang bar ro //
NK011(da)001:7967: ang gu sha mgrin par bkod do //
NK011(da)001:7969: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee mo zhes bya ba btags so //
NK011(da)001:7972: // drag po'i man ngag gi khog sdebs bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:7980: gsang ba'i rdzas drug ste drug drug sum cu rtsa drug gi man ngag go //
NK011(da)001:7983: man ngag tshig gsum ni slob dpon gyi thugs la gab par gsungs te /
NK011(da)001:7984: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dz+wa la dz+wa la /
NK011(da)001:7985: pra dz+wa la pra dz+wa la /
NK011(da)001:7987: sarba na sa a pa na ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7988: bde bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku'i ngo bo nyid kyi snying po nyid do //
NK011(da)001:7989: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:7990: bya kri pa la sarba dush+tana h+r+ai sho d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7991: gsung gi snying po nyid do //
NK011(da)001:7992: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya tshina d+ha tshina d+ha h'u /
NK011(da)001:7993: thugs kyi snying po nyid do //
NK011(da)001:7994: badz+ra lcags phur gyi k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba du sh+tan h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7995: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya skyer phur /
NK011(da)001:7997: pra su ru u tsush+ma kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7998: mchog phur badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya bing bing h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:7999: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ma ma ang gu sha tsan+dana gyi phur pa /
NK011(da)001:8001: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya bya rgod kyi gshog phur gyi /
NK011(da)001:8002: m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:8004: k+ai li k+ai la ya na mahs man+ta bi sho d+ha ya be ra be ra h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:8005: dgra bgegs m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:8006: de ni gab pa'i sngags dagu'o //
NK011(da)001:8010: // rdo rje phur pa'i don bsdus pa bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:8011: man ngag 'di don bdun du 'dus te /
NK011(da)001:8012: phur pa sgrub pa'i thabs dang /
NK011(da)001:8018: mjug gnas bstan pa dang bdun no //
NK011(da)001:8019: de la phur pa sgrub pa ni /
NK011(da)001:8020: lo gcig zla ba re re zhing zhag bdun bdun sgrub bo //
NK011(da)001:8025: gshog rus la sogs pa la byin gyis brlab cing /
NK011(da)001:8026: 'dzab dang snying po bzlas shing bsnyen pa bgrang ngo //
NK011(da)001:8028: rdo rje gshon nu'i man ngag gi go rim bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8030: spyan drangs shing rgyun mi chad par 'bul lo //
NK011(da)001:8032: dgra gang la bya ba'i rjes sa dang /
NK011(da)001:8035: gcin rtug pa la gzugs bya /
NK011(da)001:8043: dbang po kun la btab bo //
NK011(da)001:8045: 'og min gyi gnas su rgyal ba'i sras su lha'i skur bskyed de btang ngo //
NK011(da)001:8046: phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i bro gzhan dang mthun no ////
NK011(da)001:8047: phur nag chig chod kyi rtsa ba bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:8048: phur nag chig chod ces kyang bya //
NK011(da)001:8049: phur thun nag po zhes kyang bya //
NK011(da)001:8050: phur zor nag po zhes kyang bya //
NK011(da)001:8051: phur nag btab par gzas tsam na //
NK011(da)001:8052: gnod sbyin pho mo rengs par gyur //
NK011(da)001:8053: phur pa 'debs pas thun zhes bya //
NK011(da)001:8054: dngos su phur nag gcig pu btab pas go chod pas gcig chod ces kyang bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8055: rang gis ma phyin pa'i yul du byed na sngags rnam pa lnga dang /
NK011(da)001:8056: mnan pa rnam pa lnga dang /
NK011(da)001:8057: phur sngags lnga yang btab la phyogs su 'phangs na /
NK011(da)001:8058: gnod sbyin thams cad kyang phur nag re re 'phen
NK011(da)001:8059: te nam mkha' gang bar 'ong bas lha 'dre thams
NK011(da)001:8061: mgo bzhur lus bzhur yan lag bregs te gtong bas mi dga' ste rab tu gnod do //
NK011(da)001:8062: srog la bab na 'phangs pa las su la'ang mi rung ngo //
NK011(da)001:8063: phur bu nag po gcig la rgya mdud gong ma la /
NK011(da)001:8064: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzah zhes rdo rje gzhon nu bzhugs /
NK011(da)001:8065: rgya mdud bar ma la b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang /
NK011(da)001:8067: zhes lha mo lag pa g.yas na khrag gi zor thog pa /
NK011(da)001:8068: g.yon yungs kar gyi mda' thogs pa 'byung /
NK011(da)001:8069: rtse zur gsum la b+h+yo ril thum sod bris /
NK011(da)001:8070: gnod sbyin thams cad 'bod pa'i sngags /
NK011(da)001:8071: ri'u ri'u tri ma du sha sha dzah zhes 'bod do //
NK011(da)001:8073: ma tri a ru nan sha rbad /
NK011(da)001:8075: yug tri a ru nan pri du rbad /
NK011(da)001:8077: li yul pa a ru a ru nan ri ya rbad /
NK011(da)001:8079: shig tri shig tri a ru nan to ya rbad /
NK011(da)001:8081: ru ma du bya ba'i dgra rnams li kha a ru nan ga du rbad /
NK011(da)001:8083: gtan tshigs 'byung khungs skye rgyud mkhas //
NK011(da)001:8084: nyo tshong sha yi khang bug nas //
NK011(da)001:8085: ngan thabs rnam pa zhag dgu phyung //
NK011(da)001:8086: ngan sems bya ba'i dgra rnams la //
NK011(da)001:8087: las ni nam pa lnga ru bstan //
NK011(da)001:8088: mnan dang pho lha'i rdzas dang lnga //
NK011(da)001:8089: grangs lnga phur ba'i grangs lnga bstan //
NK011(da)001:8090: lnga tsho phur pa drug drug dbye //
NK011(da)001:8091: sbyin sreg bzhi po sgo sgor gdags //
NK011(da)001:8092: rno ldan le'u dog sgor gdags //
NK011(da)001:8094: rbad pa rnam pa gnyis kyis rbad //
NK011(da)001:8095: nub re las rnams 'tshogs pa ste //
NK011(da)001:8096: sbyor shes phrin las rdzogs pa ni //
NK011(da)001:8097: mi 'grub mi srid the tshom med //
NK011(da)001:8103: steng gi phyogs su kha bltas te //
NK011(da)001:8104: mi mjed tshangs pa 'khor bcas la //
NK011(da)001:8105: lta ba'i don gyi 'brel pa la //
NK011(da)001:8106: rdo rje gzhon nu'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:8107: snang srid khro bor dbang bskur nas //
NK011(da)001:8108: sgul skyod phur pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK011(da)001:8109: tshangs pa mi mjed 'khor bcas kyang //
NK011(da)001:8110: dbang med 'dar zhing skrag srid pas //
NK011(da)001:8111: rdo rje gzhon nu'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:8112: dmigs pa po la ma gtogs pa //
NK011(da)001:8114: do nub gzu dang dpang mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:8115: tri marta pra ni da la 'gi na 'gi ti sa ma ya h'u /
NK011(da)001:8116: rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzang na //
NK011(da)001:8117: lha yi dbang po brgya byin dang //
NK011(da)001:8118: nye dbang sum cu 'khor bcas kyang //
NK011(da)001:8119: snang srid khro bor bdag bsgoms pas //
NK011(da)001:8120: de kun 'dar zhing skrag srid pas //
NK011(da)001:8121: rdo rje gzhon nu'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:8122: dmigs pa po la ma gtogs pa //
NK011(da)001:8123: brgya byin gnas su mi 'debs kyi //
NK011(da)001:8124: do nub gzu dang dpang mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:8125: ngos bzhi'i rgyal chen rigs bzhi yang //
NK011(da)001:8126: snang srid khro bor bdag bsgoms pas //
NK011(da)001:8127: sgul skyod thams cad phur pa ste //
NK011(da)001:8128: rdo rje gzhon nu'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:8129: dmigs pa po la ma gtogs pa //
NK011(da)001:8130: rgyal chen bzhi la mi 'debs kyis //
NK011(da)001:8131: do nub gzu dang dpang mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:8133: snang srid khro bor bdag bsgoms pas //
NK011(da)001:8134: sgul skyod phur pa'i rang bzhin pas //
NK011(da)001:8135: sa bdag klu gnyan 'dar srid pas //
NK011(da)001:8136: rdo rje gzhon nu'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:8137: dmig pa po la ma gtogs pa //
NK011(da)001:8138: sa bdag klu la mi 'debs kyis //
NK011(da)001:8139: do nub gzu dang dpang mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:8140: bar snang khams na gnas pa yi //
NK011(da)001:8141: gza' dang rgyu skar 'khor bcas kyang //
NK011(da)001:8142: snang srid khro bor bdag bsgoms pas //
NK011(da)001:8143: rdo rje gzhon nu'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:8144: dmigs pa po la ma gtogs pa //
NK011(da)001:8145: khyed la phur bu mi 'debs kyi //
NK011(da)001:8146: do nub gzu dang dpang mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:8147: srid pa'i lha 'dre la de skad bya /
NK011(da)001:8148: phud btang zhing bden pa bdar ro //
NK011(da)001:8149: sbas pa'i tshig drug gi sdebs dang /
NK011(da)001:8150: gab sngags dgu sdoms sngags dang /
NK011(da)001:8151: sngags nyi shu rtsa gcig gis gnas nyi shu rtsa gcig tu gdab pa dang /
NK011(da)001:8152: dbyung zhing gso ba bstan pa'o //
NK011(da)001:8156: // // dpal rdo rje phur pa'i sbyin sreg rong pa chos kyi bzang pos mdzad pa bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:8157: spyir sbyin sreg gi las bagyi'o 'tshal la dang po
NK011(da)001:8158: me lha mchod nas de nas 'dod pa'i lha mchod
NK011(da)001:8160: bya ba dang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud rnams kyi nang nas me lha mchod pa'i tshul snang ste /
NK011(da)001:8161: kha cig las ni me lha'i sngags kyis btab pa'i
NK011(da)001:8162: me tog thab tu bor bas de nyid kyis byin
NK011(da)001:8164: de nas me lha la sreg blugs phul te 'dod
NK011(da)001:8165: pa'i don gsol nas me bsangs te lha rim bzhin
NK011(da)001:8166: mchod ces grags / kha cig las ni thab tu
NK011(da)001:8167: dam tshig gi me lha bskyed de ye shes kyi
NK011(da)001:8168: me lha spyan drangs te bstim /
NK011(da)001:8169: mchod pa rdzogs nas me lha de nyid kyang me 'bar ba'i rnam par bsgyur bar bya zhes grags /
NK011(da)001:8170: kha cig las ni me lha'i thugs kar lha'i gzhal yas khang bsgom zhes kyang grags /
NK011(da)001:8171: zhal drug khro bo'i rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK011(da)001:8172: phyogs gcig tu ni bzhag nas ni //
NK011(da)001:8174: spyir basngagasa pa nyid ji ltar 'thad pa bzhin byas pa la nyes pa med do //
NK011(da)001:8175: gsang sngags rnal 'byor chen pos gzhung du me lham chod pa'i tshul ni rdo rje bkod pa las /
NK011(da)001:8176: me lha snang ba mtha' yas yab yum gyis bya zhes 'byung /
NK011(da)001:8177: rnam par snang mdzad sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud las
NK011(da)001:8178: ni gzhung spyi dang mthun par 'byung ste 'di dag
NK011(da)001:8179: gang ltar yang 'gal ba med do //
NK011(da)001:8180: spyir me lha la sogs pa ye shes kyi lha
NK011(da)001:8181: dang 'jig rten gyi lha thun mong du grags pa
NK011(da)001:8182: rnams la yongs su dag pa'i lha dang /
NK011(da)001:8183: yongs su ma dag pa'i lha zhes zung ldan du yod par grags la /
NK011(da)001:8184: de la ye shes kyi lha la mchod pa'i skabs
NK011(da)001:8185: su me lha yang zung ldan du bya zhes bzhed
NK011(da)001:8186: do // des na tshul gnyis gcig tu bsreg mi dgos te /
NK011(da)001:8187: tshul gcig nyid 'jig rten pa'i tshul du 'byung ba
NK011(da)001:8188: de nyid yongs su dag pa'i lhar yang dmigs pas
NK011(da)001:8189: chog go // de la khro bo'i skabs su cung zad khro bo'i rnam par bsgom /
NK011(da)001:8190: mchod pa'i rdzas ni gsang ba nang gi skabs su
NK011(da)001:8191: bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga dang sha rnam pa lngas
NK011(da)001:8192: gzhi bzung la tshogs kyi mchod pa nyid du gang
NK011(da)001:8193: dag 'byor pa thams cad kyis mchod par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8194: de yang gtso bor me 'bar bar gyur pa'i rdzas rnams la gzhi blang bar bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8195: spyir grags pa me 'bar ba'i rdzas dang /
NK011(da)001:8199: las grub par bya ba'i rdzas lta bu 'byung ba las /
NK011(da)001:8200: 'dir bsang ba'i rdzas thams cad ni bdud rtsi nyid kyis bsangs pas chog go //
NK011(da)001:8201: yang na tshogs mchod spyi dang mthun par dri chab
NK011(da)001:8202: la khro mo dbang phyug ma'i sngags kyis bsangs pas
NK011(da)001:8203: kyang rung ngo // las grub par bya ba'i rdzas ni /
NK011(da)001:8204: drag po la dgra bgegs kyi lid+ga dang /
NK011(da)001:8205: lcags phye rdo phye dang dug dang ske mtshe dang /
NK011(da)001:8206: nyungs nag dang 'bru nag po'i chan la rak+tasa sbyar ba dag go //
NK011(da)001:8207: me ni lcags nag po las byung ba'am /
NK011(da)001:8208: bshan pa'i khyim nas blangs la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8209: thab khung dmar nag gru gsum du bya /
NK011(da)001:8210: bud shing la yang dug dang khrag gi chus gtor /
NK011(da)001:8211: sngags pa rdo rje skyil mo krung ngam rus sbal
NK011(da)001:8212: gyi 'dug stangs su 'dug ste kha lhor bltas la
NK011(da)001:8213: sbyin sreg gi rdzas g.yas su bzhag /
NK011(da)001:8214: bsang gtor gyi chu g.yon du bzhag /
NK011(da)001:8215: mdun du dgang gzar blugs gzar bzhag /
NK011(da)001:8219: dri chab la las thams cad pa'i sngags de bzlas te bsangs pa'am /
NK011(da)001:8220: yang na khro mo dbang phyug ma'i sngags sam /
NK011(da)001:8221: yang na rdo rje bdun rtsi'i sngags kyis bsang /
NK011(da)001:8222: de la a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:8224: badz+ra kro d+h+ai sarba dra byam bi sho d+ha ni h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:8226: badz+ra a mri te h'u h+r+aihth+aah rdo rje bdud rtsi'o //
NK011(da)001:8227: de dag gang yang rung bas bsangs te mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab pa tshogs spyi dang mthun /
NK011(da)001:8228: de nas thab tu b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang bskyed kyang rung /
NK011(da)001:8229: yang na me'i dkyil du yi ge ram dmar po
NK011(da)001:8230: las dam tshig me lha gsus pa che ba zhal
NK011(da)001:8234: mdog dmar po ral pa'i thor tshugs can gdan me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa /
NK011(da)001:8235: drag po'i las kyi 'od zer smug nag tu 'phro ba /
NK011(da)001:8237: phyag g.yas dang po mchog sbyin /
NK011(da)001:8239: g.yon dang po ril ba spyi blug /
NK011(da)001:8240: gnyis pa be con drang srong gi cha byad can rgyan med pa /
NK011(da)001:8241: 'khor drang srong rnams kyis bskor ba bskyed la /
NK011(da)001:8242: ye shes kyi me lha spyan drangs pa yang tshul 'di lta bu zhig gis spyan drangs par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8243: de la lag pa g.yas pa mi 'jigs pa'i phyag
NK011(da)001:8244: rgya bcas la mthe bong bskyod cing gsang sngags 'dis
NK011(da)001:8245: spyan drang ngo // tshur byon tshur byon 'byung po che //
NK011(da)001:8246: lha yi drang srong bram ze mchog /
NK011(da)001:8247: bsreg blugs zhal zas bzhes slad du //
NK011(da)001:8248: 'bar ba'i nang du bzhugs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:8249: ag+ne ye di bya di bya a bi sha ma
NK011(da)001:8250: h+aa ri she ye a bya ka bya b+ha ha
NK011(da)001:8253: lag pa g.yon pa'i rdo rjes me la bsang gtor byas te /
NK011(da)001:8254: nye ba'i mchod pa lnga drag po'i tshul dang mthun par byas te 'bul /
NK011(da)001:8255: gsang sngags ni 'di nyid kyis sbyar ba'o //
NK011(da)001:8256: de nas mar la sogs pa bsreg rdzas rnams la
NK011(da)001:8257: yang gsang sngags de nyid kyis lan gsum mam bdun
NK011(da)001:8258: nam nyi shu rtsa gcig la sogs ji ltar 'byor
NK011(da)001:8259: pa phul la bsang gtor bya ste /
NK011(da)001:8264: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK011(da)001:8265: spyan gsum ldan zhing 'gying bag can //
NK011(da)001:8266: zhal gsum dang ni phyag bzhir ldan //
NK011(da)001:8267: zhal nas rig byed smrang 'don zhing //
NK011(da)001:8268: 'od dmar ral pa thor tshugs can //
NK011(da)001:8269: me yi dkyil 'khor gdan la bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:8271: dang po'i phyag ni mchod sbyin mdzad //
NK011(da)001:8272: gnyis pa'i phyag ni bgrang phreng 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:8273: g.yon na ril pa spyi blug ste //
NK011(da)001:8274: gnyis pa don grub be con bsnams //
NK011(da)001:8275: mdog dmar rgyan ni med pa la //
NK011(da)001:8276: drang srong rnams kyis yongs bskor zhing //
NK011(da)001:8277: kun nas yongs su bstod pa la //
NK011(da)001:8278: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK011(da)001:8279: sngon gyi rgyal ba'i spyan snga ru //
NK011(da)001:8280: sbyin pa lha la stob mdzad par //
NK011(da)001:8281: ji ltar zhal gyis bzhes pa bzhin //
NK011(da)001:8282: de nyid 'grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK011(da)001:8283: cho ga lhag chad gyur pa dang //
NK011(da)001:8284: rdzas dang yo byad ma dag pa //
NK011(da)001:8285: thugs rjes bzod par bzhes nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:8286: tshangs pa yid bzhin stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)001:8288: de nas me lha 'bar ba nyid du gyur par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8289: gsang sngags thams cad kyang drag cing rgyun chags su bzlas te khros pa'i bsam pas bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8290: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la mchod par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8291: thab kyi nang du b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang khro bo'i lugs su bskyed la /
NK011(da)001:8292: de nas ye shes kyi lha rnams spyan drangs te
NK011(da)001:8293: phyag 'tshal ba dang spyi'i mchod pa 'bul ba'i rjes
NK011(da)001:8294: la / drag po'i phrin las la sbyar bar bya ste /
NK011(da)001:8295: de yang las bya ba'i tshul dang rim pa 'di skad du /
NK011(da)001:8296: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK011(da)001:8297: 'bar ba gtum chen rngams pa la //
NK011(da)001:8298: khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK011(da)001:8299: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK011(da)001:8300: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK011(da)001:8301: mtshan ma ming du bcas ba bya //
NK011(da)001:8302: bkug la rdo rje phur pas btab //
NK011(da)001:8303: dum bur byas la zhal du bstab //
NK011(da)001:8304: rdul du byas la tshogs la 'bul //
NK011(da)001:8306: drag po'i dkyil 'khor du khro bo dang khro mo
NK011(da)001:8307: 'khor dang bcas pa spyan drangs te dmar gyi a
NK011(da)001:8308: rgas gzhi bzung ba'i mchod pa sna tshogs phul la
NK011(da)001:8309: / de nas phrin las kyi dus su pho nya
NK011(da)001:8310: drag tu bskul te gzugs sam ri mo la phab
NK011(da)001:8311: la phur pa btab nas mtshon cha rnon pos gtubs
NK011(da)001:8312: te phye mar gyur pa dang /
NK011(da)001:8313: lcags phye dang dug la sogs pa dang sbyar te /
NK011(da)001:8314: phrin las bcol ba'i tshig dang sngags kyis bskul zhing
NK011(da)001:8315: lha'i zhal du bstab ste me thab tu bsreg par
NK011(da)001:8316: bya ste / de ni drag po spyi'i tshul lo //
NK011(da)001:8317: da ni skabs 'di nas mar la phrin las phur
NK011(da)001:8318: bu'i gzhung la brten te dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i las
NK011(da)001:8319: drag po'i sbyin sreg cung zad tsam bstan par bya

NK011(da)001:8624: gzigs te / yi ge 'di nyid kyang legs shing don dang ldan par gzigs nas bris so //
NK011(da)001:8625: snod ngan pa la bsdoms na bzang ngo //
NK011(da)001:8626: khong gis stong sgom la gnang ba'o //
NK011(da)001:8631: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK011(da)001:8632: bcom ldan dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yang //
NK011(da)001:8633: bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba'i skur ston pa //
NK011(da)001:8634: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs dpal gyi sku la 'khril //
NK011(da)001:8635: yum dang gnyis med rol pa thugs kyi sras //
NK011(da)001:8636: 'jigs byed khro bo pha bcu ma bcu yis //
NK011(da)001:8637: gdug rtsub 'bar ba dgra bo'i snying phyungs la //
NK011(da)001:8638: dpal chen yab yum zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK011(da)001:8639: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK011(da)001:8640: 'jigs byed chen po ye shes khro rgyal bcu //
NK011(da)001:8641: yum chen khro mo rnams kyi sku la 'khril //
NK011(da)001:8642: yab yum gnyis med rol pa'i thugs kyi sprul pa las //
NK011(da)001:8643: mkha' la rlung ltar rgyu ba'i mgo brnyan ma //
NK011(da)001:8644: gdug rtsub 'bar ba dgra bo'i snying phyungs la //
NK011(da)001:8645: khro rgyal yab yum zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK011(da)001:8646: zhe sdang dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yi //
NK011(da)001:8647: thugs las skyes pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)001:8648: dgra bgegs dkar nag dkyil du rgyab byas nas //
NK011(da)001:8649: gdug rtsub 'bar ba'i dgra bgegs snying phyungs la //
NK011(da)001:8650: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba'i sha khrag 'di //
NK011(da)001:8651: dpal chen yab yum tshogs la mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:8652: bstan pa 'jig pa'i dgra bo las ngan 'di //
NK011(da)001:8653: ming byang gtor mar mi bstab tu //
NK011(da)001:8654: rnal 'byor pa yi sku dgrar byung //
NK011(da)001:8655: bag chags drag po'i hom du sreg /
NK011(da)001:8656: hom ni za byed zhal gyi hom //
NK011(da)001:8657: za byed chen po'i zhal hom du //
NK011(da)001:8658: ye shes chen po'i me sbar te //
NK011(da)001:8659: bag chags sgrib pa bsreg par bya //
NK011(da)001:8661: dz+wa la 'bar ba'i zhal du sreg byed ram //
NK011(da)001:8662: kh+aa hi gsol cig rnam shes dbyings su sbar //
NK011(da)001:8663: dang po bskyed kyang rnam shes dbyings nas bskyed //
NK011(da)001:8664: da ltar gnas kyang rtag chad mtha' la gnas //
NK011(da)001:8665: rtag chad mtha' la gnas pa'i nyon mongs 'di //
NK011(da)001:8666: tha mar bsgral yang chos kyi dbyings su bsgral //
NK011(da)001:8667: ma h+aa tsit+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)001:8668: ma ni 'byung ba lnga yi ngang //
NK011(da)001:8669: h+aa ni rig pa ye shes te //
NK011(da)001:8670: tsit+ta rnam shes byang chub sems //
NK011(da)001:8671: kha ram bag chags gsol ba yin //
NK011(da)001:8673: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i gtor chog bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:8674: de nas mnga' bdag dbu rtse'i shar sgo na bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK011(da)001:8675: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis gtor ma'i man ngag gnang /
NK011(da)001:8676: gtor ma bzang zhing grangs mang bar btang na byin rlabs che zhing bkra shis so //
NK011(da)001:8677: de la gtor ma chen po ni nya dang stong dang tshes brgyad dang nyi shu gnyis dang /
NK011(da)001:8678: sgrub pa thon pa'i dus dang /
NK011(da)001:8680: dbang gi dus su btang ngo //
NK011(da)001:8681: gtor phran ni nyi ma'i dmar thag dang nam gung la rgyun du bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8682: gtor ma'i gong du lha'i dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs te /
NK011(da)001:8683: ting nge 'dzin gyis bsdus te lha rnams 'od du zhu nas 'khor gtso bo la 'dus /
NK011(da)001:8684: gtso bo thugs ka'i h'u la 'dus /
NK011(da)001:8686: thig le mya ngan las 'das par bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:8687: de nas bdag las kyi rdo rje gzhon nur gsal
NK011(da)001:8688: ba'i thugs ka nas gtor ma la h'u sngon po
NK011(da)001:8689: spros / de nas gtor ma de kho na nyid
NK011(da)001:8690: kyi blo dam pas bzung la dag par bsam mo
NK011(da)001:8691: spros / // yang bdag gi thugs ka nas +aahdakara po spros /
NK011(da)001:8692: de nas gtor ma'i bdud rtsi 'phel te 'o ma'i
NK011(da)001:8693: mdog can ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa'i rgya mtshor
NK011(da)001:8694: bsam / yang bdag gi thugs ka nas kha dog
NK011(da)001:8695: sna tshogs pa spros pas gtor ma la 'od zer
NK011(da)001:8696: bsam / sna tshogs byung / 'od zer la 'dod
NK011(da)001:8697: pa'i yon tan lnga bsam gyis mi khyab pa spros
NK011(da)001:8698: bsam / sna tshogs byung / te / nam mkha'i khams gang bar bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:8699: lag pa g.yon pa'i sor mo gsum gdengs te gtor ma la bstan la /
NK011(da)001:8702: gtor ma la yig 'bru lnga bkod pas /
NK011(da)001:8704: ye shes kyi lha thams cad la phog ye shes lnga'i 'od zer sna tshogs dang /
NK011(da)001:8705: sangs rgyas kyi zhal gyi dngos grub ro bro ba'i
NK011(da)001:8706: mchog ces bya ba 'bras rdog po gcig la sangs
NK011(da)001:8707: rgyas grangs med pas gsol yang mi zad cing /
NK011(da)001:8708: bdud rtsi'i ngo bor grub pa de lta bu'i ye
NK011(da)001:8709: shes kyi bcud bsdus pas gtor ma la thim pas
NK011(da)001:8710: mang zhing bcud phun sum tshogs pa mi zad par
NK011(da)001:8712: bcom ldan rdo rje srin po bde gshegs kun gyi dngos //
NK011(da)001:8713: rtsa ba mnga' bdag sprul pa phyag brnyan ma //
NK011(da)001:8714: ye shes sgo ma las bzhi'i bde gshegs la //
NK011(da)001:8715: ye shes gtor ma 'bul lo rnam par rol //
NK011(da)001:8716: e h+ye hi badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh i dan /
NK011(da)001:8723: pany+tsa p+au dza ba lid+ta g+h+ri h+na g+h+ri h+na kh+aa hi kha hi h'u phata kyis phul /
NK011(da)001:8725: bcom ldan rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK011(da)001:8727: sprul pa'i khro rgyal yab yum dang //
NK011(da)001:8728: yang sprul za byed mgyogs byed dang //
NK011(da)001:8729: dkyil 'khor gsang ba'i sgo ma bzhi //
NK011(da)001:8730: mchod sbyin gtor ma bzhes nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:8731: bdag cag rnal 'byor spyod pa la //
NK011(da)001:8732: mi mthun rkyen dang bar chad bgegs //
NK011(da)001:8733: skeg dang zor kha bzlog tu gsol //
NK011(da)001:8734: b+h+yo zhes gtor mar rak+ta sbreng /
NK011(da)001:8735: ye shes kyi lha rnams kyis gsol bas tshim par
NK011(da)001:8736: bsams nas gtor ma dal nas phab ste phyar ba
NK011(da)001:8737: nag po zur gsum gyi steng du bzhag /
NK011(da)001:8738: lha rnams dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs kar h'u zhes pas bsdus la /
NK011(da)001:8739: gtor ma de byin rlabs cung zad gsos te /
NK011(da)001:8740: ba dan rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya lag pa g.yon
NK011(da)001:8741: pa'i mthe bong dang mathe'u chung gnyis bskum la sor
NK011(da)001:8742: mo gsum phral la gtor mar bstan /
NK011(da)001:8745: lha sngar ltar cung zhig bsgom /
NK011(da)001:8746: lhag ma'i phud logs su bsags pa rnams byin gyis brlabs te /
NK011(da)001:8747: rang gi ya rkan la dpal rta mgrin tshon gang ba /
NK011(da)001:8748: ma rkan la yum rdo rje gtun khung ma /
NK011(da)001:8749: de gnyis rol pa'i byang chub kyi sems bdud rtsi
NK011(da)001:8750: mu tig ltar bsams te dza gad kyis mkhur ba
NK011(da)001:8751: bkang ba lan gsum lhag mar bran /
NK011(da)001:8752: lhag ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho 'dod yon gyi 'od zer 'phro ba zad mi shes par bsam /
NK011(da)001:8754: gu ru tra ha ka sa ma ya bak+sha su
NK011(da)001:8755: gan su tri shi tri la tish+tha thangs ya sa
NK011(da)001:8757: bka'i pham phabs la gdags pa'i tshul lo //
NK011(da)001:8758: byang chub sems kyi sprin phung las //
NK011(da)001:8759: bdud rtsi dag pa'i char phab ste //
NK011(da)001:8760: 'khor gyi ma mo ma lus la //
NK011(da)001:8761: dgyes mnyam mchog gi sbyin pas bstim //
NK011(da)001:8763: gtor ma gong ma nas lhag gtor du dum zhig
NK011(da)001:8764: blugs la bsres tshul ni rtog pa spangs shing gnyis
NK011(da)001:8766: de nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams bkug ste /
NK011(da)001:8767: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer dmar po lcags kyu'i dbyibs can 'phros /
NK011(da)001:8768: zhing khams thams cad dang sngon grub pa'i gnas kun
NK011(da)001:8769: nas mkha' 'gro pho mo dam tshig can bkug ste
NK011(da)001:8770: / mdun du dur khrod kyi gnas la gnas par mos la sngags 'dis dgug go //
NK011(da)001:8771: e h+ye hi sarba d+aa ki ni sarba yo gi
NK011(da)001:8772: n+ai ru lu ru lu sa ma ya dzahdzah zhing
NK011(da)001:8773: khams sgrub gnas dur khrod mtha' dag nas //
NK011(da)001:8774: dam la gnas pa ji snyed bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK011(da)001:8775: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor gnas 'dir spyan 'dren na //
NK011(da)001:8776: thugs dam dbang gis ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:8780: thal mo dang bshugs pa'i brda bya /
NK011(da)001:8781: de nas 'khor zil gyis mnan te /
NK011(da)001:8782: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer bsam gyis mi
NK011(da)001:8783: khyab pa re re las rdo rje gzhon nu tshon
NK011(da)001:8784: gang ba du ma sprul pa 'khor rnams kyi spyi
NK011(da)001:8785: bor bzhag ste / sa ma ya rak+sha tham zhes zil gyis mnan /
NK011(da)001:8790: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te ya /
NK011(da)001:8791: ma ra sa ni pra marta ni ya /
NK011(da)001:8792: ma ma p+aa sham ku ru ya /
NK011(da)001:8793: ma ta da nya k+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:8796: sh+ai krang karma k+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:8797: ma tha ma tha badz+ra ya /
NK011(da)001:8798: dz+wa la dz+wa la badz+ra ya /
NK011(da)001:8799: su ru su ru badz+ra ya /
NK011(da)001:8812: ma tha ma tha ma ya /
NK011(da)001:8814: che ge mo'i tsit+ta go ro tsa na ba su ta /
NK011(da)001:8820: g+h+rih+na kh+aa hi kh+aa hi phata phata phata /
NK011(da)001:8822: bdag nyid chen mo mched bzhi dang //
NK011(da)001:8823: dam can bswe yi lha mo bzhi //
NK011(da)001:8824: shwa na mu kha mched bzhi dang //
NK011(da)001:8825: mkha' 'gro ma dang ging gi tshogs //
NK011(da)001:8826: dbang phyug chen mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK011(da)001:8827: blon mo bran mo mngags gzhug bcas //
NK011(da)001:8828: bran dang g.yog dang yang bran bcas //
NK011(da)001:8829: bka' yi gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK011(da)001:8830: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:8831: rnal 'byor dbang phyug bdag cag la //
NK011(da)001:8832: dam nyams dgra dang bar chad bgegs //
NK011(da)001:8833: skeg dang mi mthun gzhan gyi zor //
NK011(da)001:8834: bzlog cing brlag par mdzad du gsol //
NK011(da)001:8836: de nas thod rnga khyer la rkang gi gling bu
NK011(da)001:8837: dang thod rnga 'khrol shing gnas kyi phyi rol tu
NK011(da)001:8838: / brtan ma bcu gnyis la gtor ma bsngosa te /
NK011(da)001:8840: dam la gnas pa'i brtan ma'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:8841: gnam gyi rgyal mo dpal 'bar ma //
NK011(da)001:8842: gnam lha dkar mo yang dag shes //
NK011(da)001:8843: kha rag khyung btsun dpal gyi yum //
NK011(da)001:8844: kong btsun de mo bod khams skyong //
NK011(da)001:8845: gangs kyi yum chen g.yu bun ma //
NK011(da)001:8846: 'brog gnas ma mo me stag ma //
NK011(da)001:8848: byang gi rgyal mo zla 'od ma //
NK011(da)001:8849: byang sman rgyal mo gser thang ma //
NK011(da)001:8850: gangs dkar sha med kun tu bzang //
NK011(da)001:8851: sa bdag chen po sh+ain+tam dpal //
NK011(da)001:8852: klu yi bu mo gzi 'bar ma //
NK011(da)001:8853: mi bsrun rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs can //
NK011(da)001:8854: mdzes pa'i sku la rin chen brgyan //
NK011(da)001:8855: dar gyi le'u mu tig dang //
NK011(da)001:8856: dril bu g.yer ka'i rgyan cha ldan //
NK011(da)001:8857: sman bran 'bum gyi gtso mo mdzad //
NK011(da)001:8858: khros pas mi sdug gzugs 'chang zhing //
NK011(da)001:8859: gcan dang 'phro rgod zhi zhing rgyu //
NK011(da)001:8860: bran g.yog 'khor bcas gtor ma longs //
NK011(da)001:8861: bdag cag rig 'dzin sgrub pa la //
NK011(da)001:8862: dgra bgegs skeg dang zor kha dang //
NK011(da)001:8863: mi mthun phyogs rnams ji snyed pa //
NK011(da)001:8864: bzlog cing zhi bar mdzad du gsol //
NK011(da)001:8866: de nas dur khrod dam chu gling la stangs ltabs
NK011(da)001:8867: kyis gtor ma 'phen tshul bya zhing phud gtor dpang
NK011(da)001:8869: bar snang lha srin sde brgyad gson //
NK011(da)001:8870: gnams sa bar gyi lha 'dre gson //
NK011(da)001:8871: 'go ba'i lha lnga thams cad gson //
NK011(da)001:8872: mchod sbyin gser chung bzhes su gsol //
NK011(da)001:8873: gtor ma'i shul phyes sku bzur cig /
NK011(da)001:8874: dgra bgegs dpung gnyen ma mdzad cig /
NK011(da)001:8875: dam nyams dgra bgegs ngan pa 'dis //
NK011(da)001:8876: dkon mchog gsum gyi dbu 'phang smad //
NK011(da)001:8877: rnam par grub pa'i dam sri byas //
NK011(da)001:8878: nam yang btang bar mi bya bar //
NK011(da)001:8879: dgra bgegs gnas khyim bla srog la //
NK011(da)001:8880: zor dmag drang ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:8881: nad rims yugs kyi dmod mo yis //
NK011(da)001:8882: dgra bgegs bla srog rlung la skur //
NK011(da)001:8883: gtor zor khrag zor dgra la b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo //
NK011(da)001:8884: byas la gtor ma dgra phyogs su khros thabs su 'phang ngo //
NK011(da)001:8887: ting nge 'dzin gyis dgra bgegs la mkha' 'gro pho mos dmag drangs te /
NK011(da)001:8888: mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs nas dgra bgegs kyi lus la sha 'bus g.yeng ba ltar bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:8889: gtor ma chen po dang gtor phran stangs stabs de ltar bya 'grub na shin tu legs so //
NK011(da)001:8891: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:8892: zhes pas bka' brtan bskyang ba 'di gsungs so //
NK011(da)001:8893: zhes mnga' bdag la slob dpon pad+mas gnang ba'o //
NK011(da)001:8894: rdo rje phur pa'i gter chog rdzogs so //
NK011(da)001:8897: // // yi dam nar mar bya ba'i rim pa bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:8898: na mo sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra ye /
NK011(da)001:8899: rdo rje gzhon nu'i yi dam nar mar byed pa ni /
NK011(da)001:8902: rdo rje khros pas zhe sdang gcod //
NK011(da)001:8903: mtshon chen sngon po 'bar ba yi //
NK011(da)001:8904: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK011(da)001:8905: srog gi go ru shar ba dang //
NK011(da)001:8906: snying gi dkyil du bsgom par bya //
NK011(da)001:8907: zhes brjod la rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang las
NK011(da)001:8908: chos thams cad nam mkha'i dkyil ltar stong pa nyid
NK011(da)001:8910: rang gi byang chub kyi sems 'od kyi thig le
NK011(da)001:8911: rten dang bcas pa'i rang bzhin yi ge h'u gcig
NK011(da)001:8912: bsgom mo // snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK011(da)001:8913: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK011(da)001:8914: phung po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK011(da)001:8915: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK011(da)001:8916: zhes brjod pas sems can thams cad kyi lus sems
NK011(da)001:8917: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rtogs te
NK011(da)001:8918: lhun gyis grub pa'i snying rje byang chub tu sems
NK011(da)001:8919: bskyed do // badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aam bam h'u h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:8920: ces brjod pas byang chub sems kyi thig le las snying rje chen po'i dbang dang /
NK011(da)001:8921: gsang sngags kyi byin gyi rlabs kyis rdo rje gzhon
NK011(da)001:8922: nu'i sku le brgan tshon gang ba gzhal yas khang
NK011(da)001:8924: de nas dbang dang byin rlabs dang ldan pa'i yongs su rdzogs pa'i skur bskyed par bya ba'i phyir /
NK011(da)001:8925: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK011(da)001:8926: srid pa rdo rjer sgrub mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:8927: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK011(da)001:8928: ye shes khro bo sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:8929: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK011(da)001:8930: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings las //
NK011(da)001:8931: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NK011(da)001:8932: sku yi dbyig tu bdag bskyed cig /
NK011(da)001:8933: thabs kyi spyod par 'gro don du //
NK011(da)001:8934: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK011(da)001:8935: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad nas //
NK011(da)001:8936: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsol cig /
NK011(da)001:8937: ces brjod pas sangs rgyas rnams kyi byin gyi rlabs
NK011(da)001:8938: kyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i skur gyur pa ni 'di
NK011(da)001:8939: ltar / sku mdog mthing nag ri rab lta bu /
NK011(da)001:8940: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang na me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa /
NK011(da)001:8941: dur khrod kyi rgyan rnams kyis brgyan pa /
NK011(da)001:8942: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad pa /
NK011(da)001:8943: zhal g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing nag /
NK011(da)001:8944: phyag g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje rtse dgu pa /
NK011(da)001:8946: g.yon dang po na me dpung /
NK011(da)001:8947: bar pa na kha t+w+aam ka'i rgyan /
NK011(da)001:8948: tha ma gnyis kyis ri rab ltar brjid pa'i phur
NK011(da)001:8949: bu 'dril ba skad cig ma'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK011(da)001:8950: bsgom / yum 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma zhal gcig
NK011(da)001:8951: phyag gnyis g.yas pa yab kyi mgul nas 'khyud cing
NK011(da)001:8952: bsgom / / g.yon dung dmar gtso la stob pa
NK011(da)001:8953: gcig lus dang grib ma'i tshul du rang byung bar
NK011(da)001:8954: bsgom / / bsgom mo // de ni bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)001:8955: de nas phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK011(da)001:8956: gtso bo yab yum gnyis su med pa las /
NK011(da)001:8957: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u ka ra h'u /
NK011(da)001:8959: ces brjod pas sa bon gyi yi ge mi dgod par yab yum gyi dbang las bskyed kyang rung /
NK011(da)001:8960: byang chub kyi sems yi ge h'u du gyur pa
NK011(da)001:8961: las bskyed kyang rung ste khro bo chen po h'u
NK011(da)001:8962: k+aa ra skad cig ma'i ting nge 'dzin gyis bskyed
NK011(da)001:8963: do // yum rdo rje sgra 'byin ma yang lus dang grib ma'i tshul du byung bar bsgom /
NK011(da)001:8964: de'i sprul pa phra men phag gi mgo can dang
NK011(da)001:8965: rmig bu'i mgo can yang lus dang yan lag gi
NK011(da)001:8967: 'di ni rdzogs pa'i tshul yin te /
NK011(da)001:8968: rim gyis bskyed pa'i tshul ni sa bon h'u sgril ma yongs su gyur pa las /
NK011(da)001:8969: yab yum gnyis ka'i sngags kyis bskul bas khro bo yab yum bcu bskyed /
NK011(da)001:8970: khro bo yab yum bcu las byang chub kyi sems
NK011(da)001:8971: yi ge dz+dza ljang gu sbrel mar gyur pa las
NK011(da)001:8972: sprul pa'i phra men ma yab yum gsang sngags kyis
NK011(da)001:8973: bskul ba las bskyed par bzhed do //
NK011(da)001:8974: khro bo rnams ni zhal gsum phyag drug g.yas g.yon
NK011(da)001:8975: gyi dang po rdo rje dang dung chen dmar gyis
NK011(da)001:8976: bkang ba dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK011(da)001:8977: g.yas bar pa na phyogs skyong gi rgyal mtshan re re rgyal rtags su bsnams pa /
NK011(da)001:8978: g.yon bar pa na rang rtags kyi mtshan ma bsnams pa /
NK011(da)001:8979: tha ma gnyis kyis ri rab ltar brjid pa'i phur bu bsnams pa /
NK011(da)001:8982: kha cig lcags kyi phur par 'dod pa ni mtshams
NK011(da)001:8983: la sogs pas mtshon skabs 'ga' zhig tu khro bo'i
NK011(da)001:8984: sku phur par byas pa ste /
NK011(da)001:8985: 'di ni 'debs pa'i phur pa sras mchog phyag na yod pas /
NK011(da)001:8986: zhabs dkyus ma nyid du rigs so //
NK011(da)001:8987: yum rnams sku mdog phyag mtshan gtso dang mthun pa dang /
NK011(da)001:8988: za byed pha bcu ni g.yas na rgyal rtags kyi phyag mtshan /
NK011(da)001:8990: gsod byed ma bcu ni g.yas rigs kyi rang rtags bsnams pa /
NK011(da)001:8991: kun kyang tshul gcer bur yang rung /
NK011(da)001:8992: gyad kyi sham thabs tsam yang rung ngo //
NK011(da)001:8993: lha rnams kyi gnas dang go rim ni gzhung ltar ro //
NK011(da)001:8994: de ltar phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs nas /
NK011(da)001:8995: skabs 'dir las nar ma lta bu la byed na
NK011(da)001:8996: phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor byin gyis brlab ste
NK011(da)001:8997: / e'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol /
NK011(da)001:8998: mchod pa dang bzlas brjod nar mar byed tsa na
NK011(da)001:8999: phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor byin gyis brlab mi
NK011(da)001:9000: dgos te mchod pa'i cho ga la 'jug go //
NK011(da)001:9001: slob dpon kha cig phur pa byin gyis brlab pa'i
NK011(da)001:9002: cho ga bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i rjes
NK011(da)001:9003: thog tu byed pa yod na'ang /
NK011(da)001:9004: phur pa'i lha thams cad kyi byin rlabs phyag rgya
NK011(da)001:9005: yin pas dkyil 'khor rdzogs nas bya bar rigs so
NK011(da)001:9006: // de nas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs te /
NK011(da)001:9007: srid pa'i phur bu sgrub pa dang //
NK011(da)001:9008: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9009: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:9010: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:9011: rtags dang mtshan ma ston pa dang //
NK011(da)001:9012: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:9013: ces thod phreng gi phyag rgya smin mtshams su bcings nas /
NK011(da)001:9014: e h+ye hi b+ha ga b+aa na ma h+aa ka
NK011(da)001:9015: ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hohs
NK011(da)001:9016: ma ya s+t+wam / ru lu ru lu /
NK011(da)001:9017: zhes brjod cing thal mo brdab cing snying po brjod cing bstim /
NK011(da)001:9019: bskyed dang spyan drangs byon pa yi //
NK011(da)001:9020: gnyis med don gyis rab mdzes pa //
NK011(da)001:9021: 'bar ba ye shes khro bo'i sku //
NK011(da)001:9022: khro bo'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:9023: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+ha p+au dza a
NK011(da)001:9024: ti pu hoh a la la hoh de nas phyag
NK011(da)001:9026: sku mdog zhal ni rab bsgyur te //
NK011(da)001:9027: sku yi gar stabs glog 'gyu bas //
NK011(da)001:9028: 'bar ba'i khro bo mnyes bya ste //
NK011(da)001:9029: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9031: khro bo'i rgyal po phyag rgya can //
NK011(da)001:9032: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK011(da)001:9033: ljang nag dmar nag mthing nag zhal //
NK011(da)001:9034: dang po rdo rje rtse dgu me dpung 'bar //
NK011(da)001:9035: bar pa rdo rje rtse lnga kha t+w+aam ka /
NK011(da)001:9036: tha ma ri rab phur bu 'dril //
NK011(da)001:9037: brkyang bskum gyad kyi dor stabs bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:9038: 'di ni khro bo'i rgyal po yi //
NK011(da)001:9039: phyag rgya yin par dpa' bos bshad //
NK011(da)001:9040: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK011(da)001:9041: h'u chen mthing skya pad+ma rdo rje bsnams //
NK011(da)001:9042: rnam par rgyal ba rdo rje 'khor lo dkar //
NK011(da)001:9043: dbyug pa sngon po me dbal rin chen dbyug /
NK011(da)001:9044: gshin rje mthing nag be con dgra s+t+wa phyar //
NK011(da)001:9045: mi g.yo smug nag ral gri zhags pa snams //
NK011(da)001:9046: rta mgrin dmar po zhags pa spu gri bsnams //
NK011(da)001:9047: 'dod rgyal dmar skya ba dan rnga yab bsnams //
NK011(da)001:9048: bdud rtsi ljang sngon dbyug to rgya gram bsnams //
NK011(da)001:9049: khams gsum rnam rgyal ser po tri shul mda' gzhu bsnams //
NK011(da)001:9050: stobs chen dud kha lcags kyu tho ba snams //
NK011(da)001:9051: kun kyang dang po rdo rje b+han dmar gsol //
NK011(da)001:9052: g.yas g.yon tha ma ri rab phur bu 'dril //
NK011(da)001:9053: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9054: khro bo rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK011(da)001:9055: 'jigs tshul rngams pa gtso dang mthun //
NK011(da)001:9056: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9057: a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:9058: sngags brjod cing phyag rgya bcing /
NK011(da)001:9059: de nas rang byung zhes pa nas /
NK011(da)001:9060: thugs dam dbyig nyid ces pas yon tan brjod /
NK011(da)001:9061: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus dang //
NK011(da)001:9062: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu 'khor bcas la //
NK011(da)001:9063: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK011(da)001:9064: bzhes te kun tu dgyes par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:9065: 'phrul gyi dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK011(da)001:9066: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:9067: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum la //
NK011(da)001:9068: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9069: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:9070: yab yum gnyis med rol pa'i thugs las sprul //
NK011(da)001:9071: 'jigs byed chen po khro bo bcu rnams la //
NK011(da)001:9072: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9073: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:9074: khro bo'i sku la so sor dgyes par 'khril //
NK011(da)001:9075: sgra 'byin la sogs khro mo bcu rnams la //
NK011(da)001:9076: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9077: thugs rjes rtse dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:9078: phyogs bcu'i khro rgyal gnyis med thugs las sprul //
NK011(da)001:9079: sprul pa'i phra men mgo brnyan nyi shu la //
NK011(da)001:9080: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9081: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:9082: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:9083: bdud 'dul mthu chen ye shes khro bo'i rgyal //
NK011(da)001:9084: 'du 'bral med pa sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK011(da)001:9085: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9086: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:9087: sprul pa yang sprul sum sprul grangs med dang //
NK011(da)001:9088: bka' yi pho nya 'gug byed ma lus la //
NK011(da)001:9089: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9090: thugs rjes rtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:9091: nges pa'i lung ston rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK011(da)001:9092: sdom la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin sgrub pa po //
NK011(da)001:9093: dam tshig zung gis 'brel ba'i mched lcam la //
NK011(da)001:9094: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9095: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:9096: bde gshegs rgya mtsho bskul zhing mchod pa dang //
NK011(da)001:9097: rnal 'byor rtog 'joms don dang ldan pa yis //
NK011(da)001:9098: yon tan mtshungs med b+han+d+ha'i snod chen du //
NK011(da)001:9099: ye shes lnga ldan bdud rtsi rin po che //
NK011(da)001:9100: yongs su bkang ba'i gnyis med bcud chen la //
NK011(da)001:9101: bde gshegs mchod nas dngos grub blang ba ni //
NK011(da)001:9102: lce yi rdo rje dam tshig pad+mo la //
NK011(da)001:9103: rdo rje can gyis gsal bar h'u bsgom nas //
NK011(da)001:9104: ye shes lnga ldan bdud rtsi sbyar ba'i sman //
NK011(da)001:9105: zos na bla med byang chub mchog thob 'gyur //
NK011(da)001:9107: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK011(da)001:9108: zhes pas dngos grub blang ngo //
NK011(da)001:9109: ye shes khro bo 'bar ba'i zhal chen du //
NK011(da)001:9110: snod bcud ma lus mchod pa rgya cher sbyar //
NK011(da)001:9111: dbying las ye shes rol pa'i mchod pa ru //
NK011(da)001:9112: so sor mchod pa bzhes te snod bcud 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9113: rgyal ba yab yum ye shes khro bo'i sku //
NK011(da)001:9114: dwangs snyigs mi phyed mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang //
NK011(da)001:9115: dug gsum skyon bral dbyings kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:9116: 'du 'bral med pa'i srid gsum mchod par rol //
NK011(da)001:9117: mtha' dang dbus med mnyam pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:9118: nga dang bdag med mkha' ltar dag pa'i klong //
NK011(da)001:9119: ye shes lhun grub mnyam pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:9120: gnyis med don chen mnyam pa'i mchod par rol //
NK011(da)001:9121: snying po byang chub longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:9122: 'dod spyod yon tan lha mo'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:9123: snang srid ma lus 'dod pa'i skur gyur pas //
NK011(da)001:9124: mkha' ltar dag pa'i dbyings su ye shes rol //
NK011(da)001:9125: rang byung ma bcos dbyibs dang kha dog bral //
NK011(da)001:9126: rnam par shes pa'i nyon mongs cir snang yang //
NK011(da)001:9127: gdod nas dag pas 'khor ba dbyings su rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:9128: khams gsum gdug pa 'dul ba'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:9129: ye shes khro bo'i zhal du stob par 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9130: nyon mongs rtsa ba 'khor ba'i khrag chen po //
NK011(da)001:9131: chags pa'i don gyis kha dog dmar por snang //
NK011(da)001:9132: ma bcos dbyings su chags pa dag bya'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9133: ye shes khro bo'i zhal du stob par 'bul //
NK011(da)001:9136: spros pa med pa'i dbyings rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa nas bzhengs te /
NK011(da)001:9137: dus gsum khams gsum ma lus par bzhugs pa'i mnga'
NK011(da)001:9138: bdag bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje gzhon nu yab
NK011(da)001:9139: yum gnyis su med pa'i khyad par las sprul pa'i
NK011(da)001:9140: khro bo bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil
NK011(da)001:9141: nas shin tu 'jigs 'jigs rngams rngams ltar bzhugs pa
NK011(da)001:9142: / 'khor gdug pa'i tshogs dang bcas pas bdag cag
NK011(da)001:9143: gi sdang ba'i dgra gnod pa'i bgegs 'di dag thal
NK011(da)001:9144: ba bzhin du brlag pa'i phrin las mdzad du gsol
NK011(da)001:9145: / / zhes phrin las bcol la bzlas pa ci nus bya /
NK011(da)001:9147: bla mas gab pa'i gter gsang ba'i man ngag rdzogs so //
NK011(da)001:9150: // // phur pa'i mnan pa bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:9151: phur pa'i las mnan pa'i rim pa la /
NK011(da)001:9152: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:9154: mi shis pa'i gnas su phyin la /
NK011(da)001:9158: de nas dong gru gsum brus la thod ngan nang du lid+ga stsal la dong du sba /
NK011(da)001:9159: gzas po de la nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi bslang ba'i phyir dug gtor steng du blug /
NK011(da)001:9165: zhes pas mtshon cha'i char 'bab par bsam /
NK011(da)001:9166: de nas g.yam pa la rdo rje rgya gram bris pas kha bcad /
NK011(da)001:9168: ri rab kyis mnan par bsgom /
NK011(da)001:9169: de'i steng du rtsa ba'i sngags brjod de /
NK011(da)001:9170: skad cig gis lha rnams bskyed la lha'i pho brang btab par bsam /
NK011(da)001:9172: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK011(da)001:9173: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i //
NK011(da)001:9174: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK011(da)001:9175: gnod cing gdug pa'i che ge 'di //
NK011(da)001:9176: stobs chen khro bo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK011(da)001:9177: byang chub sems ni ma bskyed par //
NK011(da)001:9178: nam yang btang bar mi bya'o //
NK011(da)001:9180: gnas de'i lha 'dre rnams la'ang phrin las bcol lo //
NK011(da)001:9181: mnan pa'i phrin las rdzogs so //
NK011(da)001:9184: // // phur pa'i gar bro bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:9185: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK011(da)001:9186: phyogs med dbus kyi gzhal yas nas //
NK011(da)001:9187: ku ber bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK011(da)001:9188: bcom ldan dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK011(da)001:9189: yum chen dz+aa ti 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma //
NK011(da)001:9190: yab yum gnyis med thugs kyi bro brdungs pas //
NK011(da)001:9191: thugs kyi dpal be'u rin chen zur brgyad la //
NK011(da)001:9192: k+ai la ya yi 'od zer 'phro zhing 'dus //
NK011(da)001:9193: phar 'phros pas ni rgyal ba'i sku la thim //
NK011(da)001:9194: slar 'dus pas ni rgyal ba'i gsung la thim //
NK011(da)001:9195: gnyis med byang chub sems la rab tu thim //
NK011(da)001:9196: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)001:9197: lce yi rdo rje pad+ma'i dam tshig la //
NK011(da)001:9198: phur bu'i 'dzab bzlas 'brug stong di ri ri //
NK011(da)001:9199: phyi yi dngos grub nang du bsdus //
NK011(da)001:9200: nang gi dngos grub gzugs la chud //
NK011(da)001:9201: gsang ba'i dngos grub dbyings su thim //
NK011(da)001:9202: phyi nang gsang ba'i dngos grub gsum //
NK011(da)001:9203: sku gsung thugs su a yu she //
NK011(da)001:9204: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub de //
NK011(da)001:9205: skal ldan rnams la stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)001:9206: khro bcu man chad rig pas dpyad //
NK011(da)001:9208: phur pa gar gyi bro brdung ngo //
NK011(da)001:9211: // khrag thun gyis bsad pa'i tshul bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:9212: sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra na mo /
NK011(da)001:9216: drang dang bsre dang ting 'dzin dang //
NK011(da)001:9217: bskul dang dpang gzug lam bsal dang //
NK011(da)001:9219: gong gi dkyil 'khor de nyid du //
NK011(da)001:9220: thun gyi rdzas rnams bsag bya ste //
NK011(da)001:9221: spyang ki mu su ra yi mgo //
NK011(da)001:9222: rwa'am bsre phor snod rnams ni //
NK011(da)001:9223: nub byang mtshams nas rim gyis dgod //
NK011(da)001:9224: dbus su dum bu drug pa bkod //
NK011(da)001:9225: khrag sna dug sna yungs kar dang //
NK011(da)001:9226: lcags phye zangs phye rdo rje phye dang //
NK011(da)001:9227: nyungs nag ske mtshe rnams kyang bsags //
NK011(da)001:9228: gong gi thod pa de dag tu //
NK011(da)001:9229: gang la bya ba'i lid+ga de //
NK011(da)001:9230: mthing nag dar gyis kha bkab la //
NK011(da)001:9231: sna lnga'i gzungs thag dag gis gdags //
NK011(da)001:9232: bdag gi thugs ka'i nyi ma la //
NK011(da)001:9233: ma la gang 'dod sngags kyis bskor //
NK011(da)001:9234: lce yi pad+ma nyi ma la //
NK011(da)001:9235: rang re'i rtsa ba'i yi ge la //
NK011(da)001:9236: gang 'dod rtsa ba'i sngags kyis bskor //
NK011(da)001:9237: yungs kar mtshon la khrag thun nad //
NK011(da)001:9238: lcags phye la sogs mtshon char brlab //
NK011(da)001:9239: dang po dbus nas drang ba ni //
NK011(da)001:9240: yang snying 'dus pa'i sngags kyang drang //
NK011(da)001:9241: de nas rang re'i sgo sngags ni //
NK011(da)001:9242: nub byang mtshams nas lho nub tu //
NK011(da)001:9243: mthar chags ngag gis drang ba dang //
NK011(da)001:9244: m+aa ra ya dang thun yang sbyar //
NK011(da)001:9245: mtha' nas ldog la dbus su bskyal //
NK011(da)001:9246: de nas rdzas rnams dbus su bya'o //
NK011(da)001:9247: gzhi snying dril la drang bar bya //
NK011(da)001:9248: gzungs thag srog rtsa'i rang bzhin te //
NK011(da)001:9249: sngags bzlas lam nas thun la bstim //
NK011(da)001:9250: de nyid ma mo'i skur gyur de //
NK011(da)001:9252: ma la thim pas de dag kun //
NK011(da)001:9253: thun spyod phur bu thebs pa dang //
NK011(da)001:9254: dgra bo 'gug cing rol par bsgom //
NK011(da)001:9255: dang por dbyings nas bskul ba ni //
NK011(da)001:9256: dpal ldan ye shes lha tshogs bskul //
NK011(da)001:9257: de nas thun gyi ma mo bskul //
NK011(da)001:9259: mi mngon bde chen dag pa nas //
NK011(da)001:9260: gdug pa 'dul phyir 'jigs pa'i skur byung ba //
NK011(da)001:9261: e ka dz+aa ti ral gcig mthu mo che //
NK011(da)001:9262: sngags kyi srung mar zhal 'ches sgrol ba ni //
NK011(da)001:9263: rang bzhin lhun grub gru gsum pho brang nas //
NK011(da)001:9264: ma bdun sring bzhi 'khor dang bcas te gshegs //
NK011(da)001:9265: dgra la khrag zor 'phang gi da tshul byon //
NK011(da)001:9267: dmar nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:9268: gru gsum mthing nag yum gyi b+ha ga las //
NK011(da)001:9269: gdug pa 'dul phyir srung ma'i skur ston pa //
NK011(da)001:9270: shwa na mu kha srung mar dam bcas kyi //
NK011(da)001:9271: bzhengs shig rang bzhin grub pa'i dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK011(da)001:9272: 'khor gyi lce spyang tshogs bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:9273: dgra la khrag zor 'phang gi da tshul byon //
NK011(da)001:9275: phur bu'i srung mar dam bcas re ma t+ai //
NK011(da)001:9276: sku mdog mthing nag dre'u zhon 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK011(da)001:9277: ma mo kun gyi bdag nyid gtso mo ste //
NK011(da)001:9278: nag mo 'bum dang bcas te dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK011(da)001:9279: rang bzhin gnas mchog byang shar mtshams shed nas //
NK011(da)001:9280: dgra la khrag zor 'phang gi dam la 'dus //
NK011(da)001:9282: byang chub ris su ji ltar dam bcas pa //
NK011(da)001:9283: ya byin la sogs gsang ba'i ma mo bzhi //
NK011(da)001:9284: rje blon 'bangs dang bcas te da bskyod cig /
NK011(da)001:9285: rang bzhin gnas mchog dar tsha'i yul nas bzhengs //
NK011(da)001:9286: dgra la khrag zor 'phang gi dam la 'dus //
NK011(da)001:9287: zhes bskul zhing rak+ta brlab bo //
NK011(da)001:9288: so so'i srog gi snying po yang bzlas so //
NK011(da)001:9289: h'u e ka tsa ti nam mkha'i go zu can //
NK011(da)001:9290: thor tshugs 'bar ba'i snyan cha ral pa can //
NK011(da)001:9291: nam mkhar gshog rdeng khams gsum khyab par myul //
NK011(da)001:9292: g.yas pa thun g.yo g.yon pa phur pa 'debs //
NK011(da)001:9293: khyod kyi thugs dam dus la bab po sa ma ya //
NK011(da)001:9295: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:9296: g.ya' ri gangs ri brag phug dang //
NK011(da)001:9297: yang le shod kyi brag phug tu //
NK011(da)001:9298: khas blangs dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK011(da)001:9299: bstan pa 'jig pa'i dam nyams rnams //
NK011(da)001:9300: bdun brgyud gcod pa'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:9302: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:9303: sku gcig ming dgu mtshan brgya ma //
NK011(da)001:9304: cir yang sprul nas las rnams mdzad //
NK011(da)001:9306: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:9308: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:9309: rdo rje ya byin 'phrul mo che //
NK011(da)001:9310: rdo rje bswe byin dbang mo che //
NK011(da)001:9311: rdo rje de byin rtsal mo che //
NK011(da)001:9312: rdo rje phag byin stobs mo che //
NK011(da)001:9313: mtshams bzhi dag la gnas bca' zhing //
NK011(da)001:9314: gza' bdud klu btsan btul ba bzhin //
NK011(da)001:9315: rje blon bcas pa da bskyod la //
NK011(da)001:9316: phur bus thob la khrag thun phob //
NK011(da)001:9317: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:9319: gzu dang dpang du dkon mchog bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:9320: zhal lce lha srin yongs kyis chod //
NK011(da)001:9321: bdag ni rnal 'byor sgrub pa po //
NK011(da)001:9322: sgrub pa po la dgra byung na //
NK011(da)001:9323: yang dag don chen lhur len cing //
NK011(da)001:9324: lha la gdung zhing slob dpon khur //
NK011(da)001:9325: mched la brtse zhing dam tshig bsrung //
NK011(da)001:9326: dam nyams 'di yis ma ster na //
NK011(da)001:9327: ye shes lha tshogs dpang mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:9328: lha srin sde brgyad dam can mkha' 'gro dang //
NK011(da)001:9330: lam bsal bden bdar gser skyems btang //
NK011(da)001:9331: bdud chas zhugs la sha chen mur //
NK011(da)001:9332: gtor ma thun rnams khyer nas ni //
NK011(da)001:9333: ri rtse bcad kha dur khrod du //
NK011(da)001:9334: phyin te gdug pa'i me spar la //
NK011(da)001:9335: gsur chen dud btang thun yang gtor //
NK011(da)001:9336: dam rdzas gtor ma cha gcig gis //
NK011(da)001:9337: srid pa'i dam can dam la bsdus //
NK011(da)001:9338: khro bo chen po'i ting 'dzin du //
NK011(da)001:9339: zhugs la 'di skad brjod par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:9341: nga ni khro bo kun gyi rje //
NK011(da)001:9342: nga ni ma mo kun gyi rje //
NK011(da)001:9343: nga ni e ka dz+aa ti ma //
NK011(da)001:9344: snang srid ma mo dam la 'dus //
NK011(da)001:9347: nyis brgya lnga bcu dam la 'dus //
NK011(da)001:9349: nag mo khrag 'thung e ka tsa ti ma //
NK011(da)001:9350: 'jigs pa'i ral pa gcig tu byas //
NK011(da)001:9351: ral gcig rgya mtsho'i gting nas me 'bar ma //
NK011(da)001:9352: 'jigs pa'i sku gcig stong khams mkha' la 'phyo //
NK011(da)001:9353: g.yas pa thun gyi khrag 'phyo ma //
NK011(da)001:9354: g.yon pa tri shul rtse gsum bsnams //
NK011(da)001:9355: khrag nad yongs su 'thor byed cing //
NK011(da)001:9356: nad dang rgyu yi sna 'dren ma //
NK011(da)001:9358: srin mo'i dam tshig mi sha za //
NK011(da)001:9359: srin mo'i dam tshig mi khrag 'thung //
NK011(da)001:9361: nyid kyi dam tshig khrag mda' 'di //
NK011(da)001:9362: da ni 'phang ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:9364: gru gsum mthing nag yum gyi b+ha ga las //
NK011(da)001:9365: 'jigs pa'i sku gcig byung ba ni //
NK011(da)001:9366: zangs kyi wa mo rkang gsum mo //
NK011(da)001:9367: zangs kyi ma mo bzang mo zhon //
NK011(da)001:9368: zangs kyi ral pa gyen du bardzesa //
NK011(da)001:9369: g.yas pa thun gyi khrag 'phyo ma //
NK011(da)001:9370: g.yon pa zangs kyi phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:9371: thun khrag byos la phur bus thob //
NK011(da)001:9372: da ni 'phang ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:9374: byang shar mtshams kyi grub pa mo //
NK011(da)001:9375: nag mo khrag 'thung ral pa can //
NK011(da)001:9377: lha 'a dre kun gyi sna 'dren ma //
NK011(da)001:9378: drel zhon nad kyi bkos bdag mo //
NK011(da)001:9380: g.yas na thun gyi khrag 'phyo ma //
NK011(da)001:9381: g.yon na lcags kyi phur bu 'dril //
NK011(da)001:9382: khrag thun byos la phur bus thob //
NK011(da)001:9383: nyid kyi dam tshig khrag mda' 'di //
NK011(da)001:9384: da ni 'phang ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:9386: tsha ba rong nas grub pa mo //
NK011(da)001:9387: mar khu'i mtsho las sku bzhengs shig /
NK011(da)001:9388: rdo rje ya byin 'phrul mo che //
NK011(da)001:9389: mthing nag ral pa sha ra ra //
NK011(da)001:9390: gser gyi rna cha wangs se wang //
NK011(da)001:9391: dbang gi bswe khrab si li li //
NK011(da)001:9392: na bza' za ber 'jol lo lo //
NK011(da)001:9393: chibs su bdud rta nag po bcibs //
NK011(da)001:9394: gzugs ni mi sdug lag brgya mo //
NK011(da)001:9395: brda' ni mi 'phrod lho bal mo //
NK011(da)001:9396: skad ni mi mthun da ra'i skad //
NK011(da)001:9397: g.yas rnams thun gyi khrag 'phyo ma //
NK011(da)001:9399: nyid kyi dam tshig khrag mda' 'di //
NK011(da)001:9400: da ni 'phang ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:9402: bal yul gting na grub pa mo //
NK011(da)001:9403: sbrang rtsi'i mtsho las sku bzhengs shig /
NK011(da)001:9404: rdo rje bswe byin dbang mo che //
NK011(da)001:9405: gser gyi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK011(da)001:9406: gser gyi rna cha wangs se wang //
NK011(da)001:9407: dbang gi bswe khrab si li li //
NK011(da)001:9408: na bza' za ber 'jol lo lo //
NK011(da)001:9409: chibs su gza' rta ser po bcibs //
NK011(da)001:9412: mang yul bswe nas grub pa mo //
NK011(da)001:9413: rak+ta'i mtsho las sku bzhengs shig /
NK011(da)001:9414: rdo rje de byin rtsal mo che //
NK011(da)001:9415: khrag gi ral pa shar ra //
NK011(da)001:9416: dngul gyi rna cha wangs se wang //
NK011(da)001:9417: dbang gi bswe khrab si li li //
NK011(da)001:9418: na bza' za ber 'jol lo lo //
NK011(da)001:9419: chibs su btsan rta dmar po bcibs //
NK011(da)001:9422: snye nam 'gram nas grub pa mo //
NK011(da)001:9423: 'o ma'i mtsho las sku bzhengs shig /
NK011(da)001:9424: rdo rje phag byin stobs mo che //
NK011(da)001:9425: dung gi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK011(da)001:9426: dung gi rna cha wangs se wang //
NK011(da)001:9427: dbang gi bswe khrab si li li //
NK011(da)001:9428: na bza' za ber 'jol lo lo //
NK011(da)001:9429: chibs su klu rta sngon po bcibs //
NK011(da)001:9430: gzugs ni mi sdug lag brgya mo //
NK011(da)001:9431: brda' ni mi 'phrod lho bal mo //
NK011(da)001:9432: skad ni mi mthun da ra'i skad //
NK011(da)001:9433: g.yas rnams thun gyi khrag 'phyo ma //
NK011(da)001:9435: nyid kyi dam tshig khrag mda' 'di //
NK011(da)001:9436: da ni 'phang ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:9439: so so'i dmag dpung 'khor bcas chos //
NK011(da)001:9440: cod pan mun ltar gtibs te chos //
NK011(da)001:9441: mon mo'i brda skad bsgyur zhing chos //
NK011(da)001:9442: tsi bi ri yi sgra sgrogs chos //
NK011(da)001:9444: dang po zhe sdang pha yis bskyed //
NK011(da)001:9445: bar du 'dod chags ma yi mngal //
NK011(da)001:9446: de nas dri za lte bar 'khor //
NK011(da)001:9447: de nas nyon mongs lnga yi gzugs //
NK011(da)001:9448: lnga phung rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9449: phung po lnga la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9450: dbang po'i brten sa mgo yin gyi //
NK011(da)001:9451: klad pa'i rgyas su khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9452: dran par byed pa snying yin gyi //
NK011(da)001:9453: snying gi dkyil du khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9454: lta ba'i mig la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9455: nyan pa'i rna la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9456: snom pa'i sna la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9457: smra ba'i lce la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9458: 'dzin pa'i lag la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9459: bgrod pa'i rkang la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9460: yul mkhar khyim la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9461: nor gyi dbyigs la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9462: bdun brgyud rtsa la khrag zor ya //
NK011(da)001:9464: badz+ra sho na sa ma ya b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:9465: badz+ra snying kha rag ma b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:9468: a be sha shu shu ni nga ra snying la b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:9469: thod pa 'phangs la pra brtag go //
NK011(da)001:9470: mthar thug gi las rdzogs so //
NK011(da)001:9473: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i dbang gi cho ga jo bo lang lab kyi lugs bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:9474: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:9475: de nas dbang bskur gral bca' ste //
NK011(da)001:9476: dam tshig mna' chu bcas nas ni //
NK011(da)001:9477: nang du bos la 'di skad brjod //
NK011(da)001:9481: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lam sgo 'di //
NK011(da)001:9482: skal ldan khyod la gnyer du dpog pa ni //
NK011(da)001:9483: dang po la ni mnyam pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)001:9484: de las 'das na mtha' gnyis mun par ltung //
NK011(da)001:9485: gnyis pa 'gro don rdzogs pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)001:9486: de las 'das na nyan thos sa ru ltung //
NK011(da)001:9487: gsum pa la ni sbyor pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)001:9488: de las 'das na mngal gyi srin bur skye //
NK011(da)001:9489: bzhi pa la ni spyod pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)001:9490: dngos su spyod na las kyi srin por skye //
NK011(da)001:9491: rtsa ba yan lag ji snyed grags pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:9492: lta spyod sgrub dang las kyi bye brag gis //
NK011(da)001:9493: so so'i rim pa bzhin du bsrung zhes bya //
NK011(da)001:9495: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK011(da)001:9496: dam tshig nyams na sreg par byed //
NK011(da)001:9497: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK011(da)001:9499: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u dz+ny+aa na sa t+wa a /
NK011(da)001:9500: de nas gzhal yas khang sgo phye ste /
NK011(da)001:9501: rjes byang chub phur pa'i lha tshogs la //
NK011(da)001:9502: mchod chen bgyis pas phur pa'i lha //
NK011(da)001:9503: bdag kyang rab tu bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9504: phur pa'i lha tshogs bdag la stsol //
NK011(da)001:9505: bu khyod dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK011(da)001:9506: bdag ni skal ldan bde chen la'o //
NK011(da)001:9507: rab dge 'phrul la bdag dga' ste //
NK011(da)001:9508: bla med byang chub thob bya'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9509: skal ba bzang la bdag dga' 'o //
NK011(da)001:9511: gsang rjes ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK011(da)001:9512: rig pa'i me tog 'di dor bas //
NK011(da)001:9513: sngon tshe sgrub pa'i lha ni gang yin pa //
NK011(da)001:9514: da lta nyid du bdag la 'bab par shog /
NK011(da)001:9517: dkyil 'khor dam pa lta bar gyis //
NK011(da)001:9518: sngags dang phyag rgya grub par byed //
NK011(da)001:9519: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK011(da)001:9520: de nas phyag 'tshal bshags pa bya //
NK011(da)001:9523: dbyings las ye shes gsum snang gru gsum ste //
NK011(da)001:9524: rtag chad dbu mar mnga' brnyes zla gam gsum //
NK011(da)001:9525: 'khor ba rtsad nas bcad phyir 'khor lor bstan //
NK011(da)001:9526: spros pa med pa'i tshul gyis kun nas zlum //
NK011(da)001:9527: ye shes kun tu rgyas phyir gru chad bzhi //
NK011(da)001:9528: 'das dang ma 'das mtshams su bar khyams bstan //
NK011(da)001:9529: ye shes lnga ldan thod pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)001:9530: rig pa shar sgo yon tan lho yi sgo //
NK011(da)001:9531: ma rig nub sgo bag chags byang gi sgo //
NK011(da)001:9532: yon tan mi zad sgo khyud rnam thar brgyad //
NK011(da)001:9533: rta bab mi phyed rdo rje phreng bas brgyan //
NK011(da)001:9534: skal ldan bu yis de ltar shes par gyis //
NK011(da)001:9536: tshogs brgyad rnam dag gtso bo'i sku //
NK011(da)001:9537: yul ni yum du dag pa ste //
NK011(da)001:9538: ngag khyal pa dang srog gcod pa //
NK011(da)001:9539: phra ma tshig rtsub bzhi po ni //
NK011(da)001:9540: phyogs bzhi khro bo'i rang bzhin no //
NK011(da)001:9541: rdzun dang log lta ma byin len //
NK011(da)001:9542: gnod sems rnam par dag pa ni //
NK011(da)001:9543: mtshams kyi khro bo'i rang bzhin no //
NK011(da)001:9544: 'dod chags brnab sems rnam dag pa //
NK011(da)001:9545: steng 'og khro bo'i rang bzhin no //
NK011(da)001:9546: de rnams kun gyi yon tan ni //
NK011(da)001:9547: cha rnams rnam dag yum rnams so //
NK011(da)001:9548: 'du byed sems kyi tshogs rnams la //
NK011(da)001:9549: dad dang 'dun pa la sogs pa //
NK011(da)001:9550: rnam par dag pa phra men tshogs //
NK011(da)001:9551: sems kyi las rnams 'grub pas na //
NK011(da)001:9552: phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK011(da)001:9553: bdag 'dzin gnyis dang ma bral bas //
NK011(da)001:9554: srung ma'i tshogs su bstan pa yin //
NK011(da)001:9555: de lta bu yi lha tshogs ni //
NK011(da)001:9556: rigs kyi bu yis shes par gyis //
NK011(da)001:9557: de nas las kyi bum chu blangs //
NK011(da)001:9558: mtshams kyang drag tu bcad byas la //
NK011(da)001:9559: rdo rje rnam 'joms brjod bya zhing //
NK011(da)001:9560: slob ma'i mgo lus dag par bkru //
NK011(da)001:9561: de nas dad ldan slob ma yis //
NK011(da)001:9562: bla ma mnyes pa'i yon phul te //
NK011(da)001:9563: bzang po'i gos gyon me tog thogs //
NK011(da)001:9564: dngos grub 'dod phyir gsol ba gdab //
NK011(da)001:9565: thabs rjes kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK011(da)001:9566: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK011(da)001:9567: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK011(da)001:9568: byin rlabs dbang ni bdag la stsol //
NK011(da)001:9569: bla mas tshig gsum mthun pa las //
NK011(da)001:9570: byin rlabs dbang ni bskur bar bya //
NK011(da)001:9571: de ltar brjod la byin brlabs te //
NK011(da)001:9572: rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur bskyed la //
NK011(da)001:9573: me tog lha dang bcas pa ni //
NK011(da)001:9574: slob ma'i spyir bzhag 'di skad brjod //
NK011(da)001:9575: 'di ni khyod kyi byang chub sems //
NK011(da)001:9576: srid pa gsum la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK011(da)001:9577: bcom ldan 'das dang skal ba gcig /
NK011(da)001:9578: byang chub sems ni mngon du bstan //
NK011(da)001:9579: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aam bam h'u h'u ab+hi shiny+tsa a +aah /
NK011(da)001:9580: chos dbyings yum gyi bum pa na //
NK011(da)001:9581: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK011(da)001:9582: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi chus //
NK011(da)001:9583: spyi nas bstim zhing dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9584: k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9585: da ni lha tshogs kyi dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)001:9586: lha phur rim bzhin bton la bskur ba ni //
NK011(da)001:9588: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)001:9589: shin tu mi bzad rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NK011(da)001:9590: zhe sdang thugs mchog rak+sha he ru ka /
NK011(da)001:9591: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis lha chen bardzisa //
NK011(da)001:9592: 'jigs byed sku la dur khrod rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK011(da)001:9593: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs 'jigs byed dpal gyi yum //
NK011(da)001:9594: yab yum gnyis su med pa yang //
NK011(da)001:9595: gsang ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)001:9596: bskal pa'i mtha' nas bsnyen bsnyen pa //
NK011(da)001:9597: ring pa'i dus nas bsgrub bsgrub pa //
NK011(da)001:9598: bsnyen cing bsgrub pa'i don lags kyi //
NK011(da)001:9599: skal ldan rigs kyi bu mchog la //
NK011(da)001:9600: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9601: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya tip+ta tsakra ha na a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9602: rdo rje slob dpon bdag gis slob ma khyod la
NK011(da)001:9603: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum gyi dbang bskur
NK011(da)001:9604: bas lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa rnam par
NK011(da)001:9605: dag nas sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar dbyer mi
NK011(da)001:9607: dbang phyug khro bo'i dbang bskur te //
NK011(da)001:9609: za byed rngams pa mche ba gtsigs pa las //
NK011(da)001:9610: khro bo za byed rngams pa'i 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros //
NK011(da)001:9611: zhal gyi hom khung thig le dmar po nas //
NK011(da)001:9612: ye shes khro bo mang po sprul pa'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:9613: khams gsum thal bar rlog pa'i las mdzad pa //
NK011(da)001:9614: ye shes khro bo bcu yi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9615: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u k+aa ra a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9617: khro bo chen po bcus dbang bskur bas stobs bcu'i stobs su gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9618: dbang bcu sku la rdzogs pas phyogs bcu'i dregs pa
NK011(da)001:9619: can mang po 'dus shing rin po che'i lo ka
NK011(da)001:9620: brdal ba'i mthu stobs dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9622: khro rgyal sku la gnyis med sbyor ba mo //
NK011(da)001:9623: srin po'i mgo dang srin mo'i ral pa can //
NK011(da)001:9624: sprul pa'i pho nya ci bgyi khro mo'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:9625: lha srin mang po 'dul ba'i rtags su byung //
NK011(da)001:9626: ye shes khro mo bcu yi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9627: badz+ra rak+sha ya ti h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9628: khro mo bcu'i dbang bskur bas sprul pa'i pho nya
NK011(da)001:9629: mang po dbyings nas bton nas mi mthun pa'i dgra
NK011(da)001:9630: bgegs rdul du rlog pa'i dbang dam pa dang ldan
NK011(da)001:9631: par gyur cig / khra thabs nyi shu'i dbang bskur ba //
