NK011(da)001:9632: phra men tshogs dang sbyor ba'i byin rlabs dang //
NK011(da)001:9633: 'du byed sprul pa 'byung ba'i byin rlabs ni //
NK011(da)001:9634: ral pa kham nag rdo rje'i mche ba can //
NK011(da)001:9635: ro la rngams pa ti ra 'drad pa dang //
NK011(da)001:9636: zhag la rngams shing rus pa 'cha' ba'i tshul //
NK011(da)001:9637: stag g.yag sha ba gzig gi mgo //
NK011(da)001:9638: byi la spyang ki seng ge'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:9639: dom dred phag gi mgo can dang //
NK011(da)001:9640: bya rgod bya rog 'ug pa'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:9641: khwa ta pu shud khra yi mgo //
NK011(da)001:9642: pha wang se mong byi ba'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:9643: rmig bu'i mgo can phra men tshogs //
NK011(da)001:9644: 'dab chags khrag 'thung sder mo'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:9645: stong gsum zad par bsgral yang tshim pa med //
NK011(da)001:9646: khams gsum yongs bsgral mdzad kyang tshim pa med //
NK011(da)001:9647: za byed rngams pa'i tshogs kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9648: badz+ra u ka ra mu kha h'u /
NK011(da)001:9649: badz+ra hu sho ka mu kha h'u /
NK011(da)001:9651: phra men mgo brnyan gyi dbang bskur bas khams gsum
NK011(da)001:9652: yongs bsgral mdzad pa 'gug byed pho nya'i dbang dang
NK011(da)001:9654: phur pa rdzas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK011(da)001:9655: khro rgyal 'dus pa'i sras mchog k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:9656: yon tan rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:9657: mi g.yo chos mchog sku gsung thugs kyi bdag /
NK011(da)001:9658: sdug bsngal 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i sems can rnams //
NK011(da)001:9659: thugs rjes dbyer med dbyings su sgrol mdzad pa //
NK011(da)001:9660: khro rgyal 'bar ba'i sid+d+hi'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9661: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la sarba big+h+n+aam bam h'u h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:9662: phur pa'i dbang bskur bas las rnam pa bzhi brtsams
NK011(da)001:9663: pa tsam gyi 'grub pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK011(da)001:9664: cig / sgo ma bzhi'i dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)001:9665: byams dang snying rje dga' ba btang snyoms tshul //
NK011(da)001:9666: nyon mongs log par lta ba'i dgra 'dul zhing //
NK011(da)001:9667: gzhal yas phyogs bzhi ye shes lnga yi ngang //
NK011(da)001:9668: tshad med bzhi yi ye shes 'dul la mkhas //
NK011(da)001:9669: phrin las rnam bzhi'i ye shes dbang sbyin no //
NK011(da)001:9670: dzahmh'u bam hoh a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9671: sgo ma bzhi'i dbang bskur bas ye shes bzhi'i rig
NK011(da)001:9672: pa nang nas shar nas tshad med pa bzhi'i phrin
NK011(da)001:9673: las te las rnams ji ltar dmigs pa tsam gyis
NK011(da)001:9675: phur pa'i srung ma'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK011(da)001:9676: shwa na bdag nyid bswe mo srung ma'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:9677: sprul pa'i pho nya bswe gdong mi bzad pa //
NK011(da)001:9678: ci bcol las byed pho nya mang po'i tshogs //
NK011(da)001:9679: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i sta gon ye nas mdzad //
NK011(da)001:9680: rtsal gyi khyad par dpag gis mi nus pa //
NK011(da)001:9681: sprul pas gang la ci 'dul phrin las mdzad //
NK011(da)001:9682: sprul pa sna tshogs mang po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9685: pho nya 'bum phrag mang po'i dbang bskur bas las
NK011(da)001:9686: bzhi la sogs pa bya'o 'tshal bzhed pa tsam la
NK011(da)001:9687: rag las te ji ltar dmigs pa sprul pa las
NK011(da)001:9688: la 'gyed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9689: sgom sgrub kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK011(da)001:9690: slob ma'i lus ngag yid gsum rdo rje gzhon nu
NK011(da)001:9691: dang dbyer med par byas nas lag tu sngags phur
NK011(da)001:9693: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK011(da)001:9694: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK011(da)001:9695: srid gsum phur pa'i rang bzhin du //
NK011(da)001:9696: bsgom zhing sgrub pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9697: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9698: sngags phur chen po lag tu byin te dbang bskur
NK011(da)001:9699: bas srin pa gsum ka phur bu'i skur rtogs nas
NK011(da)001:9700: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku gsung thugs dang dbyer
NK011(da)001:9703: chos nyid bdud rtsi chos kyi char //
NK011(da)001:9704: skal ldan 'di la dbab pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9705: mthun par sngags bsgrag chos kyi dbang //
NK011(da)001:9706: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK011(da)001:9707: lam h'u d+harma a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK011(da)001:9708: d+harma lag tu gtad de dbang bskur bas chos nyid
NK011(da)001:9709: don rtogs shing 'chad pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK011(da)001:9710: gyur cig / de nas phur pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK011(da)001:9711: rdo rje rab tu k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)001:9712: yum bzhi phyag rgya byin brlabs nas //
NK011(da)001:9713: khyod kyi lag tu 'di byin pas //
NK011(da)001:9714: byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9715: lam gyi sngags kyis dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9716: gdab phur lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas rdzas
NK011(da)001:9717: kyi phur bu ye shes kyi khro bo chen po'i
NK011(da)001:9718: rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang dam pa
NK011(da)001:9720: de nas snying po bzlas pa'i dbang ni /
NK011(da)001:9721: khams gsum ye shes bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9722: sgrub pa'i ye shes tshon gang ba //
NK011(da)001:9723: gsang ba sngags kyis bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9724: thugs la 'bar ba'i srog kyang shar //
NK011(da)001:9725: dus kun rgyun du bzla dgos pas //
NK011(da)001:9726: snying po 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9730: man ngag gi snying po 'di byin te dbang bskur
NK011(da)001:9731: bas de ring phan chad bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung
NK011(da)001:9732: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9735: khams gsum gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9736: tshams rngams gzi byin glog ltar 'gyu //
NK011(da)001:9737: nyes byed gsum gyi khams bsreg phyir //
NK011(da)001:9738: khams gsum sgrol ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9739: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aam bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:9740: yak+sha sh+ai he ru ka sta na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:9741: de nas phur bu tho ba'i dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)001:9742: khro mo 'bar ma'i gtun khung du //
NK011(da)001:9743: khro bo 'bar ba'i gtun tshogs kyis //
NK011(da)001:9744: khams gsum gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9745: phur bu tho ba'i dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:9746: thams cad sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)001:9747: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya mu sti h'u /
NK011(da)001:9749: phur bu tho ba 'di lag tu byin zhing dbang
NK011(da)001:9750: bskur bas dgra bgegs thams cad tshar bcad nas zhi
NK011(da)001:9751: zhing rnam par shes pa mi gnas pa'i mya ngan
NK011(da)001:9752: las 'das pa kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' dbyings su
NK011(da)001:9753: sgrol pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9754: de nas phur bu 'debs pa'i dbang ni /
NK011(da)001:9755: bdag dang lag pa mchog rnams kyis //
NK011(da)001:9756: rab tu 'dril te gsor byas na //
NK011(da)001:9757: dug gsum rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9759: pa ra bi t+wan gyi sham la /
NK011(da)001:9760: m+aa ra ya phata ab+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9761: phur pa 'di lag tu byin nas dbang bskur bas /
NK011(da)001:9762: dug gsum gyis bskyed pa'i dgra bgegs rnams rdul phran
NK011(da)001:9763: bzhin du brlag nas sgrol zhing tshar gcod pa'i mthu
NK011(da)001:9764: stobs dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK011(da)001:9765: cig / ces 'debs phur lag tu byin no //
NK011(da)001:9766: de nas dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur zhing /
NK011(da)001:9767: srid pa gsum la dbang bsgyur zhing /
NK011(da)001:9768: byang chub sems ni mngon du bstan //
NK011(da)001:9769: khams gsum ye shes bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9770: dbu la rigs lnga'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9771: bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK011(da)001:9772: badz+ra ak+sho b+h+ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK011(da)001:9773: rat+na sam+b+ha ba a b+hi shiny+tsa t+r+aam /
NK011(da)001:9774: pad+ma de ba a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih a mo g+ha
NK011(da)001:9775: sid+d+hi karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aa rdo rje slob dpon
NK011(da)001:9776: bdag gis slob ma khyod la bu rgyan gyi dbang
NK011(da)001:9777: bskur bas phung po lnga dang dug lnga gnas su
NK011(da)001:9778: dag nas rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dbang dam pa
NK011(da)001:9780: de nas cod pan gyi dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)001:9781: bag chags nyes pa'i skyon bral zhing //
NK011(da)001:9782: 'khor ba'i chos kyis ma gos pa'i //
NK011(da)001:9783: ye shes lnga yi cod pan gyis //
NK011(da)001:9784: khyod la dbang mchog bskur bar bya //
NK011(da)001:9785: badz+ra pa ra la ma pa na a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK011(da)001:9786: h+r+aih bu khyod la le brgan gyi dbang bskur bas
NK011(da)001:9787: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal por gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9788: mthing ga'i dbang bskur bas khams gsum gyi gdug pa
NK011(da)001:9789: thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK011(da)001:9790: cig / phreng ba'i dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)001:9792: byang chub mchog rnams rtogs pa'i rgyan //
NK011(da)001:9793: mi 'jigs chos dang dpe byad mtshan //
NK011(da)001:9794: 'bras bu'i chos la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9795: badz+ra na ma a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aa le t+r+aam /
NK011(da)001:9796: rigs kyi bu khyod la rin po che'i phreng ba'i
NK011(da)001:9797: dbang bskur bas mi brjed pa'i gzungs dang sangs rgyas
NK011(da)001:9798: kyi che ba'i yon tan thams cad la dbang ba'i
NK011(da)001:9799: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9800: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga'i dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)001:9802: dri chen dang ni byang chub sems //
NK011(da)001:9803: m+aam sa rak+ta dri chu lnga //
NK011(da)001:9804: de ring khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:9805: rtog sbyong bdud rtsi'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)001:9806: h'u s+w+aa +aam h+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u a /
NK011(da)001:9807: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga'i dbang bskur bas ye shes
NK011(da)001:9808: lnga'i don rtogs nas rigs lnga'i dngos grub thob ste
NK011(da)001:9809: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rnam pa lnga'i
NK011(da)001:9810: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9813: mi dang ba lang rta sha dang //
NK011(da)001:9814: bya khyi la sogs sha rnams kyis //
NK011(da)001:9815: de ring khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:9816: rig 'dzin gtso bor dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9817: ha m+aam sa a yu she h'u a /
NK011(da)001:9818: rigs kyi bu khyod la sha lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK011(da)001:9819: 'byung ba lnga gnas su dag nas rigs kyi yum lnga'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9820: de nas gsang ba'i dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)001:9821: bkra shis mtshan ldan gsang ba'i yum //
NK011(da)001:9822: bu mo lo grangs nyi shu pa //
NK011(da)001:9823: chas byas rgyan ldan bla ma la //
NK011(da)001:9824: yon dang bcas te dbul bar bya //
NK011(da)001:9825: bla mas gdams ngag don bshad de //
NK011(da)001:9826: dam tshig phog la dkyil 'khor gzhug /
NK011(da)001:9827: byin rlabs dbang ni bskur bya ste //
NK011(da)001:9829: de yi lus kyi gnas bcu la //
NK011(da)001:9830: khro mo bcu yi dkyil 'khor bkod //
NK011(da)001:9832: bdag nyid rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur //
NK011(da)001:9833: gsal ba'i gnas bcur khro bo bcu //
NK011(da)001:9834: gsang gnas rdo rje'i byin rlabs rtse mor //
NK011(da)001:9835: dzahmh'u bam hohs bsdu ba byas //
NK011(da)001:9836: bsdu dang brgyud dang phab pa las //
NK011(da)001:9837: spro bsdus sangs rgyas thams cad kun //
NK011(da)001:9838: ba spu'i bu gar thim pa las //
NK011(da)001:9839: yab yum bde ba'i ngang du gsal //
NK011(da)001:9840: slob mas tshig 'dis gsol ba gdab //
NK011(da)001:9841: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK011(da)001:9842: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings las //
NK011(da)001:9843: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NK011(da)001:9844: sku yi dbyibs nas bdag bskyed cig /
NK011(da)001:9845: bla mas slob ma byin brlabs te //
NK011(da)001:9846: yab yum gnyis med byang chub sems //
NK011(da)001:9847: slob ma'i rgyud la spros byas bas //
NK011(da)001:9848: nye bar len pa'i phung po sbyangs //
NK011(da)001:9849: 'od zhu h'u gyur thugs kar bsdu //
NK011(da)001:9850: srog dbugs brgyud de klad rgyas su //
NK011(da)001:9851: phyungs nas sgal tshigs brgyud pa las //
NK011(da)001:9852: mkha' las byang sems thig le gsal //
NK011(da)001:9853: de las yi ge h'u du gyur //
NK011(da)001:9854: de las rdo rje gzhon nur bskyed //
NK011(da)001:9855: tshig gsum gong dang 'dra ba las //
NK011(da)001:9856: tshig 'dis mkha' las gdon par bya //
NK011(da)001:9857: sku yi dbyings nas bskyed par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:9858: sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra dzah +aahmh'u /
NK011(da)001:9859: nyi ma'i gdan la bzhag nas ni //
NK011(da)001:9860: yab yum sbyor ba dngos su brtsam //
NK011(da)001:9861: byang sems phab ste me long blangs //
NK011(da)001:9862: yig 'bru gsum du byin brlabs te //
NK011(da)001:9863: sbom bo dang ni dbang mo'i rtser //
NK011(da)001:9864: nyi zla gsal bas blang byas te //
NK011(da)001:9865: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems a
NK011(da)001:9866: mri ta sbyar la b+han+d+ha mtshan dang ldan par blugs
NK011(da)001:9867: la bdud rtsir byin gyis brlab /
NK011(da)001:9868: sman gsos che ba'i yon tan brjod //
NK011(da)001:9869: sman gyi mchod pa rgyas par bya //
NK011(da)001:9870: dang po bdag nyid dngos grub blang //
NK011(da)001:9871: de nas slob mar dbang bskur te //
NK011(da)001:9873: rnam rtog bdud 'joms sman mchog bdud rtsi 'di //
NK011(da)001:9874: dus gsum sangs rgyas mnyes pa'i mchod pa'i rdzas //
NK011(da)001:9875: thig le'i dbyings nas rang byung ye shes shar //
NK011(da)001:9876: skye 'chi med pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK011(da)001:9877: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kun+da l+ai sid+d+hi h'u h+r+aih th+aah h'u /
NK011(da)001:9878: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings las //
NK011(da)001:9879: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK011(da)001:9880: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK011(da)001:9881: sku gsung thugs kyi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9882: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK011(da)001:9884: e ma ho nga ni rang byung ba'i //
NK011(da)001:9885: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NK011(da)001:9887: gnyis su med pa'i byang sems kyi //
NK011(da)001:9888: de ring khyod la dngos grub sbyin //
NK011(da)001:9889: bo d+hi tsit+ta +aahmh'u a yu she sid+d+hi h'u a /
NK011(da)001:9890: byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:9891: thabs dang shes rab kyi dbang thob ste 'khor ba'i
NK011(da)001:9892: chos mya ngan las 'das te dpal rdo rje gzhon
NK011(da)001:9893: nu'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub kyi dbyig thob
NK011(da)001:9895: ye shes khro bo h'u k+aa ra //
NK011(da)001:9896: sgra 'byin ma dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK011(da)001:9897: gnyis su med pa'i byang sems kyi //
NK011(da)001:9898: spyi bo nas ni dbang bskur zhing //
NK011(da)001:9899: lce yi steng du bzhag pa yis //
NK011(da)001:9900: h'u chen yab yum dngos grub sbyin //
NK011(da)001:9903: de nas rdo rje ming gi dbang //
NK011(da)001:9904: mtshan mchog 'di yi dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:9905: sangs rgyas zhing du grags pa'i dbang //
NK011(da)001:9907: sh+r+ai badz+ra na ma a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9908: de nas tshogs byin gyis brlabs nas zhal zas rnams gsar te /
NK011(da)001:9909: 'jig rten 'di na srid pa'i zhal zas rnams //
NK011(da)001:9910: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yi gter //
NK011(da)001:9911: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK011(da)001:9912: yid bzhin 'dod rgur bsgyur ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:9913: gu na pany+tsa a yu she h'u a /
NK011(da)001:9914: zhal zas kyi dbang bskur bas 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK011(da)001:9915: mi zad pa'i gter la dbang thob par gyur cig
NK011(da)001:9916: / de ltar zhal zas kyi dbang bskur zin pa dang /
NK011(da)001:9917: slob mas slob dpon dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang srung ma rnams rgyas par mchod do //
NK011(da)001:9918: de nas dza gad kyi dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)001:9919: b+hana d+har dza gad stsal la byin gyis brlabs te /
NK011(da)001:9921: dza gad dpa' bo'i mchod pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:9922: yon tan yum du byin brlabs las //
NK011(da)001:9923: stong khams kun gyi bcud bsdus nas //
NK011(da)001:9924: thugs rje nus pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)001:9925: a tisti ta sa ma ma k+ai ri sid+d+hi h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9929: de nas pham phab kyi dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)001:9930: tshogs kyi lhag ma rnams bsdus la //
NK011(da)001:9932: rgyal ba mchod nas dam skong zhig /
NK011(da)001:9933: mchod pa phul bas bgegs zhi nas //
NK011(da)001:9934: pham phab longs spyod bdud rtsi'i bcud //
NK011(da)001:9935: rnal 'byor longs spyod rgyas par shog /
NK011(da)001:9936: sarba p+au dza karma a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK011(da)001:9939: zla gam dmar po rdo rje dbang gi tshe //
NK011(da)001:9940: gzhan gyis mi dpog khams gsum kun las rgyal //
NK011(da)001:9941: lha mo dmar mo rdo rje 'chi med tshe //
NK011(da)001:9942: legs pa'i yon tan 'dod pa'i longs spyod rgyas //
NK011(da)001:9943: mi 'gyur 'chi med tsho lo stong phrag dang //
NK011(da)001:9944: rang nyid gang 'dod phung po rdo rje'i tshe //
NK011(da)001:9945: +aa yuhdamara po yongs su 'gyur med pa //
NK011(da)001:9946: mi 'phrog nges pa'i tshe mchog gang yin pa //
NK011(da)001:9947: yun ring dus nas bsnyen cing bsgrub bsgrubs nas //
NK011(da)001:9948: rdo rje tshe yi dbang mchog gang yin pa'i //
NK011(da)001:9949: rigs kyi bu yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK011(da)001:9950: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa gu h+ya +aa
NK011(da)001:9951: yuhdz+ny+aa na bin+d+hu yu tsi shwa ra swa b+h+aa wa
NK011(da)001:9952: +aat+ma ko&a ham / tshe bum gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK011(da)001:9953: bcom ldan 'das mgon po tshe dpag med kyi sid+d+hi
NK011(da)001:9954: thob nas skye shi med pa rdo rje tshe'i dbang
NK011(da)001:9956: de nas rnal 'byor pa rnams dbang rim pa sbyar la 'di skad do //
NK011(da)001:9957: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)001:9958: dam rdzas gnyan po mngon bkram nas //
NK011(da)001:9959: rdo rje bdag po dngos grub bdag po yin //
NK011(da)001:9960: dbang dang dngos grub rdzas mchog rnams //
NK011(da)001:9961: gang zhig dngos grub 'dod pa nga las longs //
NK011(da)001:9962: bu mchog rnams kyis dngos grub thob par shog /
NK011(da)001:9963: las dang sgrub pa'i dbang dang byin rlabs rnams //
NK011(da)001:9964: sgrub mchog rnams kyis rim bzhin thob gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:9965: da ni b+han+d+ha'i dbang bskur ba 'di skad do //
NK011(da)001:9966: thugs rje'i dbang mchog dpal chen he ru ka /
NK011(da)001:9967: ta krita 'bar tshogs bcas pa ma lus kun //
NK011(da)001:9968: snod bcud dbang bskur dbang rdzas 'dis //
NK011(da)001:9969: mu stegs gnod sbyin thod thogs dbang du bsdus //
NK011(da)001:9970: dpal gyi snod zhal lcang lo 'khyil ba 'dis //
NK011(da)001:9971: mkha' 'gro 'bar ba rol par byin brlabs la //
NK011(da)001:9972: dpa' bo'i mgo la rnam shes sna tshogs pas //
NK011(da)001:9973: ye shes rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos grub 'di byin no //
NK011(da)001:9974: ka p+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa sarba ma tra /
NK011(da)001:9975: b+han+d+ha 'phrul gyi zhal bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK011(da)001:9976: spong len byed pa'i bya ba lhun gyis rdzogs te
NK011(da)001:9977: dur khrod chen po'i gnas su sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK011(da)001:9978: byin gyis brlab pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK011(da)001:9979: / de nas chas brgyad kyi dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)001:9982: zhing lpags rtag tu g.yogs pa dur khrod bdag /
NK011(da)001:9983: g.yang gzhi tshigs su sdud pas sku la bcings //
NK011(da)001:9984: 'khor ba ma spangs gnas su dag pa yi //
NK011(da)001:9985: dur khrod tshogs kyi bdag po yin pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:9986: zhing chen rlon pa thabs la mkhas pa yis //
NK011(da)001:9987: 'khor ba'i gnas na yongs su rgyal bar shog /
NK011(da)001:9991: glang chen ko rlon brjid du che ba yi //
NK011(da)001:9992: gti mug ma lus gnas su dag pa'i brgyan //
NK011(da)001:9993: na baza'i rgyan gyis sku la mnga' gsol zhing //
NK011(da)001:9994: thabs kyi ko rlon rgyan gyi dam pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:9995: gang la dbang mchog 'di yi dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:9996: stobs kyi rgyal po'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK011(da)001:9997: ma d+aa ra ta sa sha ta h'u /
NK011(da)001:9998: stag gi sham thabs kyi dbang /
NK011(da)001:10000: zhe sdang drag po stag gi sham thabs 'di //
NK011(da)001:10001: stag lpags sham thabs dpa' bar ldan pa yi //
NK011(da)001:10002: sug sdob 'doms su bsnol ba phyi nang gsang ba gcig /
NK011(da)001:10003: phrag dog gnas 'joms stag lpags dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:10004: zhe sdang gnas 'joms phrag dog gnas 'joms pa'i //
NK011(da)001:10005: dbang mchog dam pa khyod kyis thob par shog /
NK011(da)001:10006: badz+ra bya gri tsarma a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u a /
NK011(da)001:10008: thod sbrul mnyen lcug 'jigs byed rgyan du che //
NK011(da)001:10009: sbrul nag stong gis brgyan pa'i rngams brjid can //
NK011(da)001:10010: sku la mchod phyir sku yi gnas lngar 'khril //
NK011(da)001:10011: dug lnga gnas su 'dul ba'i thabs su ston //
NK011(da)001:10012: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem zhe sdang drag po 'joms //
NK011(da)001:10013: rdzu 'phrul shugs kyis klu brgyad dbang du sdud //
NK011(da)001:10014: gti mug 'dul ba'i dbang phyug yin pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:10015: sbrul nag stong gi chun po'i dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:10016: zhe sdang 'bar ba gnas dag nas //
NK011(da)001:10017: thabs mkhas rgyal po mnyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)001:10018: n+aa ga r+aa dza hu lu hu lu h'u /
NK011(da)001:10020: dung chen khong seng dbang po lnga dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:10021: sku gsum tshul 'chang skam po ra ri'i tshul //
NK011(da)001:10022: 'khor ba gsum sdud thabs kyi phreng bas brgyan //
NK011(da)001:10023: khams gsum dbang sdud thod phreng dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:10024: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK011(da)001:10025: pad+ma b+han+d+ha ka p+aa la hasti h'u /
NK011(da)001:10028: 'bar ba'i phreng ba ye shes me ri ldan //
NK011(da)001:10029: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams nyon mongs dug bsregs pa //
NK011(da)001:10030: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na gnas //
NK011(da)001:10031: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcu'i mun nag sel //
NK011(da)001:10032: bskal pa me ri 'bar ba'i dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:10033: bar chad bgegs kyi rtog pas mi tshugs shing //
NK011(da)001:10034: mtshan ma 'dzin rtog bsreg pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)001:10035: badz+ra dz+wa la badz+ra dz+wa la ram ram h'u /
NK011(da)001:10037: rak+ta'i dbang bskur bas 'khor ba dbang du sdud par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:10038: thal chen gyi dbang bskur bas 'di dang phyi ma
NK011(da)001:10039: gnyis su dur khrod kyi rdzas la longs spyod cing
NK011(da)001:10040: dngos grub rnam gnyis thob pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK011(da)001:10041: gyur cig / zhag gi zo ris kyi dbang bskur
NK011(da)001:10042: bas ma mo dbang phyug ma la sogs pa rtag
NK011(da)001:10043: tu mi 'bral zhing bsrung ba dang skyob pa'i dbang
NK011(da)001:10046: chos kyi dbyings nyid mi 'gyur skur snang ba //
NK011(da)001:10047: ye shes lnga ldan thugs mtshan kun gyi mchog /
NK011(da)001:10048: 'dzin pa'i rgyal po rdo rje thugs mtshan 'das //
NK011(da)001:10049: skal ldan sgrub pa po la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:10051: rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas 'du 'bral skye shi med
NK011(da)001:10052: par g.yung drung tshe'i dngos grub dang sngags 'chang rgyal
NK011(da)001:10053: po rdo rje 'dzin gyi gral thob par gyur cig
NK011(da)001:10055: thugs mchog rtogs pa rig pa 'i dbang bskur bas //
NK011(da)001:10056: mya ngan 'das pa'i chos la spyod //
NK011(da)001:10057: thabs la mkhas pa sprul pa'i sras //
NK011(da)001:10059: tshogs gnyis rdzogs par dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:10060: pra dz+ny+aa pa ra yo gi ra du /
NK011(da)001:10063: dus mtha' med par sgrog pa chos kyi rnga //
NK011(da)001:10064: khams gsum dbang du sdud pa'i chos kyi sgra //
NK011(da)001:10065: thugs dam yongs su bskang ba'i rdzas mchog 'di'i //
NK011(da)001:10066: skal ldan sgrub pa po la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:10067: ma ka ra sa ya h'u /
NK011(da)001:10068: sgrub pa po ming 'di zhes bya ba la rnga'i
NK011(da)001:10069: dbang bskur bas dbyangs kyi dngos grub thob ste 'jig
NK011(da)001:10070: rten thams cad du chos kyi sgra chen po sgrogs
NK011(da)001:10071: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:10073: ral pa kham nag 'khyil ba chen po 'dir //
NK011(da)001:10074: dbang drag mthar phyin drag shul sprul pa 'phro //
NK011(da)001:10075: sku mchog mthing nag nam mkha'i rgyan bzhes pas //
NK011(da)001:10076: yon tan rgyas shing phrin las 'grub par bstan //
NK011(da)001:10077: 'khor ba ma spangs ral pa'i rgyan chen 'di'i //
NK011(da)001:10078: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:10079: ma h+aa bi du bi sha ka sid+d+hi hoh mar me'i dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)001:10080: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i bag chags bsal ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10081: ma rig rmongs pa'i mun pa 'joms pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:10082: ye shes 'od ldan gsal ba'i mar me 'di'i //
NK011(da)001:10083: skal ldan sgrub pa po la dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:10084: ram ha myi ti bi ma h+aa ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)001:10085: mar me'i dbang bskur bas rnam rtog mi mnga' cir yang sa ler mkhyen pa'i sa thob nas /
NK011(da)001:10086: ye shes kyi mes bag chags thams cad bsreg pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:10087: byug bdug brab pa'i dbang bskur te /
NK011(da)001:10089: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho chags pa'i bdag nyid ni //
NK011(da)001:10090: dgra bgegs thams cad dbang du sdud par byed //
NK011(da)001:10091: chags pa'i thugs rjes 'khor ba mi gtong ba //
NK011(da)001:10092: khams gsum dbang du sdud pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:10093: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+d+ha la h'u /
NK011(da)001:10095: gu gul gyi dbang bskur ba /
NK011(da)001:10096: gu gul sbyar ma'i rdzas mchog dam pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:10097: sdang ba'i dgra bo lha dang phral ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10098: gnod pa'i bgegs ni myos shing bsub par byed //
NK011(da)001:10099: srid gsum dbang du sdud pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK011(da)001:10100: ma gu la ta la ta la a ti sti h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10102: yungs kar rgyal po'i dbang ni /
NK011(da)001:10103: yungs kar rgyal po'i rdzas mchog dam pa 'di //
NK011(da)001:10104: gser mdog gzi 'phags rdo rje 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros //
NK011(da)001:10105: dgra bgegs ma lus rdul du brlag pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)001:10106: khams gsum sgrol ba'i bdag por dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:10107: be ta li man+d+ha la rak+sha rak+sha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10109: dbang rdzas bsdus la snying gar bzhag la /
NK011(da)001:10111: tshe yi snying po rgyud gsum po //
NK011(da)001:10112: srog gi snying po gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)001:10113: skye shi med pa byang chub sems //
NK011(da)001:10114: sku gsum sku ste sku la thim //
NK011(da)001:10115: gsung gsum gsung ste gsung la thim //
NK011(da)001:10116: thugs gsum thugs te thugs la thim //
NK011(da)001:10117: sku gsung thugs la rab tu thim //
NK011(da)001:10118: a yuhs la sid+d+hi sid+d+hi h'u /
NK011(da)001:10120: a be sha ya a +aah zhes bstim mo //
NK011(da)001:10121: de nas rdo rje slob dpon gyis dngos grub kyi
NK011(da)001:10122: zhal zas tsho bzhir bgos la bla ma la mchod
NK011(da)001:10125: mched lcam yongs la sbyin no //
NK011(da)001:10130: ma dag pa bzod par gsol lo //
NK011(da)001:10134: spyod lam rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10135: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i dbang gi chog khrigs rdzogs so //
NK011(da)001:10137: // 'di'i mtshams su tshogs mchod dang tshogs skong zhes pa de ma byung ///
NK011(da)001:10138: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i spyi thabs bsdus pa'i man ngag don gyi sgra bzhi'i bshad pa bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:10140: phur bu don gyi spyi thabs bsdus pa'i man ngag /
NK011(da)001:10141: bcom ldan 'das sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra k+ai la ya bid+yot+ta ma lar phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:10142: ye shes dbyings dang gnyis med byin rlabs kyis //
NK011(da)001:10143: phung po nyon mongs 'chi bdag rig pa ye shes kyi phur pa'i yon tan /
NK011(da)001:10145: de bzhin snying rje dga' dang btang snyoms kyi //
NK011(da)001:10146: tshad med snying rje'i phur pa'i yon tan /
NK011(da)001:10147: gtsor bzung ba'i gnyis med 'phro 'dus de bzhin no //
NK011(da)001:10148: byang chub sems kyi phur pa /
NK011(da)001:10149: zhi rgyas dbang dang drag po'i kyang de bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10150: mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa /
NK011(da)001:10151: phur bu dang po gnyis gsum bzhi pas bcom //
NK011(da)001:10152: dang po dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med ldan //
NK011(da)001:10153: gnyis pa shes rab snying rje thabs dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:10154: gsum pa thabs dang shes rab gnyis med ldan //
NK011(da)001:10155: bzhi pa bdag nyid khro bo phur par ldan //
NK011(da)001:10156: rtsa ba dang dbang phyug dang rdzas te /
NK011(da)001:10157: yang na re re la yang yon tan drug ldan no //
NK011(da)001:10159: dbyings dang ye shes rtag chad mtha' las 'das //
NK011(da)001:10160: las dang nyon mongs mtha' las snying rje 'das //
NK011(da)001:10161: 'khor ba sdug bsngal mtha' las bde chen 'das //
NK011(da)001:10162: bar chad dgra bgegs mtha' las rdzas phur 'das //
NK011(da)001:10163: sh+r+ai ni dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med dpal //
NK011(da)001:10164: ka ru snying rje phur pa'i bdag nyid de //
NK011(da)001:10165: ru ni r+aa ga chags pa'i byang chub sems //
NK011(da)001:10166: he ru rdzas kyi phur bu rgyud dang bral //
NK011(da)001:10167: badz+ra rig pa rdo rje 'du 'bral med //
NK011(da)001:10168: k+ai ni ka ru thugs rjes 'gro ba 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:10169: lak+sha byang chub bde ba'i rang bzhin las //
NK011(da)001:10170: ya ma gshin rje la sogs 'dul dbang ngo //
NK011(da)001:10171: bid ni rig pa'i phur pas mtha' gnyis 'joms //
NK011(da)001:10172: snying rje rtod de las dang nyon mongs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:10173: ta ni tsit+ta sa sdug bsngal phung po 'joms //
NK011(da)001:10174: ma h+aa sprul pa chen pos gdul bya 'dul //
NK011(da)001:10175: ma ni dbyer med spros bral thig le gcig tu 'ub //
NK011(da)001:10176: de phyir spyi thabs rnam pa bzhir bsdus pa //
NK011(da)001:10177: mi phyed dad pa blo ldan tshogs srid 'dud //
NK011(da)001:10178: rdzod byed ston dang rnal 'byor 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)001:10179: brjod bya phur bu bzhi don bsdus rgyas yin //
NK011(da)001:10180: sgra dang don spyi 'brel ba brjod pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10181: dang po lta ba'i gzhung dang rang bzhin 'brel //
NK011(da)001:10182: gnyis pa snying rje'i tshogs dang 'gro ba 'brel //
NK011(da)001:10183: gsum pa thabs dang shes rab dgongs par 'brel //
NK011(da)001:10184: bzhi pa las dang thugs rjes gdul bya 'brel //
NK011(da)001:10185: mtha' gnyis 'joms dang 'khor ba mi gtong dang //
NK011(da)001:10186: sdug bsngal sel dang gdul bya 'dul ba ste //
NK011(da)001:10187: go rim bzhin du sgra bzhi shes pa'i /
NK011(da)001:10192: yang sgos yin te dgos 'brel spyi don bshad //
NK011(da)001:10193: chu dang 'o ma ngang pa'i mchus 'byed ltar //
NK011(da)001:10194: shes rab stobs kyis bka' brgyud mtha' dag la //
NK011(da)001:10195: sgra gcig don mang la sogs bye brag rnams //
NK011(da)001:10196: mkhas pa dga' ba bskyed phyir brtsam par byed //
NK011(da)001:10197: rgyud lung man ngag kun dang mi 'gal zhing //
NK011(da)001:10198: bka' la snang zhing 'thad pa'i gtan tshigs 'di //
NK011(da)001:10199: rnal 'byor kun gyis nyams su blang bar rigs //
NK011(da)001:10200: gleng gzhi dang ni mtshan nyid rab dbye dang //
NK011(da)001:10201: rang ngo btab yul dang ni dgos ched dang //
NK011(da)001:10202: btab thabs thebs pa'i rtags dang ma thebs skyon //
NK011(da)001:10203: thabs kyi grogs dang gnas dang dus dag dang //
NK011(da)001:10204: rgyu dang 'bras bu las dang dkyil 'khor dang //
NK011(da)001:10205: dgug dang gzhug dang bcing dang dbang bya dang //
NK011(da)001:10206: mnan dang bzlog dang bsnyen dang sgrub pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10207: sdud dang spar dang bsreg dang bstab pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10208: dpral dang bdug dang gtor ma dug rdzas dang //
NK011(da)001:10209: mjug bsdu ba ste bsdus don sum cu gsum //
NK011(da)001:10210: sngon byung 'das pa'i dus na sangs rgyas rnams //
NK011(da)001:10211: gdul bya rnams la phan par dgongs pa na //
NK011(da)001:10212: dang po ye shes che la snyoms zhugs te //
NK011(da)001:10213: gnyis pa snying rjes kun la khyab mdzad cing //
NK011(da)001:10214: gsum pa shes rab thabs kyi sbyor ba mdzad //
NK011(da)001:10215: bzhi pa dkyil 'khor gsum du rnam sprul nas //
NK011(da)001:10216: gdul bya'i dbang du 'gro don rdzogs par mdzad //
NK011(da)001:10217: rgyud kun las snang sngon gyi gleng gzhi yin //
NK011(da)001:10218: dang po'i mtshan rig pa ye shes kyi phur pa /
NK011(da)001:10219: nyid stong zhing bdag med pa //
NK011(da)001:10220: gnyis pa snying rjes tshad med snying rje'i phur pa /
NK011(da)001:10222: gsum pa chos byang chub sems kyi phur pa /
NK011(da)001:10223: kun bde ba'i ngang du gsal //
NK011(da)001:10224: bzhi pa las mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur pa /
NK011(da)001:10225: bzhis don sgrub mtshan nyid yin //
NK011(da)001:10226: rab dbye ye shes spros med spros bcas gnyis //
NK011(da)001:10227: spros med brjod bral ye nas gnyis su med //
NK011(da)001:10228: ye shes chen po kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK011(da)001:10229: spros bcas ye shes chen pos kun khyab dang //
NK011(da)001:10230: ma 'gags snang ba'i rang byung ye shes dang //
NK011(da)001:10231: don gcod rig pa'i ye shes gsum du gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10232: de las spros pa ye shes bsam yas so //
NK011(da)001:10233: snying rje snying rje che dang mchog dang gsum //
NK011(da)001:10234: snying rje ngan 'gro sdug bsngal can la'o //
NK011(da)001:10235: chen po khams gsum mtha' dag kun la 'byung //
NK011(da)001:10236: mchog ni nyan thos la sogs 'phags la'o //
NK011(da)001:10237: lhag pa'i sems la rnam pa gsum yod de //
NK011(da)001:10238: bde ba'i sems dang bde chen bde mchog go //
NK011(da)001:10239: tha ma 'bring dang rab tu bstan pa yin //
NK011(da)001:10240: rdzas kyi phur pa bsdu na rnam pa bzhi //
NK011(da)001:10241: zhi rgyas dbang drag so so'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK011(da)001:10242: gdul bya thabs su bstan pa bsam mi khyab //
NK011(da)001:10243: don bzhi rang gi ngo bor gsungs pa ni //
NK011(da)001:10244: byang chub sems nyid kun gyi ngo bo ste //
NK011(da)001:10245: dang po don dam gsum ni kun rdzob yin //
NK011(da)001:10246: sems kyi rang bzhin sems kyi rnam pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10247: yul ni dbyings dang 'gro ba mkha' dang ni //
NK011(da)001:10248: gdul bya gang yin de dag go rim bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10249: mtha' gnyis 'joms dang las dang nyon mongs sel //
NK011(da)001:10250: sdug bsngal stong dang 'gro ba'i don 'grub pa //
NK011(da)001:10251: phur bu bzhi btab dgos ched yin zhes gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10252: thabs ni lus dang man ngag mthar phyin dang //
NK011(da)001:10253: don dam rtogs dang tshad med grogs tshang dang //
NK011(da)001:10254: shes rab thabs kyi yan lag tshang ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10255: gdul bya'i bsam pa'i dgongs pa rdzogs pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10256: 'di ni phur bu btab pa'i thabs bzhi yin //
NK011(da)001:10257: ci la'ang ma chags mi g.yo gnyis 'dzin bral //
NK011(da)001:10258: snying rjes sems can don la skyo ba med //
NK011(da)001:10259: cho 'phrul thabs kyis phyag rgya'i 'phro 'du gsal //
NK011(da)001:10260: rtags dang mtshan ma dus su phyin pa ni //
NK011(da)001:10261: phur bu thebs pa'i rtags bzhi go rim bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10262: yod med la sogs mtha' las 'chal ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10263: thabs med shes rab bral zhing rmongs pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10264: dngos rtog spyod pa barlanga por spyod pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10265: rdzas la 'cha' zhing don la nyams pa ni //
NK011(da)001:10266: mu stegs nyan thos mngal gyi srin bu dang //
NK011(da)001:10267: las kyi srin por skyes te go rim bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10268: de las ldog pa yon tan yin par gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10269: de yi grogs ni dad dang dam tshig dang //
NK011(da)001:10270: spyod dang ting nge dang byin rlabs lnga'o //
NK011(da)001:10271: sems kyis mnyam pa'i don gnyis 'dod pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10272: snying rjes 'gro ba'i don la dang ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10273: sbyor ba'i snyoms 'jug don la mos pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10274: mthu yis gdul bya'i don du yid ches pa //
NK011(da)001:10275: rnal 'byor dad pa rnam bzhi go rim bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10276: lta bas gnyis med don las mi 'da' zhing //
NK011(da)001:10277: spyod pas 'gro ba'i don la skyo ba med //
NK011(da)001:10278: dgongs pas bde chen don la 'du 'bral med //
NK011(da)001:10279: thabs kyis gdul bya'i don la le lo med //
NK011(da)001:10280: lta spyod mi spang dang blang dam tshig bzhi //
NK011(da)001:10281: mi 'da' dam tshig rnam bzhi go rim bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10282: rnam pa gcig tu ji ltar grags pa yi //
NK011(da)001:10283: gsang ba'i dam tshig rnams ni ci rigs bsrung //
NK011(da)001:10284: blang dor med pa mnyam nyid spyod pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10285: byams sdang med pa snying rje'i spyod pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10286: 'du 'bral med pa g.yeng bral spyod pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10287: ci 'dul thabs dang mtshan ma'i spyod pa ste //
NK011(da)001:10288: rnal 'byor dang blang spyod bzhi go rim bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10289: mnyam pa chen po stong pa'i ting 'dzin dang //
NK011(da)001:10290: snying rje 'gro ba'i don la rtse gcig dang //
NK011(da)001:10291: bde ba chen po'i ngang la snyoms 'jug dang //
NK011(da)001:10292: thabs kyi ting 'dzin cho 'phrul sna tshogs ston //
NK011(da)001:10293: de bzhin nyid dang kun snang bde rgyu rim pa bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10294: lta bas chos kyi sku ru byin brlabs dang //
NK011(da)001:10295: snying rjes 'gro la phan par byin brlabs dang //
NK011(da)001:10296: byang chub sems kyis gzi byin bskyed pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10297: thabs kyis mthu dpung che bar byin brlabs pa //
NK011(da)001:10298: rnam pa bzhi po go rim bzhin du sbyar //
NK011(da)001:10299: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs dang chos kyi dbyings //
NK011(da)001:10300: rang gi yid dang don dam byang chub dang //
NK011(da)001:10301: bde chen sku yi pho brang ting 'dzin dang //
NK011(da)001:10302: phyi nang gsang ba'i gnas te rnam bzhi ni //
NK011(da)001:10303: rnam bzhi sgrub pa'i gnas su rgyal bas gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10304: lung dang man ngag tshad du phyin pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10305: don dam byang chub sems la yid ches dang //
NK011(da)001:10306: shes rab thabs kyi ting 'dzin gsal ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10307: gdul bya gang gi dus la bab pa yi //
NK011(da)001:10308: phyi nang dus su bstan pa rnam bzhi ni //
NK011(da)001:10309: phur bu bzhi yi dus tshod go rim bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10310: rgyu rkyen med par rang sems gnas 'gyur dang //
NK011(da)001:10311: rang gi sems dang 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal dang //
NK011(da)001:10312: thabs dang shes rab dgongs pa mthun pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10313: rin chen srog rtsa phur ba rdzas kyi rgyu //
NK011(da)001:10314: gsang dang ye shes sa bon khro bo'i rgyu //
NK011(da)001:10315: rgyu bzhi go rim bzhin du bstan pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10316: rnam smin 'bras bu chos skur 'grub pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10317: rgyu mthun snying rje 'gro la 'tshams par skye //
NK011(da)001:10318: skyes bu byed pa de la nyams myong byed //
NK011(da)001:10319: 'dul byed dbang gis gdul bya 'tshams par sbyor //
NK011(da)001:10320: dri med 'bras bu kun la khyab par gnas //
NK011(da)001:10321: 'bras bzhi don bzhi 'tshams par mkhas pas bshad //
NK011(da)001:10322: ye shes phrin las mtha' gnyis 'joms shing sreg /
NK011(da)001:10323: thugs rje'i phrin las 'gro ba gnas su stob //
NK011(da)001:10324: byang chub phrin las sdug bsngal phung po sreg /
NK011(da)001:10325: sprul pa'i phrin las 'dul dbang don mthar phyin //
NK011(da)001:10326: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kun la khyab //
NK011(da)001:10327: spros med snying po rig pas len pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10328: thugs rje'i snying po mdzad pas len pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10329: bde chen snying po snyoms par 'jug pas len //
NK011(da)001:10330: nan tan snying pos phrin las rgya mtsho len //
NK011(da)001:10331: snying po len phyir man+dala go rim bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10332: yang na spros med de bzhin nyid dang ni //
NK011(da)001:10333: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gsungs pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10334: lus dang b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor nyid dang yang //
NK011(da)001:10335: mtshan ma dbyibs kyi dkyil 'khor de rim bzhin //
NK011(da)001:10336: dbyibs ni zur gsum zla gam gsum la gru chad rgyan //
NK011(da)001:10337: sgo dang sgo khyud rta babs ra bas brgyan //
NK011(da)001:10338: dbyings las ye shes gsum snang gru gsum ste //
NK011(da)001:10339: rtag chad dbu mar mnga' brnyes zla gam yin //
NK011(da)001:10340: ye shes kun tu rgyas phyir gru chad bzhi //
NK011(da)001:10341: spros pa med pa'i tshul gyis kun nas zlum //
NK011(da)001:10342: rig pa shar sgo yon tan lho yi sgo //
NK011(da)001:10343: ma rig nub sgo bag chags byang zhes bya //
NK011(da)001:10344: yon tan mi zad sgo khyud rnam thar brgyad //
NK011(da)001:10345: rta babs mi phyed rdo rje'i phreng las brgyan //
NK011(da)001:10346: rig pa rang gi bye brag lha rnams bkod //
NK011(da)001:10347: dang po'i don la dkyil 'khor rim pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10348: byang chub sems nyid sku gsung thugs zur gsum //
NK011(da)001:10349: lus dang ngag yid don dbang zla gam yin //
NK011(da)001:10350: tshad med kun tu rgyas phyir gru bzhi'o //
NK011(da)001:10351: thugs rje nyid kyang spros bral kun nas zlum //
NK011(da)001:10352: sgo bzhi tshad med bzhi yi rang bzhin la //
NK011(da)001:10353: 'dren thabs bsam gyis mi khyab sgo khyud tshul //
NK011(da)001:10354: rnam thar brgyad kyi lam stegs rta babs la //
NK011(da)001:10355: snying rje 'gro dang mi phyed rdo rje'i phreng //
NK011(da)001:10356: lha tshogs thabs kyi bye brag bsam yas bkod //
NK011(da)001:10357: gnyis pa'i don la dkyil 'khor rim pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10358: thabs kyi sku gsung thugs ni zur gsum ste //
NK011(da)001:10359: shes rab sku gsung thugs ni zla gam yin //
NK011(da)001:10360: yan lag bzhi bzhi rgyas pa'i gru chad 'bar //
NK011(da)001:10361: thabs shes yan lag dang po kun nas zlum //
NK011(da)001:10362: lus kyi sgo bzhi yan lag sgo khyud ldan //
NK011(da)001:10363: rnam shes brgyad ni rta babs mi phyed rdo rje'i phreng //
NK011(da)001:10364: phung po khams dang skye mched lha rnams bkod //
NK011(da)001:10365: gsum pa'i don la dkyil 'khor rim pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10366: drag po gru gsum dbang la zla gam ste //
NK011(da)001:10367: rgyas pa lham pa bzlum po zhi ba'i tshul //
NK011(da)001:10368: 'jug pa'i sgo bzhi 'tshams pa'i sgo khyud can //
NK011(da)001:10369: 'bab stegs brgyad dang rdo rje'i phreng bas bskor //
NK011(da)001:10370: bdag phur khro bo'i tshogs kyi lha rnams bkod //
NK011(da)001:10371: bzhi ba'i don la dkyil 'khor rim pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10372: yi ge tshad med bdud rtsi rdul tshon lnga //
NK011(da)001:10373: so so'i tshon gyi ngo bor shes par bya //
NK011(da)001:10374: der 'jug rim pa dag kyang ci rigs sbyar //
NK011(da)001:10375: ye shes rtsal gyis mtha' gnyis dbu mar 'gug /
NK011(da)001:10376: thugs rjes las dang nyon mongs gnas su 'dren //
NK011(da)001:10377: byang chub sems kyis sdug bsngal bde bar 'dren //
NK011(da)001:10378: sprul pa'i pho nyas dgra bgegs myur du 'gug /
NK011(da)001:10379: dgug pa rnam bzhi go rim bzhin du sbyar //
NK011(da)001:10380: ye shes chen pos mtha' gnyis dbu mar gzhug /
NK011(da)001:10381: thugs rjes las dang nyon mongs grol bar gzhug /
NK011(da)001:10382: sbyor bas sdug bsngal phung po bde bar bstim //
NK011(da)001:10383: zhags pas 'gal byed rnam shes rten la gzhug /
NK011(da)001:10384: gzhug pa'i don bzhi go rim ji lta ba'o //
NK011(da)001:10385: ye shes sgrog gis mtha' gnyis dbu mar bcings //
NK011(da)001:10386: thugs rjes las dang nyon mongs thar par bcings //
NK011(da)001:10387: sbyor bas sdug bsngal phung po bde bar bcings //
NK011(da)001:10388: pho nya'i sgrog gis dgra bgegs rten la bcings //
NK011(da)001:10389: mtha' gnyis dang ni las dang nyon mongs dang //
NK011(da)001:10390: 'khor ba sdug bsngal dam 'gal dgra bgegs bzhi //
NK011(da)001:10391: rim bzhin phur pa bzhi yis dbang du bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10392: rtag chad las dang nyon mongs sdug bsngal dang //
NK011(da)001:10393: dgra bgegs phyis mi 'phel bar don bzhis mnan //
NK011(da)001:10394: rig pa'i rtsal gyis rtag chad mtha' las zlog /
NK011(da)001:10395: las dang nyon mongs thugs rje'i shugs kyis zlog /
NK011(da)001:10396: mtshan ma'i sdug bsngal bde ba'i dgongs pas zlog /
NK011(da)001:10397: bar gcod dgra bgegs sprul pa'i mtshams kyis zlog /
NK011(da)001:10398: lung dang man ngag tshad mas ye shes bsnyen //
NK011(da)001:10399: don dam rtogs pa'i shugs kyis snying rje bsnyen //
NK011(da)001:10400: sbyor ba'i yan lag thabs kyis bde chen bsnyen //
NK011(da)001:10401: mtshan ma dus dang grangs kyis grub rtags bsnyen //
NK011(da)001:10402: sgrub la mchod dang rdzas dang phyag rgya dang //
NK011(da)001:10403: ting 'dzin bzlas pa nyams su blang ba lnga'o //
NK011(da)001:10404: kun bzang mchod pas ye shes lha rnams mnyes //
NK011(da)001:10405: phyi nang mchod pas thugs rje'i lha tshogs thim //
NK011(da)001:10406: g+ha na mchod pas bde chen lha tshogs mnyes //
NK011(da)001:10407: dam rdzas mchod pas sprul pa'i lha tshogs thim //
NK011(da)001:10408: lung dang man ngag rdzas brten gnyis bral sgrub //
NK011(da)001:10409: shes rab snying rje'i rdzas brten 'gro don sgrub //
NK011(da)001:10410: gtso gzungs thabs la brten nas bde chen sgrub //
NK011(da)001:10411: phur pa rdzas la brten nas 'dod pa sgrub //
NK011(da)001:10412: sku dang gsung thugs las kyi phyag rgya bzhi //
NK011(da)001:10413: chos sku longs sku bde ba sprul pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:10414: phur bu sku yi phyag rgya rnam bzhir gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10415: don gsung sgra gsung sngags gsung sprul pa'i gsung //
NK011(da)001:10416: phur bu gsung gi phyag rgya rtags bzhir gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10417: mi rtog snying rje bde thugs kun mkhyen thugs //
NK011(da)001:10418: 'bar ba'i srog bzhi thugs kyi phyag rgyar bshad //
NK011(da)001:10419: zhi rgyas dbang drag las kyi phyag rgya ste //
NK011(da)001:10420: ye shes chen pos rtag chad dngos po bzhi //
NK011(da)001:10421: snying rje chen pos las dang nyon mongs zhi //
NK011(da)001:10422: bde ba chen pos mtshan ma'i sdug bsngal zhi //
NK011(da)001:10423: zhi ba'i phur pas gdug rtsub dngos po zhi //
NK011(da)001:10424: de phyir zhi ba las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK011(da)001:10425: gnyis med ye shes ngang las tshogs gnyis rgyas //
NK011(da)001:10426: byang chub snying rje'i ngang las tshad med rgyas //
NK011(da)001:10427: mkha' gsang sbyor ba'i ngang las bde ba rgyas //
NK011(da)001:10428: 'phro 'du sprul pa'i ngang las cho 'phrul rgyas //
NK011(da)001:10429: de phyir rgyas pa las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK011(da)001:10430: dbang bzhi gong du bshad pa de dang mtshungs //
NK011(da)001:10431: ye shes drag pos rtag chad dngos po gsod //
NK011(da)001:10432: thugs rje drag pos las dang nyon mongs gsod //
NK011(da)001:10433: mkha' dbyings drag pos sdug bsngal phung po gsod //
NK011(da)001:10434: drag po'i phur pas bar gcod dgra bgegs gsod //
NK011(da)001:10435: de phyir drag po las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK011(da)001:10436: rtogs pa'i ye shes ting 'dzin kun khyab gdal //
NK011(da)001:10437: khyab pa snying rje'i ting 'dzin rgyun mi chad //
NK011(da)001:10438: bde ba chen po'i ting 'dzin rtse gcig gsal //
NK011(da)001:10439: sprul pa phyag rgya'i ting 'dzin char ltar 'bebs //
NK011(da)001:10440: nyams su blang ba'i ting 'dzin rnam bzhi'o //
NK011(da)001:10441: rig pa rtsal gyis gnyis med don la bzlas //
NK011(da)001:10442: snying rje 'khor ba ma stongs bar du bzlas //
NK011(da)001:10443: bde ba ma rnyed bar du sbyor ba bzlas //
NK011(da)001:10444: las rnams ma grub bar du snying po bzlas //
NK011(da)001:10445: nyams su blang ba'i bzlas brjod sgrub pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10446: dang por chos kun mnyam nyid ngang du bsdu //
NK011(da)001:10447: gnyis pa thams cad snying rje'i zhing du bsdu //
NK011(da)001:10448: gsum pa yab yum bde ba'i ngang du bsdu //
NK011(da)001:10449: bdag phur gzas gsum grub mtha' gcig tu bsdu //
NK011(da)001:10450: rnam pa bzhi yang dbyer med thig ler bsdu //
NK011(da)001:10451: chos rnams thams cad mnyam pa'i ngang du spar //
NK011(da)001:10452: snying rjes las dang nyon mongs grol bar spar //
NK011(da)001:10453: yab yum mkha' la 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal spar //
NK011(da)001:10454: bsgral ba'i rnam shes 'chi med gnas su spar //
NK011(da)001:10455: ye shes me yis rtag chad dngos po bsreg /
NK011(da)001:10456: las dang nyon mongs thugs rje'i me yis bsreg /
NK011(da)001:10457: byang chub zer gyis bsdug bsngal bud shing bsreg /
NK011(da)001:10458: sprul pa'i me yis 'gal byed sha rus bsreg /
NK011(da)001:10459: bla med nang gsang phyi yi sbyin sreg yin //
NK011(da)001:10460: rtag chad dngos po ye shes zhal du bstab //
NK011(da)001:10461: las dang nyon mongs thugs rje'i zhal du bstab //
NK011(da)001:10462: sdug bsngal phung po yab yum mkha' la bstab //
NK011(da)001:10463: bsgral ba'i sha khrag khro rgyal zhal du bstab //
NK011(da)001:10464: zhen pa'i sems dang rtag chad dngos po phral //
NK011(da)001:10465: snying rje'i zhing rnams sdug bsngal khur dang phral //
NK011(da)001:10466: bde ba 'dod pa g.yeng ba'i skyon dang bral //
NK011(da)001:10467: dam la gnod pa 'go ba'i lha dang bral //
NK011(da)001:10468: rtag chad mtha' la dbu ma'i dri yis bdug /
NK011(da)001:10469: snying rje'i zhing la 'dul khrims dri yis bdug /
NK011(da)001:10470: bde bar mos la snyoms 'jug dri yis bdug /
NK011(da)001:10471: 'gal byed myos phyir gu gul sogs kyis bdug /
NK011(da)001:10472: ye shes dbyings kyi gtor mas kun la khyab //
NK011(da)001:10473: tshad med snying rje'i gtor mas kun la phan //
NK011(da)001:10474: bkra gsal ting 'dzin gtor ma bde bas khyab //
NK011(da)001:10475: khyad par phrin las gtor mas 'dod pa sgrub //
NK011(da)001:10476: mtha' gnyis 'ching byed rtag chad zhen pa'i dug /
NK011(da)001:10477: las dang nyon mongs dug gis ngan song gnas su 'chi //
NK011(da)001:10478: g.yeng ba mang po'i dug gis sdug bsngal rgya mtshor 'chi //
NK011(da)001:10479: sbyar sogs dug gis lus dang sems su 'bral //
NK011(da)001:10480: lta ba rtsa ba g.yengs pa rdzas kyi dug /
NK011(da)001:10481: mjug bsdus pa la dngos grub blang ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10482: dbang bskur ba dang dam tshig blang ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10483: bshags dang las kyi lhag chad bskang ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10484: go cha dang ni 'gro nyal 'dug sdod dang //
NK011(da)001:10485: rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin dang bcu gcig go //
NK011(da)001:10486: khyad par chos sku'i dngos grub dang po yin //
NK011(da)001:10487: 'gro don rdzogs pa'i dngos grub gnyis pa yin //
NK011(da)001:10488: bde chen 'du 'bral med par gsum pa yin //
NK011(da)001:10489: thun mong ji snyed grags pa bzhi pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10490: de kun rang sems rnam pa yin par gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10491: grub pa gong nas 'byin pa phyi yi tshul //
NK011(da)001:10492: rang byung rdzogs chen bla na med pa'i tshul //
NK011(da)001:10493: rdzas la brten nas dbang bskur bzhi pa yin //
NK011(da)001:10494: gsum pa la ni gtso zungs gsang ba'i dbang //
NK011(da)001:10495: gnyis pa la ni shes rab rig pa'i dbang //
NK011(da)001:10496: dang po la ni spros bral shin tu gsang //
NK011(da)001:10497: bskur ba'i dbang ni rim par bgrod dgos kyang //
NK011(da)001:10498: rig pa rang dbang shin tu gtso bar gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10499: dang po la ni mnyam pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)001:10500: de las 'das na mtha' gnyis mun par ltung //
NK011(da)001:10501: gnyis pa 'gro don rdzogs pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)001:10502: de las 'das na nyan thos sa ru ltung //
NK011(da)001:10503: gsum pa la ni sbyor ba'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)001:10504: de las 'das na mngal gyi srin bur skye //
NK011(da)001:10505: bzhi pa la ni spyod pa'i dam tshig ste //
NK011(da)001:10506: dngos por spyod na las kyi srin por skye //
NK011(da)001:10507: rtsa ba yan lag ji ltar grags pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:10508: lta spyod sgrub dang las kyi bye brag gis //
NK011(da)001:10509: so so'i rim pa bzhin du bsrung shes bya //
NK011(da)001:10510: lta ba nyams na chos nyid ngang du sgom //
NK011(da)001:10511: spyod pa bdag gzhan gnyis su med par sgom //
NK011(da)001:10512: sgrub pa nyams na blang dor med par sgom //
NK011(da)001:10513: phrin las nyams na grub mtha' gcig tu sgom //
NK011(da)001:10514: don dam gnyis su med pa'i bye brag bzhi'o //
NK011(da)001:10515: yang na don dam la ni don dam mo //
NK011(da)001:10516: rnam pa kun la kun rdzob so sor bshags //
NK011(da)001:10517: mtha' gnyis las kyi rtag chad dbu mar bshags //
NK011(da)001:10518: las dang nyon mongs thugs rje che la bshags //
NK011(da)001:10519: sdug bsngal phung po yab yum ngang du bshags //
NK011(da)001:10520: phrin las rtag chad sprul pa'i lha la bshags //
NK011(da)001:10521: gnyis su med pa'i don la blo bzhag na //
NK011(da)001:10522: cho ga lhag gam chad kyang nyes pa med //
NK011(da)001:10523: ye shes go cha rtag chad mtha' mi bshig /
NK011(da)001:10524: snying rje'i go cha las kyi mthus mi bshig /
NK011(da)001:10525: sdug bsngal dpung gis bde ba'i go mi bshig /
NK011(da)001:10526: bar chad byed pas phyag rgya'i go mi bshig /
NK011(da)001:10527: mdor na stong pa'i go cha rab tu sra //
NK011(da)001:10528: dang po dbu ma'i don la ma yengs 'gro //
NK011(da)001:10529: 'gro la snying rje'i sems 'gro gnyis pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10530: shes rab thabs su snang grags rtog gsum po //
NK011(da)001:10531: chos kun bdag phur khro bor lta ba ste //
NK011(da)001:10534: nyal tshe stong pa'i ngang la mnal ba dang //
NK011(da)001:10535: snying rje chen po'i ngang la bzhag pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10536: rang gi lha mo sems la bsdus nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:10537: bde ba chen po'i ngang las mi nyams dang //
NK011(da)001:10538: dkyil 'khor thams cad rang la bsdus nas su //
NK011(da)001:10539: rang nyid ye shes thugs la bsdus nas ni //
NK011(da)001:10540: ma yengs langs nas dkyil 'khor slar bskyed bya //
NK011(da)001:10541: 'dug tshe de nyid rnam bzhi bsam bya ste //
NK011(da)001:10542: ye shes thugs rje bdag dang sprul pa yin //
NK011(da)001:10543: de nyid sems shing g.yeng ba gzhan mi bsam //
NK011(da)001:10544: skad cig sdod tshe'ang rgyun gyi bsam mi dor //
NK011(da)001:10545: lus ngag gzhan du spyod kyang sems nyid drang por gnas //
NK011(da)001:10546: rang gi ting 'dzin le lo'i dbang mi btang //
NK011(da)001:10547: lta bas rgyun du mnyam pa'i don mi btang //
NK011(da)001:10548: mdzad pas rgyun du 'gro ba'i don mdzad cing //
NK011(da)001:10549: thabs dang shes rab ldan pas rgyun du sgrub //
NK011(da)001:10550: sprul pa'i 'phro 'du rgyun du nan tan bya //
NK011(da)001:10551: de ltar byas na 'bras bu chud mi za //
NK011(da)001:10552: lnga phung mi spang dgongs pa dpal gyi sku //
NK011(da)001:10553: rdo rje sems dpa' nga nyid yin zhes gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10554: thub pas brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10555: gsang sngags rgya mtsho rgyud lung man ngag gi //
NK011(da)001:10556: spyi yi sgrub pa'i thabs ni don bzhi po //
NK011(da)001:10557: phur bu sgra yi skabs su bsdud pa yin //
NK011(da)001:10558: bzhi ru bstan kyang don du gcig las med //
NK011(da)001:10559: gcig nyid rtogs par bya phyir tha dad bstan //
NK011(da)001:10560: byang chub sems ni rdo rje gcig pu nyid //
NK011(da)001:10561: gcig pu nyid du ma grub kun gyi ngang //
NK011(da)001:10562: gcig dang du ma'i bdag nyid chen po yin //
NK011(da)001:10563: snang dang mi snang stong dang mi stong dang //
NK011(da)001:10564: yod dang med dang don dam kun rdzob dang //
NK011(da)001:10565: rtag dang chad dang bde dang sdug bsngal sogs //
NK011(da)001:10566: kun kyang bdag nyid chen po'i ngo bo yin //
NK011(da)001:10567: de skad rgyal ba nyid kyi zhal nas gsungs //
NK011(da)001:10568: mnyam nyid can gyi blo la de ltar snang //
NK011(da)001:10569: blo zhan rnams la bstan na yid ches med //
NK011(da)001:10570: des na sgro skur stung ba'i sgor 'gyur te //
NK011(da)001:10571: de bas thugs la brnag la khar byung min //
NK011(da)001:10572: don 'dis rmongs na srid pa'i 'khor lor 'khyams //
NK011(da)001:10573: dge dang mi dge'i dbang 'gro chu bos g.yengs //
NK011(da)001:10574: 'di med gzhan gyi 'bras bus sangs mi rgya //
NK011(da)001:10575: 'di don rtogs na 'khor ba'i gseb las thar //
NK011(da)001:10576: dge dang mi dge las kyi dbang mi 'gro //
NK011(da)001:10577: mthong ba'i chos la mngon du ma gyur kyang //
NK011(da)001:10578: tshe 'di 'das ma thag tu mngon du 'gyur //
NK011(da)001:10579: don gyi sgra bzhi'i dgongs pa mi shes par //
NK011(da)001:10580: gsang sngags ji bzhin sgra phyir 'brangs pa rnams //
NK011(da)001:10581: seng ge'i gzugs kyis wa skad 'byin pa dang //
NK011(da)001:10582: pho rogs 'gros kyis sa gzhi khod snyoms 'dra //
NK011(da)001:10583: des ni gsang sngags dgongs pa mi shes te //
NK011(da)001:10584: de ma shes pas dngos grub ring du spang //
NK011(da)001:10585: thabs mchog sla zhing bde ba dag gis ni //
NK011(da)001:10586: 'bras mchog khyad par can rnyed phyir man ngag /
NK011(da)001:10587: gsang sngags rgya mtsho'i dgongs pa'i don mchog 'di //
NK011(da)001:10588: lung dang man ngag rig pas thag bcad de //
NK011(da)001:10589: gab cing sbas pa cung zad gsal phye ba'i //
NK011(da)001:10590: bsod nams gang yin 'gro ba'i don du bsngo //
NK011(da)001:10593: // slob dpon d+ha na samskri ta'i dgongs pa /
NK011(da)001:10594: blo ldan mchog sred kyis bris te mdzad /
NK011(da)001:10595: bod yul du slob dpon pad+ma thod phreng gis mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan la gnang /
NK011(da)001:10597: brang ti dza ya rak+shi tas sgra bsgyur byas te gab cing gsang ngo //
NK011(da)001:10601: // // dpal rdo rje phur pa'i drag sngags mchog tu gsang
NK011(da)001:10602: ba slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa pad+ma 'byung gnas
NK011(da)001:10603: kyi thugs kyi bcud phyungs pa lang lab byang chub
NK011(da)001:10604: rdo rje'i man ngag gzhan la med pa'i khyad chos
NK011(da)001:10605: gud du sbas pa'i skor rnams bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:10607: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:10608: phur pa rtsa dum gyi man ngag yang dag pa /
NK011(da)001:10609: thugs kyi nying khu sgrub pa las kyi rtags 'byin par thugs kyi spu gri /
NK011(da)001:10611: dgra bo phung bar byed pa'i phung sgrub /
NK011(da)001:10612: lang lab byang chub rdo rje sna nam shes rab tshul khrims la gnang ba lags so //
NK011(da)001:10613: sna nam gyi thugs kyi phur gcig ces bya ba
NK011(da)001:10614: dgra bo phug par byed pa'i phung bsgrub 'di la
NK011(da)001:10615: / dang po thod pa btsal ba'i man ngag bstan pa dang 1 /
NK011(da)001:10616: thod pa la dkyil 'khor bri ba'i man ngag bstan pa dang 2 /
NK011(da)001:10617: thod pa chas su gzhug pa'i man ngag bstan pa dang 3 /
NK011(da)001:10618: sngags bri ba'i man ngag bstan pa dang 4 /
NK011(da)001:10619: drag sngags brab pa'i man ngag bstan pa'o5 //
NK011(da)001:10621: rang bkra shis shing 'phel bar bya ba'i thod pa btsal ba dang /
NK011(da)001:10622: dgra bo phung zhing lag par bya ba'i thod pa btsal ba dang gnyis so //
NK011(da)001:10623: rang bkra shis shing 'phel bar bya ba ni /
NK011(da)001:10626: rmang bu med mang ba'i thod pa gcig la phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i dkyil 'khor bri'o //
NK011(da)001:10627: mo thod ni pha ming dar ba cho rigs che
NK011(da)001:10628: ba gcig gi thod pa la sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK011(da)001:10630: thod pa de gnyis ni rang bkra shis shing 'phel
NK011(da)001:10631: bar byed pa'i rdzas yin te tshon rtsi bzang pos
NK011(da)001:10632: dkyil 'khor kha dog legs par bsgyur la /
NK011(da)001:10633: dus rtag tu rang gi sngas 'og tu e gru gsum brus la de la bsnyen sgrub bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10634: dgra bo phung zhing brlag par byed pa'i thod pa ni /
NK011(da)001:10635: pho thod mi rmang zhing bu tsha bu mo gang
NK011(da)001:10636: yang med pa'i thod pa gcig la gsod pa'i ma
NK011(da)001:10637: dal phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i dkyil 'khor 'bri /
NK011(da)001:10638: mo thod ni mi rmang ba nyung ba bkra mi
NK011(da)001:10639: shis shing bu tsha pho mo gang yang med pa
NK011(da)001:10640: khyo gsum shi ba rabs chad pa de lta bu'i
NK011(da)001:10641: thod pa gcig la 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad bri /
NK011(da)001:10642: de yang tshon gyis kha dog bsgyur //
NK011(da)001:10643: sngags bri ba'i man ngag ni /
NK011(da)001:10644: sgrub pa'i thod pa dang dkyil 'khor la bri /
NK011(da)001:10645: mo thod kyi dkyil la gru gsum la rtsa ba'i snying po 'bru dgu bri /
NK011(da)001:10646: zla gam gsum la sku gsung thugs kyi snying po bri /
NK011(da)001:10647: rtsibs brgyad la khro bo bcu'i sngags bri /
NK011(da)001:10648: sgo bzhi la phrin las bzhi'i sngags bri /
NK011(da)001:10649: sgrub pa'i pho thod la drag sngags bri ste /
NK011(da)001:10653: gab pa'i sngags drug kun bri'o //
NK011(da)001:10654: thod pa de gnyis kyi phyogs bzhi phug nas ling
NK011(da)001:10655: ga bcug la dkar nag gis bsdams shing rgyas gdab
NK011(da)001:10657: pho thod la bsad sngags thams cad bri /
NK011(da)001:10658: mo thod la lam la sogs te mnan sngags thams cad bri'o //
NK011(da)001:10659: da ni ngan sngags brab pa'i man ngag la //
NK011(da)001:10660: pho thod kyi dkyil du khung gru gsum btod la
NK011(da)001:10661: de nas mar drag sngags thams cad kyis brab bo
NK011(da)001:10662: // sgrub pa'i thod pa'i dkyil 'khor la ni dus rtag tu bsnyen pa dgra med kyang 'bul lo //
NK011(da)001:10663: de ni rang shi yang gzhan du mi btang bar bsre la /
NK011(da)001:10664: des ni bkra shis pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:10665: phur pa ni lcags phur gcig la 'gro nyal 'dug tu bsnyen pa dbul lo //
NK011(da)001:10666: rang 'gro tsa na phur pa lid+ga'i snying gar btab la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:10667: dgra byung dus gtor ma la brtson par bya ste /
NK011(da)001:10668: nangs par skya rengs shar dus la btang /
NK011(da)001:10669: nub mo dmar thag chad pa la btang /
NK011(da)001:10670: 'di'i mnan pa ni lha 'dre che sar mnan no //
NK011(da)001:10671: gnas su byed na yang rang gi sngas 'og tu mis ma tshor bar bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10672: rtags ni zla ba gnyis las 'gyangs re dkon mchog dpang /
NK011(da)001:10674: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10675: ka tang ka te dza ye bi dza ye a tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK011(da)001:10676: on ma tri ma ho byi to /
NK011(da)001:10677: ra sho ra sha tsit+ta zung sod /
NK011(da)001:10682: b+ha ti ma ma karma sh+ai krang kar ya ma
NK011(da)001:10683: ra sa ni pra mar ta na ye h'u phata
NK011(da)001:10684: / ces drag sngags 'di la nyin stong mtshan stong du 'don no //
NK011(da)001:10685: drag sngags rtags byung byung du bzlas so //
NK011(da)001:10686: drag sngags 'di ni thams cad kyi thun du brab bo //
NK011(da)001:10687: rtags me stag gam 'od dam rmi ltas bzang po byung ba dang gdab pa'i las bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10688: sgrub pa'i tho yig chen po ltar byas la gdab bo //
NK011(da)001:10689: drag sngags 'di la rtag tu bsgrubs na phur pa kha gang bstan par 'dag go //
NK011(da)001:10690: phur pa rtsa dum gyi man ngag 'di la //
NK011(da)001:10691: sngags phyi nang gsang ba gsum yod de /
NK011(da)001:10694: sngags de rnams kyi nang nas man ngag tu phyungs pa ni /
NK011(da)001:10696: las rtags 'byin gyi drag sngags yin no //
NK011(da)001:10697: sngags kyi bgrang thabs rnam pa gsum la d+ha ti
NK011(da)001:10698: rgyas 'bring gsum phyes nas bgrang ba ni phyi'i drag
NK011(da)001:10699: sngags yin te phyi sgrub kyi dus su bgrang ngo
NK011(da)001:10700: // thams cad 'dus pa'i drag sngags ni nang sngags yin te nam skabs su bgrang ngo //
NK011(da)001:10701: gsang ba'i drag sngags ni las rtags 'byin gyi sngags
NK011(da)001:10702: yin te thod sgrub gsang ba'i 'khor lo dang sbyar
NK011(da)001:10703: ro // phur pa'i thod sgrub gsang ba 'di rang gi sngas 'og tu bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10704: thod sgrub la sgrub pa'i dus su nub re la
NK011(da)001:10705: dkyus phog re bsrangs la smad mchod phog re bya
NK011(da)001:10706: / gtor ma re nub re la gtong /
NK011(da)001:10707: phur pa thod sgrub gsang ba'i drag sngags 'di lang
NK011(da)001:10708: lab kyis dgra bo phung ba'i phung sgrub sna nam
NK011(da)001:10709: dang / rgya ston sangs rgyas kyi'ang dgra bo phung ba'i phung sgrub /
NK011(da)001:10710: 'di med phur pa gzhan kun sngags bzlas tshi chad klad pa 'bru la /
NK011(da)001:10711: 'di ni mtshon bas rno bas thugs kyi spu gri zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10712: reg pa tsam gyis chod pas thugs kyi reg chod ces bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10713: btsan dug kha tshir ma cis kyang gsor mi btub
NK011(da)001:10714: pa dang 'dra bas bal mo'i dug sngags zhes bya'o
NK011(da)001:10716: mig 'bras phyungs nas su la sbyin //
NK011(da)001:10717: sa la snubs pa dge rtsa yin //
NK011(da)001:10720: // dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:10721: zab cing kha tshang ba mang na yang /
NK011(da)001:10722: yang dag pa'i man ngag gi sngags 'adi'o //
NK011(da)001:10723: rtsa dum gyi drag sngags 'dril ba slob dpon pad+ma'i thugs kyi man ngag rgya gar gyi ngan sngags /
NK011(da)001:10725: mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal gyis slob dpon gyi thugs zin nas drag sngags mo la gtad /
NK011(da)001:10726: des la byid ye shes brtsegs la gtad /
NK011(da)001:10727: des mi nub rgyal ba'i snying po la gtad /
NK011(da)001:10728: des ngam 'bre klu'i rgyal mtshan la gtad /
NK011(da)001:10729: des ngam 'bre sa le shes rab dbang phyug la gtad /
NK011(da)001:10730: des lang lab byang chub rdo rje la /
NK011(da)001:10731: des sna nam shes rab tshul khrims la /
NK011(da)001:10732: des rgya ston sangs rgyas la /
NK011(da)001:10733: des jo bo nyi ma la gtad do //
NK011(da)001:10734: rtsa dum gyi drag sngags thog dang 'dra ba dgra bo'i srog la dbab pa'i drag sngags so //
NK011(da)001:10735: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+r+auna bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10740: m+aa ra sa ni pra mar ta ni ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10741: khro bo 'dus pa'i drag sngags so //
NK011(da)001:10742: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+r+aa na bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10743: dzahmh'u bam hoh ma ta ma ta /
NK011(da)001:10746: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK011(da)001:10747: ma ma pa sham ku ru /
NK011(da)001:10748: ma ta nya ka ra i nan /
NK011(da)001:10749: d+ha ti ma ma karma sh+r+ai krang ka re ya /
NK011(da)001:10751: m+aa ra sa ni pra ma rta ni ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10752: ma mo 'dus pa'i drag sngags yin te /
NK011(da)001:10753: nyin zhag gnyis la drug re drug re 'don no //
NK011(da)001:10755: sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra badz+ra kro ta k+ai li
NK011(da)001:10756: k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh ma ta ma ta
NK011(da)001:10759: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK011(da)001:10760: ma ma pa sham ku ru /
NK011(da)001:10761: ma ta ma nyaya&a&a&a ka ra i nan d+ha ti ma ma karma sh+r+ai krang ka re ya /
NK011(da)001:10763: m+aa ra sa na pra mar ta ni ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10764: thams cad 'dus pa'i drag sngags so //
NK011(da)001:10765: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahmh'u bam hoh ma ta ma ta /
NK011(da)001:10770: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK011(da)001:10772: m+aa ra sa ni pra mar ta ni h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10775: brnag pa las kyi 'gug byed ngan sngags gab pa la 'jug ste /
NK011(da)001:10776: dang po la lha dang phral ba'i sngags bzlas te /
NK011(da)001:10777: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:10778: ch+gee mo ha sa ya ra na h+r+ai ta na ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10780: bdag yab yum du gsal ba las sprul pa gu
NK011(da)001:10781: gul thogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa byung nas
NK011(da)001:10782: dgra bgegs kyi pho lha la sogs pa bya rog
NK011(da)001:10783: rdos bskrad pa bzhin byer bar bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:10786: dam nyams pa'i dgra bo 'di pho lha dang phrol cig /
NK011(da)001:10789: chos kyi srung ma dang phrol cig /
NK011(da)001:10790: bon gyi lha gsas dang phrol cig /
NK011(da)001:10794: yul lha gnyan po dang phrol cig /
NK011(da)001:10795: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee mo +aa be sha ya a be sha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10797: lha rnams las sprul pa grangs med byung nas dgra
NK011(da)001:10798: bgegs bye ma la mar thim pa bzhin du lid+ga
NK011(da)001:10800: dam nyams pa 'di gzugs la phob cig /
NK011(da)001:10801: phung po khams dang skye mched rnam par shes pa
NK011(da)001:10802: tshogs brgyad lid+ga la phob cig badz+ra k+ai li k+ai
NK011(da)001:10803: la ya ch+gee mo sh+ai krin a na ya h'u
NK011(da)001:10805: sprul pa tshon sna lnga'i skud pa thogs pa mang
NK011(da)001:10806: pos dgra bgegs kyi gzugs gru gu thul du bcings
NK011(da)001:10807: par bsam / dam nyams pa 'di byad du chug cig /
NK011(da)001:10808: lus gru gu thul du chings shig /
NK011(da)001:10809: tshon sna lngas byad du chug cig /
NK011(da)001:10810: lus 'gyur mi shes par gyis shig /
NK011(da)001:10811: lnga phung yan lag chings shig /
NK011(da)001:10812: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee mo dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la ba ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10814: gzas pa po des las snga phyi ci byas pa 'gyod nas thol thol smra bar bsam /
NK011(da)001:10815: dam nyams pa 'di smrar chug cig /
NK011(da)001:10820: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee mo ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10821: ting nge 'dzin ni dgra bgegs kyi gzugs phung tshogs
NK011(da)001:10822: pa brdung legs pa bzhin nal nal gyur par bsam
NK011(da)001:10823: / dam nyams pa'i dgra bo 'di'i lus ngag yid gsum thal brdul du lhogs shig /
NK011(da)001:10824: phung po khams dang skye mched thal ba rdul du lhogs shig /
NK011(da)001:10826: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ch+gee mo bi da ya bi da ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:10828: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyis dgra bo de'i sha la gtod nas za bar bsam /
NK011(da)001:10829: dam nyams pa'i dgra bo 'di'i sha la rol khrag la rol /
NK011(da)001:10830: phung po khams dang skye mched la rol /
NK011(da)001:10831: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad la rol /
NK011(da)001:10832: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi zhal du bstab pas kha khol yang ma lus par bzhes shig /
NK011(da)001:10835: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:10836: phur pa rtsa dum gyi man ngag so so na kha tshang zhing mang na yang /
NK011(da)001:10837: man ngag yang dag pa 'di yin no //
NK011(da)001:10838: de la drag sngags las kyi rtags 'byin gyi ngan
NK011(da)001:10839: sngags kyi 'khor lo 'di med par gzhan ma kun
NK011(da)001:10840: tshi chad do // 'di sgrub pa'i rdzas ni pho mo'i thod pa nag po la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10841: mis ma tshor bar rang gi sngas 'og tu bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10842: gsang sngags shin tu gsang bas 'grub bo //
NK011(da)001:10843: dgra bo phung bar byed pa'i phung sgrub 'di'i dus su sngags kyi 'khor lo 'di ltar bskor ro //
NK011(da)001:10844: sngags kyi 'grel pa sbas pa mtshor ro //
NK011(da)001:10845: sngags kyi them yig 'di med par phur pa'i sngags bzla ba kun yid 'byung tshi chad do //
NK011(da)001:10846: 'di bzla tsa na thod pa'i nang du lid+ga bcug la 'khor lo bskyon la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10849: gsang ba ltar bskor bas the tshom med do //
NK011(da)001:10850: drag sngags las kyi rtags 'byin gsang ba'i sgrub thabs dgra bo phung par byed pa'i phung sgrub 'di /
NK011(da)001:10851: mkhar chen mtsho rgyal ngas ni gsum po las bstan re dkon mchog dpang /
NK011(da)001:10852: de skad gsungs nas mo la gtad do //
NK011(da)001:10853: las kyi rtags 'byin gyi them yig /
NK011(da)001:10854: yig 'bru brgyad pas mgo mnan no //
NK011(da)001:10855: yig 'bru bdun pas dam can rnam gsum gnad la dbab bo //
NK011(da)001:10856: 'di pho mo dkrug pa'i rgyud las btus pa yin /
NK011(da)001:10857: yig 'bru dgu pas pho rgyud thams cad gnad la dbab /
NK011(da)001:10858: yig 'bru bcu pas dam can rnam gsum gnad la dbab /
NK011(da)001:10859: yig 'bru bcu gcig pas dam can rnams las la rbad do //
NK011(da)001:10862: bshan pa lag ring mon mo nag mo'i tshogs /
NK011(da)001:10863: der ma zad lha ma srin sde brgyad gnad la dbab pa'i yig 'bru bcu gcig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10867: badz+ra ni rdo rje gzhon nu'o //
NK011(da)001:10868: k+ai ni dbang phyug khro bo'o //
NK011(da)001:10870: k+ai ni mche gshog can no //
NK011(da)001:10872: yang sprul sum sprul mgyogs pa mgyogs ma'i tshogs la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10873: k+ai ni yab yum gyi sku'i chas bdun dang /
NK011(da)001:10874: ye shes sems dpa' rta mgrin dang /
NK011(da)001:10875: khro chen kun gsal ba la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10876: la ni dam can mtha' dag las la gzhug pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10877: ya zhes pa sras mchog k+ai la ya la bya /
NK011(da)001:10878: gzas pa po la ma thebs kyi bar du mi gtong bas ya zhes bya la /
NK011(da)001:10879: der ma zad dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum ka dang /
NK011(da)001:10880: dam nyams la rtags thon gyi bar du rtags thon par byed pas ya zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10882: mgo mnon gyi yig 'bru brgyad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10883: on ni shwa na ma la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10884: zangs kyi wa mo la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10885: ma tri ni bdag nyid ma la bya ste /
NK011(da)001:10886: der ma zad ma mor gyur pa tsam la bya /
NK011(da)001:10887: dgug pa'i yig 'bru bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10888: ma ho byi to ni dam can bswe mo la bya ste /
NK011(da)001:10889: ma mo dmar mo'i tshogs sha stag la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10890: der ma zad rgyal mo dang /
NK011(da)001:10893: de'i ming po bzhi la yang bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10894: ra sho ra sha tsit+ta ni srog bdag dang gnam the'u dang /
NK011(da)001:10895: bdud nag po bkrag med dang /
NK011(da)001:10898: dgra lha dang kun gyi las gyis shig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10899: sod ni de rnams kyis dam nyams dgra bo la m+aa ra ya phung bar gyis shig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10901: mu le ra ga sha tsit+ta rbad ni bswe'i skyes bu gdug pa can /
NK011(da)001:10903: mon pa nag po srog zan /
NK011(da)001:10905: 'dzin ging bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10906: der yang ma zad srin pa pho rgyud thams cad la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10907: der ma zad pho thams cad kyi snying po 'dir dril bas yig 'bru bdun pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10908: snying srog ni srog bdag las kyi ging bzhi la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10909: der ma zad pho dang ma mo dang pho mo thams cad dril ba'i yig 'bru gnyis pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10910: kha rag rbad ni pho rgyud mo rgyud thams cad
NK011(da)001:10911: kyi dgra bo'i srog la sbar sha thob cig pa
NK011(da)001:10912: yang yin / srog rtsa chod cig pa yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10913: snying rtsa phyungs shig pa yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10914: las kyi ging gi tshogs kyis la 'ur srog la hur thum gyis shig pa'i yig 'bru gsum pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10915: ka tang ka te ni sho na mu kha'i srog gi snying po drangs te /
NK011(da)001:10918: ye shes kyi spyang mo brgyad /
NK011(da)001:10919: bstan skyong gi tshogs tsam 'bod pa'i snying po yang dag pa'i yig 'bru bzhi pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10920: dza ye bi dza ye ni bswe mo bzhi'i srog snying yang dag pa ste /
NK011(da)001:10921: der ma zad ma mo dmar mor gyur pa tsam la bya ba'i yig 'bru lnga pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10922: a pa ra tsi ta ni e ka dz+aa ti'i srog sngags yang dag pa ste /
NK011(da)001:10923: ma mo nag mo thams cad 'bod pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10924: der ma zad brtan ma'i tshogs kyi yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10925: ma mo bdun gyi yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10927: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10928: mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10929: mched bzhi mu kha le'i yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10931: rje mo bcu bzhi'i yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10932: sman mo'i tshogs kyi yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10933: re ma ti mched bzhi'i yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10935: phung byed ma bzhi'i yang yin /
NK011(da)001:10936: der ma zad ma mor gyur pa tsam gyi'ang yin pas yig 'bru lnga pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10937: ma mor gyur pa thams cad gnad la dbab pa'i yig 'bru bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10938: d+ha ti ni shwa na ma la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10939: ma ma ni nag mo'i tshogs rnams la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10940: kar+m+aa ni ging bco brgyad la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10941: bswe'i skyes bu la yang bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10942: sh+ai krang ni mo'i tshogs la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10943: ka ra ye ni dam can ma mo'i rgyud //
NK011(da)001:10944: pho rgyud mtha' dag rbad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10946: ra ni ma mo nag mo'o //
NK011(da)001:10947: sa ni sa bdag gi rgyal mo bzhi la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10948: pra mar ta ni ye h'u phata ni lha srin
NK011(da)001:10949: sde brgyad las la rbad pa'i yig 'bru bdun pa'o
NK011(da)001:10950: // sngags kyi mtha' sdud kyi yig 'bru gcig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10951: de ltar tshang bas a ti zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10952: las kyi rtags 'byin man ngag srog gi spu gri /
NK011(da)001:10953: phung bar byed pa'i phung sgrub gnas dang khyim gang byed kyang rang gi sngas 'og tu bya'o //
NK011(da)001:10954: slob dpon lang lab kyis thugs sras sna nam tshul shes /
NK011(da)001:10955: de la rgya ston sangs rgyas kyis gser srang bco lnga phul nas zhus pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:10956: de nas rgya ston grongs khar kha chems su bris
NK011(da)001:10957: nas jo sras nyi ma la dbugs dang 'grogs nas
NK011(da)001:10958: gtad do // de la khyung pos zhus /
NK011(da)001:10959: de la me nyag dbang phyug g.yung drung gis zhus nas thugs dam du bcangs so //
NK011(da)001:10960: bskal pa 'khrugs kyang khar dbyung min //
NK011(da)001:10961: srid pa zhu yang sems dang 'grogs la bya //
NK011(da)001:10962: snying gi dkyil du bcang bar bya //
NK011(da)001:10964: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i man ngag so so nas
NK011(da)001:10965: zab cing mang na yang man ngag yang dag pa
NK011(da)001:10966: 'di yin no // rdo rje gzhon nu rtsa dum gyi skor /
NK011(da)001:10967: lta spyod log pa'i dgra bo'i srog la dbab pa'i
NK011(da)001:10968: sgrub thabs 'di la drag sngags kyi 'khor lo bzhi
NK011(da)001:10969: la rtsa sngags ye shes lha'i bsnyen pa sngags kyi
NK011(da)001:10971: ngan sngags gab pa srog gi thig pa sngags kyi 'khor lo bstan pa dang /
NK011(da)001:10972: drag sngags yang thig ge 'khor lo bstan pa dang /
NK011(da)001:10973: drag sngags las kyi rtags 'byin srog gi bshan pa'i drag sngags bstan pa'o //
NK011(da)001:10974: drag sngags 'dus pa bzhi bstan pa la /
NK011(da)001:10975: khro bo 'dus pa'i drag sngags bstan pa dang gcig /
NK011(da)001:10976: ma mo 'dus pa'i drag sngags dang gnyis /
NK011(da)001:10977: ngan sngags 'dus pa'i gnod pa'i drag sngags dang gsum /
NK011(da)001:10978: thams cad 'dus pa'i drag sngags hril gyis dril ba'i drag sngags bstan pa dang bzhi'o //
NK011(da)001:10979: da ni sngags la 'jug pa'i man ngag la /
NK011(da)001:10980: drag sngags kyi them yig sngags kyi bgrang thabs bstan pa ni /
NK011(da)001:10982: sgrub pa lo dang zla ba'i zhag grangs su byed kyang /
NK011(da)001:10983: zhag grangs sum cha yan chad lha 'dzab la 'jug ste /
NK011(da)001:10984: gtso bo'i sngags ni k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:10985: nyin lnga stong mtshan lnga stong dbul /
NK011(da)001:10986: sngags brgya mtshams su sngags kyi mchod pa lan gsum bya /
NK011(da)001:10987: stong mtshams su stong tshig gi mchod pa sngags kyis bya /
NK011(da)001:10989: dus la bab drug gi bskul bya /
NK011(da)001:10990: gung gnyis dro gnyis la phur pa dkyus bsrang la sman mchod rgyas par bya /
NK011(da)001:10991: phur pa gdab cing 'dul sbyong bya /
NK011(da)001:10992: sngags kyang gtso bo la stong stong gis 'bul lo //
NK011(da)001:10996: sku gsung thugs la brgya brgyas 'bul lo //
NK011(da)001:10998: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams zhes pas bya /
NK011(da)001:11000: de'i rjes la sku la bstod pa ni /
NK011(da)001:11003: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i 'od zer 'phro 'du'i klong dkyil nas zhes pas bstod /
NK011(da)001:11006: h'u bzhi tshogs la rgyan zhes pas bstod /
NK011(da)001:11008: he ru ka las kyi rgyal po 'di bzhengs su
NK011(da)001:11009: gsol ba'i dus na 'jig rten gyi khams ni gzhal
NK011(da)001:11010: yas khang gi rang bzhin du gyur pa yin /
NK011(da)001:11013: 'og klu'i srid pa dang gsum po de rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku'i rang bzhin du gyur tsa na /
NK011(da)001:11014: gzugs su gyur pa thams cad sku'i rang bzhin du mer mer shig shig par bsgom /
NK011(da)001:11015: sngags bzlas tsa na thams cad k+ai la ya'i gsung du di ri ri bzlas par bsgom /
NK011(da)001:11016: ri rab 'dzam bu gling sogs gling bzhi dang nyi
NK011(da)001:11017: zla dang gza' skar yang phur bu'i rgyan dang gzi
NK011(da)001:11019: 'jig rten khams kyi dregs pa can phyogs skyong bcu gdan du bting /
NK011(da)001:11020: der ma zad skur bsgoms pas stong gsum la thogs pa med par gu gul bdug pa /
NK011(da)001:11021: der ma zad sprul pas stong gsum dus gcig tu
NK011(da)001:11022: khengs nas 'dug pa grog tshang slog ba'am 'bu tshang
NK011(da)001:11023: bshig pa bzhin du gnas pa'i dus na /
NK011(da)001:11026: 'bros pa'i gnas ga na yod med do //
NK011(da)001:11027: lha 'dzab kyi dgongs pa de ltar bzhag go //
NK011(da)001:11028: de yan chad lha bsnyen gyi man ngag bstan pa lags so //
NK011(da)001:11029: da ni 'di nas mar dgra 'dzab la 'jug ste /
NK011(da)001:11030: da ni ngan sngags gab pa'i sngags drug la 'jug ste /
NK011(da)001:11031: sngags drug khong khrar btang ba'i man ngag dang gcig /
NK011(da)001:11032: sngags drug ngan sngags su btang ba'i man ngag dang gnyis /
NK011(da)001:11033: sngags drug kun gyi mjug la gdags pa dang gsum las /
NK011(da)001:11034: sngags drug khong khrar btang ba ni /
NK011(da)001:11035: 'jug pa'i skabs dang sbyar la khong khrar btang /
NK011(da)001:11036: sngags drug ngan sngags su btang ba ni /
