NK011(da)001:11037: sngags drug so so'i rdzas dang gcig /
NK011(da)001:11038: sngags drug so so'i dgongs pa dang gnyis /
NK011(da)001:11039: sngags drug so so'i smon lam dang bcas pa drangs so //
NK011(da)001:11040: da ni drag sngags srog gi yang thig la 'jug ste /
NK011(da)001:11041: khro bo 'dus pa'i drag sngags la nyin stong mtshan stong dbul /
NK011(da)001:11042: ma mo 'dus pa'i drag sngags la nyin sum stong mtshan sum stong dbul /
NK011(da)001:11044: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing gis 'dzab bstod bya /
NK011(da)001:11045: stong tshig gi mchod pa dang /
NK011(da)001:11047: dus rtag tu 'bod rbad bsad gsum gyi drag sngags hril gyis dril ba bzlas pa bya /
NK011(da)001:11048: drag sngags brgya mtshams su sngags kyi mchod pa ma mo rnams la lan gsum bya /
NK011(da)001:11049: stong mtshams su stong tshig gi mchod pa ma mo rnams la rgyas par bya /
NK011(da)001:11050: thugs dam gnad nas bskul zhing khrag gi sbreng mchod bya /
NK011(da)001:11051: dgra 'dzab la 'jug tsa na 'phro 'du'i dgongs pa 'di ltar bya /
NK011(da)001:11052: bdag nyid las kyi lhar bsgoms pa'i thugs kar nyi
NK011(da)001:11053: ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du yi ge h'u mthing
NK011(da)001:11054: nag kyang rung / bzlas par bya ba'i yi ge las 'byung yang rung ste /
NK011(da)001:11055: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya'i sngags brjod pas /
NK011(da)001:11056: gong du bstan pa'i phur pa'i khro bo ci 'dra ba gcig byung ste /
NK011(da)001:11057: dkyil 'khor gsum dang bde gshegs thugs dam bskang /
NK011(da)001:11058: sems can gyi don byas nas gzas pa po'i spyi
NK011(da)001:11059: gtsug tu thim nas rkang pa'i mthil du phyung nas
NK011(da)001:11060: / slar spyi gtsug tu phyung nas lus kyi bag chags bsgral /
NK011(da)001:11061: de nas lce steng nas lkog ma'i 'og tu phyungs te ngag ngan pa'i bag chags bsgral /
NK011(da)001:11062: de nas snying gar thim nas srog 'khor steng du
NK011(da)001:11063: dril te snying gar phyungs te sems kyi bag chags
NK011(da)001:11064: ngan pa bsgral nas kho'i phung po lhag ma ma
NK011(da)001:11065: lus par ril li li 'ongs nas lid+gara bstim mo
NK011(da)001:11066: // de yang mtsho chen po'i rlabs bzhin gcig phyir na phar gcig rgyun mi chad par bsgom mo //
NK011(da)001:11067: dgra 'dzab kyi dgongs pa de ltar bzhag go //
NK011(da)001:11069: sna la a be sha ya brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas la dgug pa'i las bya /
NK011(da)001:11071: ha sa ya ra na h+r+ai da na'i sngags brgya rtsa brgya bzlas la dbye ba'i las bya /
NK011(da)001:11072: de nas bal tshon sna lnga'i byad thag thogs la /
NK011(da)001:11073: sh+ai kring a na ya'i sngags brgya rtsa brgyad bgrang la bcing ba'i las bya /
NK011(da)001:11074: byung tshor gyi sgo dgag pa ni /
NK011(da)001:11075: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa de rtsa la zhon dbugs la rgyu /
NK011(da)001:11076: phar 'phros tshur 'phros pa de sngags 'dis 'bros dbang med par sgo bkag /
NK011(da)001:11077: ka tam ka te m+aa ra sa ni pra mar ta ni ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11078: ces brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas la sgo bkag /
NK011(da)001:11079: de nas gdab pa'i las bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11080: da ni khro bo rnams kyi drag sngags 'dus pa'i man ngag ni /
NK011(da)001:11081: khro bo 'dus pa'i drag sngags yig 'bru bzhi pa ni /
NK011(da)001:11082: pa ra bid tan zhes pa ni khro bo thams cad kyi drag sngags dril ba yin te /
NK011(da)001:11083: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs kyi rtsa ba'i sgo lnga'i dbang po lte ba la 'dus te /
NK011(da)001:11084: lte ba'i rtsa chen po chod la chags pa'i rgyu rtsad nas chod cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11085: su ru su ru ni khra thabs mche ba can bcu'i drag sngags te /
NK011(da)001:11086: yid la thun phob la yid 'khrug tu chug cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11087: mu ru mu ru ni khra thabs gshog pa can bcu'i drag sngags mi zad pa yin te /
NK011(da)001:11088: shes pa rmugs su chug cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11089: de tsho ni khro bo 'dus pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11090: ma mo 'dus pa'i ngan sngags ni /
NK011(da)001:11091: ma mo thams cad kyi ngan sngags yang dag pa
NK011(da)001:11092: hril gyis dril ba'i yig 'bru bzhi pa yin no
NK011(da)001:11093: // ka tang ka te ni shwa na mu kha'i drag sngags yin te gnad nas bskul pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11094: dza ye bi dza ye ni bswe mo bzhi'i drag
NK011(da)001:11095: sngags mi bzad pa yin te gnad nas bskul ba'o
NK011(da)001:11096: // a tsi te a pa ra tsi ta ni
NK011(da)001:11097: bdag nyid chen po'i drag sngags yin te gnad nas
NK011(da)001:11098: // bskul ba'o // ma ma p+aa sham gyi sngags
NK011(da)001:11099: tsho la ni srung ma rnam pa gsum du bas
NK011(da)001:11100: // bskul ba'o // te / ma mo thams cad
NK011(da)001:11101: kyi drag sngags yod pas ma mo 'dus pa zhes
NK011(da)001:11102: // bskul ba'o // te / bya'o // ma bdun gyi dmod mo zhes kyang bya /
NK011(da)001:11103: ma bdun zhes pa ni ma bdun rang ni cung min no //
NK011(da)001:11104: ma mo bdun tsho bdun la bya ba yin te /
NK011(da)001:11105: shwa na mu khas sna drangs pa'i ce spyang gi tshogs tsho gcig /
NK011(da)001:11106: bdag nyid chen mos sna drangs pa'i nag mo'i tshogs tsho gcig /
NK011(da)001:11107: bswe mo bzhis sna drangs pa'i dmar mo'i tshogs tsho gcig /
NK011(da)001:11111: dbang mo tsho gcig ste bdun la ma bdun bya ba'o //
NK011(da)001:11112: ni rtsa ba'am gzhi thams cad kyi mchog mtshon pa
NK011(da)001:11113: mya ngan las 'das pa'i thugs sku lnga ye shes
NK011(da)001:11115: sh+r+ai ni rnal 'byor pa thams cad kyi ye shes kyi lhar gyur pas kyang dpal zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11116: mkha' 'gro ma dang gnod sbyin mo thams cad kyi rjer gyur pas yab dang dpal zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11117: badz+ra ni dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i chos kyi sku la gnyen po cis kyang mi shigs pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11118: ku m+aa ra ni chos kyi sku la skye shi
NK011(da)001:11119: 'pho 'gyur bsgres rgud dang rtag chad mi mnga' bas
NK011(da)001:11120: / de lta bu la rdo rje gzhon nu zhes bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11121: kro ta ni khro bo zhes 'bod pa ste khro bo thams cad 'bod pa'i snying po'o //
NK011(da)001:11122: k+ai ni khro bo bcu'i snying po /
NK011(da)001:11123: li ni khro mo bcu'i snying po /
NK011(da)001:11124: k+ai 'og ma khra thabs bcu'i snying po /
NK011(da)001:11125: li 'og ma khra thabs gshog pa can bcu'i snying po /
NK011(da)001:11126: k+ai la ya ni sprul pa dang yang sprul sum sprul gyi tshogs kyi snying po /
NK011(da)001:11127: ya zhes pa khra thabs yan chad kyi bskul ba'i snying po 'bru gcig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11129: dzahlcagasa kyu mas zungs shig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11130: h'u zhags pa mas chings shig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11131: bam lcags sgrog mas sdoms shig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11132: hohdrila bu mas sems 'khrug par gyis shig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11133: phrin las rnam bzhi'i rang bzhin yang yin /
NK011(da)001:11134: a tsi te a pa ra tsi ta ni bdag nyid chen mo'i srog sngags yang dag pa ste /
NK011(da)001:11135: dam nyams pa'i dgra bo 'di'i kun gzhi rtsad chod cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11136: dza ye bi dza ye ni bswe mo bzhi'i srog snying yang dag pa ste /
NK011(da)001:11137: dam nyams pa'i dgra bo 'di'i sems dkrugs la sems kyi dbyings phyungs shig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11138: ka tang ka te ni shwa na mu kha'i srog gi snying po nas drangs pa ste /
NK011(da)001:11139: dam nyams pa'i kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa 'di
NK011(da)001:11140: gar yang 'bros su ma gzhug par sgo khog cig
NK011(da)001:11141: / byung tshor gyi sgo khog cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11142: ma ma ni shwa na mu kha dang /
NK011(da)001:11144: dam can bswe mo bzhi dang kun 'bod pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11145: der ma zad ma bdun dang sring mo bzhi dang /
NK011(da)001:11148: phur srung thams cad 'bod pa'i sngags so //
NK011(da)001:11149: der ma zad mo thams cad 'bod pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11150: p+aa sham ni brtan ma bcu gnyis kyi srog snying drag po'i sngags so //
NK011(da)001:11151: ku ru zhes pa dbang phyug ma'i srog gi yang snying ste /
NK011(da)001:11152: dbang phyug ma'i drag sngags so //
NK011(da)001:11153: ma thams nyaya&a&a&a ni ma mo bdun dang /
NK011(da)001:11154: sring mo bzhi'i yang snying ste ma bdun sring bzhi'i drag sngags so //
NK011(da)001:11155: ka ra ni ging bco brgyad kyi srog gi yang snying ste ging gi drag sngags so //
NK011(da)001:11156: a nan ni dgra bo 'di gnon cig gzir cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11157: d+ha ti ni shwa na mu kha gnad nas bskul ba ste gnad nas bskul ba'o //
NK011(da)001:11158: ma ma karma ni bdag nyid chen mo gnad nas bskul ba'i drag sngags so //
NK011(da)001:11159: sh+ai krang ka re ni bswe mo bzhi gnad nas bskul ba'o //
NK011(da)001:11160: ya ni dam can rnams rbad pa'i snying po gcig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11162: ga ni ming dang rus su bcas pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11163: ya ni la 'ur rgyug cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11164: dgra la rtags la 'ur myur du ston cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11165: m+aa ra ni la 'ur sod cig /
NK011(da)001:11166: pra mar ta ni ye ni ma 'gor bar bdun brgyud rtsad nas chod cig bya ba yin /
NK011(da)001:11168: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya ni gtogs byed kyi snying po yin te /
NK011(da)001:11169: bag chags kyi phung po brlag par bya ba'i phyir
NK011(da)001:11170: pho nya gtun sprugs can gyis gzugs kyi phung po
NK011(da)001:11171: gtsang khol gyi bye ma bzhin du rdul du brlag
NK011(da)001:11172: par bsgom / ha sa ya ra ha na ta
NK011(da)001:11173: na h'u phata ni nye 'byed kyi snying po yin
NK011(da)001:11174: par bsgom / te / dper na pho rang sgo zhan yang rgyab brten bzang ba dang 'dra bar /
NK011(da)001:11175: sdig pa'i grogs dang bral bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK011(da)001:11177: stong grogs byed pa'i grogs dang bral bar gyis shig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11178: sh+ai krin a na ya h'u phata ni 'ching byed kyi snying po yin te /
NK011(da)001:11179: nyon mongs pa'i dbang po rang yan du mi btang
NK011(da)001:11180: ba'i phyir pho nya zhags pa can gyis yan lag
NK011(da)001:11181: chigs shig pa'o // dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la
NK011(da)001:11182: pa ya h'u phata ni smra byed kyi snying po
NK011(da)001:11183: yin te mthol bshags byed du gzhug pa'i phyir pho
NK011(da)001:11184: nya smra byed kyis smrar chug cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11185: +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya h'u phata ni 'bebs byed kyi snying po yin te /
NK011(da)001:11186: thugs rjes zin par bya ba'i phyir pho nya 'bebs
NK011(da)001:11187: byed kyis bkug nas gzugs dang ri mo la dbab
NK011(da)001:11189: bi ta ya bi ta ya h'u phata ni stob byed kyi snying po ste /
NK011(da)001:11190: bsgral ba'i phung po lhag ma ma lus par bya
NK011(da)001:11191: ba'i phyir dbang phyug khro bo rnams kyi zhal du
NK011(da)001:11192: stob cig pa'o // gsol cig rol cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11193: rtsa ba k+ai la ya dang spel la bzlas par bya /
NK011(da)001:11194: sngags kyi lde mig man ngag go //
NK011(da)001:11196: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya badz+ra shwa na mu
NK011(da)001:11197: kha sa ma ya zhung tri ma ma ma zer
NK011(da)001:11198: ba mang / mo trig nan m+aa ra ni rbad /
NK011(da)001:11200: trag rak+sha ma ma ma zer ba mang /
NK011(da)001:11201: mo dun snying la rbad ka ru na rbad /
NK011(da)001:11202: snying khrag tshal bu gtubs tsit+ta myogs rmugs /
NK011(da)001:11203: snying khrag tshal sa na se du /
NK011(da)001:11204: k+ai la ya hur thum srog la k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:11205: on ma trang mo ha byi tu /
NK011(da)001:11207: ra sho r+aa tsi tsit+ta sod /
NK011(da)001:11209: snying srog zer ba mang snying kha rag rbad /
NK011(da)001:11210: a tsi te a pa ra tsi ta /
NK011(da)001:11214: d+ha ti ma ma karma sh+ai krang ka re ya /
NK011(da)001:11215: m+aa ra se na pra mar ta na ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11216: thams cad gcig tu dril ba'o //
NK011(da)001:11219: gab pa'i sngags drug dang sbrags la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11221: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dgra bgegs m+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:11222: ha sa ya ra na h+r+ai ta na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11223: +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11224: sh+ai kring a na ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11225: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11226: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11227: bi da ya bi da ya /
NK011(da)001:11228: ra sho r+aa tsa tsit+ta sod /
NK011(da)001:11231: a tsi te a pa ra tsi ta /
NK011(da)001:11234: d+ha ti ma ma karma sh+ai krang ka re ya /
NK011(da)001:11235: m+aa ra se na pra mar ta ni h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11236: 'di ni phung sgrub thod sgrub gsang ba'i ngan sngags /
NK011(da)001:11238: dgra bo phung bar byed pa'i phung sgrub 'di la drag sngags thams cad thun brab dgos pa ste /
NK011(da)001:11239: de la drag sngags thams cad ni 'di la 'dus so //
NK011(da)001:11240: thun sngags gsang ba logs su gab pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11241: thams cad dril sngags ni gong ma de ga'o //
NK011(da)001:11242: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:11245: sna nam gyi thugs dam phur gcig ma /
NK011(da)001:11246: gzas pa po brnag pa mthar bskyal ba 'di las lhag pa med do //
NK011(da)001:11247: 'di la rtags thon pa dang gdod gdab pa'i las bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11248: nyi shu rtsa gcig gis gdab pa dang phur bu gsum gyis gdab pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11249: sngags ni gnyis te dkyus su bcug pa dang /
NK011(da)001:11251: logs su gab pa 'di med na phur pa sgrub pa rnams yi chad /
NK011(da)001:11253: mgo 'gas pa 'di ni shin tu gsang la sgrub par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11254: h'u badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:11255: rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum khro mo mche gshog yang sprul sum sprul rbad /
NK011(da)001:11256: on shwa na ma trang mo bdag nyid ma ho
NK011(da)001:11257: byi rang bswe mo ra sho r+aa tsa tsit+ta sod
NK011(da)001:11258: / srog bdag gis tsit+ta la rgyob /
NK011(da)001:11259: mu le rak+sha bswe'i skyes bu la las bcol /
NK011(da)001:11261: snying lag ring bdud bzhi btsan bzhi /
NK011(da)001:11263: ka tang shwa na ma ka te bswe mo dza
NK011(da)001:11264: ye bi dza ye a tsi te a pa ra
NK011(da)001:11265: tsi ta nag mos bsad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11266: d+ha ti ma ma ma mo mtha' dag go //
NK011(da)001:11267: karma sh+ai kram ging bco brgyad /
NK011(da)001:11268: ka ra ya bswe'i skyes bu bzhi /
NK011(da)001:11269: m+aa ra sa na lha ma srin sde brgyad las la yang bskul lo //
NK011(da)001:11270: pra ma ra ta ni h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11271: drag sngags 'di la nyin lnga stong //
NK011(da)001:11273: gzhan ma logs na zhib bo //
NK011(da)001:11275: man+dala khrag gis byug pa'i steng //
NK011(da)001:11276: thod pa khrag gis byug la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:11277: de yi nang du bsag pa'i rdzas //
NK011(da)001:11278: sha sna khrag sna 'byor tshad dang //
NK011(da)001:11280: dbyi spyang dom dred la sogs 'byor tshad btsal //
NK011(da)001:11281: de dag kun kyang ra yi thod par blug /
NK011(da)001:11282: zhag gsum bsgrubs shing thebs re dbyung //
NK011(da)001:11283: btsan nam klu yod nges par bsreg /
NK011(da)001:11284: rang gi ting nge 'dzin gang mos gsal la /
NK011(da)001:11285: sa ma ya sa ma ya tri tog ma ma /
NK011(da)001:11286: sag sag tshil ma ma 'ur 'ur sag /
NK011(da)001:11290: ma ma tig tig btsan ma sha la rag rag btsan ma ma /
NK011(da)001:11291: yag du dgra la phob phob /
NK011(da)001:11292: ra tsi ra tsi chum chum b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:11293: de skad ces ni bsreg pa dang //
NK011(da)001:11294: thal ba dang ni sol ba dang //
NK011(da)001:11295: khrag dang bsres te khyer nas kyang //
NK011(da)001:11296: gang la 'os par gtor bar bya //
NK011(da)001:11297: gnyan po rgyu phyogs shes byas la //
NK011(da)001:11298: de dang bsgril la 'phang gtor bya //
NK011(da)001:11299: thog dang ser ba mod la 'ong //
NK011(da)001:11300: thog ser la ni khud bur ro //
NK011(da)001:11301: bzlas pa rgyun du bya ba gces //
NK011(da)001:11302: rdzas la rgyun du bya ba'o //
NK011(da)001:11306: phur pa thod sgrub gsang ba'i ngan sngags yang dag pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11309: slob dpon chen po pad+mas mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal
NK011(da)001:11310: la zhal chems kyi yi ge dang bcas nas gtad
NK011(da)001:11311: / des la byid ye shes brtsegs la /
NK011(da)001:11312: des mi nub rgyal ba'i snying po la /
NK011(da)001:11313: des lo dpal gyi blo gros la /
NK011(da)001:11314: des lce yon tan bzang po la /
NK011(da)001:11315: des ngam 'bre klu'i rgyal mtshan la /
NK011(da)001:11317: des lang lab byang chub rdo rje la /
NK011(da)001:11318: slob dpon lang lab na so gzhon nu la pha grongs pas /
NK011(da)001:11319: pha spun bcu gsum po dgrar langs nas /
NK011(da)001:11320: ma shi ba'i gson rab khong gis khyer nas /
NK011(da)001:11321: ma smad la khang pa mig gcig /
NK011(da)001:11322: zhing lhu gcig las ma ster ba la ngam 'bres thugs rjes gzigs nas /
NK011(da)001:11324: ngas khyod la gab sbas ma byas par bstan pa yin gyis /
NK011(da)001:11325: nga'i snying 'di phyung yang dmar po ldad ldad bu
NK011(da)001:11326: las med pas 'di las lhag pa bya ba ye
NK011(da)001:11327: rang med kyi 'di la the tshom ma za bar
NK011(da)001:11330: a tsa ra sa le'i mthu yin no gyis la dbyung cig byas la gtad do //
NK011(da)001:11331: slob dpon lang lab kyi thugs kyi bu bzhi las
NK011(da)001:11332: sna nam gyi thugs zin nas lang lab kyi phur
NK011(da)001:11334: des bye ma gtsang khar rgya ston sangs rgyas la /
NK011(da)001:11335: lung dang man ngag gi chos 'grel pa dang phra
NK011(da)001:11336: mo ru phul nas rgya ston la lo sum cu
NK011(da)001:11338: des gur zhogs khams lung du dbon po jo sras nyi ma la /
NK011(da)001:11339: u khu chos 'di spyad dbang med pas nga'i thugs
NK011(da)001:11340: kyi man ngag 'di ngas ni sngon chad su la
NK011(da)001:11342: 'di nga min te gter du sbas /
NK011(da)001:11343: de min te me la bsreg pa kho na yin pa las /
NK011(da)001:11344: ngas ma phod kyi nga ni dur nas lta'o zhes so //
NK011(da)001:11345: nga la rnam smin gsog mi gsog khyod la rag lus so //
NK011(da)001:11346: chos 'di chud gzon mi gzon khyod shes so //
NK011(da)001:11347: zhes gsungs nas dbon po la gtad do //
NK011(da)001:11348: jo sras nyi ma la khyung pos zhus /
NK011(da)001:11349: de la mi nyag sgom chen gyis zhus /
NK011(da)001:11350: mi nyag sgom chen gyi nyid ro phug tu po ti phyag tu bzhes te /
NK011(da)001:11351: dgung lo brgyad cu rtsa gnyis bzhes /
NK011(da)001:11352: dkon mchog gsum po dpang du btsugs nas /
NK011(da)001:11353: ngas chos 'di la sems phyogs dang /
NK011(da)001:11359: e ka dz+aa ti byar rnying ma dang /
NK011(da)001:11360: e ka dz+aa ti sbyar bo can gyi man ngag dang /
NK011(da)001:11364: zla gam gsum zhabs nas btegs nas zhus pa yin pas /
NK011(da)001:11365: ngas 'di la bri bcad byas re dkon mchog gsum
NK011(da)001:11366: gyis mgo khos gsungs nas lo ston la gnang nas
NK011(da)001:11368: rgya rim pa gsum gyis btab nas gtad do //
NK011(da)001:11371: drag sngags dkyus su bcug pa logs su gab bo //
NK011(da)001:11372: logs su gab pa 'di med na phur pa mkhan po rnams yang yi chad /
NK011(da)001:11374: mgo 'gas pas 'di shin tu gsang la bsgrub par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11375: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:11376: mo ha g+ha ya m+aa ra ya sa ma ya /
NK011(da)001:11377: dzahmh'u bam hoh tsit+ta srog la bam trak+mo rak+mo /
NK011(da)001:11378: thib thib tseg tseg 'ur 'ur sod sod srog la yam yam /
NK011(da)001:11383: m+aa ra ya dzah d+ha ti ma ma karma /
NK011(da)001:11385: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK011(da)001:11386: tsa tri sum tri rag sha n+aa ga ra tri
NK011(da)001:11387: ma ra sa ni pra ma ra ta ni h'u
NK011(da)001:11388: phata / drag sngags kyi 'phyong gzhan du gab pa 'di shin tu gsang la bsgrub par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11389: bka'i sgye'u chung gi drag sngags so //
NK011(da)001:11392: slob dpon pad+ma thod phreng gis phyi rabs don du yang le shod du mdzad nas /
NK011(da)001:11393: rnal 'byor ba phur pa bsgrub nas yun ring du /
NK011(da)001:11394: mthu med cing dgra la 'phar du mi 'dod cing 'tsheg tu mi 'dod na /
NK011(da)001:11396: spyir lha srin sde brgyad 'khrugs pas nyen che //
NK011(da)001:11397: bzlas pa tshad du ma phyin par mi btub //
NK011(da)001:11399: de'i nang nas kyang dam can rnam pa gsum shwa na /
NK011(da)001:11402: ming po ging dang bcas pa bswe'i skyes bu srog bdag dang btsan du bcas pa /
NK011(da)001:11403: rnams gnad la dbab dgos so //
NK011(da)001:11404: po ti rgyud kyi pho mo dkrug pa'i rgyud nas btus /
NK011(da)001:11405: bcud phyung rdo rje thod phreng ngas //
NK011(da)001:11406: ma mo shi sa 'khor lo phar bskor la bzlas /
NK011(da)001:11407: bstan pa lcur gyis logs su phyungs byas nas //
NK011(da)001:11408: phyi rabs rnal 'byor don du phur pa sgrub pa la //
NK011(da)001:11409: rtags phur pa la dang drod tshad byin 'gyangs nas /
NK011(da)001:11414: de min par ni sgrub pho mo dkrug pa nyen che'o //
NK011(da)001:11415: tshad du ma bskyal ba la mi bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11417: ci ste 'jig rten lha 'dre dkrug pa yi //
NK011(da)001:11418: de phyir rang la nyes gyong 'ong //
NK011(da)001:11419: de bas 'di ni sgrub pa thon nas brtsam //
NK011(da)001:11420: thod phreng yi dam lha dpang rab gsol nas //
NK011(da)001:11421: rang dang phyi rabs rnal 'byor don du brtsams //
NK011(da)001:11422: rang dang 'dra ba'i bu la gtad pa las //
NK011(da)001:11423: phrag dog kha 'jam che la mtho gnon byed //
NK011(da)001:11424: slob dpon dmod la rang che 'byin //
NK011(da)001:11425: ngo so tshul 'chos kha gsag mkhan //
NK011(da)001:11426: de ltar bu la gtad par ma gsungs so //
NK011(da)001:11427: ci ste gtad pas rang la nyes pa 'ong //
NK011(da)001:11428: rang dang pha rol gnyis ka la //
NK011(da)001:11429: dam tshig med par kun gyis mthong //
NK011(da)001:11431: de bas 'jig rten srog la gtod //
NK011(da)001:11432: bswe mo srog la gtod nas gsod du 'ong /
NK011(da)001:11433: de bas bstan par ma gsungs so //
NK011(da)001:11434: gal te nam zhig 'chi srid na //
NK011(da)001:11435: snod dang ldan pa'i bu mchog la //
NK011(da)001:11436: lag tu rdo rje gtad la mgo ru gtor ma bzhag /
NK011(da)001:11437: de ltar byas la gtad la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:11438: snying la dam tshig phog la gtad la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:11439: phyi rabs kyi rnal 'byor pa phur pa'i sgrub pa yun ring du byas nas /
NK011(da)001:11440: mthu med dgra la rtags ma thon na snying rje ba gcig yin pas /
NK011(da)001:11441: de'i don du thod phreng ngas brtsams /
NK011(da)001:11442: ma mo shi sa bstan pa yang /
NK011(da)001:11443: phyi ltar bstan phyi ltar kho rang la bsad pa yin /
NK011(da)001:11447: phyi ltar gnad la dbab pa 'dis bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11448: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:11449: dang po kho rang gis slob dpon gyi spyan sngar srog snying phul ba yin pas sngags 'adi'o //
NK011(da)001:11450: lha srin sde brgyad gnad la dbab /
NK011(da)001:11451: yag mo rag mo ka la r+au pa /
NK011(da)001:11453: 'di bzlas pa tsam gyis kho rang yo ga 'dzin
NK011(da)001:11454: gyi lha srin kun snying skyur skyur song bar bsam
NK011(da)001:11455: / dred nas 'dar yed yed 'dug pa la phur pa bstan par bya /
NK011(da)001:11456: sam tri rag sha thib thib /
NK011(da)001:11460: tsa tri su tri snying kha rag thib thib rgyal
NK011(da)001:11461: po gnad la dbab pa'o srog bdag pe dkar sogs
NK011(da)001:11462: gnad la dbab / tsit+ta srog gtung gtung /
NK011(da)001:11464: myogs myogs sod sod se na gtubs gtubs /
NK011(da)001:11466: nang bdag dpal chen du gsal bas gzir ro //
NK011(da)001:11467: ltar gnad la dbab pa ni /
NK011(da)001:11468: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:11470: shwa na'i tshogs nag mo'i tshogs bswe mo'i tshogs /
NK011(da)001:11471: ka la ru pa snying rtsa la yam yam /
NK011(da)001:11472: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te sod sod srog la yam yam /
NK011(da)001:11473: 'di bzlas pa tsam gyis ltad mo chen mo tshogs
NK011(da)001:11474: pa bzhin du kun phung phung rib rib 'dus par
NK011(da)001:11476: shwa na ma gnad la 'bebs nas 'dar phril phril song bar bsam mo //
NK011(da)001:11479: ka tang ka te myogs myogs /
NK011(da)001:11482: ma mo gnad la dbab pas dgra bo gsod pa'i las bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11483: sum tri rag sha thib thib /
NK011(da)001:11485: tsig tsig phur pa gnas su me stag ltar /
NK011(da)001:11487: tsi tra sa ma tri snying srog bdag gnad la phab /
NK011(da)001:11488: pho rgyud thams cad kyi dgra bo bsad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11490: d+ha ti ma ma karma sh+ai krang ka re ye /
NK011(da)001:11491: m+aa ra sa na pra ma rta na ye lha srin gyi sngags 'ub kyis dril ba'o //
NK011(da)001:11493: ces pas nang ltar gnad la dbab pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11494: gsang ba ltar gnad la dbab pa ni /
NK011(da)001:11495: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:11496: bdag dpal chen du gsal ba'i lag g.yas kyi phur
NK011(da)001:11497: pa gzas po la btab pas khrag rgyang rgyang song
NK011(da)001:11498: bar bsam / de ltar bzlas pas /
NK011(da)001:11499: 'dar phri li li gum gum mchi ma shar shar gnag sting sting /
NK011(da)001:11500: gzas pa po rang dbang med par gum gum khrid la shog /
NK011(da)001:11501: btsan pos bsgo ba bzhin khyer nas 'ong bar bsam /
NK011(da)001:11502: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te /
NK011(da)001:11504: ka la ru pa snying rtsa la yam yam /
NK011(da)001:11509: myogs myogs sod sod jo bos bran gcun pa bzhin
NK011(da)001:11510: gcun pas ma srin rnams nag 'drad 'drad rgyang rgyang
NK011(da)001:11511: song bar bsam la bzlas pa bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11512: tsit+ta sam tri ser gtubs gtubs snying phril phril srog la chum chum /
NK011(da)001:11513: ka tang ka te snying rtsa la yam yam /
NK011(da)001:11514: tsi tra sa ma tri snying kha rag dun tri
NK011(da)001:11515: ma mo rang nang dkrug pa'i sngags kyang yin no
NK011(da)001:11516: // nan shig shig ma ma pa sham ku ru /
NK011(da)001:11517: d+ha ti ma ma ka ra i nan /
NK011(da)001:11518: sh+ai krang ma tha nyaya&a&a&a ka re ya /
NK011(da)001:11519: ma ra sa na pra marta ni mtha' btul mtha' btul 'khor ba'i bdun brgyud rtsad nas bcad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11521: ces pas gsang ba ltar gnad la dbab pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11523: zhes phyi ltar gnad la dbab bas dam can sde
NK011(da)001:11524: gsum lha srin sde brgyad po rnams kyis dang po
NK011(da)001:11525: slob dpon gyi spyan sngar khas blangs /
NK011(da)001:11526: rang gi snying po kho rang gis phul ba yin pas /
NK011(da)001:11527: kun gyi snying lcur lcur song bar bsam la bzlas pa bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11528: nang ltar bzlas pas dam can ma mo kun gyi
NK011(da)001:11529: kha nas khrag rgyang rgyang song bar bsam la bzlas
NK011(da)001:11530: pa bya'o // gsang ba ltar na lhag par yang /
NK011(da)001:11531: dam can ma gsum lus myags myags seng seng shwa na ma ser ba bab pa bzhin /
NK011(da)001:11532: nag 'drad 'drad kho rang la phar bskor la bzlas pa bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11533: de ltar byas pas grub par the tshom med do //
NK011(da)001:11534: dang po kho rang gis dmod btsugs pa yin pas the tshom med do //
NK011(da)001:11536: pad+ma thod phreng gi yang dag mar me dgu pa bsgrub pa'i dus su /
NK011(da)001:11537: bid+h+yot+ta ma la 'bul sde'i nang nas rdo rje gzhon
NK011(da)001:11538: nu'i skor dang phun sum tshogs pa'i cha rkyen rgyud
NK011(da)001:11539: phyi ma khong la phul bas /
NK011(da)001:11541: de'i nang nas kyang phur pa'i rgyud ro langs bshad pa'i rgyud dang /
NK011(da)001:11542: srog gi spu gri'i rgyud do //
NK011(da)001:11543: de'i nang nas kyang pho mo dkrug par bya ba'i nang nas btus nas /
NK011(da)001:11544: slar yang rdo rje gdan gyi 'og tu rgya gar chos kyi rgyal pos rgyas btab nas sbas so //
NK011(da)001:11547: bzhi snying gcig tu dril ba dang /
NK011(da)001:11548: pho mo rabs chad nag po'i thod pa la sgrub pa kun btus nas mdzad pa las /
NK011(da)001:11549: bod yul du byon nas mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal
NK011(da)001:11550: gyis gzungs ma mdzad pas slob dpon gyi thugs zin
NK011(da)001:11552: de nas gcig nas gnyis su brgyud pa'i mtha' lang lab byang chub rdo rje'o //
NK011(da)001:11553: rgyud sde kun da lta bod yul dbus na mi bdog skad do /
NK011(da)001:11555: slob dpon pad+ma thod phreng gis bid+yot+ta ma la 'bum
NK011(da)001:11556: sde'i nas nas spyir lha srin sde brgyad de'i nang
NK011(da)001:11557: nas dam can rnam pa gsum /
NK011(da)001:11558: bswe'i skyes bu gdug pa can dang /
NK011(da)001:11559: ma mo mtha' dag gi srog gi snying po gcig tu dril nas phyungs pa 'di /
NK011(da)001:11560: bod yul dbus su mchims dang /
NK011(da)001:11562: sna nam gsum la ni spyir phur pa mtha' dag bshad nas spyir rgyal mkhas /
NK011(da)001:11563: de'i dus su mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal la /
NK011(da)001:11564: khyod bud med kyi blo yang yin /
NK011(da)001:11565: col yang chung bas ngan sngags kyi yi ge 'di gtad do gsungs nas gnang ngo //
NK011(da)001:11566: de'i las ni dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum gyis don gyi khog phub /
NK011(da)001:11567: ngan sngags srog gi spu gri 'dis las kyi mtha' btul /
NK011(da)001:11568: de'i rdzas ni lcags phur dang rdzas rnams tshogs par bsags /
NK011(da)001:11569: 'gro nyal 'dug sdod du bsnyen pa de la dbul lo //
NK011(da)001:11570: rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum /
NK011(da)001:11572: k+ai li sprul pa khra thabs /
NK011(da)001:11585: ka la r+au pa snying rtsa la yam yam /
NK011(da)001:11590: sam tri rag thib thib tsa tri sa ma tri /
NK011(da)001:11591: snying kha rag dun tri nan shig shig se na gtub gtub /
NK011(da)001:11592: thum ri li li tseg tseg 'ur 'ur shig shig
NK011(da)001:11593: gul gul myags myags sod sod d+ha ti ma ma
NK011(da)001:11594: karma sh+ai krang ka re ya /
NK011(da)001:11595: m+aa ra sa ni pra marta ni ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11596: 'di med par phur pa bsgrub na sngags pa klad pa bzang ba /
NK011(da)001:11597: ngang ring ba zhes che ba dgos 'dug gi rtags ni mi 'gor bar 'ong ngo //
NK011(da)001:11598: lang lab byang chub rdo rje'i man ngag ngan sngags srog gi spu gri /
NK011(da)001:11599: dgra bo'i srog la spu gri gdab pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11601: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i man ngag so so na kha tshang zhing za ba pa mang na yang /
NK011(da)001:11602: lta spyod log pa'i dgra bo'i srog la spu gri btab pa 'di 'khor lo phyi ltar bskor ba /
NK011(da)001:11605: la bskyon la shin tu gsang la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11606: de'i sngags kyi man ngag yid ches pa /
NK011(da)001:11607: ngos 'dzin gyi them yig 'di med par gzhan ma
NK011(da)001:11608: mgo med mjug med kun gyi zab kyang zab zab
NK011(da)001:11609: 'dra bar byas nas 'ong ste gar song song du
NK011(da)001:11610: ma byed cig / de'i sngags yig 'di ltar gdams /
NK011(da)001:11611: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11612: sngags de ni dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum ka'i srog gi snying por 'agro'o //
NK011(da)001:11613: rdo rje gzhon nu gcig pu'i yang sngags su shes par bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11615: badz+ra ni rdo rje gzhon nu /
NK011(da)001:11616: k+ai ni yum 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma /
NK011(da)001:11617: li ni yab yum gnyis ka'i ye shes sems dpa' rta mgrin sku'i rgyan chas bdun pa /
NK011(da)001:11618: ba spu'i bu ga'i rdo rje gzhon nu mtshon gang ba yan chad gsal lo //
NK011(da)001:11621: k+ai 'og ma gshog pa can dang mche ba can no //
NK011(da)001:11622: la ni sprul pa yang sprul sum sprul gyi tshogs la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11624: dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum dang sprul pa dang yang
NK011(da)001:11625: sprul sum sprul thams cad rbad pa'i snying po 'bru
NK011(da)001:11626: gcig pa'o // ma ma ni ma mo thams cad 'bod pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11627: der ma zad ma mor gyur pa tsam 'bod pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11628: rag mo ni ma mo mtha' dag gi snying po ste la 'ur rgyug cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11629: yag mo ni bswe mo'i tshogs 'bod pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11630: der ma zad ma mor gyur pa tsam gyi snying po ste /
NK011(da)001:11631: ka la r+au pa ni shwa na ma'i snying po ste /
NK011(da)001:11632: brtan skyong gi tshogs mtha' dag la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11633: snying rtsa ni bswe'i skyes bu la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11634: yam yam ni bsnyur cig bsnyur cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11635: srog la yam yam ni bshan pa lag bzhi la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11636: snying phril phril gong ma ni srog bdag pe dkar spyan gcig pa la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11637: phril 'og ma ni yam shud dmar po la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11638: srog la chum chum ni btsan 'gong ngo //
NK011(da)001:11639: tsit+ta srog la gtung gtung ni bdud bskos rje brang kun nag po'o //
NK011(da)001:11640: thum ri li li ni gaza'o //
NK011(da)001:11641: der ma zad klu'i yang de na yod pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:11642: der ma zad nag po mgo dgu dang yum klu mo sbal mjug yang yin no //
NK011(da)001:11643: tsig tsig ni spyir lha ma srin sde brgyad la bya na /
NK011(da)001:11644: de'i nang nas phur bu'i srung mar gyur pa tsam gyis phur bu 'di 'tsheg tu chug cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11645: 'ur 'ur ni gnas khang du sgra chen po 'ong
NK011(da)001:11646: du gzhug pa dang med dang du ba 'ong du
NK011(da)001:11647: chug cig pa'o // shig shig ni lid+ga phur bu'i
NK011(da)001:11648: srung mar gyur pa tsam gyis che mthong chung gis
NK011(da)001:11649: mthong bar smyo ru chug cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11655: dbang po lnga'i rnam shes 'khrug tu chug /
NK011(da)001:11656: skye mched dang khams rnams smyo ru chug cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11657: gul gul ni lid+ga la shes pa khug la 'phar du chug cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11661: yan lag rdebs su chug cig /
NK011(da)001:11662: khrag tu skyugs su chug cig /
NK011(da)001:11663: 'o dod gnam du 'bod du chug cig /
NK011(da)001:11666: gzas pa po sgro lung do chad pa bzhin du brub khung du khrid la shog cig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11667: myogs myogs ni gzas pa po lus rdul du chug cig /
NK011(da)001:11671: sod sod ni lid+ga la shes pa khug la phur
NK011(da)001:11672: bu'i srung mar gyur pa tsam gyis phur pa rub
NK011(da)001:11674: srog rtsa rbad kyis chod la nag 'drad 'drad du thong zhig pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11675: d+ha ti ni shwa na ma ste /
NK011(da)001:11678: der yang ma zad shwa na brtan skyong gi tshogs la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11679: ma ma ni ma mo nag mo'i tshogs la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11680: der ma zad brtan ma'i tshogs dang /
NK011(da)001:11682: der ma zad ma mor gyur pa tsam 'bod pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11683: karma ni pho rgyud thams cad gnad la dbab pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11684: sh+ai krang ni bswe mo'i tshogs gnad la dbab /
NK011(da)001:11685: der ma zad ma mor dmar mo gyur pa tsam gnad la dbab pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11686: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi spyan sngar yul tsha
NK011(da)001:11687: ba tsha shod du ji ltar gnad la dbab pa
NK011(da)001:11689: ka re ya ni dam can rnam pa gsum dang
NK011(da)001:11690: gdug pa'i tshogs rbad pa'i snying po 'bru gsum pa'o
NK011(da)001:11691: // m+aa ra sa ni pra ma rta ni ye
NK011(da)001:11692: h'u phata ni pho rgyud mo rgyud phur pa'i srung
NK011(da)001:11693: mar gyur pa tsam la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11694: sngags kyi mtha' bsdus kyang yin /
NK011(da)001:11696: rtsa chu chod cig chod cig pa yin /
NK011(da)001:11697: bdun brgyud rtsad nas chod cig pa yin /
NK011(da)001:11698: de'i nang nas kyang dam can rnam pa gsum dang /
NK011(da)001:11699: bswe'i skyes bu gdug pa can /
NK011(da)001:11701: mon pa nag po srog zan /
NK011(da)001:11702: mon mo nag mo gser gyi rna cha rnams kyis
NK011(da)001:11703: dgra bo'i srog la snyur cig snyur cig pa'i yig
NK011(da)001:11705: spyir lha ma srin sde brgyad gnad la dbab pa'i them yig 'di med na /
NK011(da)001:11706: mgo med mjug med kun gyis mgo 'gas /
NK011(da)001:11708: klad pa 'brul bas dka' la phan mi thogs so //
NK011(da)001:11709: gnad la dbab pa'i sngags rgod 'di med na mthu mi 'ong ngo //
NK011(da)001:11710: rdzas zad pa las phan pa med do //
NK011(da)001:11711: zhes gsungs nas mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal la gtad do //
NK011(da)001:11712: des la byid ye shes brtsegs la /
NK011(da)001:11720: des rgya ston la bye ma gtsang khar gtad /
NK011(da)001:11721: des rgya thung shes rab rgyal mtshan la /
NK011(da)001:11723: des jo sras khyung po la /
NK011(da)001:11724: des mi nyag sgom chen dbang phyug g.yung drung la /
NK011(da)001:11726: glan ston gzi brjid 'bar shangs nya tshal ba yin /
NK011(da)001:11727: des gnyan ston dbang grub la /
NK011(da)001:11732: des bsod nams shes rab la /
NK011(da)001:11733: des thod ban seng ge dpal la /
NK011(da)001:11734: des kahthoga pa dge 'dun rin chen la /
NK011(da)001:11736: des bla ma dam pa rdo rje seng ge la /
NK011(da)001:11737: des bdag rong ban blo gros bzang po la mon
NK011(da)001:11738: yul bum thang seng ge khyi tshugs brag gi dben
NK011(da)001:11739: gnas su rdo rje phur pa'i skor jo lugs man
NK011(da)001:11742: sa phur dbang dang 'phags pa'i sgrub dkyil gyi lung thob /
NK011(da)001:11743: khyad par du 'phags pa lang lab kyi gdams pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK011(da)001:11744: phur nag bshad 'bum rdo rje don gsal dang bcas pa bka' drin gyis bstsal ba lags so //
NK011(da)001:11745: slob dpon pad+ma thod phreng gis bid+yot+ta ma la 'bum
NK011(da)001:11746: sde nas spyir lha ma srin sde brgyad tsam tshang
NK011(da)001:11747: na yang / de'i nang nas kyang dam can rnam
NK011(da)001:11748: pa gsum dang ming po ging dang bcas pa'i man
NK011(da)001:11749: ngag srog gi spu gri pho mo dkrug pa'i rgyud
NK011(da)001:11750: kyi nang nas btus pa'i man ngag 'di mkhar chen
NK011(da)001:11752: zhal mthong med par ston na khyod la bsdigs /
NK011(da)001:11753: snying phyungs nas mi ster na nga la bsdigs /
NK011(da)001:11754: ster ba'i dus su yang re re la mna' bsgag la gtod cig gsung /
NK011(da)001:11755: tha mar ngam 'bre la babs nas 'khor re'i brag gseb tu dgra la zhag bcur dus btab bo //
NK011(da)001:11756: de las 'gor na zla ba gcig go //
NK011(da)001:11757: slob dpon lang lab kyi man ngag 'di shin tu zab par mthong nas logs su phyung ba'o //
NK011(da)001:11758: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dzahbam hoh ma ma p+aa sham ku ru /
NK011(da)001:11759: phur pa rdzas dpal lha mo nag mo sku'i snying po /
NK011(da)001:11763: sum tri rag sha thib thib /
NK011(da)001:11764: dngos su srog bdag bdud nag po bkrag med /
NK011(da)001:11765: se na gtubs e ka dza ti /
NK011(da)001:11768: r+aa tsa sum tri chod chod /
NK011(da)001:11769: ging rnams las la rbad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11770: ma mo mkha' 'gro rnams las la rbad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11771: phyi nang gsang gsum gcig tu dril nas brnag pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11772: m+aa ra sa ni pra marta ni h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11773: slob dpon lang lab kyis bu shes rab tshul khrims
NK011(da)001:11774: la zhal mthong med par ston na dam tshig nyams
NK011(da)001:11775: so gsung / rgya ston sangs rgyas kyis zhal mthong /
NK011(da)001:11776: rta gnyis khrab gnyis sha mar drug phul nas zhus /
NK011(da)001:11777: rgya thung gi zhal mthong ring la rta gnyis phul
NK011(da)001:11778: nas zhus kyis steng la gzhan las gtod ri bar
NK011(da)001:11779: mna' bsgags so // 'di la pho 'khor mo 'khor gnyis yod de /
NK011(da)001:11780: bar du ming byang bcug la bzlas /
NK011(da)001:11781: bskor ba man ngag las shes par bya /
NK011(da)001:11782: de ltar byas na the tshom med /
NK011(da)001:11783: slob ma gsum las bstan du med /
NK011(da)001:11784: de las mang na rdo rje'i dmyal bar skye /
NK011(da)001:11787: 'jig rten gyi dpe dang 'dra bar pho dang mor
NK011(da)001:11788: ma sbrel na ci byas kyang mi 'grub pas 'di
NK011(da)001:11789: ni shin tu zab pa pho mo sbrel ba'o //
NK011(da)001:11790: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:11791: byi to rgyud kyi snying phyung dam can srog snying bsdus /
NK011(da)001:11792: ming po srung ma bcu gnyis /
NK011(da)001:11793: ging dang bcas pa'i lha srin sde brgyad srog snying dang /
NK011(da)001:11794: pho mo phyi nang gsang gsum 'khor lo dril ba 'di /
NK011(da)001:11796: slob dpon chen pos mkhar chen bza' la gtad /
NK011(da)001:11797: de nas rim brgyud mtha' ni ngam 'abre'o //
NK011(da)001:11799: 'gor na zla ba gcig de ltar dgongs nas shin tu zab par mthong /
NK011(da)001:11800: ngan sngags srog gi 'khor lo sngags kyi mchog /
NK011(da)001:11801: phyi nang gsang gsum gcig tu dril ba'i 'khor lo
NK011(da)001:11802: drag sngags kyi them yig 'di las ma gtogs pa
NK011(da)001:11804: 'di la de bas nan tan bskyed /
NK011(da)001:11805: lcam sring srog gi 'khor lo 'di 'bod rbad bsad
NK011(da)001:11806: gsum gcig tu dril zhes bya 'bod bskul bsnyen dang
NK011(da)001:11808: ngan sngags kyi tshul du srog la 'khor lo bskor ba zhes kyang bya /
NK011(da)001:11809: pho mo kha sprod ces kyang bya ste 'di lta bu ni shin tu dkon pa yin no //
NK011(da)001:11810: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya zhes pa mtha' nas dbus su gsod pa'i yig 'bru dgu pas bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11811: dzahmh'u bam hohns thib thib kyi bar /
NK011(da)001:11812: yig 'bru nyi shu rtsa gsum pas rtsibs mchan dag las dkyil du bsad /
NK011(da)001:11813: de nas drag sngags ngos bzung basngagasa kyi them yig
NK011(da)001:11814: 'di ltar bskor ba med par sngags la yid mi
NK011(da)001:11815: ches / de bas 'di ni 'di ltar bstan par bya /
NK011(da)001:11816: ni ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK011(da)001:11817: badz+ra ni rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum chos kyi dbyings la bya /
NK011(da)001:11818: k+ai ni dbang phyug khro bo bcu'o //
NK011(da)001:11820: k+ai ni sprul pa'i tshogs la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11821: li ni yang sprul gyi tshogs la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11822: k+ai ni sum sprul gyi tshogs la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11823: la ni dam can rnam gsum ming po ging dang bcas pa las la gzud pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11824: ya zhes pa sras mchog la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11825: dzahzhesa pas lcags kyus dgug pa ste dam nyams pa'i snying ga nas bzung nas /
NK011(da)001:11826: rang dbang med par khrid nas 'ongs nas lid+ga la bstim pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11827: h'u zhes pas zhags pa mas dam nyams pa'i dgra bgegs bcings nas las byed pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11828: bam zhes pas lcags sgrog mas dam nyams pa'i dgra
NK011(da)001:11829: bgegs gru gu bzhin du bsgongs nas hril hril brub
NK011(da)001:11831: hohzhesa pa dril bu mas myos myos tsam du byas nas byad bzhin dang mdog lus gsal ba'o //
NK011(da)001:11832: ma ma zhes pa ni ma mo mtha' dag tsam 'bod pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11833: p+aa sham zhes pa ni brtan ma rnams la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11834: ma bdun sring bzhi la yang bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11835: ku ru ni dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11836: ma mo nag mo sku'i snying po'o //
NK011(da)001:11837: ma tam ni shwa na ma la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11838: brtan ma'i tshogs la yang bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11839: dngos su ni zangs kyi wa mo'i sku'i snying po la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11840: ka ra i nan zhes pa ma mo dmar mo'i sku'i snying po bsdus pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11841: sum tri rag sha thib thib ces pa ni /
NK011(da)001:11842: srog bdag dang bdud mo nag mo bkrag med dang /
NK011(da)001:11845: gza' mchog chen po r+aa hu la la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11846: der yang ma zad pho rgyud thams cad la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11847: se na gtubs gtubs zhes pa nag mo'i tshogs tsam dang /
NK011(da)001:11848: e ka dz+aa ti ma la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11849: shwa na tsam zangs kyi wa mo la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11850: ma mo dmar mor gyur pa tsam bswe'i lha mo mched bzhi la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11851: de rnams kyis dam nyams pa'i dgra bo'i srog rtsa chod cig pa yin /
NK011(da)001:11852: der ma zad ma mor gyur pa tsam la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11853: r+aa tsa sum tri cho cho zhes pa ni ging rnams las la rbad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11854: srid pa'i pho rgyud du gtogs pa tsam /
NK011(da)001:11855: dngos su srog bdag la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11856: der yang ma zad pho mor gyur pa tsam las la rbad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11857: yig 'bru sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis mu khyud kyi dkyil du bsad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11858: m+aa zhes pa ni shwa na ma la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11859: ra zhes pa ni bdag nyid ma la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11860: sa zhes pa ni sa bdag chen mo bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11861: ni zhes pa ni gzas pa po'i snying po'o //
NK011(da)001:11862: pra ma rta ni ye h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:11863: ces pa ni srid pa pho ru gtogs pa tsam
NK011(da)001:11864: gcig tu dril ba'i snying po phyi nang gsang ba
NK011(da)001:11866: srid pa po'i 'khor lo zhes kyang bya /
NK011(da)001:11867: kha sprod gcig tu dril ba zhes kyang bya'o //
NK011(da)001:11868: shin tu gces pa'i brnag pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11869: yig 'bru sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis mu khyud kyi dkyil du bsad pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11871: slob dpon lang lab kyi gdams pa shin tu gsang ngo //
NK011(da)001:11872: mo ni 'gug par byed pa ste //
NK011(da)001:11873: pho ni gsod par byed pa'o //
NK011(da)001:11874: de phyir pho mo sbrel na 'grub //
NK011(da)001:11875: sna nam gyi lid+ga kha sprod kyi them yig phyi
NK011(da)001:11876: nang gsang ba gsum gcig tu dril ba rdzogs so
NK011(da)001:11879: 'di yan chad kyis rong zom lugs yongs su rdzogs pa yin /
NK011(da)001:11880: 'di man chad jo mo'i lugs kyi skor yin kyang re zung las mi snang bas /
NK011(da)001:11881: gter chen gsan yig ltar na tshe'i dbang bskur /
NK011(da)001:11883: phur bu lung sde bzhi'i las kyi bskos gdab /
NK011(da)001:11884: phur pa'i sgom byang gi gnad yig /
NK011(da)001:11886: gzhi bstod gud du phyung ba /
NK011(da)001:11887: las byang gi rtsa ba mngon rtogs las kyi tho byang zhes pa ru pad+mas mdzad pa /
NK011(da)001:11888: phur bu don gyi man ngag /
NK011(da)001:11892: bswe'i lha mo bzhi'i sgrub thabs srog tig dmar nag
NK011(da)001:11893: bcas bzhugs kyang 'dir der gtogs pa dngos bstan tshan
NK011(da)001:11894: pa gnyis tsam las mi snang yang de dag dang
NK011(da)001:11895: gzhan yang dpe rgyun la yod pa 'di lta ste
NK011(da)001:11896: /// rig 'dzin bskul rgyas pa bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:11898: byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed cing //
NK011(da)001:11899: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung 'tsho ba pa //
NK011(da)001:11900: rig 'dzin rnams kyi dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:11901: phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11903: slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis //
NK011(da)001:11904: tsan+dana nags me mched tshe bsnyen phur bsgril //
NK011(da)001:11905: tsha ba'i me shi nags tshal sngon bas bzang //
NK011(da)001:11906: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11907: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11908: slob dpon chen po bi ma la mi tra yis //
NK011(da)001:11909: gad+g+aa'i chu la btab nas dum bur bcad //
NK011(da)001:11910: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11911: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11912: bal po'i slob dpon sh+ai la many+dzu yis //
NK011(da)001:11913: man+dala brag la btab nas phye mar bsnyil //
NK011(da)001:11914: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11915: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11916: ma cig jo mo mkhar chen mtsho rgyal gyis //
NK011(da)001:11917: 'o yug mkhar ba sna yi dben rtsa ru //
NK011(da)001:11918: spyang ki'i rjes kyi sa la phur pa btab //
NK011(da)001:11919: srog bdag sprul pa spyang ki bcu gsum bsgral //
NK011(da)001:11920: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11921: de ring phur pa bsgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11922: mchims ston lo ts+aa sh+aakya pra b+ha yis //
NK011(da)001:11923: yar klungs phug nas gtsang po gyen du slog /
NK011(da)001:11924: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11925: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11926: shud pu lo ts+aa dpal gyi seng ge yis //
NK011(da)001:11927: 'u shang rdo yi brag la thogs med 'dzul //
NK011(da)001:11928: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11929: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11930: sna nam lo ts+aa rdo rje bdud 'joms kyis //
NK011(da)001:11931: has po ri ru nam mkhar rnga chen brdungs //
NK011(da)001:11932: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11933: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11934: ming po mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug gis //
NK011(da)001:11935: rtsibs kyi spyang ki sngon po gnya' nas bzung //
NK011(da)001:11936: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11937: de ring phur bsgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11938: 'dir la byid ye shes brtsegs chad 'dra /
NK011(da)001:11940: gar sha mkha' 'gro'i gling gi dbe na sa ru //
NK011(da)001:11941: slob dpon mi nub rgyal ba'i snying po yi //
NK011(da)001:11942: bdud kyi sprul pa bya rog thang la lhung //
NK011(da)001:11943: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11944: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11945: lo pan dpal blos spa gro stag tshang du //
NK011(da)001:11946: mon gyi dmag tshogs thams cad kha phung bsgral //
NK011(da)001:11947: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11948: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11949: nyang stod srin mo ri yi co to ru //
NK011(da)001:11950: slob dpon ngam 'bre klu yi rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK011(da)001:11951: dgra la btab pas bgegs kyang zhar la bsgral //
NK011(da)001:11952: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11953: de ring phur ba sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11954: ngam 'bre sa le shes rab dbang phyug gis //
NK011(da)001:11955: 'od la btab pas dkor bdag rgyal po bsgral //
NK011(da)001:11956: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11957: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11958: grub chen lang lab byang chub rdo rje yis //
NK011(da)001:11959: rkun ma'i rjes la btab nas nor rnams khug /
NK011(da)001:11960: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11961: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs madzodaciga /
NK011(da)001:11962: sna nam shes rab tshul khrims yab sras kyis //
NK011(da)001:11963: gnubs ban mthu chen stag ram mi dgu bsgral //
NK011(da)001:11964: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11965: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11966: skyi nag ban de byang chub rin chen gyis //
NK011(da)001:11967: dgra la thebs te khang pa'i gyang yang 'gyel //
NK011(da)001:11968: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11969: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11970: 'o yug rol po rmog sgar dben pa ru //
NK011(da)001:11971: nyang nag ban+d+he dbang gi shes rab kyis //
NK011(da)001:11972: phur pa grub nas dgra bgegs thams cad btul //
NK011(da)001:11973: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11974: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11975: de nas sh+aakya rgyal mtshan sku mched kyis //
NK011(da)001:11976: 'dar nag rta pa bcu dgu phur pas bsgral //
NK011(da)001:11977: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11978: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11979: g.yas ru lhan gyi stag lung grog po ru //
NK011(da)001:11980: slob dpon drag pos sgrub pa mthar phyin nas //
NK011(da)001:11981: nor rdzas phrogs pa'i ban+d+he bcu gsum bsgral //
NK011(da)001:11982: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11983: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11984: rgyan mkhar ngo dmar phug gi dben rtsa ru //
NK011(da)001:11985: so ston khri rgyal rdo rje gter sgrub kyis //
NK011(da)001:11986: phur bu bsgril te dgra bgegs dus gcig bsgral //
NK011(da)001:11987: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11988: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11989: de yi slob ma lha rje phur ston gyis //
NK011(da)001:11990: la stod khra ri rdo rje gnam rdzong du //
NK011(da)001:11991: rtags tshad phebs nas dgra bgegs gnyis ka bsgral //
NK011(da)001:11992: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11993: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11994: ban+d+he rgya ston nam mkha' rgyal po yis //
NK011(da)001:11995: dbang steng dgon par dgra bgegs gnyis la thebs //
NK011(da)001:11996: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:11997: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:11998: sras kyi thu bo nyi ma rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK011(da)001:11999: phur pa grub pas dgra bgegs phye mar byas //
NK011(da)001:12000: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:12001: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12002: nyang ban chen pos shu mngas lung pa yis //
NK011(da)001:12003: gnas dben sa rong rgyan mkhar gyi thog phug /
NK011(da)001:12005: gdug pa'i dgra bgegs phur pa'i sgo nas btul //
NK011(da)001:12006: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:12007: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12008: sngags 'chang nag po 'dzam gling pan+di tas //
NK011(da)001:12009: smu lung bsam gtan gling gi sgrub khang du //
NK011(da)001:12010: phur pa grub nas dgra bgegs zhing bcu bsgral //
NK011(da)001:12011: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:12012: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12013: bres phu bsam gtan rdo rje'i khang bu ru //
NK011(da)001:12014: slob dpon chen mo chu bar nyi phug pas //
NK011(da)001:12015: bsnyen sgrub tshad phyin dgra bgegs cham la phab //
NK011(da)001:12016: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:12017: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12018: ban grong ston pa gsang sngags rdo rje yis //
NK011(da)001:12019: mnga' ris rdzong kha rgyal po'i pho brang du //
NK011(da)001:12020: thun gtor me dpung gyur te dgra bgegs bsgral //
NK011(da)001:12021: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:12022: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12023: lho brag mkhar chu dpal gyi gnas mchog tu //
NK011(da)001:12024: o rgyan sprul pa rdo rje seng ge yis //
NK011(da)001:12025: phur pa 'phar zhing bzhad pa'i bar du bsgrubs //
NK011(da)001:12026: bstan pa bshig pa'i dgra bgegs thams cad bsgral //
NK011(da)001:12027: sngon tshe ji ltar rtags bstan ma bsnyel bar //
NK011(da)001:12028: de ring phur pa sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12029: khyed kyi thugs rje phrin las dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12030: rtags dang mtshan ma ston pa'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12031: mthu rtsal mngon du phyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12032: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)001:12034: rdo rje phur pa'i gzhi bstod gud du phyung ba bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:12036: shin tu mi bzad dpal chen rdo rje'i sku //
NK011(da)001:12037: zhe sdang thugs mchog rak+sha he ru ka /
NK011(da)001:12039: chos sku ye shes lnga brnyes gzhon nu'i tshul //
NK011(da)001:12040: rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12041: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i yum //
NK011(da)001:12042: bde chen dbyings nas sprul pa 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK011(da)001:12043: rak+sha he ru'i sku la dgyes bar 'khril //
NK011(da)001:12044: chos dbyings 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12045: rol pa'i stobs kyis nyi zla tshar gcod cing //
NK011(da)001:12046: 'dod chags skyon spangs sku yi dbang phyug che //
NK011(da)001:12047: ye shes mthar phyin nyi zla'i 'od bzhin gsal //
NK011(da)001:12048: skye bzhi mos la dbang mdzad h'u k+aa ra //
NK011(da)001:12049: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12050: zlog pa'i stobs kyis thabs yang snang /
NK011(da)001:12052: ma byin len pa spangs pa'i bdag nyid che //
NK011(da)001:12053: rab tu shes pas shes rab mthar phyin pa //
NK011(da)001:12054: yo byad dbang mdzad gzhan gyis mi thub rgyal //
NK011(da)001:12055: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12056: 'jigs pa'i stobs kyis drang srong tshar gcod cing //
NK011(da)001:12057: log pa'i skyon spangs yang dag nyid dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:12058: tshul khrims mthar phyin drang srong spyod pa che //
NK011(da)001:12059: ye shes dbang mdzad khro chen dbyug sngon can //
NK011(da)001:12060: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12061: 'jigs byed stobs kyis 'chi bdag tshar gcod cing //
NK011(da)001:12062: srog gcod skyon spangs sku yi dbang phyug che //
NK011(da)001:12063: gzung 'dzin gnyis spangs bsam gtan dag la gnas //
NK011(da)001:12064: tshe la dbang mdzad khro chen gshin rje gshed //
NK011(da)001:12065: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12066: brdeg pa'i stobs kyis srin po tshar gcod cing //
NK011(da)001:12067: rdzun gyi skyon spangs ngag gi dbang phyug che //
NK011(da)001:12068: dbu ma'i stobs kyis mtshan ma 'dul mdzad pa //
NK011(da)001:12069: skye la dbang mdzad dran tshul mi g.yo mgon //
NK011(da)001:12070: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12071: brjid pa'i stobs kyis klu rnams tshar gcod cing //
NK011(da)001:12072: phra ma'i skyon spangs dag pa'i dbang phyug che //
NK011(da)001:12073: 'bad pa med pa'i brtson 'grus shugs dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:12074: chos la dbang mdzad khro chen rta mchog dpal //
NK011(da)001:12075: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12076: shugs 'chang stobs kyis rlung lha tshar gcod cing //
NK011(da)001:12077: ngag 'khyal skyon spangs ngag gi dbang phyug che //
NK011(da)001:12078: 'dod pa kun sbyin mdzad pa rgyal po'i tshul //
NK011(da)001:12079: sems la dbang mdzad khro chen 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK011(da)001:12080: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12081: sngags 'khor stobs kyis gnod sbyin zhabs kyis gnon //
NK011(da)001:12082: ngag rtsub skyon spangs ngag gi dbang phyug che //
NK011(da)001:12083: smon lam rnam par dag pas bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK011(da)001:12084: las la dbang mdzad khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK011(da)001:12085: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12086: gnon pa'i stobs kyis 'byung po tshar gcod cing //
NK011(da)001:12087: gnod sems skyon spangs thugs kyi dbang phyug che //
NK011(da)001:12088: gnyen po'i stobs kyis thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK011(da)001:12089: rdzu 'phrul dbang mdzad khro chen khams gsum rgyal //
NK011(da)001:12090: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12091: gzi brjid stobs kyis thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK011(da)001:12092: brnab sems skyon spangs thugs rje'i dbang phyug che //
NK011(da)001:12093: drag rtsal shugs kyis gdug pa 'dul mdzad pa //
NK011(da)001:12094: smon lam dbang mdzad khro chen stobs po che //
NK011(da)001:12095: khro bo chen po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12096: bskyod pa'i ye shes sa rnams dus gcig spyod //
NK011(da)001:12097: thugs rje chen pos 'khor ba gnas su 'dren //
NK011(da)001:12098: thabs dang shes rab spyod pas mtha' gnyis spangs //
NK011(da)001:12099: khams gsum h'u mdzad mnyes mdzad sgra 'byin ma //
NK011(da)001:12100: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12101: ye shes thugs rjes zin pas mthar mi ltung //
NK011(da)001:12102: thugs rjes ye shes zin pas srid pa grol //
NK011(da)001:12103: gnyis la mi gnas mtha' gnyis dbu mar sdigs //
NK011(da)001:12104: rnam par rgyal ba mnyes mdzad snyems ma'i sku //
NK011(da)001:12105: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12106: rig pa ye shes chos kyi sku nyid 'dzin //
NK011(da)001:12107: thabs dang shes rab ldan pas 'gro don mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12108: dbyug pa sngon po mnyes mdzad rdo rje sder //
NK011(da)001:12109: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12110: ye shes mtshan bsdud thugs rjes dur khrod 'byung //
NK011(da)001:12111: thugs rje'i sprul pa sku dang ye shes 'phro //
NK011(da)001:12112: shes pa snyigs ma dbu ma rig par bskyel //
NK011(da)001:12113: gshed po mnyes mdzad rdo rje dur khrod bdag /
NK011(da)001:12114: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12115: shes rab tho bas mtshan ma dbyings su brdung //
NK011(da)001:12116: chos dbyings gtun du shes bya'i bag chags 'joms //
NK011(da)001:12117: mi dmigs gtun du mtshan ma'i bag chags brdung //
NK011(da)001:12118: mi g.yo mgon po mnyes mdzad gtun khung ma //
NK011(da)001:12119: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12120: rdo rje gtum mos mtshan ma'i bag chags 'joms //
NK011(da)001:12121: thugs rjes rngams tshul gnod pa thal bar rlog /
NK011(da)001:12122: gnyis las mi gnas mtha' bral dbu mar sdigs //
NK011(da)001:12123: rta mchog rgyal po mnyes mdzad ral gcig ma //
NK011(da)001:12124: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12125: phra mo 'bigs shing ye shes dbyings su sdud //
NK011(da)001:12126: phra mo'i 'da' ni ye shes dbyings su 'phen //
NK011(da)001:12127: dbu ma'i mda' ni gnyis su med par mgyogs //
NK011(da)001:12128: gzhan gyis mi thub mnyes mdzad mda' snyems ma //
NK011(da)001:12129: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12130: mtshan ma med pa'i dbyings rig thos pa'i sgra //
NK011(da)001:12131: dbyings nyid rig par shes pa snyan pa'i sgra //
NK011(da)001:12132: rig pa ye shes chos kyi dbyings su 'byin //
NK011(da)001:12133: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba mnyes mdzad rlung 'byin ma //
NK011(da)001:12134: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12135: bdag rtog log pa'i mtshan ma kun bcom nas //
NK011(da)001:12136: za byed mche bas skye shi rtsad nas gcod //
NK011(da)001:12137: sku dang ye shes ma skyes mi dmigs pas //
NK011(da)001:12138: khams gsum rnam rgyal mnyes byed gsod byed ma //
NK011(da)001:12139: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12140: thugs dam rnam dag dbang gis dbyings nas bskul //
NK011(da)001:12141: thugs rje'i shugs kyis 'gro ba gnas nas 'dren //
NK011(da)001:12142: gnyis med mchod bskul dbu mar dgyes pa bskyed //
NK011(da)001:12143: ma h+aa ba la mnyes byed bskul byed ma //
NK011(da)001:12144: khro mo yum mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12145: lhag mthong chos nyid zhi gnas lam las rgyal //
NK011(da)001:12146: smon lam thugs rjes 'khor ba'i stobs las rgyal //
NK011(da)001:12147: 'gro ba'i don mdzad smon lam shugs dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:12148: de phyir phra men myos byed phag mgo can la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12149: thugs rje phrin las mi bzad sdug bsngal ba //
NK011(da)001:12150: yal bar ma 'dor gtum chen brtson 'grus shugs //
NK011(da)001:12151: 'khor ba mtha' gtug gdod nas dag par sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12152: de phyir dpal gtum stag mgo can la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12153: thugs rje'i sdang mig 'khor ba zhe la gnon //
NK011(da)001:12154: mthu rtsal chen po'i nyon mongs 'joms par byed //
NK011(da)001:12155: 'chams pa'i ral pa gsig cing 'jig rten 'gengs //
NK011(da)001:12156: de phyir mi 'gyur g.yag mgo can la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12157: rtog pa'i dgra spangs dran pa'i dgon par 'jug /
NK011(da)001:12158: 'khrul skyon dri ma shes bya'i rdzi tshogs spong //
NK011(da)001:12159: 'gro don dus la bab na thugs rje 'jug /
NK011(da)001:12160: de phyir 'jug byed sha ba'i mgo can la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12161: chos dbyings snang lam rtog pa'i skyon sel cing //
NK011(da)001:12162: thugs rje'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas //
NK011(da)001:12163: dug gsum mi spong sha khrag lus la rol //
NK011(da)001:12164: de phyir sel byed gzig mgo can la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12165: ya nga bag zon 'gro don thabs dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:12166: gdul bya dus la babs tshe thugs rjes 'jug /
NK011(da)001:12167: mi 'dul zin gtubs btang snyoms chen por bzhugs //
NK011(da)001:12168: de phyir mkhas brtson byi la'i dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12169: ye shes dbyings la 'jug pas shes bya za //
NK011(da)001:12170: dbyings la ye shes 'jug pas nyon mongs za //
NK011(da)001:12171: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med 'khor ba za //
NK011(da)001:12172: de phyir za byed spyang ki'i dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12173: ris btsun gnyen por gyur pas thams cad 'dul //
NK011(da)001:12174: phrin las stobs kyis bdud dpung ma lus 'dul //
NK011(da)001:12175: stong nyid sgra sgrog mu stegs wa tshogs 'joms //
NK011(da)001:12176: de phyir rtsal ldan seng ge'i dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12177: ye shes thugs rje'i stobs kyis mtha' gnyis 'dul //
NK011(da)001:12178: 'chams stabs ral pa gsig pas bdud dpung 'joms //
NK011(da)001:12179: las su ci mdzad brtson 'grus stobs dang ldan //
NK011(da)001:12180: de phyir mgyogs 'gros dred kyi dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12181: dbyings las ye shes nyal bas thugs rje rmi //
NK011(da)001:12182: mthing nag gcer bu drag po'i skur ston pa //
NK011(da)001:12183: thugs mchog rnam dag ye shes dbyings su mkhyen //
NK011(da)001:12184: de phyir smyo byed dom gyi dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12185: 'jug pa rang dbang med par bskyod gyur pas //
NK011(da)001:12186: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs thams cad myos par byed //
NK011(da)001:12187: snyan pa'i chos rtogs log lta myos byed pa //
NK011(da)001:12188: de phyir myos byed rmig bu'i mgo la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12189: yid g.yo las can sems par gyur nas ni //
NK011(da)001:12190: ye shes dbang gi thugs rjes 'gro ba g.yo //
NK011(da)001:12191: don mdzad 'od 'phro ye shes dbyings nas mkhyen //
NK011(da)001:12192: de phyir tshul khrims bya rgod mgo la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12193: bsam pa'i dngos po 'dod pas 'dun pa 'byung //
NK011(da)001:12194: dbyings dang ye shes mkhyen pas shes bya za //
NK011(da)001:12195: thugs rje'i 'dun pas bag chags mtshan ma za //
NK011(da)001:12196: de phyir za byed bya rog dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12197: dmigs pa'i sems 'dzin yid la byed par bsgyur //
NK011(da)001:12198: ye shes dbyings su rtogs pas nyin mo nyal //
NK011(da)001:12199: thugs rjes 'gro don dgongs pas mtshan mor blta //
NK011(da)001:12200: de phyir drang mkhan 'ug pa'i dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12201: brtags pa'i dngos po rtse gcig ting 'dzin bsgyur //
NK011(da)001:12202: mnyam nyid mtha' bral dbyings las mi g.yo bar //
NK011(da)001:12203: rtog pa spyod pa byis pas mi mthong sbed //
NK011(da)001:12204: de phyir sbed byed khwa ta'i dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12205: mnyam nyid dbyings las ye shes shugs kyis mgyogs //
NK011(da)001:12206: zhi gnas spyan zlum 'gro ba'i don tshogs 'byung //
NK011(da)001:12207: las 'bras bden pas yid ches dad par bsgyur //
NK011(da)001:12208: de phyir mgyogs byed pu shud dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12209: nges pa'i dngos po 'dzin pa med par bsgyur //
NK011(da)001:12210: lhag mthong ye shes dbyings la mnyam par gnas //
NK011(da)001:12211: zhi gnas rteng po'i 'dzin pas mi 'phrog pa //
NK011(da)001:12212: de phyir phra men khra yi dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12213: 'dres pa'i dngos po ma 'dres dran par bsgyur //
NK011(da)001:12214: 'bum phrag ting 'dzin lhag mthong so sor gsal //
NK011(da)001:12215: ye shes dbyis las sprul pa bsam mi khyab //
NK011(da)001:12216: de phyir sgron me pha wang dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12217: chos rnams 'byed pa med par gnas bsgyur la //
NK011(da)001:12218: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du log lta sel //
NK011(da)001:12219: rig pa skyen pas sems nyid rtse mo gcod //
NK011(da)001:12220: de phyir gcod byed sre mong mgo la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12221: sa 'og spyod pas rig pa gnas bsgyur ba //
NK011(da)001:12222: phrin las bye brag mang po ci mdzad kyang //
NK011(da)001:12223: phyag rgya bzhi las mi bskyod dur khrod nyul //
NK011(da)001:12224: de phyir mgyogs byed byi ba'i dbu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12225: 'khor ba rdo rjer brjod pas mya ngan 'das //
NK011(da)001:12226: chos sku rdo rjer brjod pas mtha' gnyis spangs //
NK011(da)001:12227: brjod med spros bral don dam tshig las 'das //
NK011(da)001:12228: de phyir brjod med lcags kyu ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12229: chos nyid rdo rje dngos po mtshan ma 'joms //
NK011(da)001:12230: ye shes rdo rjes gzung 'dzin log rtog bsreg /
NK011(da)001:12231: phyag mtshan rdo rje dregs pa lha bdud 'joms //
NK011(da)001:12232: de phyir 'joms byed zhags pa ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12233: 'chi med rdo rje yul sems 'gag pa med //
NK011(da)001:12234: grub pa'i rdo rjes bsam pa'i 'bras bu thob //
NK011(da)001:12235: thugs rje'i rdo rjes 'khor ba'i rtsa ba gcod //
NK011(da)001:12236: de phyir gtso mchog lcags sgrog ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12237: ye shes 'khrol byed yon tan rgya mtsho 'grub //
NK011(da)001:12238: thugs rje 'khrol byed 'jig rten dbang du sdud //
NK011(da)001:12239: ye shes rdo rjes gnyis med dbyings su sdud //
NK011(da)001:12240: de phyir dril 'khrol khra mgo ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK011(da)001:12241: dpal rdo rje phur pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi gzhi bstod rdzogs so //
NK011(da)001:12244: // // rdo rje phur pa'i bka' srung dang bcas pa'i bskul byang bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:12246: phrin las rol pa drag po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK011(da)001:12247: gru gsum mthing nag e yi gzhal yas khang //
NK011(da)001:12248: lha chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng na //
NK011(da)001:12249: bdud dang dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i lha mchog ni //
NK011(da)001:12250: drag gtum mi bzad rngams shing brjid pa'i sku //
NK011(da)001:12251: che mchog dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu che //
NK011(da)001:12252: zhe sdang rdo rje rak+sha he ru ka /
NK011(da)001:12253: ye shes sku mchog rigs rnams kun gyi bdag /
NK011(da)001:12254: brjod med dbyings nas h'u phata sgra chen sgrog /
NK011(da)001:12255: mi dmigs spros dang bral ba don dam dang //
NK011(da)001:12256: dbyings nas byin rlabs khro bcu las la 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12257: chos dbyings mi 'gyur sku mdog mthing nag la //
NK011(da)001:12258: 'jigs pa'i rgyan cha dur khrod dpal chas rdzogs //
NK011(da)001:12259: zhal g.yas dkar po chos sku mngon du ston //
NK011(da)001:12260: g.yon zhal dmar nag dbang drag phrin las mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12261: dbus zhal mthing nag phrin las thams cad grub //
NK011(da)001:12262: skye 'gro rtsad nas gcod pa'i mche ba gtsigs //
NK011(da)001:12263: spyan dgu sdang mig 'bar bas bdud dpung 'joms //
NK011(da)001:12264: nyon mongs dang ni log lta mtha' dag 'dul //
NK011(da)001:12265: gar dgu'i nyams kyis 'jigs byed 'jigs mdzad cing //
NK011(da)001:12266: rdo rje rtse dgus sa dgu'i rtog pa 'joms //
NK011(da)001:12267: rdo rje rtse lngas rgyud lnga gnas su 'joms //
NK011(da)001:12268: ye shes me dpung 'khor ba'i bag chags bsreg /
NK011(da)001:12269: kha t+w+aam bdud bzhi thal bar brlag par mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12270: ri rab phur bu 'debs pas 'gal byed grol //
NK011(da)001:12271: che btsan dpe med khams gsum 'gran zla med //
NK011(da)001:12272: ye shes rtsal shugs stobs kyis dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12273: phrin las lhun grub rak+sha dpal gyi sku //
NK011(da)001:12274: sman raka gtor tshogs mchod sprin rgya mtshos mchod //
NK011(da)001:12275: thugs rjes brtser dgongs dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)001:12276: thugs dam thugs rjes dgra bgegs myur du sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12278: gnyis med yum mchog 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma //
NK011(da)001:12279: e ka dz+aa ti gu h+ya gsang ba'i yum //
NK011(da)001:12280: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug mkha' klong na //
NK011(da)001:12281: bee d+aur sngon po sku mdog gsal la 'tsher //
NK011(da)001:12282: in+d+ra n+ai la'i ral pa gcig tu 'khyil //
NK011(da)001:12283: khro gnyer rab bsdus rngams pa'i mche ba gtsigs //
NK011(da)001:12284: me 'od bsreg pa'i 'od zer kun tu 'phro //
NK011(da)001:12285: sha rus chem chem gsol ba'i rkan sgra can //
NK011(da)001:12286: khrag 'dzag mi mgo'i phreng ba sbrul chun 'phyangs //
NK011(da)001:12287: zhing chen g.yang gzhi gsar pa'i stod g.yogs la //
NK011(da)001:12288: gzigs lpags khrag 'dzag rlon pa'i smad dkris can //
NK011(da)001:12289: khrag mtsho khongs su 'dren pa'i ljags rlabs ma //
NK011(da)001:12290: 'khor lo rtse gsum 'bar ba g.yas na thogs //
NK011(da)001:12291: thod rlon klad khrag 'dres pa g.yon na thogs //
NK011(da)001:12292: gzir mnan drag po za byed dpal gyi yum //
NK011(da)001:12293: thams cad dbang du sdud pa'i sring gcig ma //
NK011(da)001:12294: bar snang 'phyo ba'i me za brag gyon ma //
NK011(da)001:12295: srid gsum phung byed bal mo kun tu ma //
NK011(da)001:12296: srog gi snying po 'don no ma 'da' zhig /
NK011(da)001:12297: dam tshig dmar gyi ar+g+ham 'di sbrengs pas //
NK011(da)001:12298: thugs dam ma g.yel rtse gcig rgyun du dgongs //
NK011(da)001:12299: rang rgyud dag pa'i rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos //
NK011(da)001:12300: brda' dang spyugs pa rngams pa thal mo'i sgra //
NK011(da)001:12301: rak+ta chags pa'i brda' yig g.yab 'dor na //
NK011(da)001:12302: glog ltar myur ba'i thugs rjes 'dir gshegs shig /
NK011(da)001:12303: thal mo rdeb cing 'jigs pa'i bshug glu len //
NK011(da)001:12304: srid pa'i gad mo rgod cing khrag chen 'thung //
NK011(da)001:12305: dus gsum kun nas ma bsgribs mkhyen pa mnga' //
NK011(da)001:12306: dmar gyi dri snom khrag gi ro myong ma //
NK011(da)001:12307: dpag tshad brgyad khri'i gnas nas 'dir gshegs la //
NK011(da)001:12308: sha za khrag 'thung rtsub pa'i las byed ma //
NK011(da)001:12309: ye shes rmad byung don dam dgongs pa can //
NK011(da)001:12310: gzhan gyis ma bcol nyid kyi zhal 'ches pa //
NK011(da)001:12311: dam tshig bskul lo rtag tu grogs mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12312: phrin las gzhung bzhin pho nya mang po 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12313: dam tshig gzhung bzhin thams cad dbang du bsdud //
NK011(da)001:12314: phrin las dus la bab po sring gcig ma //
NK011(da)001:12315: mngon sum grub pa'i las mdzad da tshur byon //
NK011(da)001:12317: steng nas sprul pa khro chen h'u k+aa ra //
NK011(da)001:12318: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis tshangs pa gnon //
NK011(da)001:12319: ri rab phur bu 'debs shing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12320: sgra 'byin yum mchog pho nya phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12321: phyag brnyan rnam rtog mi mnga' phag mgo can //
NK011(da)001:12322: phyag g.yas rdo rje g.yon na phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12323: myongs byed rmig bu'i mgo can dril bu bsnams //
NK011(da)001:12324: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chings //
NK011(da)001:12325: gzir cig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12327: shar nas sprul pa khro chen rnam par rgyal //
NK011(da)001:12328: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis lha dbang gnon //
NK011(da)001:12329: ri rab phur bu 'debs shing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12330: yum mchog snyems ma sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12331: phyag bsnyan za byed dpa' gtum stag gi mgo //
NK011(da)001:12332: phyag g.yas lcags kyu g.yon na phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12333: thogs med bya rgod mgo can rnga yab thogs //
NK011(da)001:12334: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chings //
NK011(da)001:12335: gzir cig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12337: shar lho sprul pa khro chen dbyug sngon can //
NK011(da)001:12338: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis drang srong gnon //
NK011(da)001:12339: ri rab phur bu 'debs shing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12340: rdo rje sder mo pho nya phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12341: phyag brnyan mi 'gyur g.yag gi mgo bo can //
NK011(da)001:12342: phyag g.yas dbyug to g.yon pa phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12343: rig shes bya rog mgo can med dpung thogs //
NK011(da)001:12344: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chings //
NK011(da)001:12345: gzir cig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12347: lho nas sprul pa khro rgyal gshin rje'i gshed //
NK011(da)001:12348: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis gshin rje gnon //
NK011(da)001:12349: ri rab phur bu 'debs shing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12350: dur khrod bdag mo pho nya phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12351: phyag brnyan 'jug byed sha ba'i mgo bo can //
NK011(da)001:12352: phyag g.yas dbyug pa g.yon pa phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12353: mun 'thoms 'ug pa'i mgo can dgra s+t+wa thogs //
NK011(da)001:12354: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chings //
NK011(da)001:12355: gzir cig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12357: lho nub sprul pa khro rgyal mi g.yo mgon //
NK011(da)001:12358: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis srin po gnon //
NK011(da)001:12359: ri rab phur bu 'debs shing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12360: yum chen gtun khung pho nya phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12361: phyag brnyan spyod rdzogs gdug pa gzig gi mgo //
NK011(da)001:12362: phyag g.yas ral gri g.yon pa phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12363: sbed byed khwa ta'i mgo can zhags pa thogs //
NK011(da)001:12364: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chigs //
NK011(da)001:12365: gzir cig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12367: nub nas sprul pa khro chen rta mchog dpal //
NK011(da)001:12368: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis klu dbang gnon //
NK011(da)001:12369: ri rab phur bu 'debs shing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12370: yum chen gtum mo sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12371: phyag brnyan mkhas brtson byi la'i mgo bo can //
NK011(da)001:12372: phyag g.yas pad+ma g.yon pa phur bu 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12373: gsal bkra pu shud mgo can sbrul zhags thogs //
NK011(da)001:12374: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chings //
NK011(da)001:12375: gzir cig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12377: nub byang sprul pa khro chen 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK011(da)001:12378: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis rlung lha gnon //
NK011(da)001:12379: ri rab phur bu 'debs shing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12380: yum chen mda' snyems sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12381: phra men za byed phyed 'dzin lce spyang mgo //
NK011(da)001:12382: phyag g.yas rdo rje g.yon pa phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12383: gsod byed khra yi mgo can 'khor lo thogs //
NK011(da)001:12384: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chings //
NK011(da)001:12385: gzir cig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12387: byang nas sprul pa'i khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK011(da)001:12388: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis gnod sbyin gnon //
NK011(da)001:12389: ri rab phur bu 'debs shing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12390: yum chen rlung 'byin sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12391: phra men 'joms byed rtsal 'chang seng ge'i mgo //
NK011(da)001:12392: rdo rje rgya gram g.yon pa phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12393: sgrin gsal pha wang mgo can be con thogs //
NK011(da)001:12394: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chings //
NK011(da)001:12395: gzir cig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12397: byang shar sprul pa khro chen khams gsum rgyal //
NK011(da)001:12398: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis dbang ldan gnon //
NK011(da)001:12399: ri rab phur bu 'debs shing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12400: yum chen gsod byed sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12401: phyag brnyan stobs chen ldan pa dred kyi mgo //
NK011(da)001:12402: phyag g.yas rdo rjer g.yon pa phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12403: gsod byed sre mong mgo can rtse gsum thogs //
NK011(da)001:12404: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chings //
NK011(da)001:12405: gzir cig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12407: 'og nas sprul pa khro chen stobs po che //
NK011(da)001:12408: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis sa bdag gnon //
NK011(da)001:12409: ri rab phur pa 'dril zhing dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12410: yum chen bskyod ma sprul pa phyogs bcur 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:12411: phyag brnyan smyo byed dom gyi mgo bo can //
NK011(da)001:12412: phyag g.yas tho ba g.yon pas phur bu 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12413: sa spyod byi ba'i mgo can gtun shing thogs //
NK011(da)001:12414: dgra bgegs khug cig phob cig yan lag chings //
NK011(da)001:12415: gzir chig khrag tu skyugs la rdul du rlog /
NK011(da)001:12416: shar gyi sgo bas dgra bgegs lcags kyus bzung //
NK011(da)001:12417: lho yi sgo bas dgra bgegs zhags pas chings //
NK011(da)001:12418: nub kyi sgo bas dgra bgegs sgrog gis sdoms //
NK011(da)001:12419: byang gi sgo bas dgra bgegs rdul du log /
NK011(da)001:12420: dkyil 'khor chen po'i bar khyams phyi rol du //
NK011(da)001:12421: rnal 'byor dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK011(da)001:12422: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod gtor 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12423: zhi rgyas dbang drag phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12425: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12426: nam ni srod kyi dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12427: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu ma //
NK011(da)001:12428: kha gdangs mig bgrad 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK011(da)001:12429: rkan sgra 'brug sgra chems se chem //
NK011(da)001:12430: mche ba gangs ri bsnol 'dra yis //
NK011(da)001:12431: dgra bo'i sha khrag rngams zas byed //
NK011(da)001:12432: de la lcags kyi ma mo zhon //
NK011(da)001:12433: lcags kyi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK011(da)001:12435: khrag gi char ba dmar mo 'bebs //
NK011(da)001:12436: spyang gdong dmar nag dgra la rngams //
NK011(da)001:12437: phyag na lcags phur dgra la rdeg /
NK011(da)001:12438: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12439: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12440: dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12442: nam ni srod kyi dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12443: gser gyi 'phar ba lce brgyad ma //
NK011(da)001:12444: ya 'gal nyi ma'i ngos la reg /
NK011(da)001:12445: ma 'gal rgya mtsho'i steng du bzed //
NK011(da)001:12446: rnam shes tshogs brgyad gnas su sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12447: spu ni ral gri chu gri'i so //
NK011(da)001:12448: bang ni glog gis bskyod du med //
NK011(da)001:12449: de la gser gyi ma mo zhon //
NK011(da)001:12450: mche ba dmar pos dgra snying za //
NK011(da)001:12451: ral pa sprugs pa'i skra gseb nas //
NK011(da)001:12452: sdom dang sdig pa'i char du 'bebs //
