NK011(da)001:12453: 'phar gdong ser nag dgra la rngams //
NK011(da)001:12454: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12455: sri ka mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12456: dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12458: nam ni srod kyi pho nya mo //
NK011(da)001:12459: zangs kyi wa mo rkang gsum ma //
NK011(da)001:12460: dpag tshad brgyad khrir dmar dri mnam //
NK011(da)001:12461: gzugs ni me yi phung po 'dra //
NK011(da)001:12462: mjug ma lcags kyi sog le ma //
NK011(da)001:12463: mig ni nyi ma'i zer bas 'tsher //
NK011(da)001:12464: spu ni ral gri'o so dang 'dra //
NK011(da)001:12465: sder mo lcags kyu me stag 'phro //
NK011(da)001:12466: bang ni rlung gis bskyod du med //
NK011(da)001:12467: skad ni stong khams khyab par sgrog /
NK011(da)001:12468: de la zangs kyi ma mo chibs //
NK011(da)001:12469: sku la me yi phung po 'bar //
NK011(da)001:12470: zhal ni khro chu'i me mda' 'phen //
NK011(da)001:12471: g.yas pa'i rdo rjes ri rab bsnyil //
NK011(da)001:12472: g.yon pa zangs kyi phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12473: wa gdong dmar nag dgra la rngams //
NK011(da)001:12474: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12475: sri la mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12476: dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12478: nam ni srod kyi pho nya mo //
NK011(da)001:12479: lcags kyi khyi mo ral pa can //
NK011(da)001:12480: mthing nag ral pas gnam sa gang //
NK011(da)001:12481: ngus pa'i mchi ma ser ba 'gril //
NK011(da)001:12482: zug pa'i skad kyis lha srin brgyal //
NK011(da)001:12483: mche bas ri rab dum bur gtubs //
NK011(da)001:12484: lce yis rgya mtsho hub kyis 'debs //
NK011(da)001:12485: de la zhon pa'i pho nya mo //
NK011(da)001:12486: mthing gi ma mo ral pa can //
NK011(da)001:12487: mun pa'i go zu sku la gsol //
NK011(da)001:12488: bdud kyi dmag dpung bran du 'khol //
NK011(da)001:12489: kha rlangs sprin du 'khrigs pa la //
NK011(da)001:12490: rkan sgra brdabs pas thog stong 'bebs //
NK011(da)001:12491: mthing gi phur bas dgra bgegs sgrol //
NK011(da)001:12492: khyi gdong dmar nag dgra la rngams //
NK011(da)001:12493: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12494: sri la mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12495: dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12497: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12498: nam gyi gung gi dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12499: dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti //
NK011(da)001:12500: ri rab chen po'i rtse mo nas //
NK011(da)001:12501: gling bzhi skyong bar byed pa'i tshe //
NK011(da)001:12502: gling bzhi kun 'byams drag mo rgyal //
NK011(da)001:12503: rgya mtsho'i gting na bzhugs pa'i tshe //
NK011(da)001:12504: sring mo b+ha ga hri ti ma //
NK011(da)001:12505: nam mkha'i khams kyi dpal mo btsan //
NK011(da)001:12506: mu le lding gi mtsho bdag mo //
NK011(da)001:12507: ming brgya ma la mtshan stong ma //
NK011(da)001:12508: dre'u rta rkang gsum chibs su bcibs //
NK011(da)001:12509: phyag g.yas me long sbrul zhags thogs //
NK011(da)001:12510: g.yon pa kha t+w+aam phur pa thogs //
NK011(da)001:12511: 'du ba rnam bzhi'i nad bdag mo //
NK011(da)001:12512: 'dir byon mchod sbyin gtor ma bzhes //
NK011(da)001:12513: dgra bgegs sgrol ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK011(da)001:12515: rak+ta'i mtsho las skur bzhengs pa //
NK011(da)001:12516: nam ni gung gi dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12517: dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti //
NK011(da)001:12518: dbang gi sku mdog dmar mo la //
NK011(da)001:12519: btso dmar la'u sku la gsol //
NK011(da)001:12520: khrag skam lcags kyu phur pa thogs //
NK011(da)001:12521: bal nad le brgan nad bdag mo //
NK011(da)001:12522: 'dir byon mchod sbyin gtor ma bzhes //
NK011(da)001:12523: dgra bgegs bla tshe dbang du sdud //
NK011(da)001:12524: re ma ti yi dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12526: nam ni gung gi dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12527: dpal ldan lha mo re ma dzah rgyas pa'i sku mdog ser nag la //
NK011(da)001:12528: rma bya'i thul pa sku la gsol //
NK011(da)001:12529: gcod byed gser gyi zor ba bsnams //
NK011(da)001:12530: chibs su sha ba yu mo chibs //
NK011(da)001:12531: ri rab rtse nas las mdzad ma //
NK011(da)001:12532: mkhris pa sha ya'i nad bdag mo //
NK011(da)001:12533: thog dang ser ba'i sna 'dren ma //
NK011(da)001:12534: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12535: dgra la rims nad dal yams phob //
NK011(da)001:12536: re ma dzahyi dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12538: nam ni gung gi dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12539: dpal ldan lha mo re ma dzu //
NK011(da)001:12540: sku mdog ljang nag phrin las bdag /
NK011(da)001:12541: chu dar sngon po'i ber chen gsol //
NK011(da)001:12542: rnga mong sngo nag chibs su bcibs //
NK011(da)001:12543: khram shing gru gu phur pa bsnams //
NK011(da)001:12544: pho logs lhogs brgyal nad bdag mo //
NK011(da)001:12545: kha ba bu yug sna 'dren ma //
NK011(da)001:12546: re ma dzu yi dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12547: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12548: dgra bgegs bsgral ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12550: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12551: nam gyi tho rangs dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12552: rgya gar bal po'i so mtshams nas //
NK011(da)001:12553: chu mig byang chub bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK011(da)001:12554: me tog dgun yang skye ba'i sar //
NK011(da)001:12555: tsha ba nad kyi bdag mo bzhi //
NK011(da)001:12556: mthu stobs ches nas so sor bzhag /
NK011(da)001:12557: bal yul ya byin sa shod nas //
NK011(da)001:12558: mar khu'i mtsho mo mer ba na //
NK011(da)001:12559: rdo rje ya byin dbang mo che //
NK011(da)001:12560: sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba la //
NK011(da)001:12561: mthing gi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK011(da)001:12562: dbang gi bswe khrab si li li //
NK011(da)001:12563: rna ba slang tsam lhebs se lheb //
NK011(da)001:12564: gser gyi rna cha wangs se wang //
NK011(da)001:12565: ral pa re zhing phur pa re //
NK011(da)001:12566: ba spu re zhing lcags kyu re //
NK011(da)001:12567: me lce dgu phreng sku yi rgyan //
NK011(da)001:12568: dar nag cod pan pu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:12569: chibs su g.yu 'brug sngon mo chibs //
NK011(da)001:12570: chibs kyi snga long phyi long la //
NK011(da)001:12571: mi thod rta thod phru lu lu //
NK011(da)001:12572: g.yas na bdud zhags nag po bsnams //
NK011(da)001:12573: g.yon pa lcags phur dgra la brdeg /
NK011(da)001:12574: brda ni mi 'phrod lho bal skad //
NK011(da)001:12575: gzugs ni mi ston lag brgya mo //
NK011(da)001:12576: gsang ba'i spyugs pa kyu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:12577: bal yul ya byin yul mdo na //
NK011(da)001:12578: khrag mtsho mer ba'i nang shed na //
NK011(da)001:12579: ya byin chen mo'i blon mo ni //
NK011(da)001:12580: sa bdag chen mo ral gcig ma //
NK011(da)001:12581: ral pa sprug pas stong gsum khyab //
NK011(da)001:12582: nag mo spyan dmar mi bzad pa //
NK011(da)001:12583: sa bdag 'bum gyi khad dpon mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12584: bal yul ya byin yul phu na //
NK011(da)001:12585: bdud kyi rgyal po rnam rol gnas //
NK011(da)001:12586: jo mo ya byin mthu mo che //
NK011(da)001:12587: blon mo nag mo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK011(da)001:12588: nam phyed dus kyi mun pa la //
NK011(da)001:12589: skad cig yud la yul phur phyin //
NK011(da)001:12590: bdud kyi rgyal po rnam rol bsgral //
NK011(da)001:12591: de phyir bdud 'dul chen mor grags //
NK011(da)001:12592: phur pa sgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:12593: sha khrag dmar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK011(da)001:12594: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12595: ku lan d+ha ri'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12597: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12598: nam ni tho rangs dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12599: yul ni tsha ba rong gi gnas //
NK011(da)001:12600: de byin bya ba'i sa gshongs nas //
NK011(da)001:12601: sbrang rtsi'i mtsho mo mer ba na //
NK011(da)001:12602: sprul pa'i bswe mkhar smug po na //
NK011(da)001:12603: rdo rje de byin rtsal mo che //
NK011(da)001:12604: sku mdog ser nag 'bar ba la //
NK011(da)001:12605: gser gyi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK011(da)001:12606: ral pa re zhing phur pa re //
NK011(da)001:12607: phur pa'i lan phran khra la la //
NK011(da)001:12608: spyi gtsug gser gyi rdo rjes brgyan //
NK011(da)001:12609: rna ba slang tsam lhebs se lheb //
NK011(da)001:12610: dar nag cod pan pu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:12611: gzi yi rna cha wangs se wang //
NK011(da)001:12612: ba spu re zhing lcags kyu re //
NK011(da)001:12613: me lce dgu phreng sku yi rgyan //
NK011(da)001:12614: mdzes byed rma bya'i thul pa gsol //
NK011(da)001:12615: dbang gi bswe khrab si li li //
NK011(da)001:12616: chibs su gza' rta ser po bcibs //
NK011(da)001:12617: gser zhags gser phur dgra la brdeg /
NK011(da)001:12618: chibs kyi snga long phyi long la //
NK011(da)001:12619: mi mgo rta mgo phru lu lu //
NK011(da)001:12620: brda ni mi 'phrod lho bal mo //
NK011(da)001:12621: skad ni mi go da ra'i skad //
NK011(da)001:12622: gsang ba'i spyugs pa kyu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:12623: gzugs ni mi ston lag brgya mo //
NK011(da)001:12624: tsha ba rong gi de byin mo //
NK011(da)001:12625: zhag mtsho sbrang mtsho mer ba'i nang //
NK011(da)001:12626: blon mo nag mo klong dgu ma //
NK011(da)001:12627: ye shes don rtogs gnyis med pas //
NK011(da)001:12628: khrag gi thig le 'bum gyis brgyan //
NK011(da)001:12629: sa bdag 'bum gyi khad dpon mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12630: de byin yul gyi phu shed na //
NK011(da)001:12631: khrag mtsho mer ba'i nang shed na //
NK011(da)001:12632: gza' rgyal mig dmar sprul nas gnas //
NK011(da)001:12633: jo mo de byin mthu mo che //
NK011(da)001:12634: blon mo klong dgu 'khor bcas kyis //
NK011(da)001:12635: nam phyed dus kyi mun pa la //
NK011(da)001:12636: skad cig yud la yul phur byin //
NK011(da)001:12637: gza' rgyal mig dmar sprul pa bsgral //
NK011(da)001:12638: de phyir gza' 'dul chen mo bya //
NK011(da)001:12639: sa bdag rgyal mo yal gam can //
NK011(da)001:12640: phur pa sgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:12641: sha khrag dmar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK011(da)001:12642: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12643: shu lan d+ha ri'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12645: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12646: nam ni tho rangs dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12647: mang yul se byin steng shed nas //
NK011(da)001:12648: khrag zhag mtsho mo mer ba na //
NK011(da)001:12649: sprul pa'i bswe mkhar smug po na //
NK011(da)001:12650: rdo rje bswe byin 'phrul mo che //
NK011(da)001:12651: sku mdog dmar nag 'bar ba la //
NK011(da)001:12652: khrag gi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK011(da)001:12653: ral pa re la phur pa re //
NK011(da)001:12654: gser gyi rdo rje thor tshugs brgyan //
NK011(da)001:12655: rna ba slang tsam lhebs se lheb //
NK011(da)001:12656: dngul gyi rna cha wangs se wang //
NK011(da)001:12657: dar nag lce'u phran cod pan 'phur //
NK011(da)001:12658: ba spu re zhing lcags kyu re //
NK011(da)001:12659: me lce dgu phreng sku yi rgyan //
NK011(da)001:12660: rma bya'i thul pa zha la la //
NK011(da)001:12661: dbang gi bswe khrab si li li //
NK011(da)001:12662: spyugs pa'i brda skad di ri ri //
NK011(da)001:12663: chibs su ri dwags bse la bcibs //
NK011(da)001:12664: chibs kyi snga long phyi long la //
NK011(da)001:12665: mi mgo rta mgo phru lu lu //
NK011(da)001:12666: btsan zhags seng phur dgral brdeg /
NK011(da)001:12667: brda ni mi 'phrod lho bal mo //
NK011(da)001:12668: gzugs ni mi ston lag brgya mo //
NK011(da)001:12669: mang yul se byin yul mdo na //
NK011(da)001:12670: sa bdag nag mo dam tshig can //
NK011(da)001:12671: lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu ma //
NK011(da)001:12672: mtshan mo dur khrod khyab par rgyu //
NK011(da)001:12673: stong gsum ma lus rjes kyis 'gengs //
NK011(da)001:12674: gdug pa'i dgra la ngu zhing 'drad //
NK011(da)001:12675: mche ba gnam lcags mtshon cha bsnol //
NK011(da)001:12676: sa bdag 'bum gyi khad dpon mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12677: se byin yul gyi phu shed na //
NK011(da)001:12678: btsan brag ser kha'i nang shed na //
NK011(da)001:12679: btsan gyi rgyal po zla ba gnas //
NK011(da)001:12680: jo mo se byin mthu mo che //
NK011(da)001:12681: blon po spyang mo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK011(da)001:12682: nam phyed dus kyi mun pa la //
NK011(da)001:12683: skad cig yud kyis yul phur phyir //
NK011(da)001:12684: btsan gyi rgyal po zla ba bsgral //
NK011(da)001:12685: de phyi btsan 'dul chen mo bya //
NK011(da)001:12686: sa bdag rgyal mo yal gam can //
NK011(da)001:12687: phur ba sgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:12688: sha khrag dmar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK011(da)001:12689: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12690: tsa mun d+ha ri'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12692: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12693: nam ni tho rangs dam can ma //
NK011(da)001:12694: snyen ma 'gram gyi phag byin gshongs //
NK011(da)001:12695: 'o ma'i mtsho mo mer ba na //
NK011(da)001:12696: sprul pa bswe mkhar smug po na //
NK011(da)001:12697: rdo rje phag byin mthu mo che //
NK011(da)001:12698: sku mdog dkar nag 'bar ba la //
NK011(da)001:12699: dung gi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK011(da)001:12700: ral pa re zhing phur pa re //
NK011(da)001:12701: phur pa'i lan phran khra la la //
NK011(da)001:12702: rna ba slang tsam lhebs se lheb //
NK011(da)001:12703: gser gyi rdo rjes thor tshugs brgyan //
NK011(da)001:12704: dar nag lce phran cod pan 'phur //
NK011(da)001:12705: dung gi rna cha wangs se wang //
NK011(da)001:12706: me lce dgu phreng sku yi rgyan //
NK011(da)001:12707: rma bya'i thul pa zha la la //
NK011(da)001:12708: dbang gi bswe khrab si li li //
NK011(da)001:12709: chibs su chu rta sngon po chibs //
NK011(da)001:12710: chibs kyi snga long phyi long la //
NK011(da)001:12711: mi mgo rta mgo phru lu lu //
NK011(da)001:12712: g.yu zhags g.yu phur dgra la 'phen //
NK011(da)001:12713: brda ni mi 'phrod lho bal mo //
NK011(da)001:12714: gzugs ni mi ston lag brgya mo //
NK011(da)001:12715: snye nam phag byin yul mdo na //
NK011(da)001:12716: mkha' la sprul pa'i g.yu mtsho na //
NK011(da)001:12717: sprul pa'i bswe mkhar smug po na //
NK011(da)001:12718: phag byin chen mo'i blon po ni //
NK011(da)001:12719: nag mo chen mo brang mig ma //
NK011(da)001:12720: mgo med brang na mig gis gang //
NK011(da)001:12721: brang gi 'og nas zhal gdangs pas //
NK011(da)001:12722: sdang ba'i dgra bgegs khyur mid byed //
NK011(da)001:12723: stong khams sprul pa nag mos 'gengs //
NK011(da)001:12724: sa bdag 'bum gyi khad dpon mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12725: snye nam phag byin yul phu nas //
NK011(da)001:12726: stong skyal bya ba'i yul phu na //
NK011(da)001:12727: mtsho yi dam pa ma dros na //
NK011(da)001:12728: klu yi rgyal po deng po gnas //
NK011(da)001:12729: jo mo phag byin mthu mo che //
NK011(da)001:12730: blon po brang mig 'khor bcas kyis //
NK011(da)001:12731: nam phyed dus kyi mun pa la //
NK011(da)001:12732: skad cig yud kyis yul phur byin //
NK011(da)001:12733: klu yi rgyal po deng po bsgral //
NK011(da)001:12734: de phyir klu 'dul chen mo bya //
NK011(da)001:12735: sa bdag rgyal mo yal gam can //
NK011(da)001:12736: phur pa sgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:12737: sha khrag dmar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK011(da)001:12738: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12739: dzah shar phyogs sgo nang dgra bgegs steng //
NK011(da)001:12740: dung gi skyes bu gdug pa can //
NK011(da)001:12741: sku mdog dkar po 'tsher ba la //
NK011(da)001:12742: g.yas na shel gri zangs yag bsnams //
NK011(da)001:12743: g.yon pa shel gyi phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12744: dgra bgegs snying la gzir zhing 'debs //
NK011(da)001:12745: chibs su seng ge dkar mo chibs //
NK011(da)001:12746: sku la spyang dkar slog pa gsol //
NK011(da)001:12747: 'khor du ging chen tshogs kyis bskor //
NK011(da)001:12748: dkar po 'bum gyi dmag dpon mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12749: khyod kyang phur pa'i srung ma ste //
NK011(da)001:12750: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12751: bcol pa'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12752: lho phyogs sgo nang dgra bgegs steng //
NK011(da)001:12753: lcags kyi skyes bu gdug pa can //
NK011(da)001:12754: sku mdog sngo nag 'bar ba la //
NK011(da)001:12755: g.yas pa lcags kyi ral gri 'phyar //
NK011(da)001:12757: chibs su lcags kyi spyang ki bcibs //
NK011(da)001:12758: sku la dar nag ber chen gsol //
NK011(da)001:12759: 'khor du bdud pho tshogs kyis bskor //
NK011(da)001:12760: nag po 'bum gyi dmag dpon mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12761: khyod kyang phur pa'i las mkhan te //
NK011(da)001:12762: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12763: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12764: nub phyogs sgo nang dgra bgegs steng //
NK011(da)001:12765: bswe yi skyes bu gdug pa can //
NK011(da)001:12766: sku mdog dmar nag 'bar ba la //
NK011(da)001:12767: g.yas pa zangs kyi ral gri 'phyar //
NK011(da)001:12768: g.yon pa zangs kyi phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:12769: chibs su bswe rta dmar po bcibs //
NK011(da)001:12770: sku la dbang gi bswe khrab gsol //
NK011(da)001:12771: 'khor du bdud btsan tshogs kyis bskor //
NK011(da)001:12772: dmar nag 'bum gyi dmag dpon mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12773: khyod kyang phur pa'i srung ma ste //
NK011(da)001:12774: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12775: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12776: byang phyogs sgo nang dgra bgegs steng //
NK011(da)001:12777: ta ki nag po rab 'jigs pa //
NK011(da)001:12778: sku mdog ljang nag 'bar ba la //
NK011(da)001:12779: g.yas pa gri gug dgra srog gcod //
NK011(da)001:12781: chibs su lcags spyang sngon po bcings //
NK011(da)001:12782: sku la lcags kyi go khrab gsol //
NK011(da)001:12783: bshan pa pho mo'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK011(da)001:12784: las mkhan 'bum gyi dmag dpon mdzad //
NK011(da)001:12785: khyod kyang phur pa'i srung ma ste //
NK011(da)001:12786: sha khrag gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:12787: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12788: srid pa phur par bdag sgrub kyi //
NK011(da)001:12789: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12790: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12791: dam bcas bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12792: dpal gyi bka' nyan las byed ma //
NK011(da)001:12793: ma tshogs dbang phyug nyer brgyad kyi //
NK011(da)001:12795: ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa yang //
NK011(da)001:12796: g.yo sgyu med cing gus ldan pas //
NK011(da)001:12797: sems kyis blangs te spyi bo yi //
NK011(da)001:12798: gtsug tu bkur bar bya'o zhes //
NK011(da)001:12799: de skad khyed kyi zhal bzhes pas //
NK011(da)001:12800: dpal gyi bka' bzhin bdag sgrub kyi //
NK011(da)001:12801: 'dir byon sha khrag gtor ma longs //
NK011(da)001:12802: bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:12803: ces bskul zhing gser skyems dang rak+ta gtor la /
NK011(da)001:12804: gdab pa la sogs pa'i las bya'o //
NK011(da)001:12808: // rdo gtor dang zlog pa spu gri'i 'khor lo bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:12809: dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)001:12812: sde brgyad kyi gnod pa dang /
NK011(da)001:12814: tha na gcan gzan gdug pa dang /
NK011(da)001:12815: sbrang bu yan chad kha 'ching ba dang /
NK011(da)001:12816: zlog pa spu gri'i 'khor lo 'di ni /
NK011(da)001:12818: nyi ma dang gza' skar ngan pa'i dus dang /
NK011(da)001:12819: thog ser 'bab pa'i dus rnams su bya'o //
NK011(da)001:12820: shin tu gnyan pas gang rung rung du mi bya'o //
NK011(da)001:12821: rang lha'i nga rgyal gyis sgra drag pos bazla'o //
NK011(da)001:12822: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u h'u h'u /
NK011(da)001:12823: bdud pra m+aa ra ya rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:12824: kha la dza ma li rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:12825: r+aa tsa dun ling shag rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:12826: shig shig dum dum rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:12827: tshal pa tshal pa rbad khram khram b+h+yo b+h+yo rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:12833: rang nub mo gan rkyal du nyal la sor mo sprad /
NK011(da)001:12834: kha gdangs la bzlas pas bzlog pa dang /
NK011(da)001:12835: 'gro dus su sdigs mdzub 'phyar la sngags bzlas pas bzlog pa dang /
NK011(da)001:12836: ldang tshe skad sgra gdong tshugs byas te bzlog pa dang /
NK011(da)001:12837: mtshon cha thogs te 'debs tshul byas nas bzlog pa dang /
NK011(da)001:12838: yungs kar la basngagasa nas phyogs bcur 'thor zhing phur pa yang phyogs bcur 'dril /
NK011(da)001:12839: lid+ga la btab nas bzlog pa dang lnga ni gang byed kyang rgyun khyer yin pas go sla'o //
NK011(da)001:12840: khyad par rdo zor gyi bzlog pa ni /
NK011(da)001:12845: phur kha bzlog pa la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:12846: re ba'am phub bam sla nga'i nang du brag rgod
NK011(da)001:12847: kyi rdo dmar nag gang rung blangs la re re
NK011(da)001:12848: la khrag gis b+h+yo b+h+yo zlog zlog bri /
NK011(da)001:12849: dbus su zur gsum che ba gcig bzhag /
NK011(da)001:12850: gzhan rnams mthar spungs la rus pa dang /
NK011(da)001:12852: +aahmh'u gis ru tra'i ming rus mtshon cha 'bar ba'i
NK011(da)001:12853: khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil nas skye bar bsam ste
NK011(da)001:12855: phud gtor dpang gzug bden pa ba dar la /
NK011(da)001:12856: rdo mtshon cha'i phung po la me 'bar bas dgra bgegs thal bar brlag par bsam ste /
NK011(da)001:12857: pha rol gyi nus pa dang /
NK011(da)001:12858: rmi ltas kyi cho 'phrul dang bstun nas /
NK011(da)001:12861: gcig sogs nyams dang bstun nas sngags bzlas /
NK011(da)001:12862: dgra bgegs kyi phyogs su 'phang ngo //
NK011(da)001:12863: gnad la dbab dus dam tshig can 'gas gdong bzlog drag po 'ur 'don byas te /
NK011(da)001:12864: dgra bgegs kyi lid+ga la 'phang ba'am /
NK011(da)001:12865: grogs la bskor te phyogs su 'phangs /
NK011(da)001:12869: gnod 'tshe thams cad hur thum du bzlog par the tshom med do //
NK011(da)001:12871: bswe yi lha mo bzhi'i sgrub thabs srog tig zab pa dmar nag bzhugs so //
NK011(da)001:12872: slob dpon pad+ma sam+b+ha wa rdo rje thod phreng gis
NK011(da)001:12873: sgrub thabs kyi man ngag tu bka' stsal ba 'di
NK011(da)001:12874: / sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:12876: rdo rje gnod sbyin ma ro tsa'i ngan sngags /
NK011(da)001:12877: bswe yi lha mo bzhi'i sgrub thabs 'di ni /
NK011(da)001:12878: gtan tshigs ci'i phyir 'byung ba ni /
NK011(da)001:12879: slob dpon pad+ma sam+b+ha wa rdo rje thod phreng gi sku tshe'i rig 'dzin brnyes kyang /
NK011(da)001:12880: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub ma brnyes nas /
NK011(da)001:12881: bal yul yang le shod du lo gsum du bsgrub nas /
NK011(da)001:12882: dge bsnyen ma nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
NK011(da)001:12885: lha dang klu la sogs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:12888: lha ma yin rnams kyis dgongs pa la bar chad gtong ste /
NK011(da)001:12889: nam mkha' la char sprin ma chags /
NK011(da)001:12890: lo gsum du char ma babs pa las /
NK011(da)001:12891: +aa tsa ra'i dgongs pa la 'di su'i yin te /
NK011(da)001:12892: 'di nga'i dgongs pa la bar chad btang bar 'dug ste /
NK011(da)001:12894: bal po kun da kun gzhi dang /
NK011(da)001:12895: bal mo ji la ji sa gnyis la /
NK011(da)001:12896: gser phye gser gyi bre gang bskur nas /
NK011(da)001:12897: rgya gar gyi yul du phur bu'i tan+t+ra zhu ru btang ba las /
NK011(da)001:12898: mtha'i mon bu dkor dad che bas /
NK011(da)001:12899: gser phul bas rab tu mnyes te /
NK011(da)001:12900: slar la phur bu'i tan+t+ra khur theg tshad gnyis bskur te btang /
NK011(da)001:12901: de bal yul yang le shod du byon pa tsam
NK011(da)001:12902: gyis de'i byin gyis brlabs kyis gnas la sprin chags
NK011(da)001:12905: nags tshal skam po kun sngo lhub kyis song ba las /
NK011(da)001:12906: de nas pad+ma sam+b+ha wa sa /
NK011(da)001:12908: lta ba byi to dang gcig /
NK011(da)001:12910: las byang kha tshar dang gsum btus te /
NK011(da)001:12912: rgya gar yul du pan+di ta mkhas pa lnga brgya'i spyan sngar zhu tig la gshegs par chas /
NK011(da)001:12913: smad khams kyi rgyal mo'i yul /
NK011(da)001:12914: tsha ba tsha shod du bya ba me tog dgun na skyes pa'i drung du /
NK011(da)001:12915: chu mig byang chub ris su byon tsa na /
NK011(da)001:12916: +aa tsa ra nyid skur yur thum thum mdzad nas /
NK011(da)001:12917: dbu la yug gi byugs pas /
NK011(da)001:12918: bur bur bo gcig zin nas dbu zhwa'i nang du bstsal nas kha rgyas bsdams te /
NK011(da)001:12919: dbu zhwa sngas 'og tu bstsal nas gzims pa las /
NK011(da)001:12920: nangs par dbu zhwa kha phye nas gzigs tsa na /
NK011(da)001:12921: bu mo khyad par gyis legs pa mi'i bu mo dang mi 'dra lha'i sras mo 'dra ba /
NK011(da)001:12922: bzang sdug la 'od chags pa bzhi 'byung nas /
NK011(da)001:12923: +aa tsa ras khyod rnams su zhig yin zhes bka' stsal bas /
NK011(da)001:12924: bu mo rnams kyis smras pa /
NK011(da)001:12925: bdag cag ni me tog dgun na skyes pa'i bdag mo bzhi lags te /
NK011(da)001:12926: sa bdag chen mo da ra tsa ba'i lcugs len srog gi mnga' bdag mo bzhi lags te /
NK011(da)001:12927: rgyud bswe rgyud gsang ba yang gter gyi nang nas
NK011(da)001:12928: bswe'i lha mo nyis brgya lnga bcu zhig bzhugs pa'i
NK011(da)001:12929: nang nas / de'i nang nas grangs 'dams pa bcu
NK011(da)001:12930: gnyis bod yul du 'ong ba ni bdag cag lags
NK011(da)001:12931: nang nas / te / nangs kyi bu mo da ra tsa ba'i srog len ma /
NK011(da)001:12932: de'i 'og ma da ra tsa ba'i srog skems ma /
NK011(da)001:12933: de'i 'og ma da ra tsa ba'i srog gcod ma /
NK011(da)001:12934: de'i 'og ma da ra tsa ba'i srog 'jib ma /
NK011(da)001:12935: phyi'i 'khor brgyad ni rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad la dbang byed de /
NK011(da)001:12936: yo rol chen po gnas te /
NK011(da)001:12937: bdag cag las dbang che ba ni med de /
NK011(da)001:12938: ma mo thams cad kyi rgyal mo /
NK011(da)001:12939: lha 'dre thams cad kyi ni jo mo lags te /
NK011(da)001:12940: sngar yang skye rgu thams cad kyi srog la dbang byed pa'i mthu mo che lags te /
NK011(da)001:12941: da yang mi phyugs mang po'i tshe srog la dbang
NK011(da)001:12942: byed pa'i mthu mo cher dbang bskur du gsol zhes
NK011(da)001:12943: zhus pa dang / +aa tsa ras bka' bstsal pa /
NK011(da)001:12944: sngar yang skye rgu thams cad kyi tshe srog la dbang byed pa ma legs /
NK011(da)001:12945: da yang tshe srog la dbang byed par dbang mi bskur gyis /
NK011(da)001:12946: bdag gis sku tshe'i rig 'dzin brnyes kyang /
NK011(da)001:12947: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin ma brnyes nas /
NK011(da)001:12948: bal yul yang le shod du bsgrubs pa las /
NK011(da)001:12949: dge bsnyen nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
NK011(da)001:12950: tshangs dang brgya byin la sogs pas bar chad btang ba yang bzlas /
NK011(da)001:12951: de dag 'dul ba'i don ched du phur bu'i tan+t+ra zhur btang ba'i lo rgyus bshad nas /
NK011(da)001:12952: khyed dang nga 'phrad pa ni nga'i ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba yang yin /
NK011(da)001:12953: lung tshad du phyin pa yang yin /
NK011(da)001:12954: sdebs legs pa'i don yang yin te /
NK011(da)001:12955: khyed rnams ni phur bu'i srung mar dbang bskur ro //
NK011(da)001:12957: rtags kyi phyag rgya ru spyi bo'i gtsug tu gser gyi rdo rje bzhag /
NK011(da)001:12958: lag tu rdo rje phur bu byin nas /
NK011(da)001:12960: rdo rje ya sman 'phrul mo che //
NK011(da)001:12961: rdo rje bswe sman dbang mo che //
NK011(da)001:12962: rdo rje de sman rtsal mo che //
NK011(da)001:12963: rdo rje phag sman mthu mo che //
NK011(da)001:12964: zhes rdo rje'i ming btags te /
NK011(da)001:12965: cig car dkyus su stsal te /
NK011(da)001:12966: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab bya ba dang sbyar te /
NK011(da)001:12967: phur bu mgo gzhug las rtags 'byin pa ni 'dir thug ste /
NK011(da)001:12968: de lta bu'i don la phur bu srog gi chan pa zhes kyang 'di ka la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:12969: bswe mo snying zan ma zhes kyang 'di ka la bya'o //
NK011(da)001:12970: mthu che ches nas yul so sor bzhag go //
NK011(da)001:12971: de yan chad ni byung khung dang gleng gazhi'o //
NK011(da)001:12972: de yi dkyil 'khor ci ltar bya ba ni /
NK011(da)001:12973: dkyil 'khor ni bang rim bzhi bya ste /
NK011(da)001:12974: dbus zur gsum nag po hom khung can du bya ste /
NK011(da)001:12975: de'i phyi rim zla gam dmar po gsum gyis bskor bar bya'o //
NK011(da)001:12976: de'i phyi rim la sgo bzhi dang bar khyams dod /
NK011(da)001:12981: bar khyams bzhi ka ser por bya'o //
NK011(da)001:12982: de yang sgrub pa'i rten bca' ba ni /
NK011(da)001:12983: smyug ma tshigs pa gcig khrag gis byug la /
NK011(da)001:12984: bya rgod kyi sgro rtsa'i smyu gu na yar smyug ma'i rtse mo da dgos bcug la /
NK011(da)001:12985: de dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi hom khung gi khar gzug /
NK011(da)001:12986: lcags phur sor bcu'am brgyad pa gcig smyug ma'i rtse ru gzug /
NK011(da)001:12987: seng ldeng gi phur bu sor brgyad pa gsum zla gam gsum la dgod /
NK011(da)001:12988: phur bu sor brgyad pa bzhi sgo bzhi la yang bkod /
NK011(da)001:12989: bswe'i lha mo chen mo bzhi'i sku ni /
NK011(da)001:12990: dbus kyi smyug ma'i tshigs dang po la btags la bzhugs su gsol lo //
NK011(da)001:12991: de nas ru skyogs bzhi dam rdzas bshams pa ni /
NK011(da)001:12992: ba men gyi rwa gcig gi nang du /
NK011(da)001:12993: sbrang rtsi dang khrag dang snying sna tshogs bstsal /
NK011(da)001:12994: dkyil 'khor gyi bang rim dang po'i hom gyi zur gcig la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:12995: bswe phor gcig gi nang du mar khu khrag dang snying sna tshogs bstsal zla gam gcig la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:12996: dngul phor gcig gi nang du zhag dang tshil bu dang khrag dang snying sna tshogs bstsal la /
NK011(da)001:12997: de yang zla gam gcig la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:12998: mdzo'i rwa co gcig gi nang du 'o ma dang khrag dang snying sna tshogs bstsal la /
NK011(da)001:12999: de yang zla gam gcig la bzhag go //
NK011(da)001:13000: skyogs gzhan med kyang ba men gyi rwa gcig med
NK011(da)001:13001: du yang mi rung ste ru skyogs la spyan drangs
NK011(da)001:13002: dgos so // yang na gzas pa po'i ming rus bris la /
NK011(da)001:13003: ra rog po gcig gi sker btags la /
NK011(da)001:13004: ra de dkyil 'khor gyi 'gram du brtod la /
NK011(da)001:13005: gzas pa po'i dmigs pa'i rten de la baca'o //
NK011(da)001:13006: de nas ra bsgral nas snying phyungs la /
NK011(da)001:13007: da ci'i ming byang de snying gi rtsa ba'i sbu gu ru bcug ste /
NK011(da)001:13009: de nas ra'i mgo bo nas lce lkog mar drangs la /
NK011(da)001:13010: snying ra mgo'i khar bcug la /
NK011(da)001:13011: ra mgo dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi hom khung du gzhug /
NK011(da)001:13012: phags pa dkyil 'khor gyi 'gram du brgyangs la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:13013: ra med na ra rog po'i sog pa g.yas pa la sngon dmar gyi bcings la /
NK011(da)001:13014: gzas pa po'i ming rus dang gzugs bris la /
NK011(da)001:13015: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi hom khung du re ba gcig bting la /
NK011(da)001:13016: de'i steng du thal chen gyis hom gru gsum gcig bris la /
NK011(da)001:13017: de'i steng du lid+ga sngon dmar gyis bkyigs la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:13019: bswe phor gcig gi nang du /
NK011(da)001:13023: rta khrag mi khrag sna tshogs pa bstsal la /
NK011(da)001:13024: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi hom khung gi zur gcig la bzhag /
NK011(da)001:13025: de yang mon mo mched bzhi'i thugs dam ni /
NK011(da)001:13026: bya nag mo'am lug nag mos thugs dam bskang ngo //
NK011(da)001:13027: yang na bya nag mo'am lug nag mo spyi dkar la 'ben bcas la /
NK011(da)001:13029: rtags phyin nas thugs dam bskang /
NK011(da)001:13030: rtags phyungs nas la mor ma bskang na /
NK011(da)001:13031: sgrub pa po nyid kyi tshe la bar chad 'ong /
NK011(da)001:13032: 'khor du yang rims nad 'bebs pas le lo mi bya bar la mor gtang rag btang ngo //
NK011(da)001:13033: de nas dang por bdag nyid kyang chas su 'jug ste /
NK011(da)001:13035: dbu la dar sngon po bcings /
NK011(da)001:13037: lag pa g.yas pa'i mkhrig ma man chad khrag gis byugs la /
NK011(da)001:13038: sle'u nag brdab cing dpang gzug go //
NK011(da)001:13039: de yang dregs pa mthu bo che thams cad kyi yang gshed ni gshin rje yin pas /
NK011(da)001:13040: bdag nyid gshin rje'i rgyal po ya ma r+aa dza bsgom mo //
NK011(da)001:13041: der yang bal mo mched bzhi yang bsgom zhing spyan drangs 'tshal te /
NK011(da)001:13042: bswe mo snying zan ma bzhi'i rtsa ba'i sngags 'di bzlas /
NK011(da)001:13046: ya ma tsit+ta h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /

NK011(da)001:13049: khros pas mon mo nag mo rna cha can bzhi
NK011(da)001:13050: ru nag rug gis song bar bsgom par mthong ste
NK011(da)001:13051: / de yang bswe'i lha mo bzhi'i sku mdog phyag mtshan dang /
NK011(da)001:13052: chibs dang rol par bcas te bsgom pa ni /

NK011(da)001:13054: spyan gsum khro tshul ston pa /

NK011(da)001:13060: sku la mdzes byed rma bya'i thul pa can /

NK011(da)001:13332: skad ni mi mthun da ra'i skad //
NK011(da)001:13333: gsang ba'i spyugs pa su ru ru //
NK011(da)001:13334: pho nyar srin po'i bu mo 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:13335: rol du khyi mo nag mo gser mig khrid //
NK011(da)001:13336: gdug byed ni dbang du bsdud //
NK011(da)001:13338: thugs kyi ni sprul pa yis //
NK011(da)001:13340: ma thogs ni drag tu khug /
NK011(da)001:13341: tsa mun da ri da tshur byon //
NK011(da)001:13342: rdo rje phur bu'i srung mar dam bcas shing //
NK011(da)001:13343: phur bu bsgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:13344: sha khrag dmar gyi mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:13345: bdag gis bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:13347: klu yi bu mo snye nam phug nas bzhengs //
NK011(da)001:13348: rdo rje phag byin mthu mo che //
NK011(da)001:13349: 'o ma'i mtsho la gnas bcas shing //
NK011(da)001:13350: phag byin chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:13351: sku mdog dmar mdangs chen mo la //
NK011(da)001:13352: zhal gsum spyan dgu phyag bzhi ma //
NK011(da)001:13353: g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje'i phyag mtshan ni //
NK011(da)001:13354: bswe yi rnge'u chung brdung zhing 'khrol //
NK011(da)001:13355: g.yas kyi 'og ma'i phyag mtshan ni //
NK011(da)001:13357: g.yon gyi dang po'i phyag mtshan ni //
NK011(da)001:13358: mi yi snying dang rgyu ma'i mgo nas za //
NK011(da)001:13359: g.yon gyi 'og ma'i phyag mtshan ni //
NK011(da)001:13361: zhal gsum ni rngams la brjid //
NK011(da)001:13362: spyan dgu ni sdang mig khro tshul can //
NK011(da)001:13365: mthing gi ral pa sha ra ra //
NK011(da)001:13366: ral pa re zhing phur bu re //
NK011(da)001:13367: phur bu'i lan phran khra la la //
NK011(da)001:13368: spyi gtsug gser gyi rdo rje'i thor tshugs can //
NK011(da)001:13369: dar nag lce'u phran cod pan pu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:13370: dung gi rna cha wangs se wang //
NK011(da)001:13371: ba spu re zhing lcags kyu re //
NK011(da)001:13372: me lce dgu phreng sku yi rgyan //
NK011(da)001:13373: mdzes byed rma bya'i thul pa zha la la //
NK011(da)001:13374: dbang gi bswe khrab si li li //
NK011(da)001:13375: chibs su chu rta sngon po bcibs //
NK011(da)001:13376: chibs kyi snga long phyi long la //
NK011(da)001:13377: mi mgo rta mgo phru lu lu //
NK011(da)001:13378: khyod ni klu 'dul chen mo ste //
NK011(da)001:13379: klu 'dul chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK011(da)001:13380: brda ni mi 'phrod lho bal mo //
NK011(da)001:13381: skad ni mi mthun da ra'i skad //
NK011(da)001:13382: gsang ba'i spyugs pa su ru ru //
NK011(da)001:13383: pho nyar gshin rje'i bu mo 'gyed //
NK011(da)001:13384: rol du khyi mo nag mo shel mig khrid //
NK011(da)001:13385: kun la de ni mnga' mdzad ma //
NK011(da)001:13386: klu rnams ni dbang du bsdud //
NK011(da)001:13387: bgegs la ni gong zhags thob //
NK011(da)001:13388: thugs kyi ni sprul pa yis //
NK011(da)001:13389: dgra bo'i ni snying nas drongs //
NK011(da)001:13390: ma thogs ni drag tu khug /
NK011(da)001:13391: kang ka da ri da tshur byon //
NK011(da)001:13392: rdo rje phur bu'i srung mar dam bcas pa //
NK011(da)001:13393: phur bu bsgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)001:13394: sha khrag dmar gyi mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK011(da)001:13395: bdag gis bcol ba'i las rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NK011(da)001:13396: sman phud dang dmar gyi ar+g+ham sbreng zhing phrin las bcol /
NK011(da)001:13397: bstab pa la sogs pa bya'o //
NK011(da)001:13398: gsang ba'i lha mo mched sde bzhi //
NK011(da)001:13399: rgya gar yul nas byon tsa na //
NK011(da)001:13400: dgra bcom chen mo bzhi ru bgyis //
NK011(da)001:13401: sku stod dar gyi chos gos gsol //
NK011(da)001:13402: sku smad dar khra'i sham thabs can //
NK011(da)001:13403: phyag na seng ldeng phur bu 'dril //
NK011(da)001:13404: zhal nas phur bu'i 'dzab bzlas pas //
NK011(da)001:13405: mgrin par glu len kyu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:13406: phur bu'i dbang bskur phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:13407: mon yul da ra'i gting nas byon tsa na //
NK011(da)001:13408: mon mo chen mo bzhi ru bgyis //
NK011(da)001:13409: lus la man tri'i za ber gsol //
NK011(da)001:13410: rna ba sge'u tsam re re la //
NK011(da)001:13411: mu tig chun 'phyang pu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:13412: rna cha sil snyan khra la la //
NK011(da)001:13413: lag na gsang ba'i mchog phur 'dril //
NK011(da)001:13414: zhal nas phur bu'i 'dzab bzlas shing //
NK011(da)001:13415: mgrin par klu len kyu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:13416: phur pa'i dbang bskur phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:13417: tsha ba rong nas byon tsa na //
NK011(da)001:13418: bswe yi lha mo mdog bzang ma //
NK011(da)001:13419: zangs kyi lha mo rdzu 'phrul can //
NK011(da)001:13420: gser gyi lha mo 'od zer can //
NK011(da)001:13421: lcags kyi lha mo dgra 'dul ma //
NK011(da)001:13422: lag na lcags kyi phur pa 'dril //
NK011(da)001:13423: zhal nas phur pa'i 'dzab bzlas shing //
NK011(da)001:13424: mgrin par glu len kyu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:13425: phur bu'i dbang bskur phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:13426: bod yul dbus nas bzhengs tsam na //
NK011(da)001:13427: na chung sgegs ma bzhi ru bgyis //
NK011(da)001:13428: lus la dar dang ber gyis brgyan //
NK011(da)001:13429: lag na tsher shing phur bu 'dril //
NK011(da)001:13430: zhal nas phur bu'i 'dzab bzlas shing //
NK011(da)001:13431: mgrin par glu len kyu ru ru //
NK011(da)001:13432: phur pa'i dbang bskur phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:13433: nam gyi phar phyed tshul phyed na //
NK011(da)001:13434: rnal 'byor sgrub pa byed pa la //
NK011(da)001:13435: b+ha ga gsang ba'i mdangs 'bul la //
NK011(da)001:13436: phur bu'i dbang bskur phrin las mdzod //
NK011(da)001:13438: tsi bi ri tsakra sa na tshal pa /
NK011(da)001:13439: a n+ri tri m+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:13440: ad+gu sha dzah dzah n+aa ga ma ra tsa tshal pa a n+ri tri m+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:13441: ang+gu sha dzahdzah shu shu rag sha ya tshal pa /
NK011(da)001:13442: a n+ri tri m+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:13443: ang+gu dzahdzah a be sha tshal pa /
NK011(da)001:13444: a n+ri tri m+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:13445: ang+gu sha dzahdzah zhes bzlas shing sle'u nag gam /
NK011(da)001:13446: bud med kyi zhabs mas brdab bo //
NK011(da)001:13447: de nas thun gyi sngags rdzogs pa dang /
NK011(da)001:13448: sngags 'di bzlas la phur bu gdab bo //
NK011(da)001:13450: badz+ra mu ka mu ti gri na mu ti gri na /
NK011(da)001:13451: ka bi r+aa tsa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13454: phata me ri kun da ri /
NK011(da)001:13455: bam thums khrag ti smrar phata phata rbad rbad /
NK011(da)001:13466: ces rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad la brnag cing gdab bo //
NK011(da)001:13467: ra'i mgo bo dang snying la /
NK011(da)001:13468: de nas cho gas phur bu btab nas /
NK011(da)001:13469: ra mgo dang ra snying ra lpags su bstums la /
NK011(da)001:13470: stag rgya bo'i mkhar mnan te /
NK011(da)001:13472: de'i nang du ra lpags gzhug /
NK011(da)001:13473: ra lpags thog tu gtor ma kun blug go //
NK011(da)001:13474: de nas sas legs par byib bo //
NK011(da)001:13475: de'i steng du phrin las rnam bzhi'i bro brdung ngo //
NK011(da)001:13476: bswe'i lha mo'i srog tig gi sgrub pa rdzogs so //
NK011(da)001:13478: // rdo rje phur pa las ngan sngags drug gi 'khor
NK011(da)001:13479: lo srog gi spu gri bzhugs so sangs rgyas gling
NK011(da)001:13480: pa'o bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la
NK011(da)001:13481: na mo ngan sngags drug gi 'khor lo 'di de
NK011(da)001:13482: yang rtsa ba las gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar
NK011(da)001:13483: gyis zhes pas gang zhig dbye bar 'dod pas bya
NK011(da)001:13484: rog dang 'ug pa'i lpags pa la de nyid kyi
NK011(da)001:13485: rak+ta dang dur khrod kyi sol ba sbyar bas 'khor
NK011(da)001:13486: lo rtsibs brgyad pa tshul dang tshul ma yin pa
NK011(da)001:13487: bris la lte bar k+ai la ya dang gang dbye
NK011(da)001:13488: bar bya ba bri'o bya rog rtsibs la ha sa
NK011(da)001:13489: ya ra na hri d+ha ya na zhes pas sngags
NK011(da)001:13490: bkod thabs gong ras la gtogs shig grogs dang bral
NK011(da)001:13491: bar gyis zhes phyogs rang phyogs ma yin par bris
NK011(da)001:13492: la 'khor lo ltos sbyar te tshon skud kyis bcings
NK011(da)001:13493: la yugs sa'i thod par bcug ste man+dala gyi dbus
NK011(da)001:13494: su bzhag la sgrub pa gzhung bzhin du bya zhing
NK011(da)001:13495: rdzas gu gul la sogs pas bdug ste badz+ra k+ai
NK011(da)001:13496: li k+ai la ya che ge mo m+aa ra ya
NK011(da)001:13497: ha sa ya ra hri d+aa ya ni h'u phata
NK011(da)001:13498: ces pas rtags dang mtshan ma ma byung gi bar
NK011(da)001:13499: du bzlas so mchod dang gtor ma'i phrin las la
NK011(da)001:13500: sogs pa gzhung bzhin bya'o 'khor lo zhal gsal la
NK011(da)001:13501: sbyin sreg byas te thal ba thod par blugs la
NK011(da)001:13502: brag dang chu 'thab sar sbas na 'jig rten gyi
NK011(da)001:13503: khams kyang g.yo zhing 'byed par 'gyur na gzhan phran
NK011(da)001:13504: bu la ni lta ci smos kyang 'tshal sngags mas
NK011(da)001:13505: ldog tu bya gal te mdza' bar 'dod na 'khor
NK011(da)001:13506: lo phyir bskor zhing sngags khri bzlas te 'o mas
NK011(da)001:13507: bkrus la zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bya zhing ngan sngags
NK011(da)001:13508: kyi sbyor ba las thar bar gyur cig ces brjod
NK011(da)001:13509: pas grol bar 'gyur ro sa ma ya rgya rgya
NK011(da)001:13510: rgya kha tham yang rtsa ba las phob cig rnam
NK011(da)001:13511: par gzir bar gyis zhes 'byung ste gang zhig gzugs
NK011(da)001:13512: la dbab par 'dod na mdze pho'i khrag gis 'khor
NK011(da)001:13513: lo tshul dang tshul ma yin pa gong bzhin du
NK011(da)001:13514: bris la rtsibs la +aa be sha +aa be sha
NK011(da)001:13515: ya bkod de gong ras la 'phyong bris kha sbyar
NK011(da)001:13516: te bud med mdze mo'i thod par bcug la gong
NK011(da)001:13517: bzhin du sbyin sreg bya ste sngar bzhin du la'i
NK011(da)001:13518: 'og gam rang gi mal 'og tu mnan na lag
NK011(da)001:13519: na rdo rje yang gzugs la phebs shing dbang du
NK011(da)001:13520: gyur na gzhan la lta ci smos gal te gtong
NK011(da)001:13521: bar 'dod na snga ma ltar bya'o sa ma ya
NK011(da)001:13522: yang rtsa ba las zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par
NK011(da)001:13523: chings zhes 'byung bas gang zhig bcing bar 'dod na
NK011(da)001:13524: gdug pa can gyi lto ba la ra khrag gis
NK011(da)001:13525: 'khor lo phyogs dang phyogs mtshams ma yin pa gong
NK011(da)001:13526: bzhin bris la rtsibs la ch+gee mo sh+r+ai krin a
NK011(da)001:13527: na ya h'u phata ces pa bris te gong ras
NK011(da)001:13528: la yang 'phyong bri zhing 'khor lo kha sbyor zhing
NK011(da)001:13529: spyang dar ma'i thod par bcug la tshon sna lnga
NK011(da)001:13530: dang khyi spu'i skud pas bshad du bcug la sngags
NK011(da)001:13531: sgrub la sogs pa phrin las gzhung bzhin rtags thems
NK011(da)001:13532: pa dang gong ltar lam rgya gram du mnan byi
NK011(da)001:13533: tri pa tra yang 'ching bar 'gyur na gzhan lta
NK011(da)001:13534: ci smos 'grol bar 'dod na snga ma bzhin no
NK011(da)001:13535: sa ma ya rgya rgya rgya yang rtsa ba las
NK011(da)001:13536: rings par khug la smrar chug cig ces 'byung bas
NK011(da)001:13537: gang zhig smra bar 'dod na mngal khrag dang dug
NK011(da)001:13538: dang rda du ra dang kim ni ka chang dang
NK011(da)001:13539: ra khrag rnams la snag tsha bya mi rus sam
NK011(da)001:13540: dug shing gi smyu gus rlung gi dal gyi dbus
NK011(da)001:13541: su 'khor lo snga ma bzhin du bri rtsi bas
NK011(da)001:13542: la dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya zhes
NK011(da)001:13543: pa bris nas phyogs dang phyogs ma yin pa'i 'khor
NK011(da)001:13544: lo gnyis kha sbyar la spre'u'i thod par bcug ste
NK011(da)001:13545: snga ma bzhin thal ba blugs nas dur khrod dang
NK011(da)001:13546: rkang gcig pa'i sar sbas nas lag na rdo rje
NK011(da)001:13547: yang khrag tu skyug cing smra bar byed na gzhan
NK011(da)001:13548: lta ci smos 'grol bar 'dod na snga ma bzhin
NK011(da)001:13549: no sa ma ya rgya rgya rgya yang rtsa ba
NK011(da)001:13550: las lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du rlog ces pas
NK011(da)001:13551: gang zhig gsod par 'dod na dur khrod kyi ras
NK011(da)001:13552: la dug dang khrag dang tsha ba gsum dang ldong
NK011(da)001:13553: ros dang ske tshe la sogs pa dur khrod kyi
NK011(da)001:13554: sol ba dang sbyar la mtshon cha'i 'khor lo bri
NK011(da)001:13555: rtsibs la ch+gee mo ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya
NK011(da)001:13556: zhes pa gong bzhin du phyogs dang phyogs mtshams ma
NK011(da)001:13557: yin par bris la mu ran gyi nang du mtshon
NK011(da)001:13558: cha'i sngags a brum zhes pa dang m+aa ra yas
NK011(da)001:13559: bskor ba bri'o des nas 'khor lo lto sbyar la
NK011(da)001:13560: tshon skud kyis bcings te rabs chad kyi thod par
NK011(da)001:13561: bcug la gong bzhin thal ba yang blugs la dur
NK011(da)001:13562: khrod du sbas na tshangs pa yang srog 'phrog par
NK011(da)001:13563: byed na gzhan lta ci smos gal te gso bar
NK011(da)001:13564: 'dod na sngags sum khri bzlas shing bdag gi thugs
NK011(da)001:13565: ka'i ye shes sems dpa' las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK011(da)001:13566: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul
NK011(da)001:13567: bas sku gsung thugs las bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun byung
NK011(da)001:13568: bas gzas pa po gso bar bsam zhing 'khor lo
NK011(da)001:13569: 'o mas bkrus la thal ba chu la dor te
NK011(da)001:13570: ngan sngags kyi sbyor ba las grol bar gyur cig
NK011(da)001:13571: ces brjod pas grol bar 'gyur ro sa ma ya
NK011(da)001:13572: rgya rgya rgya yang rtsa ba las badz+ra yak+sha kro
NK011(da)001:13573: ta kh+aa hi zhes pas gang dag zhal du bstab
NK011(da)001:13574: par 'dod na me'i 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad gnod sbyin
NK011(da)001:13575: 'jigs pa kha gdangs pa bris te lte bar k+ai
NK011(da)001:13576: la ya dang gang bstab par bya ba bri rtsibs
NK011(da)001:13577: la b+hin+d+ha ya b+hin+d+ha ya kh+aa hi zhes phyogs dang
NK011(da)001:13578: phyogs ma yin par bris te phyi nang gi mu
NK011(da)001:13579: ran la badz+ra yak+sha kro ta kh+aa hi zhes pa
NK011(da)001:13580: dang / kha tam zhes pas bskor 'khor lo gnyis
NK011(da)001:13581: lto sbyar la dril te tshon skud kyis bcings sha
NK011(da)001:13582: khrag sna tshogs kyi gtor ma chen por bcug la
NK011(da)001:13583: man+dala gyi dbus su bzhag nas sgrub pa gzhung bzhin
NK011(da)001:13584: bya ste dus drug dang bcas pa la btab la
NK011(da)001:13585: rtags thon pa dang 'khor lo zhal bsrungs te sha
NK011(da)001:13586: khrag mang po'i gtor ma dang bsreg rdzas sna tshogs
NK011(da)001:13587: dang bcas par gdug pa can gyi shing la me
NK011(da)001:13588: sbar te sbyin sreg stong byas na snod bcud thams
NK011(da)001:13589: cad kyang zhal du btab par 'gyur na gzhan lta
NK011(da)001:13590: ci smos thar bar 'dod na gtor ma dang tshogs
NK011(da)001:13591: brgya rtsa brgyad kyis bskang zhing 'khor lo 'o mas
NK011(da)001:13592: bkrus la zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bya zhing 'khor lo
NK011(da)001:13593: phyir bskor sngags kyi sbyor ba las grol bar gyur
NK011(da)001:13594: cig zhes brjod pas thar bar 'gyur ro sa ma
NK011(da)001:13595: ya rgya rgya rgya yang rtsa ba las lam h'u
NK011(da)001:13596: lam s+t+wam b+ha ya nan zhes 'byung ste gang zhig
NK011(da)001:13597: mnan par 'dod na ni chu srin nam nya'i lpags
NK011(da)001:13598: pa la ldong ros sam shing skyer pa kar ti
NK011(da)001:13599: ka'i khu bas byugs la ri rab gling bzhi dang
NK011(da)001:13600: bcas pa bris te ri rab kyi steng du rtsibs
NK011(da)001:13601: bcu drug pa bris lte bar k+ai la ya dang
NK011(da)001:13602: gang mnan par bya ba bris rtsibs rnams la lam
NK011(da)001:13603: h'u lam s+t+wam b+ha ya la sogs pa phyogs dang
NK011(da)001:13604: phyogs ma yin par bris steng ma la rdo rje
NK011(da)001:13605: rgya gram bri 'og ma la me ri bri de
NK011(da)001:13606: gnyis lto sbyar te thod par gzhug +aam gu sha
NK011(da)001:13607: dkar du dril te tshon skud kyis rgya gram du
NK011(da)001:13608: dkris la 'jim pa las byas pa'i srin po lta
NK011(da)001:13609: bu gzugs mi sdug pa khru gang byas te de'i
NK011(da)001:13610: lag tu gtad la ngag tu bgegs kyi rgyal po
NK011(da)001:13611: khyod la gnod byed bstan pa bshig par byed pa
NK011(da)001:13612: 'di la gtad do bskal pa'i bar du ma btang
NK011(da)001:13613: zhig ces brjod de dur khrod du dong gru gsum
NK011(da)001:13614: nang du kha sbub la bzhag go mchog phur sor
NK011(da)001:13615: drug gam brgyad pas steng du gzir la sngags dang
NK011(da)001:13616: phyag rgya tshul bzhin du bya ste g.yam pa la
NK011(da)001:13617: rdo rje rgya gram bris la kha bcad steng du
NK011(da)001:13618: mchod rten dkar nag spyi dang gting bzlog la gzir
NK011(da)001:13619: ro de nas sgrub pa gzhung bzhin du byas la
NK011(da)001:13620: rtags thon pa dang mnan pa bya byi tri pa
NK011(da)001:13621: tra yang non par gyur na gzhan lta ci smos
NK011(da)001:13622: gal te gtong bar 'dod na gong gi sbyor ba
NK011(da)001:13623: gshin rje'i gzugs dang mchod rten de dur khrod du
NK011(da)001:13624: bskyal nas 'khor lo thod pa 'o mas bkrus la
NK011(da)001:13625: zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bya ste thod pa rgya mtsho'i
NK011(da)001:13626: nang du dor nas ngag sngags kyi sbyor ba las
NK011(da)001:13627: grol bar gyur cig ces brjod pas thar bar 'gyur
NK011(da)001:13628: ro sa ma ya ngan sngags drug gi kha tshar
NK011(da)001:13629: rgya rgya rgya d+ha thim dbal rdo rje phur pa'i
NK011(da)001:13631: &&& bcom ldan dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag
NK011(da)001:13632: 'tshal lo sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba dang sngags
NK011(da)001:13633: 'chang rnal 'byor dam pa de rgyal po'i sku ltar
NK011(da)001:13634: bstod pa'i phyir bka' yi srung ma sde gsum bsgrub
NK011(da)001:13635: gru gsum ldan pa bcu drug e drag po'i thugs
NK011(da)001:13636: kyi dkyil 'khor te rdo rje thod phreng me rir
NK011(da)001:13637: ldan shar phyogs gru gsum dkyil 'khor ni rin chen
NK011(da)001:13638: shel dang gser zangs lcags gru gsum rin chen pho
NK011(da)001:13639: brang bzhir rin chen phur bu sor brgyad pa rnal
NK011(da)001:13640: 'byor mos pa'i ting 'dzin gyis he las shwa na
NK011(da)001:13641: mched bzhir bskyed lho phyogs gru gsum pho brang ni
NK011(da)001:13642: khrag zhag mar khu 'o ma dang gru gsum rgya
NK011(da)001:13643: mtsho bzhi nang du lcags phur sher shing mdzo mo
NK011(da)001:13644: dang mchog gi phur pa sor brgyad la srog rtsa'i
NK011(da)001:13645: yi ge bzhi bkod la dpal chen ting 'dzin gsal
NK011(da)001:13646: ba yis sa bdag chen mo mched bzhi bskyed nub
NK011(da)001:13647: byang gru gsum e dkyil na mi khrag rta khrag
NK011(da)001:13648: tu tra'i khrag rak+ta'i rgya mtsho chen po bzhi mi'i
NK011(da)001:13649: mchog gi phur pa bzhi de la ma tri'i snying
NK011(da)001:13650: po bri rnal 'byor ting 'dzin ma rmugs pas thun
NK011(da)001:13651: spyod re ti mched bzhi bskyed yi ge gsum gyis
NK011(da)001:13652: dbang yang bskur dbus kyi pho brang nag po la
NK011(da)001:13653: nyi shu rtsa gcig k+ai la ya dbang du bsdu
NK011(da)001:13654: phyir dbu gnon dgod dbang bskur byin rlabs tshul bzhin
NK011(da)001:13655: bya me ri la ni dbang phyug ma las rnams
NK011(da)001:13656: myur du bsgrub phyir dgod de nas sgrub bsad gnyis
NK011(da)001:13657: kyi rdzas shar gyi zangs gling pho brang de srid
NK011(da)001:13658: la mi yi thod nang du wa spyang 'phar ba
NK011(da)001:13659: khyi snying bzhi zangs phur de la brtod nas kyang
NK011(da)001:13660: de la shwa na mched bzhi 'bod lho nub khrag
NK011(da)001:13661: gi rgya mtsho der la byung mon gyi thod pa
NK011(da)001:13662: ru mdzo bong bya lug nag mo'i snying lcags phur
NK011(da)001:13663: de la brtod nas kyang sa bdag rgyal mo mched
NK011(da)001:13664: bzhi 'bod byang gi mi khrag pho brang der lcang
NK011(da)001:13665: lo mchan ldan b+han+d+ha ru mi dbang tsit+ta sha khrag
NK011(da)001:13666: de mchog phur de la brtod nas kyang de la
NK011(da)001:13667: re ti mchod bzhi 'bod de nas gsad pa thun
NK011(da)001:13668: gyi rdzas shar lho thod phreng gru gsum du shwa
NK011(da)001:13669: na sngon mo'i thod pa ru drag po'i rdo thun
NK011(da)001:13670: dgod par bya lho nub thod phreng gru gsum du
NK011(da)001:13671: rabs chad nag po'i thod pa ru dug khrag srog
NK011(da)001:13672: thun dgod par bya byang gi thod phreng gru gsum
NK011(da)001:13673: du nal gri mo yi thod pa ru mngal khrag
NK011(da)001:13674: la sogs khrag thun dgod phyogs bzhir mo rgyud sde
NK011(da)001:13675: gsum la pho nya sde gsum dam rdzas gsog bswe
NK011(da)001:13676: mo bzhi yi pho sde ni bswe yi skyes bu
NK011(da)001:13677: bzhi yi rdzas gri ru shi ba'i thod pa ru
NK011(da)001:13678: 'bru nag gtor ma chen po la snying sna tshogs
NK011(da)001:13679: kyis brgyan pa bzhag shwa na bzhi yi pho sde
NK011(da)001:13680: ni lcags kyi skyes bu bzhi yi rdzas gsang phye'i
NK011(da)001:13681: gling tshad bre thags ma smyug ma tshig gsum dar
NK011(da)001:13682: zab brgyan dgra yi ling+ga stag gzig ras rgyan dang
NK011(da)001:13683: ldan pa gzug par bya re ti mched bzhi'i pho
NK011(da)001:13684: sde ni dung gi skyes bu bzhi yi rdzas mkhar
NK011(da)001:13685: thabs bre tshad mda' gang la phyogs bzhir mar khu
NK011(da)001:13686: byug par bya smyug ma tshig gsum dar zab dang
NK011(da)001:13687: rgod kyi spu dang lpags bu dang bswe byang rin
NK011(da)001:13688: chen sna tshogs brgyan dgra yi ling+ga btags la bzhag
NK011(da)001:13689: phyogs bzhi tshang phung rgya phor bzhir rin chen sna
NK011(da)001:13690: lnga brdar la bzhag de ltar rdzas rnams bsags nas
NK011(da)001:13691: ni de nas 'bod rbad gsod dang gsum thun du
NK011(da)001:13692: bcad de so sor bzlas shwa na mched bzhi 'bod
NK011(da)001:13693: pa ni shwa na mu kha dza dza h'u shwa
NK011(da)001:13694: na mu kha dza dza h'u sri la mu kha
NK011(da)001:13695: dza dza h'u sri la mu ka dza dza h'u
NK011(da)001:13696: zhes bos shing mchod pa 'bul shwa na mched bzhi
NK011(da)001:13697: rbad pa ni badz+ra shwa na mu kha che ge
NK011(da)001:13698: mo'i bla srog rtsa la he b+h+yo shwa na mu
NK011(da)001:13699: kha che ge mo'i lus srog sha la he b+h+yo
NK011(da)001:13700: sri la mu kha che ge mo'i dbang po lnga
NK011(da)001:13701: la he b+h+yoh sri ka mu kha che ge mo'i
NK011(da)001:13702: srog rtsa snying la he b+h+yo zhes phrin las bcol
NK011(da)001:13703: shwa na mched bzhis bsad pa ni badz+ra shwa na
NK011(da)001:13704: mu kha snying gong chod rtsa mug glo rtsa la
NK011(da)001:13705: thun thun rbad rbad badz+ra shwa na mu kha klad
NK011(da)001:13706: pa'i rtsa la thibs thibs khong khrag la thun rbad
NK011(da)001:13707: rbad badz+ra sri la mu kha srog rtsa la yam
NK011(da)001:13708: yam rgyu mi'i mthil du zhugs thun rbad badz+ra sri
NK011(da)001:13709: ka mu ka mchin khrag rtsa la thums dbang po
NK011(da)001:13710: lnga la thun thun rbad rbad ces nyungs kar dang
NK011(da)001:13711: rdo phye'i thun gyis bsad do tad ya tha trag
NK011(da)001:13712: rak+sha ru bi ru bi nan mug ti bam ru
NK011(da)001:13713: lu b+h+yo pad+ma da ri ru ma ti b+h+yo tsi
NK011(da)001:13714: ta tsi ta dgra bo'i snying la b+h+yo b+h+yo ru
NK011(da)001:13715: lu ko ru me se na mo nan dza dza
NK011(da)001:13716: mu ti du ru du ru tsa pa la me
NK011(da)001:13717: dza dzah zhes 'bod cing mchod pa 'bul lo ma
NK011(da)001:13718: h+aa yak+sha tig na nag mo dun b+h+yo ma lha
NK011(da)001:13719: mo lu ma lha mo dgra bo'i snying la dza
NK011(da)001:13720: dza b+h+yo b+h+yo rbad lo kha ru lu dgra bo
NK011(da)001:13721: la b+h+yo rak+moo rak+mo shan shan ni kha thun yak+sha
NK011(da)001:13722: snying shad shad b+h+yo b+h+yo zhes rbad cing phrin las
NK011(da)001:13723: bcol trag rak+sha ru re ma ti dgra bo'i snying
NK011(da)001:13724: mugs du yam rbad trag rak+sha du re ma ti
NK011(da)001:13725: dgra bo'i snying khrag sha la gtubs thum yam rbad
NK011(da)001:13726: trag rak+sha ru re mdzad dgra bo'i snying rtsa thum
NK011(da)001:13727: yam ri la b+h+yo trag rak+sha ru re mdzu dgra
NK011(da)001:13728: bo'i srog rtsa rbad ril rak+sha du li b+h+yo zhes
NK011(da)001:13729: nyungs nag khrag la bstim zhing bsad do pra mun
NK011(da)001:13730: da ri dza dzahmh'u tsa mun da ri dza dzahmh'u
NK011(da)001:13731: shu la da ri dza dzahmh'u ke mun da ri
NK011(da)001:13732: dza dzahmh'u zhes bswe mo 'bod cing mchod do ya
NK011(da)001:13733: byin yak+sha tshal pa b+h+yo de byin rak+sha tshal pa
NK011(da)001:13734: b+h+yo bswe byin rak+sha du ma bu b+h+yo phag byin
NK011(da)001:13735: yak+sha du ru shag b+h+yo zhes rbad cing phrin las
NK011(da)001:13736: bcol lo rag mo tsi bi ri dgra bo ni
NK011(da)001:13737: m+aa ra ya thul las mdzod rak+mo tsi bi ri
NK011(da)001:13738: dgra bo ni m+aa ra ya 'ub thul las mdzod
NK011(da)001:13739: gang za tsi bi ri dgra bo m+aa ra ya
NK011(da)001:13740: 'ub thul las mdzod hu lu ma tsi bi ri
NK011(da)001:13741: dgra bo ni m+aa ra ya 'ub thul las mdzod
NK011(da)001:13742: ces srog rtsa la gdug pa'i rdzas sna tshogs kyi
NK011(da)001:13743: thun dbab bo de nas bswe'i skyes bu bzhi'i 'bod
NK011(da)001:13744: rbad bsad gsum dril bas brdeg ste su tri ba
NK011(da)001:13745: ya ba ra tsit+ta yo gi shwa ra ya ma
NK011(da)001:13746: tsit+ta h'u phata rbad lcags kyi skyes bu bzhi'i 'bod
NK011(da)001:13747: rbad bsad gsum dril ba dgra bo ni m+aa ra
NK011(da)001:13748: ya n+ri m+aa ra du ya ma snying ya ma
NK011(da)001:13749: khrag tshal pa bdud pra ma ya snying la khug
NK011(da)001:13750: bam ril rbad dung gi skyes bu bzhi'i 'bod rbad
NK011(da)001:13751: bsad gsum dril ba ma ra na pra ma r+aa
NK011(da)001:13752: tsa tsit+ta sa li a me sa ma ya che
NK011(da)001:13753: ge mo'i srog la thibs thibs dun dun h+r+ai nan
NK011(da)001:13754: ces ling+ga la thun brdeg go rtags ni bud med
NK011(da)001:13755: shar mo rgyan can dang bud med nag mo mang
NK011(da)001:13756: po dang mi shar tshogs su 'ong ba yin mtshon
NK011(da)001:13757: thogs pa dang dmag 'dren dang srog chags bsad dang
NK011(da)001:13758: glo snying ster de ltar byung na phur pa gdab
NK011(da)001:13759: thun khrag dgra yi phyogs su 'phang dam nyams dgra
NK011(da)001:13760: bo'i phyogs su skyol gang la bya ba kha phung
NK011(da)001:13761: 'gro bdag 'dra pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis bstan pa dam
NK011(da)001:13762: pa bsrung ba'i phyir mnga' bdag rgyal por btsas su
NK011(da)001:13763: gtad bstan pa dam pa bsrung don du ma spel
NK011(da)001:13764: rin chen gter du sbas rdo rje phur pa'i bka'
NK011(da)001:13766: rdo rje phur pa'i las tshogs gtor bzlog la brten pa'i mde kha bcu gnyis pa bzhugs /
NK011(da)001:13767: rdo rje phur pa'i las tshogs ni /
NK011(da)001:13768: 1bdag gam gzhan la srung 'khor bya ba ni /
NK011(da)001:13770: skyer phur sor bzhi pa bzhi la byug bdug rdeg gsum byas nas sras mchog bzhir mnga' gsol /
NK011(da)001:13771: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad mu khyud bzhi pa'i lte bar gang 'dod kyi bsrung bya bri /
NK011(da)001:13772: phyi'i mu khyud la k+ai la ya 'bru bcu gsum bri /
NK011(da)001:13773: rtsibs bzhi la bzhi snying dril ba bri /
NK011(da)001:13775: sarba ru tri hring hring dzah sarba dush+tam b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:13777: de'i phyi rim la khro bo bcu'i sngags bri /
NK011(da)001:13778: de'i phyi rim la rten 'brel snying po bri /
NK011(da)001:13782: tshon skud kyis dkris la mgul du btags /
NK011(da)001:13783: gnod byed kyi ling+ga ming rus dang bcas pa bris te /
NK011(da)001:13784: dur khrod kyi sa nag la nya bo byas pa'i snying gar bcug /
NK011(da)001:13785: de'i snying gar skyer phur btab la bzhi snying gcig
NK011(da)001:13786: dril brgya 'am stong bzlas nas khang pa'i phyogs bzhir
NK011(da)001:13789: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu sogs nyes pa thams cad thub par the tshom med do //
NK011(da)001:13790: rang bsrung rdo rje'i go cha ni /
NK011(da)001:13793: rang gi chos skyong 'khu ba sogs la sbyor ba 'dis gnad la dbab ste /
NK011(da)001:13795: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad mu khyud dang bcas pa dang bzhi pa'i rtsibs rtse nang du bstan nas /
NK011(da)001:13796: mu khyud nang ma la bzhi snying gcig dril bri /
NK011(da)001:13797: rtsibs brgyad la spu gri'i sngags bri /
NK011(da)001:13798: rtsibs mchan la gzir sngags ni sarba dush+tam trig nan
NK011(da)001:13799: e hur thum dzah m+aa ra ya rbad rbad ces
NK011(da)001:13800: mtshan brgyad bri / de'i phyi la bzhi snying dang /
NK011(da)001:13801: +amo pa ra big+h+n+aam nam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13804: gri h+na gri h+na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13805: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13806: ban d+ha ban d+ha h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13807: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13808: ha sa ya ra h+r+ai da na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13809: sh+ai kring +aa na ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13810: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13811: +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13812: b+hin+d+ha ya b+hin+d+ha ya h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:13813: dam nyams ru tra byad ma lha srung dang bcas pa thams cad m+aa ra ya rbad sod zlog /
NK011(da)001:13814: ces pha rol po dang chos skyong dang bcas pa'i mang yang bri /
NK011(da)001:13815: rang gi chos skyong yin na phyir bzlog dgra la rbad ces bri /
NK011(da)001:13816: shi lteb byas la tshon skud kyis bcings nas thod par bcug la brub khung du bstsal /
NK011(da)001:13817: de steng lcags sam seng ldeng gang rung gi phur pa many+dzi'i steng du gzug /
NK011(da)001:13818: lha 'dre thams cad la barngana dang gser skyems btang la rang gis ma nyes pa'i dpang gzug /
NK011(da)001:13823: yug sa'i zhabs ma'i du bas bdug /
NK011(da)001:13824: bzhi snying gcig dril thun la basngagasa te brab /
NK011(da)001:13826: lha'i nga rgyal brtan pos zil gyis mnan /
NK011(da)001:13827: rtags ni ri nyil chu 'brub dmag dpung 'du dang 'thab rtsod brdeg sogs 'byung /
NK011(da)001:13828: rjes la phyag 'tshal las byed bsgo ba nyan pa de rnams 'byung /
NK011(da)001:13829: slar dbyung na 'khor lo phyung nas 'o ma dang rtsi sman gyis bkru /
NK011(da)001:13830: rang gi 'phyong yin na bskang gso bya /
NK011(da)001:13831: rbod gtong yin na rang gis ma nyes pa'i dpang gzug /
NK011(da)001:13832: pha rol gyis nyes pa'i shags gdab /
NK011(da)001:13834: 'khor lo klad la bskor zhing brdeg /
NK011(da)001:13835: rjes la ldog rtags byung na pha rol gyi 'phyong la bka' bsgo /
NK011(da)001:13838: des ni gnod 'tshe dang 'khu mi nus te bsgo ba'i bka' nyan par 'gyur ro //
NK011(da)001:13839: srung zlog gcun pa'i lam mtha' 'o //
NK011(da)001:13840: 2yang rnal 'byor pa'i tshe la bar chod dam sri dgra bgegs gsum che ste /
NK011(da)001:13841: de dag bsgral ba dang srung zlog gi las ni gtor bzlog bya zhing /
NK011(da)001:13842: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad mu khyud bzhi pa'i dbus su gang gnod kyi ling+ga bri /
NK011(da)001:13843: de la dgra bgegs gang yin gyi srog yig m+aa ra ya thum ri li li rbad bri /
NK011(da)001:13844: rtsibs rtse nang bstan la spu gri'i sngags bri /
NK011(da)001:13845: rtsibs mchan la gang gnod de'i gzugs bri /
NK011(da)001:13846: phyi rim la dgra bgegs dam sri n+ri tri hur thum dzahm+aa ra ya rbad /
NK011(da)001:13847: dgra bgegs dam sri m+aa ra ya rbad /
NK011(da)001:13848: n+ri tri hur thum dzah gnod byed 'byung po bka'
NK011(da)001:13849: la mi nyan cing dam la mi gnas pa k+aa
NK011(da)001:13855: ha la b+ha ti rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:13856: gnod byed dam sri lus ngag yid gsum k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta h'u phata bri'o //
NK011(da)001:13857: de'i phyi la mtshon cha'i 'khor lo rtse nang bstan bri /
NK011(da)001:13858: de la gnod byed dgug gzhug bya /
NK011(da)001:13861: mgo nas dril la yug skras bcings te brub khung du bcug /
NK011(da)001:13862: thun sna dug khrag sbyar ba dang lcags sam seng phur gyis gzir /
NK011(da)001:13863: rang dpal chen po dang phur pa sras mchog 'khor
NK011(da)001:13864: lo ling+ga dgra bgegs dngos su gsal ba'i ngang nas
NK011(da)001:13865: spu gri gcig shur du bzlas shing thun brab /
NK011(da)001:13874: sems can bla dwags bsad pa sogs byung ba dang /
NK011(da)001:13875: pho nya bskul zhing bskang gso bya /
NK011(da)001:13876: gtor ma dgra bgegs steng du btul /
NK011(da)001:13878: thal ba mchod rten 'og tu mnan /
NK011(da)001:13882: 3yang gson 'dre gshin 'dre lha 'dre'i rigs gang yang bskrad cing tshar bcad pa ni /
NK011(da)001:13885: mi phag khyi spyang gi brun /
NK011(da)001:13890: rta dre'u'i spu gzhob rnams nus pa can gyi dri
NK011(da)001:13891: chu dang chang rgod sbyar la g.yag rgod kyi rwa
NK011(da)001:13892: nang rlon thun dang skam thun du bas bdug /
NK011(da)001:13893: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad mu khyud bzhi pa'i dbus su gang gnod kyi r+au pa /
NK011(da)001:13895: rtsibs mchan la tri ra tsa shag dun /
NK011(da)001:13896: r+aa tsa has ling m+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:13898: bzlog na r+aa tsa dum bur shig /
NK011(da)001:13899: ma zhung tri m+aa ra ya rbad nan sod /
NK011(da)001:13901: tsa mun tri m+aa ra ya sod bri /
NK011(da)001:13902: de'i phyi rim spu gri'i sngags bri /
NK011(da)001:13904: brub khung du gan rkyal du bcug /
NK011(da)001:13905: spu gri gcig shur du bzlas /
NK011(da)001:13911: skyes shar bud med bsad pa /
NK011(da)001:13912: smra sgra dang tsi sgras khengs pa sogs 'byung ste /
NK011(da)001:13913: de nas ling+ga mgo nas lteb la tshon skud kyis bcings /
NK011(da)001:13914: brub khung mkhyid gang pa gcig tu bcug la ro g.yam gyi kha bcad /
NK011(da)001:13915: zla ba mar ngo la gza' thebs dang bstun la
NK011(da)001:13916: lha khang them 'og gam mchod rten rab gnas can
NK011(da)001:13917: gyi byang du dong gru gsum brus te mnan /
NK011(da)001:13918: des ni tshangs pa dang brgya byin yang tshar chod na gzhan smos ci dgos te zab /
NK011(da)001:13919: 4gzhan yang 'dre gdon khyim nas bskrad na gong gi rdzas kyi du bas bdug /
NK011(da)001:13920: rdo thun dug khrag gis sbags la drag sngags kyis rim par brab cing /
NK011(da)001:13921: sgo la sgrib shing btags na nges par thub bo //
NK011(da)001:13924: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad mu khyud gsum pa'i dbus su
NK011(da)001:13925: gang gnod pa'i klu sa dmigs dang bcas pa sbrul
NK011(da)001:13927: rtsibs la spu gri'i sngags dang /
NK011(da)001:13928: rtsibs mchan la klu gzir sngags /
NK011(da)001:13930: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:13937: n+aa ga r+aa tsa la'i has phob /
NK011(da)001:13938: n+aa ga dum pa le le /
NK011(da)001:13939: n+aa ga r+aa tsa shag dun /
NK011(da)001:13940: n+aa ga r+aa tsa srog dung dung /
NK011(da)001:13941: gnod byed n+aa ga'i lus ngag yid gsum chings chings bri /
NK011(da)001:13942: de'i phyi rim la klu'i bsad sngags 'di bri'o //
NK011(da)001:13943: n+aa ga r+aa tsa m+aa ra ya /
NK011(da)001:13944: n+aa ga'i sha la chems chems /
NK011(da)001:13945: n+aa ga'i rus la krum krum /
NK011(da)001:13946: n+aa ga'i khrag la hab hab /
NK011(da)001:13947: n+aa ga'i rtsa rgyus la chod chod /
NK011(da)001:13951: n+aa ga m+aa ra ya sod /
NK011(da)001:13952: n+aa ga m+aa ra ya nan bri'o //
NK011(da)001:13953: de nas ling+ga brub khung du skyer phur sor brgyad pa la brgyangs /
NK011(da)001:13954: bskyed rim gsal bas gang gnod pa'i klu dgug bstim drag tu bya /
NK011(da)001:13955: lcags sam seng ldeng gi phur pas gzir /
NK011(da)001:13958: mu zi nag po'i thun gyis brab /
NK011(da)001:13959: sngags bzhi snying dril ba la /
NK011(da)001:13960: klu'i gzir sngags btags la bzlas /
NK011(da)001:13964: ba dmar glang dmar bdas pa dang /
NK011(da)001:13966: sdom sdig sbal pa bcom pa /
NK011(da)001:13967: yul khams sam lha khang bsregs pa /
NK011(da)001:13969: babs pa sogs byung nas 'khor lo dril /
NK011(da)001:13971: tsh+wa tsh+wa nag po'i nang du gzhug /
NK011(da)001:13972: klu la thebs pa'i dus tshod du /
NK011(da)001:13973: rten nam lha khang them 'og tu mnan /
NK011(da)001:13974: ro g.yam la rgya gram bris pas bcad /
NK011(da)001:13975: byugs pa rgyun 'khor ram rang srung gang rung gis bsrung /
NK011(da)001:13977: gzhan gnod pa tsam la smon ci dgos /
NK011(da)001:13978: phyis nas kyang klu la las 'di brtsams pas chog /
NK011(da)001:13979: yang 'khor lo 'di'i lte ba'i klu shul du 'chang ba'i bsrung bya bris te /
NK011(da)001:13980: gzhan sngags rnams gzhung ltar la gang dgos kyi 'dod gsol bri /
NK011(da)001:13983: rab gnas byas nas btags na srung ba'i mchog tu 'gyur to //
NK011(da)001:13984: klu bsrung ba dang bsad pa'i las mtha' zab bo //
NK011(da)001:13985: 5smyo 'dre 'dul na bskyed rim dang ldan pa'i rnal
NK011(da)001:13986: 'byor pas 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad mu khyud dang bcas
NK011(da)001:13987: pa bskor la / dbus su smyo 'dre'i r+au pa bri /
NK011(da)001:13988: yan lag sgrog dang dza'i gzer gyi bsdams /
NK011(da)001:13989: rtsibs brgyad la bzhi snying dril ba bri /
NK011(da)001:13990: rtsibs mchan la r+aa tsa pra mnan /
NK011(da)001:13991: r+aa tsa shag dun kha ling dza ya rbad /
NK011(da)001:13992: rag sha ra hu la a ya ma du ru tsa sha na bri /
NK011(da)001:13994: smyo 'dre gang yin pa tri hur thum dzahm+aa ra ya rbad /
NK011(da)001:13995: smyo 'dre'i rnam par shes pa dza ya dza ya /
NK011(da)001:13998: chings m+aa ra ya rbad sod bri'o //
NK011(da)001:14000: sngon dmar skud pa'i byad kyis bskor /
NK011(da)001:14001: smyon pa'i rked la thag nag btags nas phur pa la brtod la brgyangs nas bzung /
NK011(da)001:14002: skabs su yungs kar nag dang rdo phye'i thun brab /
NK011(da)001:14012: te lo'i sha rnams kyis mgo bstums te bdug /
NK011(da)001:14013: de ltar thun ma chag par byas na zhag nyer
NK011(da)001:14014: gcig na smyo 'dre thul bar the tshom med do
NK011(da)001:14015: // de nas 'khor lo dril la sngo dmar gyis
NK011(da)001:14016: bcings te mchod rten 'og tu mnan pas ldang mi
NK011(da)001:14017: nus te shin tu zab bo //
NK011(da)001:14018: pha rol gyi rbod gtong bzlog pa ni /
NK011(da)001:14019: mtshams dam par bcad la gtor zlog bshams la /
NK011(da)001:14021: dbus su ming rus bsrung bya 'dod gsol dang bcas bri /
NK011(da)001:14022: de'i phyi la k+ai la ya'i sngags bri /
NK011(da)001:14023: phyi rim rtsibs bcu la khro bo bcu'i sngags bri /
NK011(da)001:14025: a ya ma du ru tsa sha na bzlog ces tshan bcu bri /
NK011(da)001:14030: pra ha ra na h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:14031: sa ma ya a ti pra ma ni pa ra b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:14037: k+aa ya gling zlog zlog b+h+yo /
NK011(da)001:14039: de'i phyi rim la +aa li k+aa li dang ye d+harmasa bskor la tshon dang dri bzang gis byug /
NK011(da)001:14040: dur khrod dam drag po'i gnas nas sa blangs la mchod rten khru gang bya /
NK011(da)001:14041: dgra'i zag rdzas dang bag zan la nya bo byas pa'i nang du ling+ga gzhug /
NK011(da)001:14042: de'i snying gar skyer pa'am seng phur sor brgyad pa btab /
NK011(da)001:14043: brub khung khru gang par gzhug /
NK011(da)001:14044: de steng mchod rten nag po'i bum par gong gi 'khor lo dang /
NK011(da)001:14045: gzhan yang bdag mi nor 'khor dang bcas pa la srungs shig sogs bris pa gzhug /
NK011(da)001:14046: 'khor lo de lta bu bdag dang 'khor gces pa rnams la yod na'ang rab /
NK011(da)001:14047: ma grub na mchod rten gyi bum par bcug ste
NK011(da)001:14048: khang pa'i byang ngos su gzhug na srung ba'i mchog
NK011(da)001:14049: tu 'gyur ro // nyes pa kun thub bo //
NK011(da)001:14051: bum pa'i nang du gzungs thag drangs nas rang gis bzung /
NK011(da)001:14052: ling+ga byad ma yang yang dgug bstim byas te pho nya bskul /
NK011(da)001:14054: dgra bo'i bla dzahmh'u bam hoh sa dgug cing brub
NK011(da)001:14055: khung lcags khang nag por bsgyur bas kho skyob byed
NK011(da)001:14058: kho rang gi srung ma kho rang gi gshed du
NK011(da)001:14059: babs nas sha zos khrag 'thung rjes med du gtor
NK011(da)001:14060: bar bsams la / dmigs pa nga rgyal brtan pos sngags 'di thog mar bzlas te /
NK011(da)001:14061: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u h'u h'u /
NK011(da)001:14062: bdud pra m+aa ra ya rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:14063: kha la dza la li rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:14064: r+aa tsa dun ling shag rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:14065: shig shig dum dum rbad rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:14066: tshal pa tshal pa rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:14067: khram khram b+h+yo b+h+yo rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:14068: rmugs rmugs b+h+yo b+h+yo rbad nan /
NK011(da)001:14072: skabs su mchod rten bshus pa'i 'og tu yungs kar nag /
NK011(da)001:14074: lcags zangs phye dug khrag gis sbags pa'i thun brab /
NK011(da)001:14077: kho rang gi srung ma rang gshed du dbab /
NK011(da)001:14078: rtags ni dmag dpung bcom pa /
NK011(da)001:14080: rgyal po'i pho brang bshig pa /
NK011(da)001:14081: mtshon cha kha bsnol ba dang dum bur bcad pa /
NK011(da)001:14090: ling ro dgra phyogs su rlung la bskur ba'am /
NK011(da)001:14091: nye na khang rmang du mnan /
NK011(da)001:14092: gtor zor thebs dang bstun nas dgra phyogs su 'phang /
NK011(da)001:14093: des ni kho rang phung zhing rtsa ba chad de bzlog pa'i zab gnad do //
NK011(da)001:14094: 7yang rgyal bsen ma rung pas gnod dam khyim nas
NK011(da)001:14095: ma thon na shog bu la lcags kyi rdo rje
NK011(da)001:14096: nag po bris pa'i lte bar 'khor lo bskor te
NK011(da)001:14097: mu khyud gsum pa'i lte ba la /
NK011(da)001:14098: r+aa tsa tri du ma le dzah srog la hur thum dzah tsa du sod /
NK011(da)001:14099: gnod byed 'byung po m+aa ra ya sod bri'o //
NK011(da)001:14102: a tri thum zhes brgyad bri /
NK011(da)001:14104: ma zhung ma zhung tri du ma le dza sod /
NK011(da)001:14109: r+aa tsa ha'u ha'u kha dun shag shag /
NK011(da)001:14110: gnod byed 'byung po'i tsit+ta srog la ha ba ha ba rbad rbad /
NK011(da)001:14112: de nad pa'i steng nas gdags /
NK011(da)001:14113: bskyed rim dang ldan pas lcags rdor gyis gzir /
NK011(da)001:14114: gu gul dang rdzas rgod kyis sna nas bdug /
NK011(da)001:14115: srin lag g.yon pa bsdams te spu gri'i sngags gsham
NK011(da)001:14116: du gnod byed 'byung po'i srog la r+n+ri hur thum
NK011(da)001:14118: tri hur thum dza m+aa ra ya rbad sod /
NK011(da)001:14119: ces rdo rje dang phur thun gyis brab /
NK011(da)001:14120: de nas 'dre ngan skad ngan tse re re 'bros te gdon bgegs thul bar the tshom med do //
NK011(da)001:14121: rjes la rdo rje nag po'i 'khor lo la gang
NK011(da)001:14122: gnod pa'i gdon bgegs srungs shig sgribs shig rak+sha zhes
NK011(da)001:14126: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa mu khyud gsum pa'i lte
NK011(da)001:14127: bar gang gnod kyi skyur 'dre dang chang 'dre srungs
NK011(da)001:14128: shig bri / rtsibs la bzhi snying sril ba bri //
NK011(da)001:14134: 'byung po'i kha la rak+sha rbad chings kha sdoms srog gzir kha tham kha tham /
NK011(da)001:14135: za 'dre shi 'dre kha la tsi ti nan /
NK011(da)001:14136: dkar 'dre skyur 'dre byed pa srungs shig sgribs shig rak+sha bri'o //
NK011(da)001:14139: rtsibs dang mchan gyi sngags gong ma gnyis po de
NK011(da)001:14140: stong ngam khri bzlas la sbal pa la yang yang
NK011(da)001:14141: gdab / zho chang gang bsrung ba'i steng du bzhag /
NK011(da)001:14142: yang sngags 'di rde'u dkar nag la stong khrir bzlas te zho chang gi nang du bzhag /
NK011(da)001:14143: des thub par the tshom med do //
NK011(da)001:14150: gnyan la sogs 'joms par byed pa ni /
NK011(da)001:14165: ra thug lug thug gi sbre /
NK011(da)001:14166: khrag sna dug sna tshogs tshad g.yag rgod dam ba
NK011(da)001:14167: men gyi rwa ru sbyar la chu srin kha la
NK011(da)001:14168: rdo rjes bcad / dge slong khrims ldan nam sngags
NK011(da)001:14169: pa nus ldan gyi dri chu chang rgod dang sbyar
NK011(da)001:14170: rdo rjes bcad / la / rlangs pa ma shor
NK011(da)001:14171: bar kha dam du bcad la sngags 'dis btso zhing
NK011(da)001:14172: rdo rjes bcad / la / sgrub / badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aam bam h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:14173: n+aa ga du tsan d+he tsan d+he /
NK011(da)001:14175: bna d+ha bna d+ha n+aa ga ni h'u phata /
NK011(da)001:14176: smra ba bcad la mang du bzlas shing hus gdab /
NK011(da)001:14177: phyis kyang nus pa can gyi dri chu dang /
NK011(da)001:14178: chang gi nying khus kha gso ste /
NK011(da)001:14179: byug bdug ltor btang ba skam thun sogs gang dgos la rig pas dpyad do //
NK011(da)001:14180: des ni gdug pa'i mdze yang thon na /
NK011(da)001:14181: gzhan gnyan rims pa tsam la sleb pas chog go //
NK011(da)001:14182: 10des na bsrung bzlog bsad mnan sogs las tshogs rim par bstan pa las /
NK011(da)001:14183: gtor zlog ni zur du gsal la /
NK011(da)001:14184: kha bsgyur zor skong nyer brgyad la dug khrag byugs te /
NK011(da)001:14186: dbang mo nyer brgyad kyi sngags bzlas shing phyogs mtshams thams cad brdeg go //
NK011(da)001:14189: gtor ma dgra phyogs su brdeg /
NK011(da)001:14190: rak+ta rkang gi gzar bus gtor /
NK011(da)001:14191: sngags nag stong dang 'gras kyang bzlog go //
NK011(da)001:14192: rgyud las yul khams gnas sogs gang bsrung yang /
NK011(da)001:14193: gtor ma'i sbyor ba gong nyid las /
NK011(da)001:14195: 11yang rbod gtong mnan gtad sel dang 'gong chog khong
NK011(da)001:14196: sel dur sel rlung 'khor sogs sbyor ngan thams cad
NK011(da)001:14197: bsrung ba ni / 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad mu khyud sum brgya pa snag gis bris /
NK011(da)001:14199: nang gi mu khyud la k+ai la ya /
NK011(da)001:14200: rtsibs bcu la khro bo bcu'i sngags kyi sham bur btags la srungs shig /
NK011(da)001:14202: rtsibs mchan la e sa b+h+yo zlog /
NK011(da)001:14204: phyi'i mu khyud la spu gri'i sngags dang b+h+yo zlog dmod mo'i rigs gang 'os bri /
NK011(da)001:14207: de'i zla la gser dngul mtshal gang rung gis sngags 'di phreng gcig tu bris la gzhug go //
NK011(da)001:14215: sha ma ra sha ma ra /
NK011(da)001:14218: b+han pi ya dun h'u h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK011(da)001:14223: rus sbal bzhi byas te khang pa'i phyogs bzhir sba'o //
NK011(da)001:14224: bzhi ma 'grub na sgrub khang gi dbus su bzhag /
NK011(da)001:14225: des ni nyes skyon thams cad thub /
NK011(da)001:14226: de'i zla la gtsug tor rnam rgyal dang /
NK011(da)001:14227: yig sna kun thub yod na yang legs so //
NK011(da)001:14228: 12yang shwa 'od dang chu dmag bzlog na /
NK011(da)001:14230: khro bo bcu dang bzhi snying dril ba /
NK011(da)001:14231: dbang mo'i zlog pa'i sngags rnams shog bu phra mo la bris /
NK011(da)001:14232: tsha tsha mang po'i nang du bcug la /
NK011(da)001:14233: spu gri dbang mo'i zlog sngags bzlas shing chu dmag shwa 'ud gang byung steng du brdeg /
NK011(da)001:14234: rgya mtsho'i rlabs kyang bzlog par 'gyur /
NK011(da)001:14236: dge ba 'di yis mnyam med gter bdag gling //
NK011(da)001:14237: zag med thugs kyi dgongs pa yongs rdzogs shing //
NK011(da)001:14238: rnying bstan mi nyams dar zhing rgyas pa yi //
NK011(da)001:14239: rtsa lag srog gi ka bar 'di gyur cig /
NK011(da)001:14241: de dag gis rong phur gyi gzhung pod da ltar
NK011(da)001:14242: bzhugs rigs thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa yin no
